<style type="text/css">.ritz .waffle a { color: inherit; }.ritz .waffle .s3{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:#000000;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:16pt;vertical-align:bottom;white-space:nowrap;direction:ltr;padding:0px 3px 0px 3px;}.ritz .waffle .s0{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:center;color:#000000;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:10pt;vertical-align:middle;white-space:nowrap;direction:ltr;padding:0;}.ritz .waffle .s2{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-weight:bold;color:#000000;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:10pt;vertical-align:middle;white-space:normal;overflow:hidden;word-wrap:break-word;direction:ltr;padding:0px 3px 0px 3px;}.ritz .waffle .s6{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;color:#000000;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:10pt;vertical-align:bottom;white-space:nowrap;direction:ltr;padding:0px 3px 0px 3px;}.ritz .waffle .s4{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:#000000;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:16pt;vertical-align:bottom;white-space:normal;overflow:hidden;word-wrap:break-word;direction:ltr;padding:0px 3px 0px 3px;}.ritz .waffle .s5{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-weight:bold;color:#000000;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:16pt;vertical-align:bottom;white-space:nowrap;direction:ltr;padding:0px 3px 0px 3px;}.ritz .waffle .s8{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;color:#1155cc;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:10pt;vertical-align:bottom;white-space:nowrap;direction:ltr;padding:0px 3px 0px 3px;}.ritz .waffle .s7{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;color:#000000;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:10pt;vertical-align:bottom;white-space:normal;overflow:hidden;word-wrap:break-word;direction:ltr;padding:0px 3px 0px 3px;}.ritz .waffle .s1{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:#000000;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:23pt;vertical-align:middle;white-space:normal;overflow:hidden;word-wrap:break-word;direction:ltr;padding:0px 3px 0px 3px;}.ritz .waffle .s9{background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;color:#1155cc;font-family:docs-Nunito,Arial;font-size:10pt;vertical-align:bottom;white-space:nowrap;direction:ltr;padding:0px 3px 0px 3px;}</style><div class="ritz grid-container" dir="ltr"><table class="waffle" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><thead><tr><th class="row-header freezebar-origin-ltr"></th><th id="1909413307C0" style="width:420px;" class="column-headers-background">A</th><th id="1909413307C1" style="width:888px;" class="column-headers-background">B</th><th id="1909413307C2" style="width:198px;" class="column-headers-background">C</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style="height: 73px"><th id="1909413307R0" style="height: 73px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 73px">1</div></th><td class="s0"><div style="width:420px;height:73px;"><img src="resources/cellImage_1909413307_0.jpg" style="width:inherit;height:inherit;object-fit:scale-down;object-position:center center;pointer-events:none;"/></div></td><td class="s1" dir="ltr">The Magic N8N Bundle</td><td class="s2" dir="ltr">❓ Want to search? Use CTRL+F or CMD+F on Mac and start typing!</td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">2</div></th><td class="s3" dir="ltr">Title</td><td class="s4" dir="ltr">Description</td><td class="s5" dir="ltr">Download Link</td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R2" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">3</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Social Media Content Publisher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow utilizing OpenAI GPT-4 and LangChain that automates content creation and publishing across Twitter (X), Instagram, Facebook, LinkedIn, Threads, and YouTube Shorts. It dynamically composes prompts and schemas from Google Docs, generates contextual posts with AI, creates matching images using pollinations.ai, and publishes or archives content with approvals and notifications.</td><td class="s8" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JGKsHoGn_N9U7UtAHGSA6r5lGxnsgQcC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R3" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">4</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Telegram Assistant with Email, Calendar &amp; Tasks</td><td class="s7">An AI assistant on Telegram integrating OpenAI GPT-4, Google Calendar, Gmail, and Baserow for task and contact management. It handles voice/text inputs, transcribes voice notes, fetches and summarizes emails and calendar events, and manages tasks, providing seamless personal assistance.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FFTnKRCKYUPjNV_UnbdGqwpwZUAHLL8w">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R4" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">5</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Automated Research Report Generator</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates research report creation using OpenAI GPT-4 for query refinement and summarization, Wikipedia, NewsAPI, Google Custom Search, SerpApi for scholarly papers, and integrates PDFShift for PDF generation. Reports are sent via Gmail and Telegram, streamlining professional research delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1w31DkItPISHU4ljvTSNBt2osVooseTuC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R5" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">6</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Social Media Content Publisher &amp; Prompt Composer</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating content creation and publishing across TikTok (YouTube Shorts), Instagram, Facebook, Twitter (X), LinkedIn, and Threads using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Langchain for AI content generation, Pollinations.ai for image creation, imgbb API for image hosting, Google Docs for prompts/schema storage, and platform APIs for auto-posting. It supports human approval via Gmail and structures posts per platform specs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1h--PD49T6qwncwjBX5LhOjJKU5eG8yVQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R6" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">7</div></th><td class="s6">AI Social Video Generator &amp; Auto Social Posting</td><td class="s7">An automated n8n workflow leveraging Telegram, GPT-4, Kling AI video API, Cloudinary, and Blotato to create AI videos with voice-over and captions, then auto-publish to Instagram, YouTube, TikTok, Facebook, Twitter (X), LinkedIn, Threads, Bluesky, and Pinterest.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-LmujZkZuSlZuoiIwfG1lzUuzAr6pJn_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R7" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">8</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Summaries &amp; Transcripts via Gemini API</td><td class="s7">Automate extraction of YouTube video transcripts, summaries, scene descriptions, and social media clips using Google Gemini API and n8n automation. Easily customize prompts and output for versatile video content analysis and marketing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sS2QGNeGPjVSzVW6brK-qO0HRd50LppC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R8" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">9</div></th><td class="s6">n8n AI &amp; App Node Reference Library</td><td class="s7">Comprehensive n8n workflow showcasing various AI nodes (OpenAI, Langchain agents, Anthropic, Google Gemini) and app integrations (Google Suite, Dropbox, Bitly, Reddit, YouTube, etc.) designed as a visual reference for automation and AI-enhanced workflow building.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sYWIDNvMFDs3DXgK7cVmbEYq9v173SHu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R9" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">10</div></th><td class="s6">AI TikTok/YouTube Shorts Reel Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of POV short-form videos for TikTok, YouTube Shorts, and Reels using OpenAI for captions &amp; scripts, PiAPI&#39;s Flux &amp; Kling for AI image and video generation, Eleven Labs for voiceover, Creatomate for video rendering, plus Google Sheets/Drive for data and file management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JxGuthg0m8WhGiQ2Es5djhFfacoZU_ED">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R10" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">11</div></th><td class="s6">AI Social Video Auto-Creation &amp; Multi-Platform Posting</td><td class="s7">Automates video creation from Telegram prompts or images using AI (GPT-4, Piapi, Blotato), merges voice-over and captions, saves metadata to Google Sheets, and auto-publishes videos to 9 social platforms (Instagram, YouTube, TikTok, Facebook, Threads, Twitter, LinkedIn, Bluesky, Pinterest) via Blotato API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gM0Eu7dBDx0faEj1AybGRz5SkP_7i8zG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R11" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">12</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Driven Sales Meeting Follow-Up Scheduler</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating sales follow-ups using Google Calendar and Gmail APIs. It retrieves past meetings, checks email interaction, uses OpenAI GPT-4 powered AI agents to suggest and book next meeting slots, with human approval for final booking. Supports calendar management and contextualized follow-ups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VssExPR-qeGBtKNmg4JuLsfJf9jYZ_jH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R12" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">13</div></th><td class="s6">AI Stock Analysis Bot via Telegram</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that enables real-time stock technical analysis through Telegram. It uses Telegram APIs for message interaction, OpenAI GPT-4 for chat and audio transcription, Chart-img API for generating stock charts, Airtable for saving tickers, plus LangChain tools to orchestrate AI agent processes and chat memory.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yTNLUgZwMVmM_1NxqNKXlRf04UFkP4CI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R13" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">14</div></th><td class="s6">ChatGPT Image Generation to Google Drive &amp; Sheets</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrates OpenAI GPT-image-1 API for image generation from chat prompts, saves images to Google Drive, and logs images with thumbnails and cost details in Google Sheets for tracking and analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15Rse2Jiw059Q4JHnXDy07dkS-GlwWnoq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R14" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">15</div></th><td class="s6">Google Calendar to Outlook Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Google Calendar events to Microsoft Outlook. Uses Google Calendar triggers for event creation/cancellation and Outlook API to create/delete events, including email notifications on cancellations. Integrates Google Calendar and Microsoft Outlook APIs via n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fG2ycSxlIfOUxYmNgrOr14y7tDZbgR-u">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R15" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">16</div></th><td class="s6">Notion Daily Posts to LinkedIn</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching daily posts from a Notion database, formats content and images, then publishes them on LinkedIn. Uses Notion API, LinkedIn API, and n8n&#39;s schedule, code, HTTP request, and merge nodes for seamless content automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wn7jP0LRreTcszDctrcm__W76MOgrlRo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R16" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">17</div></th><td class="s6">Multi-Agent AI Chat Conversation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow enabling conversations with multiple AI agents concurrently using OpenRouter API for models like GPT-4o, Claude, and Gemini. It supports customized agent personalities, dynamic selection via @mentions, session memory, and aggregated responses for scalable multi-agent chats.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1j4q_KLMfCk7Xt6kK6yCCNJoTNKHUkZ7s">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R17" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">18</div></th><td class="s6">Property-Based Lead Qualification Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates lead qualification by integrating CRM leads with BatchData&#39;s Property Lookup API. Fetches lead data, verifies property details, applies a scoring system, updates CRM, and routes high-value leads with Slack alerts and task creation. Uses webhook, HTTP requests, and code nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=172yg5xLowRj48xiazrWWuw2IKBPtdKTp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R18" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">19</div></th><td class="s6">Stripe Invoice Payment to HubSpot and Slack Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates workflow for Stripe invoice payments: triggers on payment success, searches and updates HubSpot deals by PO number, and sends detailed Slack notifications to accounting team. Uses Stripe API, HubSpot API (OAuth2), and Slack for seamless payment tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lD128ta7AFmq0vsNhIA2IGHHi3I_sePd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R19" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">20</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Order Automation Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates Shopify order processing integrating Zoho CRM, Trello, Gmail, Mailchimp, and Harvest. It updates CRM contacts, creates tasks, sends conditional emails, tags customers, and generates invoices to streamline order management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NQsKs5CAojCS3RslNW-ccCIYhEwuYZ4s">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R20" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">21</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Interaction to Email Campaign Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates creating email campaigns from LinkedIn post interactions using Phantombuster to scrape likers and commenters, Dropcontact for contact enrichment, Airtable for contact management, and Lemlist plus Hubspot for campaign and CRM integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YdZy_T5OiKcQvVYiHdJQQMMcuF7wUj2v">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R21" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">22</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Enrichment &amp; Airtable Update Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates lead data enrichment from Typeform via Dropcontact, manages contacts in Airtable, and sends notifications on Slack. Integrates Typeform, Dropcontact API, Airtable, and Slack for streamlined lead capture and CRM updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u5dzKC3NI8VghwNIixJuezb5D25JpWNW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R22" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">23</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Fulfillment to Onfleet Task Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates task creation in Onfleet upon new Shopify fulfillment via Shopify Trigger node and Onfleet API. Seamlessly integrates Shopify and Onfleet for streamlined delivery task management in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yb-LCTKJvA16aMxSZgdMK0FoDLFe6F6C">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R23" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">24</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Email Appointment Scheduler</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Gmail API, Google Calendar, and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to detect appointment requests in incoming emails, check calendar availability, compose precise meeting proposals, and automatically reply and mark emails as read.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-68j-xjZMauLkSdHGydTU_FI_QNX22Q7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R24" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">25</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Agent with Memory and Search</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o-mini chat model, SerpAPI for web search, and a memory buffer to create an AI chat agent that handles incoming chat messages, performs real-time web queries, and maintains context for conversational interactions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uYZ-kWVSwOCgc2pta1anOuQc3FCu0xwP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R25" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">26</div></th><td class="s6">AI Conversational Agent with External Tools</td><td class="s7">An AI chatbot workflow using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini, integrated with SerpAPI and Wikipedia for enhanced real-time info retrieval. It stores recent chat history in a 20-message buffer to maintain context, enabling dynamic, informed human-like conversations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ozjg9N0ztcP8N15zdHN5ZAJGLg_wDH3m">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R26" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">27</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Receipt Expense Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates expense tracking by parsing receipt images sent via Telegram using Mindee API, logs details to Google Sheets, confirms via Telegram, and sends SMS notification via Twilio. Streamlines receipt management and bookkeeping.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11vArAZa38md_q3V-kXxbLArXxjZ-cGNw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R27" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">28</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Lead Qualification and Deal Creation</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates cold email response analysis using Gmail, OpenAI GPT-4, and Pipedrive CRM. It checks replies for interest in meetings, qualifies leads with AI, and creates deals in Pipedrive for interested prospects, streamlining sales outreach processes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XZo_8L4e3oy9QcM560xJpQK25thaK0KC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R28" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">29</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Qualification &amp; Slack Notification</td><td class="s7">Automates lead capture from a form, verifies email via Hunter API, scores leads using MadKudu API, and sends qualified lead alerts to Slack. Utilizes n8n form trigger, Hunter email verifier, MadKudu lead scoring, and Slack API integration for streamlined lead management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14ymgOvT-KoVNMI4r5hAc7GHE2tvXQjtM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R29" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">30</div></th><td class="s6">RAG AI Agent with Milvus &amp; Cohere</td><td class="s7">Automates Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) using Cohere embeddings, Milvus vector DB, OpenAI GPT-4o, and Google Drive. Upload PDFs to Drive, auto-embed and store in Milvus, then query via an AI chat agent for contextual AI responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ogW_itSayGMpytnfqOXyOENDEkfAA0El">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R30" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">31</div></th><td class="s6">Social Media Post Generator &amp; Twitter Poster</td><td class="s7">Automates social media post creation by fetching content ideas from Google Sheets, generating posts using OpenAI GPT-4, posting to Twitter via Twitter API, and updating Google Sheets with posting info. Integrates Google Sheets, OpenAI, and Twitter APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zzcvdqrDf5BoFGXsqOAa61iqBPRichAe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R31" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">32</div></th><td class="s6">Incident Management: PagerDuty, Jira &amp; Mattermost</td><td class="s7">Automates incident lifecycle by integrating PagerDuty, Jira, and Mattermost. Creates Jira issues from PagerDuty incidents, updates statuses on acknowledgment &amp; resolution, and posts real-time messages with interactive buttons in Mattermost channels.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ljzC_OVLp3Hi3Z5RB7-gl-lBNQVUfp1h">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R32" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">33</div></th><td class="s6">Daily AI News Summary &amp; Translation to Telegram</td><td class="s7">An automated workflow fetching daily AI news from NewsAPI and GNews, summarizing and translating top articles into Traditional Chinese using GPT-4, and delivering the digest via Telegram bot. Integrates NewsAPI, GNews, OpenAI GPT-4, and Telegram API for seamless news updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LCzALbYVvnUmn8A5X14yylo_nZHQYepM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R33" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">34</div></th><td class="s6">Two-Way Sync Between Pipedrive and MySQL</td><td class="s7">Automates bidirectional data synchronization between Pipedrive CRM and a MySQL database. Utilizes n8n nodes including Pipedrive API, MySQL integration, dataset comparison, and conditional logic to create, update, and maintain consistent contact records.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aOJPzze8zDoGQk9EH7oHp2_nxfWh_H_t">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R34" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">35</div></th><td class="s6">Event Attendee Automation with Mattermost &amp; Google</td><td class="s7">Automates attendee registration for events using Typeform, Google Sheets, Mattermost chat, Google Calendar, and Gmail. It registers attendees, creates Mattermost accounts, adds them to teams/channels, updates event calendars, and sends confirmation emails.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1N2K_PHmlZa5gXYf88YJgfxrM_AwK-Wgm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R35" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">36</div></th><td class="s6">Notion-Triggered AI SEO Content Publisher</td><td class="s7">Automates creation and publishing of SEO-optimized blog posts by detecting Notion database updates. Integrates Notion API, Langchain AI, WordPress API, Gmail, and DeepSeek AI to write, publish, notify, and log content seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HdZhmsT2ByVKWauCJXWd2AX6aOAZSp3m">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R36" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">37</div></th><td class="s6">Phishing URL Analyzer with URLScan and VirusTotal</td><td class="s7">Automates phishing URL detection from unread Outlook emails by extracting URLs, scanning via URLScan.io and VirusTotal APIs, and sending detailed Slack alerts. Integrates Microsoft Outlook, Python ioc-finder lib, URLScan.io, VirusTotal, and Slack for automated cybersecurity threat analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ooal9yLE6seJ_sHx1znUGJHOdhCGDKBf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R37" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">38</div></th><td class="s6">Blotato Multi-Platform Social Media Publisher</td><td class="s7">Automates publishing of videos and images to Instagram, Facebook, YouTube, TikTok, Twitter, LinkedIn, Pinterest, Threads, and Bluesky using Blotato API. Integrates Airtable for content management and OpenAI GPT-4 for optimizing YouTube titles, enabling streamlined multi-channel social media scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1E1ed3uviVQYbsLwViz4hOyBeXAlpliwJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R38" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">39</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered RAG Chatbot with Google Drive &amp; Qdrant</td><td class="s7">An advanced n8n workflow that creates a Retrieval-Augmented Generation chatbot integrating Google Drive, Google Gemini AI, Qdrant vector store, OpenAI embeddings, and Telegram for notifications. It processes documents, extracts metadata, stores vectors, enables conversational search, and supports secure vector data management with human confirmation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XtNI3srJ2vzHuxDDJXIqssxa8M-tQAlt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R39" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">40</div></th><td class="s6">Crypto News Sentiment Telegram Bot</td><td class="s7">Telegram bot leveraging OpenAI GPT-4o, integrated with multiple crypto news RSS feeds. It analyzes user queries, fetches relevant articles, summarizes news and market sentiment for cryptocurrencies or companies, and delivers concise AI-generated insights via Telegram messages.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LvnMbo67I4THoN2isIk-obVFXFtTfRWb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R40" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">41</div></th><td class="s6">Email Expense Extractor to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of expense data from email receipts using Gmail IMAP and Mindee Receipt OCR API, then appends data to Google Sheets. Ideal for streamlining expense tracking with n8n automation workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YWOBCmMaJP9_ch2MvmGZie_dQgNfa1Mm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R41" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">42</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Video Upload &amp; Caption for Social Media</td><td class="s7">Automates uploading videos from a Google Drive folder to TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube using upload-post.com API. Extracts audio with OpenAI to generate engaging captions, sending error alerts via Telegram. Tech: Google Drive, OpenAI, upload-post.com API, Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KTs1Y0fk9NzW6v5bZCH-o_zmUwvhOPSW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R42" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">43</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube to SEO Blog Post Automator</td><td class="s7">Automate SEO blog post creation from YouTube videos using Dumpling AI for transcripts and image generation, OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o for content writing, and Gmail for emailing the finished post. Converts video content into optimized, structured blog-ready HTML with engaging images.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QDpszgihbVf-TCpMt9w0CPaELc3_MDyT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R43" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">44</div></th><td class="s6">Discord AI Management Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Discord bot API and OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini model to manage Discord server channels with AI-driven message responses. Features workflow &amp; chat triggers, context memory, and multi-channel posting for automated, stylish Discord communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16xsnJdd4r48UDSAnelEplgjJGMTv0DtU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R44" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">45</div></th><td class="s6">Movie Recommender Chatbot with Qdrant &amp; OpenAI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that builds a conversational movie recommendation chatbot using GitHub-stored IMDb data, OpenAI embeddings and chat models, and a Qdrant vector database for similarity search to deliver personalized movie recommendations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18II50J9uByP8NtmUZxY-Iv56H3CjbqRF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R45" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">46</div></th><td class="s6">AI Meeting Summary &amp; Follow-Up Scheduler</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Google Meet transcripts, uses OpenAI-powered AI agent to summarize meetings, identify key points, and schedule follow-up Google Calendar events with attendees. Integrates Google Calendar, Google Drive, Google Meet APIs, and OpenAI Langchain AI agent.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OKNg6mSU_mFygZwSh8bJWC1dJ0RTLxz3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R46" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">47</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Calendar Assistant with PDF Q&amp;A</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o, Pinecone vector store, Google Calendar API, and Langchain to automate appointment booking with Max Tkacz, classify emails, and enable chat-based Q&amp;A on PDFs like the BTC whitepaper, all via a chat interface and Slack notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MmJsRgy5fXXyivJ6yN6o4QcSTi0yylzI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R47" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">48</div></th><td class="s6">AI Meeting Task &amp; Scheduling Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automates meeting transcript processing from Fireflies using OpenAI GPT-4 to create Airtable tasks, notify clients via Gmail, and schedule follow-up calls in Google Calendar. Streamlines project management by converting meeting notes into actionable workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IUX9udWgUaT-qIhX-_Um3F7SokkCtXvt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R48" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">49</div></th><td class="s6">AI Real-Time Meeting Transcription &amp; Notes</td><td class="s7">Automates real-time meeting transcription and note-taking using Recall.ai for transcription, OpenAI GPT-4 for AI insights, and Supabase/Postgres for data storage. Captures, structures, and analyzes meeting dialogue for productivity boosts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tw-gltfELcw4Vd782PkXu7fMQXhVtYzU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R49" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">50</div></th><td class="s6">Supabase File AI Chatbot Integration</td><td class="s7">Automates document processing from Supabase storage by fetching files, extracting text/PDF content, vectorizing data with OpenAI embeddings, storing vectors in Supabase, and enabling conversational queries via an AI chat interface using Langchain and OpenAI APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1psAMpxeqLvt1z5qsQ3s_yMSMEP0c_qr5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R50" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">51</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Agent for Supabase DB</td><td class="s7">N8N workflow integrating OpenAI and Supabase PostgreSQL to create an AI-powered chat assistant for database queries. It dynamically generates SQL based on user input, retrieves schema info, runs queries, and returns data via conversational AI.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-AFo-NHVoH_eny3imCWE-OxkDCX_f8mz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R51" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">52</div></th><td class="s6">AI Google Calendar Assistant with OpenAI</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o and Google Calendar API to create and retrieve calendar events. It uses Langchain for AI agent management, supports natural language chat input, and dynamic memory buffer for session context.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xfv36C4nh1q4h86BoaSiFvOyFtL4WPBI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R52" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">53</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable PDF Data Extractor with LLM Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of data from PDFs stored in Airtable using dynamic prompts and OpenAI LLM. Utilizes Airtable webhooks, PDF extraction, LangChain LLM nodes, and HTTP requests for real-time AI-based field updates in Airtable records.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VGNKODhEKfvzsUTw0Col9PpPiS6RBB2m">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R53" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">54</div></th><td class="s6">AI Triathlon Coach with Strava &amp; Gemini</td><td class="s7">Automates personalized triathlon coaching by analyzing Strava activity data using Google Gemini (PaLM) AI. Generates detailed, motivational feedback and improvement plans for swimming, cycling, and running, then formats and sends insights via email or WhatsApp.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Xsm-KbyyCqQdi5Ddnd_iBw6OC3PgE1FM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R54" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">55</div></th><td class="s6">AI Voice Chat with OpenAI, Gemini &amp; ElevenLabs</td><td class="s7">An AI voice chat system that transcribes speech using OpenAI, generates conversational responses with Google Gemini Chat model, manages context via LangChain memory nodes, and creates speech audio using ElevenLabs API. Integrates webhook for real-time voice interaction.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZoZo9LXfiA7TsJgyRWSwItQDAQrrumun">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R55" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">56</div></th><td class="s6">Voice RAG Chatbot with ElevenLabs &amp; OpenAI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow creating a voice-interactive RAG chatbot using ElevenLabs voice agents, OpenAI language models &amp; embeddings, Qdrant vector store, and Google Drive for document ingestion. Enables answering user questions via voice by integrating speech &amp; AI-driven document retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wWq30yX4O5Xx8C5aLKGXTntODOneqYtC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R56" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">57</div></th><td class="s6">AI Company Research &amp; Data Enrichment</td><td class="s7">Automates company info research using n8n with OpenAI GPT-4, SerpAPI, ScrapingBee, and Google Sheets. Extracts data like domain, LinkedIn URL, pricing, plans, APIs, integrations, and case studies for B2B/B2C markets, enabling scalable enrichment workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1azz6SwY5xkasADNY2_RohXhWEysGGv1t">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R57" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">58</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Trend Analyzer AI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using LangChain AI, OpenAI GPT, YouTube API, and custom memory management to help YouTube creators discover trending videos and content patterns in their niche from the last 2 days. It provides insightful analytics with video stats and channels links.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yrXkXeiQK3N1vl8jCX-G9CVQtsyIXE99">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R58" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">59</div></th><td class="s6">AI Lead Processing &amp; Email Notification System</td><td class="s7">Automates analysis of incoming lead notes, categorizes inquiries, finds appropriate contacts from a database, and generates email notifications. Integrates ERPNext for lead data, OpenAI for NLP analysis, Google Sheets for contact lookup, and Microsoft Outlook API to format/send emails.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VO1n4wmngJRNqmmo_VJRpYB5MhRO9Ee7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R59" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">60</div></th><td class="s6">AI Summary Automation for WordPress Posts</td><td class="s7">Automates creating AI-generated summary blocks for WordPress posts using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, WordPress REST API, Google Sheets for tracking, and Slack for notifications. It fetches posts, checks summary existence, generates summaries in HTML bullet format, updates posts, logs data, and alerts teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GoLrM9s4kSnxB1YQcAUmWuE6sfpBHQIK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R60" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">61</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered ERPNext Recruitment Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates candidate screening and job application processing by integrating ERPNext ERP, Google Gemini AI, and communication tools like WhatsApp and Outlook. Extracts resume text, evaluates fit via AI scoring, updates ERPNext with decisions, and notifies applicants.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LAJbrpxnFPm9rMANDoGxHKe7_-T9-EHg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R61" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">62</div></th><td class="s6">AI Email Autoresponder with Approval</td><td class="s7">Automates email handling using IMAP trigger, OpenAI GPT and DeepSeek models for summarization and response generation, Qdrant vector DB for business info retrieval, and Gmail for draft approval before sending. Ideal for professional, concise business email replies.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BaK9hQ85itMWnwjiHCpLoF5F8OJcpLm9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R62" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">63</div></th><td class="s6">AI Topic Monitoring with RSS, OpenAI, Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates topic monitoring by fetching RSS feeds from Google Sheets URLs, classifying relevance with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, scraping content via Jina AI, summarizing articles for Slack, and storing metadata in Google Sheets. Ideal for professionals tracking AI-related news.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Vh_e9hh7p8JFsxolqs_PMPdYsV1IvK5P">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R63" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">64</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce Customer Order Chat Assistant</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating WooCommerce API, DHL tracking, and OpenAI GPT-4 to provide customers with secure, real-time order and shipping info via chat. Features encrypted email handling, order querying, DHL status checks, and AI-powered conversational support.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_dB7eSMPmySwvuzQT99V7uBuJp8SW2Ae">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R64" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">65</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress AI Content Creator with Multi-Level Rewrites</td><td class="s7">Automates creating WordPress blog drafts using OpenAI GPT models for structured content generation and rewriting at Grade 2, 5, and 9 reading levels. Integrates Pollinations.ai for featured image creation, Google Drive for backups, and Telegram for notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17DiQBXsAO7UR3gsT0Gj-7WVe0QxiEp2c">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R65" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">66</div></th><td class="s6">Automated GitHub PR Code Review</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates GitHub pull request code review using OpenAI GPT-4 for inline comments. It triggers on PR events, fetches code diffs, creates AI review prompts, posts comments, optionally adds labels, and references Google Sheets for best practices.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ArxuTGGYI_cGsEU65O9S5B0flexFr2B7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R66" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">67</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Phishing Email Detection &amp; Jira Reporting</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates phishing email detection by integrating Gmail and Outlook triggers, uses hcti.io API to create email body screenshots, applies OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o model for phishing analysis, and auto-generates Jira tickets with detailed reports and attachments for security teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15VWx0Ykvmdpc_X4ew-Amtanqx7bn5ouH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R67" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">68</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Phishing Email Detection &amp; Jira Reporting</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates phishing email detection by monitoring Gmail and Outlook inboxes, extracting email content and headers, generating email screenshots via hcti.io API, analyzing with ChatGPT-4, and creating detailed Jira tickets with reports and attachments for streamlined security incident management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gPmFLfDCX2lTKsQ2jU8GKxO4GuX1OF6b">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R68" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">69</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Google Calendar Event Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of Google Calendar events from new rows in Google Sheets using n8n. Integrates Google Sheets API for event data retrieval and Google Calendar API for event creation, including date formatting, event details, and color-coding for efficient event management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VN_X8t5ZnJSKMlzYk-ICr8J23APLdEEW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R69" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">70</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Blog Writer &amp; Publisher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating blog content creation and publishing. Uses Google Sheets for scheduling/configuration, OpenAI (via OpenRouter) for AI content generation, and WordPress XML-RPC API for posting. Includes data preprocessing, content merging, and status logging to Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VNd91WE-MXMfpKkV_fhHklpSVOlCwMjt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R70" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">71</div></th><td class="s6">BambooHR AI Chatbot for Company Policies</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered chatbot built with n8n using BambooHR API, OpenAI&#39;s GPT models, LangChain nodes, and Supabase for vector storage. It helps employees query company policies, benefits, and find employee or department contacts efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ziKQNzotbKqwSU-dCDbOs1w8-9__aE7s">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R71" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">72</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Interview Scheduling Assistant</td><td class="s7">An automated interview scheduler using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Google Calendar APIs. It checks calendar availability, generates 30-min weekday slots (9am-5pm EST), interacts via AI chat to gather candidate info, and books interviews without double booking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16FoEfW547H6G1j79kZIE8iylFj_ZmwY9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R72" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">73</div></th><td class="s6">AI Document Note Generator from Folder</td><td class="s7">Automates note creation by monitoring a folder for new docs (PDF, DOCX, TEXT), extracting and summarizing content using Mistral Cloud LLM, LangChain text splitter, and Qdrant vector store. Generates study guides, timelines, and briefings, then exports files locally.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-XtUJQfdGnzIII2qVy7G81usu2qoqYRc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R73" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">74</div></th><td class="s6">Movie Recommender Chatbot with Qdrant &amp; OpenAI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to build a movie recommendation chatbot using GitHub-hosted IMDB movie data, OpenAI embeddings and GPT-4o-mini chat model, and Qdrant vector database for vector similarity search. It processes user requests, embeds them, queries Qdrant, and returns top-3 personalized movie recommendations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Nmz2kf2o-DdiHhah0LMGE8tMgKsZ_70f">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R74" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">75</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered HubSpot Chat Assistant</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating HubSpot Conversations with OpenAI Assistants and Airtable. Automates receiving chat messages, processing via OpenAI APIs, invoking external business data APIs, and replying in HubSpot, enabling intelligent chat automation and CRM interaction.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14aYlDpuc3THDDt1u6xiwYKKL90fGc_LI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R75" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">76</div></th><td class="s6">Auto-Post to 9 Social Platforms</td><td class="s7">Automates video publishing across Instagram, YouTube, TikTok, Facebook, LinkedIn, Threads, Twitter, Bluesky, and Pinterest using n8n, Google Sheets, and Blotato API. Scheduled to fetch video data, upload it, then post simultaneously to all platforms without manual effort.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yQ-m3jrz_GVuBV4wHegaykrrS_cB7Jbv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R76" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">77</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chat Assistant</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram and OpenAI&#39;s Chat API via Langchain to create a responsive AI assistant that listens to Telegram messages and replies with helpful, emoji-enhanced answers in real-time.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RQajAs7KxH70xfbl7Mbjw2CPYF4ehJXD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R77" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">78</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive Document QA with Pinecone &amp; OpenAI</td><td class="s7">Automates Q&amp;A on documents fetched from Google Drive by indexing text chunks into Pinecone vector DB using OpenAI embeddings. Supports chat queries with contextual answers and citations. Tech stack: Google Drive API, Pinecone vector DB, OpenAI embeddings &amp; chat models, n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17UKUybsrE_bOLlNPSxefRudkwOFQYGew">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R78" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">79</div></th><td class="s6">Audio Transcription and Summary with OpenAI &amp; Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates audio file transcription and summarization using OpenAI&#39;s API, stores raw and processed transcripts as JSON and markdown in Google Drive, and sends notifications via Gmail and Telegram. Includes optional user approval and advanced transcript structuring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OkTRCXu33pxM6cXOT5fbAKfmXK4FM3gs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R79" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">80</div></th><td class="s6">WhatsApp AI Chatbot with Qdrant RAG</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered WhatsApp Business chatbot leveraging Meta Webhooks, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, Qdrant vector database, and Google Drive for document retrieval. It uses a Retrieval-Augmented Generation system to answer customer queries about electronics products with contextual knowledge base support.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=159VN7uEnvnoDupI9WrpEHytZI1Pk1XB-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R80" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">81</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Gmail Reply Draft Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates email reply drafting by fetching Gmail threads with specific labels, sending email content to OpenAI Assistant for a reply, generating HTML, and saving drafts in Gmail. Utilizes Gmail API, OpenAI API, and n8n automation platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FVEkN2AuF3Kwii9hJdVFwRzXminbU1wB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R81" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">82</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Dynamic User Interview Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates AI-driven user interviews using n8n forms, Groq LLM, Redis session management (via Upstash), and Google Sheets for transcript storage. It dynamically asks interview questions, records answers in sessions, and displays transcripts on completion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_I4AT2z0hdlyyy2swiIp6bkI9bUs5cFd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R82" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">83</div></th><td class="s6">Adaptive RAG Query Processor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow utilizing Google Gemini and Qdrant vector store to classify user queries into Factual, Analytical, Opinion, or Contextual types, and adaptively retrieve and generate precise answers with tailored strategies for each query type.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VbBcaxvK3uxD0A8AQzNixP-b71iWvU_T">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R83" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">84</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Appointment Scheduler Chatbot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4, Microsoft Outlook API, and LangChain to create an intelligent personal assistant chatbot. It handles calendar availability, books meetings, and manages enquiries with timezone-aware scheduling and email notifications for a seamless appointment booking experience.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GUkdOspgQ1x7dq8M0FuZY-WDwB35Oj3h">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R84" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">85</div></th><td class="s6">Fastmail Email Auto-Reply with GPT-4</td><td class="s7">Automates email reply drafts in Fastmail using IMAP email triggers, Fastmail JMAP API, and OpenAI GPT-4. Extracts incoming email content, generates personalized responses, and uploads replies as drafts for review and sending.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-lawrY_6BtPyrDLIzlZvI78uFo4igmY_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R85" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">86</div></th><td class="s6">Slack AI Assistant with Google Gemini</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that receives Slack messages via webhook, processes them with Google Gemini AI and Langchain memory, and sends contextual AI-powered replies back to Slack channels, enabling interactive and persistent AI assistance within Slack.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=102HkIFWa_XxTm-ULbsYrX6w8Kr_kDikH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R86" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">87</div></th><td class="s6">Trustpilot Reviews Insight Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping Trustpilot reviews, stores embeddings in Qdrant vector DB, clusters reviews using K-means, summarizes insights via OpenAI GPT-4, and exports results to Google Sheets. Stack: n8n (automation), Trustpilot (reviews), Qdrant (vector DB), OpenAI (LLM), Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bF3VyzN50lzGvoYeeGnHTq_NRHUoKkf5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R87" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">88</div></th><td class="s6">Slack to Linear AI Ticket Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates support ticket creation by monitoring Slack with ticket emoji, uses OpenAI GPT for summarizing, titling, prioritizing issues, and creates tickets in Linear. Tech: Slack API, Linear API, OpenAI (ChatGPT) via n8n nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SwuK0R7BlyQhp4BIddUtoOUJyl9zwHkI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R88" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">89</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Comment Analysis &amp; Reporting</td><td class="s7">Automates analysis of YouTube video details and up to 100 comments using YouTube Data API, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and n8n. Generates detailed creator reports with sentiment, themes, engagement, and content suggestions. Saves reports to Google Drive and sends via Gmail.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1O5LwSmnYVRqoHZOp2KemnzHv2zhS8kw_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R89" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">90</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Meeting Summary with Gemini AI &amp; Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates daily meeting summaries by retrieving Google Calendar events, processing them with Google Gemini AI model, and sending concise summaries to a Slack channel. Uses Google Calendar API, Google PaLM API, Slack API for seamless team communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13zhcqbybM80EZ9kzq1zhL86mTF2FCbkH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R90" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">91</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Assistant with Baserow Memory</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered Telegram assistant integrating OpenAI GPT-4o mini, Baserow databases for long-term memory and notes, Postgres chat memory, with voice, photo processing, and personalized responses. Automates note-taking, memory recall, and multi-modal input handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aM708et7z04JKb6Rp2kINOe2ogY5IDhu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R91" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">92</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Gmail Spam &amp; Marketing Filter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates Gmail inbox cleaning by classifying emails as unwanted, marketing, or spam using Google Gemini AI. It deletes flagged emails and sends Telegram notifications about deletions or skips. Integrates Gmail API, Google PaLM AI, and Telegram API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10p2sN97yloOw7V6R7oyvsgvQby3H0hu6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R92" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">93</div></th><td class="s6">Tech Radar AI Insight &amp; Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Tech Radar data from Google Sheets into MySQL and Google Docs, enriches it using Google Gemini embeddings and Pinecone vector store, and provides AI-powered querying via RAG and SQL agents for strategic tech adoption insights across multiple companies.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19rwiIN4K_eSAWkJkdP0m-a3PrnRZ5Qk8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R93" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">94</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Study Assistant for Signal Processing</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram API, OpenAI (including transcription and GPT models), Google Gemini, Airtable, and Langchain tools to build an AI-powered interactive tutor for signal processing students via Telegram, featuring memory, calculator, Wikipedia lookup, and content/email agent tools.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lBUkSHVjx4M3SJZIJV8siwFI-hAx8mMr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R94" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">95</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chatbot for BambooHR Policies &amp; Benefits</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered chatbot built in n8n using BambooHR API, OpenAI LLMs, Supabase vector DB, Langchain tools, and text splitting to assist employees with company policies, benefits, and contact info by searching documents and BambooHR employee data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xa1y0IARU_lrlqbartrOB7_g0k6CE56s">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R95" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">96</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Incident Management with NocoDB</td><td class="s7">Automates incident ticketing by integrating NocoDB for data storage, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for AI-driven incident categorization, Slack and SMTP for notifications. Streamlines issue reporting, AI prioritization, and timely alerts for clients and assignees.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ifKOSihOFkFLW84oClFYKNWLPiuGTLs4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R96" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">97</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Email Automation &amp; Management</td><td class="s7">Automates email reading, summarization, reply drafting, and approval using IMAP, Gmail, OpenAI (