-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">106</div></th><td class="s6">PDF to WordPress Blog Creator with Human Approval</td><td class="s7">Automates converting PDFs into SEO-friendly WordPress blog drafts using OpenAI GPT for content, Pollinations.ai for images, with Gmail for human approval and Telegram notifications for publishing updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oHsWyr0t2DeVAfx77AOGoYAuEbQMUUj6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R106" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">107</div></th><td class="s6">WP CF7 Contact Form Auto Response &amp; Classification</td><td class="s7">Automates classification and drafting of responses to WordPress Contact Form 7 inquiries using Google Gemini AI and Gmail API. Saves categorized responses to Google Sheets, streamlining customer support for businesses handling diverse requests.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rZm5rDpVEsh2i70ZFTn6a6N712C4QamN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R107" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">108</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail AI Auto-Responder Draft Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates Gmail replies by detecting if an incoming email needs a response using OpenAI GPT-4o, then drafts professional replies in the thread via Gmail API. Utilizes n8n workflow with Gmail OAuth2, LangChain nodes, and OpenAI GPT models for smart email management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1P6e1JS5OQ3YM9LfslEXFk_Y0gV90AWio">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R108" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">109</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Meeting Summarizer with Gemini AI &amp; Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval and summarization of Google Calendar meetings using Google Gemini AI model and Langchain Calendar AI Agent, then posts concise summaries back to a Slack channel. Integrates Google Calendar API, Google Gemini (PaLM) AI, Slack API, and n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JqSASfQLTeSMbXWVjIP1267TYqfwX44T">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R109" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">110</div></th><td class="s6">Automate LinkedIn Posts from Notion with AI</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates daily LinkedIn posts by fetching content and images from Notion databases, enhancing text using OpenAI&#39;s GPT, and publishing to LinkedIn. Includes scheduled triggers, OpenAI API, Notion API, and LinkedIn OAuth integration for seamless social media management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NQwEAqtEudLCfnsnPQF4ENye-ytzap4H">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R110" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">111</div></th><td class="s6">AI Web Search Agent with Memory</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow combining OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini, SearchAPI.io, and LangChain to create an AI agent that performs web searches on demand. It uses SearchAPI as a tool and retains recent chat context with a sliding memory buffer for smarter responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HCACVaKwv48Gfh226OdoqaNib6YYD9IY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R111" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background">