x;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">121</div></th><td class="s6">TechFin Customer Support Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates customer support by integrating Voiceflow, Zendesk, Google Sheets, Google Calendar, and Airtable via n8n workflows. It fetches customer data, creates Zendesk tickets, schedules meetings, and logs transcripts for product analysis, streamlining tech customer success processes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Q52VUF__DP-woE0rNwvyCmuVM6yr0AUA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R121" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">122</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Audio Translator (55 Languages)</td><td class="s7">Automates translation of Telegram voice messages using OpenAI&#39;s speech-to-text and chat models. Supports 55 languages, converting speech to text, auto-detecting language, translating between native and target languages, and replying with translated text and audio. Tech: Telegram API, OpenAI API, n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ccn-2UDhTrag87eD9xE8z0G8hik4MGmz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R122" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">123</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Chapter Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates generating YouTube video chapters by extracting captions via YouTube API, processing transcripts with Google Gemini AI, and updating video descriptions. Integrates n8n, YouTube OAuth2 API, Google Gemini PaLM model, and Langchain nodes for structured output.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19aWAbNsQIO9gm_eLDBBducYIGHczwbt-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R123" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">124</div></th><td class="s6">AI Social Media Publisher from WordPress</td><td class="s7">Automates social media posting from WordPress content using AI-generated, platform-tailored captions and images. Integrates WordPress, Google Sheets, OpenRouter (Gemini 2.0), OpenAI, and APIs for X (Twitter), Facebook, Instagram, and LinkedIn for multi-platform publishing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1j5M-ww8YaZxouGHm3eLiAYhpqWqE0-DC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R124" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">125</div></th><td class="s6">Selenium Web Scraper with OpenAI Analysis</td><td class="s7">An advanced n8n workflow integrating Selenium via Docker, Google Search, and OpenAI GPT-4 to extract, analyze, and retrieve web data even behind login or restricted access. Supports cookie injection, screenshots, proxy use, and AI-based info extraction for dynamic web scraping.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1q5_9qPxo2xalpXLwX6GmtwrxVIN7-2si">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R125" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">126</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Personal Assistant</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram, OpenAI GPT-4o, Tavily web search API, and specialized agent workflows for email, calendar, contacts, and content creation. It processes user commands via chat, routes requests to proper agents, transcribes voice messages, and replies seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?expo