sending concise WhatsApp pre-meeting notifications. Integrates Google Calendar, Gmail, Apify web scraping, and WhatsApp API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zQ_-M0KIdb0z78l3f0d1gGem4OMjYom1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R132" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">133</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Factoid Email Subscription Service</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates sending personalized educational fact emails using Airtable for subscriber data, LangChain AI for content and image generation (Groq and OpenAI APIs), Gmail for delivery, and web forms for subscription management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1t-aOM6LV0vAakyEaL-a4PymKkFMZTPgH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R133" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">134</div></th><td class="s6">Automated API Schema Crawler &amp; Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates researching API documentation for services, scraping relevant pages using Apify, extracting REST API operations with Google Gemini LLM, storing data via Qdrant vector DB, and saving results in Google Sheets and Drive. Tech stack: Google Sheets, Google Drive, Apify web scraper, Qdrant vector store, Google Gemini LLM, n8n orchestrator.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VxRrFo4p1QJplcZjMybXqyDn9ROsST5R">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R134" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">135</div></th><td class="s6">Email Header Authentication &amp; IP Analysis</td><td class="s7">Automates email header analysis using Microsoft Graph API and IPQualityScore API to extract and evaluate SPF, DKIM, DMARC authentication and IP reputation, enabling detection of spam, phishing, and email spoofing threats.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1S2a-fvqrKz0Xj0MvX57IJUdvKr4YFr-u">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R135" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">136</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Assistant for Airtable Data</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI Chat (including LangChain) with Airtable API to enable conversational querying, data retrieval, filtering, aggregation, and analysis of Airtable bases. Includes tools for dynamic search filter generation, code processing, and map image creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dlqB83fZ5ZxXAJQM49oz06WiU2jylpwz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R136" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">137</div></th><td class="s6">Slack-ServiceNow Incident Search Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Slack API and ServiceNow API to let Slack users search for ServiceNow incidents by priority and state via a Slack modal interface. It sends incident summaries to a selected Slack channel or DM, enhancing IT service management communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17kO_POz7JVYmmbd66oiaz20N1-lSZtQu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R137" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">138</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Candidate Shortlisting for ERPNext</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates recruitment by integrating ERPNext with AI models (Google Gemini) to evaluate resumes against job descriptions, scoring and justifying candidate fit. Uses PDF extraction, HTTP API, and communication via Outlook and WhatsApp.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15y1iyVZOYzRsowPgEXF6K8gTOqXFGyUZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R138" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">139</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable PDF Data Extractor with AI</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of data from PDFs in Airtable using dynamic prompts and AI/LLM. Utilizes Airtable API, n8n nodes, and OpenAI models to update records based on webhook-triggered events. Ideal for enriching Airtable data with AI-powered document processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EE-vcVcPeHOWAX1fk8c2shLbcGGzAx8M">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R139" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">140</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Calendar Appointment Scheduler</td><td class="s7">An intelligent n8n workflow using OpenAI GPT-4, Microsoft Outlook API, and Langchain to handle customer chat, check calendar availability, suggest free slots within UK business hours, and book appointments or escalate to human support with detailed email notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-XZNeNORV7gCF4GUPuIUTxghpc04cuFQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R140" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">141</div></th><td class="s6">Spotify to YouTube Playlist Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates one-way synchronization from a Spotify playlist to a YouTube playlist using Spotify, YouTube Data API v3, and Supabase. It matches tracks by title, artist, and duration, updates playlists, manages deletions, and stores data persistently, with optional Discord notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AUOUZ375a7Xqu1zU73l6q-lybEcJ3i_e">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R141" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">142</div></th><td class="s6">n8n DeepResearcher Automated Research</td><td class="s7">Automates deep multi-step research using OpenAI (o3-mini) and Google Gemini LLMs, Apify web scraping, and Notion API to recursively generate, refine, and compile research insights into detailed reports in Notion. Ideal for complex topic exploration with configurable depth and breadth.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B9UHQYnpMlWhDCnl4PycCokNu43XBIVQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R142" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">143</div></th><td class="s6">AI Phone Agent with RetellAI &amp; RAG</td><td class="s7">An AI phone agent workflow using RetellAI for voice calls, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for transcript summarization, RAG with Qdrant vector DB for knowledge retrieval, and Google Calendar for appointment booking. Sends summaries via Telegram and automates customer support calls effectively.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BrSJb51sdZo_CCPfNQdn3Ee_CSxti2ui">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R143" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">144</div></th><td class="s6">CallForge Sales Call AI Insights</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of structured insights from sales call transcripts using n8n with Azure OpenAI GPT-4o-mini models. Provides detailed marketing, sales, and product feedback analysis, competitor comparison, and integration status to support sales, marketing, and product teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UstinqIpGrXdnObo4v9sJtOpFAf_tDni">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R144" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">145</div></th><td class="s6">Email to Notion Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates processing of incoming Gmail emails using OpenAI GPT-4, extracts tasks and summaries, and creates detailed pages in Notion databases. Uses Airtable to manage routing and labels to prevent duplicate processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fyLP1LQ7SmcdgW2OZIbrcxQehXYLJErH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R145" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">146</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Weekly Team Activity Report</td><td class="s7">Automates the creation of weekly team activity reports from Slack messages using Slack API and Google Gemini LLM. It fetches last week&#39;s messages, summarizes threads, generates individual and team reports, and posts them back to Slack every Monday at 6am.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B4bPBs5yw28oEippz5SyscbjiM3jhVJW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R146" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">147</div></th><td class="s6">Auto SEO Blog Writer with GPT-4, Perplexity &amp; WordPress</td><td class="s7">Automates full SEO blog content creation: collects fresh research via Perplexity API, generates SEO-optimized articles with GPT-4o, publishes to WordPress, sends Gmail &amp; Slack notifications, and logs to Notion. Integrates OpenAI, Perplexity, WordPress, Gmail, Slack, and Notion via n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fj3hFn--ETihnkIhsEQdWLhLUlvsv5P1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R147" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">148</div></th><td class="s6">Survey Response Insights Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates in-depth survey analysis by importing Google Sheets responses, vectorizing with OpenAI embeddings, clustering via K-means in Qdrant, and summarizing insights with GPT-4. Exports detailed sentiment and trends back to Sheets for actionable survey insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ru1-x-TB-E6zZxuOViTranz-7_sXMAzy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R148" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">149</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube RSS Feed Notifier with Email &amp; Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of YouTube channels via RSS feeds, fetching video details using YouTube Data API, and delivers custom notifications via Gmail (individual or digest emails) and Telegram. Includes OpenAI for generating responsive HTML email cards. Ideal for content creators and marketers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1U35Wd_EINZNcjgFiZANE4vCj2KXzYuuB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R149" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">150</div></th><td class="s6">Automated AI Graphic Design Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates graphic design from prompt to final image review using Ideogram API, OpenAI GPT-4 for image prompt evaluation, Google Drive and Sheets for storage and logging, and Gmail for notifications. Tailored for creative teams producing audience-optimized visuals.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IlwXwFMW6ODYgmAWF1npaJotH_4Ijjdu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R150" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">151</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Website Content SEO Audit</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow generates a detailed SEO content audit report for up to 1000 pages of any website using DataForSEO On-Page API and Google Search Console API. It analyzes technical SEO, content quality, metadata, linking, and performance, delivering a branded HTML report with key recommendations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NDE6XW5mvSpFd4n9624FmpzPcBU9cT6f">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R151" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">152</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Bot with Human-in-the-Loop Handoff</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram, Redis, and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for a state-driven chatbot that collects customer info, performs AI onboarding and after-sales support, and seamlessly hands off dialogs to human agents using human-in-the-loop with session memory and conversation summaries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17drkFXo0rCDAWQ6XQ8HJgiMDZB-qPd6a">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R152" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">153</div></th><td class="s6">UTM Link &amp; QR Generator with GA Reports</td><td class="s7">Automates UTM link creation with custom parameters, stores links in Airtable, generates QR codes via QuickChart, and schedules Google Analytics reports analyzed by OpenAI GPT-4. Integrates OpenAI, Airtable, Google Analytics, Gmail, and QuickChart APIs for marketing campaign tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ghT2nrfK5KNbkzxhNMV3Qs_y1wDCwfC0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R153" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">154</div></th><td class="s6">AI Instagram Caption Generator with Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of Instagram captions by integrating Airtable editorial plans with OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4 via n8n. Uses Airtable for briefing and background info on target audience, then generates creative, CTA-focused captions tailored for social media posts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=169tMPb159GqIKBKGhdDXrzekl_fwJFDq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R154" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">155</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Visual Regression Testing Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates visual regression testing by comparing webpage screenshots using Google Gemini AI vision model, Apify screenshot API, Google Drive &amp; Sheets, and Linear for issue tracking. Detects UI changes and reports them automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16SPjLXIn302RUiJoPwQjCMqLOELWG4PG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R155" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">156</div></th><td class="s6">AI SQL Agent with Dynamic Charting</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that integrates OpenAI GPT-4 with a SQL database to answer user data queries. It dynamically determines if a chart is needed, generates Chart.js definitions via OpenAI, and produces visual charts using Quickchart.io for enhanced data analysis and visualization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AYroqDKYA55c5LjbYIkolRMfHlvekqiP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R156" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">157</div></th><td class="s6">AI Workplace Discrimination Analysis</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and analysis of workplace discrimination patterns by scraping Glassdoor reviews using ScrapingBee, analyzing demographic ratings with OpenAI, and visualizing disparities via QuickChart. Identifies biased experiences across demographic groups with statistical insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qWsDa5wY3E4NBDupTwwVcvy95XOC8Hvg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R157" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">158</div></th><td class="s6">Semantic Web Search &amp; Result Re-Ranking</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Brave Search API for web queries combined with advanced LLMs (OpenAI GPT, Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini) to generate, refine, and semantically re-rank search results for precise info retrieval. Ideal for research with AI-powered query optimization and detailed result extraction.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OuUBW2Dt9NUHAonhU5q5H9vhM2YHYt93">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R158" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">159</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify to Google Sheets Product Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Shopify product data (title, tags, description, price) to Google Sheets using Shopify GraphQL API and Google Sheets API. Includes pagination, cursor tracking, daily schedule, and incremental updates for efficient product management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IogbPpVk5zVGaZ7GY7mTf_WKCi27qN_C">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R159" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">160</div></th><td class="s6">Service Page SEO Blueprint Generator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that analyzes competitor service pages and user intent using Jina Reader API and Google Gemini AI. It generates a detailed SEO content blueprint with competitor insights, user intent analysis, gap identification, and optimized page outline to maximize conversions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11IvtlKok8cv6v60ybbHy_PZF6DEbYahz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R160" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">161</div></th><td class="s6">OpenSea NFT Insights via AI &amp; Telegram</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that integrates Telegram, OpenAI GPT-4o Mini, and OpenSea API agent workflows to deliver AI-powered real-time NFT market analysis, collection stats, listings, and ownership insights directly via Telegram chat.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1djL4YYva3JLieHH5QaQh1iM2PUEoSfN3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R161" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">162</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Autonomous Research Workflow</td><td class="s7">An advanced n8n workflow automating deep research by generating search queries via LLM (OpenRouter), querying SerpAPI (Google Search), analyzing content with Jina AI, referencing Wikipedia, and synthesizing a comprehensive report using LangChain agents and memory buffers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GZIqnEsjIG-OH76Wz2QoVuACwtEg--Vb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R162" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">163</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress RAG &amp; GenAI Content Chatbot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating WordPress API, OpenAI embeddings (text-embedding-3-small), GPT-4o-mini chat model, Supabase vector DB, and Postgres for chat memory. It automates content embedding, updates, and provides a semantic search chatbot using website content.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NrnIlfZ0DMbaNvw_TYknuzA2iOEPzDlq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R163" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">164</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered WordPress Post Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of SEO-friendly WordPress draft posts from keywords using OpenAI GPT-4 for text and DALL-E for featured images, integrates Wikipedia for fact-checking, and uploads content and images via WordPress API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17dSH09ss9hQsFdPJ3Q_wk622_ADhVsWf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R164" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">165</div></th><td class="s6">Clockify Time Logging Assistant for Slack</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered n8n workflow integrating Clockify API and Slack to manage time entries via conversational chat. Uses OpenAI GPT for natural language processing, supports creating, updating, deleting time logs with user confirmation, and includes tools for date conversion and calculations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JKkzwC9_YYXJzg1O-a_lUzJOxzNrS4Hm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R165" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">166</div></th><td class="s6">Real Estate Market Scanner &amp; Alert System</td><td class="s7">Automates real estate property scanning using BatchData API. Schedules hourly searches, compares new and changed listings, filters high-equity absentee owner properties, and sends detailed email and Slack alerts to sales teams. Built with n8n, BatchData API, email SMTP, and Slack API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SCTdVFcbM0crPzVsRAUYBfwDZGH3oawx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R166" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">167</div></th><td class="s6">AI Knowledge Base Article Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates creating and editing knowledge base articles using Langchain AI agents, Perplexity API for deep research, and OpenAI GPT models. Ensures high-quality content with iterative editorial feedback and publishes directly to Contentful CMS.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18OjahLQvAa9OCZ3Q_WokXNV0BlktjkZk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R167" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">168</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chatbot with Jina.ai Webpage Scraper</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered chatbot workflow integrating Langchain and OpenAI&#39;s gpt-4o-mini model with Jina.ai&#39;s real-time web scraping tool. It scrapes live website data from user-supplied URLs, retains conversation memory, and delivers accurate, context-aware answers dynamically, ideal for research and support.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eO0f8_9-cRNJIq5HAV4cI9KD63tUQ3La">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R168" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">169</div></th><td class="s6">SEO Blog Generator with GPT-4o &amp; Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates SEO blog post creation using OpenAI GPT-4o, integrated with Perplexity AI for research and Telegram for notifications. It generates blog drafts, SEO-friendly titles, slugs, metas, and merges content for streamlined content marketing workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17da1DdFhc2ZsFDDyup06Y_P1j87cUbVb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R169" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">170</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Topic Monitoring &amp; Summarization</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of RSS feeds with AI using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini for relevance classification and article summarization, Jina AI for content extraction, Google Sheets for data storage, and Slack for delivering formatted summaries. Keeps teams informed about relevant topics efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kI8KMq3oyOWVRwcRq4qJ2sDm7T5WKsvv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R170" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">171</div></th><td class="s6">Suspicious Login Detection Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow for detecting suspicious logins using GreyNoise API for IP threat intelligence, IP-API for geolocation, UserParser for user agent analysis, and Postgres for login history. It prioritizes alerts and notifies via Slack and email for security response.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_YhZSysnd7B6IbcO2bneS25G5Ka2dUDs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R171" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">172</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered WooCommerce Product Import &amp; SEO</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates WooCommerce product creation from Google Sheets, leveraging OpenRouter AI to generate SEO-optimized meta titles and descriptions per product. It updates WooCommerce via API and notifies progress via Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cAiEudJqXGaQujgUyaK0SrWrsXPiYm1L">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R172" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">173</div></th><td class="s6">AI Image Data Extraction API with Gemini</td><td class="s7">Creates an API endpoint that extracts structured data from images using Google&#39;s Gemini AI (Flash Lite) model. The workflow fetches an image URL, converts it to base64, calls the Gemini API for OCR, and returns custom JSON with extracted fields, ideal for document and form automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oxe7_bdGUMxE7Za7JmGFb19dtepK2-iO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R173" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">174</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Scheduled WordPress Blog Publisher</td><td class="s7">Automates generation, scheduling, and publishing of SEO-optimized WordPress blog posts using GPT-4o for content, Pexels API for images, and Google Sheets for data management. Features randomized delay for natural posting cadence.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1flmzKewvZVdfvNY9_y2iO8pp-XhLAdZc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R174" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">175</div></th><td class="s6">AI-powered GitHub Trending Auto Social Poster</td><td class="s7">Automates curation of trending GitHub projects from Hacker News, fetching project details, generating tailored Twitter and LinkedIn posts using OpenAI GPT-4, and posting via X (Twitter) and LinkedIn APIs. Includes Airtable tracking and Telegram notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1thu3_g-Qpjn_Hj_W0gMz8KmYSeM54XGE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R175" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">176</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Email to Vector Embeddings Pipeline</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Gmail emails, structuring metadata in PostgreSQL and generating vector embeddings with Ollama&#39;s nomic-embed-text model stored in PGVector for semantic search and analysis. Built with n8n, Gmail API, PostgreSQL, and Ollama embeddings.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1faRwmjPn7FeDheXOCp84E4ASVxmN67j1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R176" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">177</div></th><td class="s6">HR &amp; IT Helpdesk Chatbot with Voice Support</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram, OpenAI for text and audio transcription, PostgreSQL vector DB, and Langchain AI agent to build an interactive HR &amp; IT helpdesk chatbot that answers employee queries with internal policy data from PDFs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13-L2DmDaNjc2v-MYMcJUYtitGdc05aZH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R177" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">178</div></th><td class="s6">AI WhatsApp Chatbot: Text, Voice, Image, PDF</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered WhatsApp chatbot built with n8n integrates WhatsApp API, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for chat, image analysis, audio transcription, and PDF extraction. It processes text, voice, images, and PDFs to generate intelligent, context-aware replies for versatile user interactions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1elJkGUauM1Yz7UQ8n6wYnsAquXtC6T9h">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R178" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">179</div></th><td class="s6">Zoom AI Meeting Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automates Zoom meeting data retrieval, transcript extraction, and participant info to generate formal meeting summaries using OpenAI GPT-4. Integrates with ClickUp for task creation and Microsoft Outlook for scheduling follow-ups. Sends summary emails via SMTP.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1meeoB8_S14ATzeYw2u_0z8bZizpFU1iD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R179" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">180</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Google Calendar Assistant</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4 via Langchain with Google Calendar API to create, update, get, and delete calendar events intelligently. Handles single and attendee events, using AI to interpret user queries and manage schedules seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iGi4YTC-47BWfSQ0lreiVDXQbVfgk7KD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R180" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">181</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Blog Content Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates blog writing by combining the Tavily search API for real-time web data with Anthropic&#39;s AI language model to craft well-structured, SEO-optimized HTML content with proper citations and a natural tone.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1T7M5z9stFIamkOeIa9VahWtu0RnrUSMY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R181" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">182</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Gmail Assistant</td><td class="s7">An AI-driven email management workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o with Gmail API to automate composing, sending, replying, drafting, labeling, and managing emails efficiently. Designed for professional HTML emails signed as &#39;Nate&#39;.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Oansl19GIzbE7vE5DEjivWN-nvqWZnMy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R182" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">183</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Financial News Summary Emailer</td><td class="s7">Automates daily extraction of top financial news from ft.com using HTTP request and CSS selectors, summarizes with Google Gemini AI, and emails a structured HTML recap via Microsoft Outlook. Ideal for investors seeking concise market updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1C_ziPqWJtZgadtFqVXXlMpf4vFrd74i7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R183" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">184</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chatbot with Long Term Memory &amp; Telegram</td><td class="s7">An AI chatbot workflow integrating OpenAI GPT models with long-term memory and note storage in Google Docs. It processes Telegram messages, retrieves and saves user memories and notes, and provides personalized, context-aware responses via Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kLinHUsdWcrfGQce3GmFot3xN0UzL6mJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R184" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">185</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Stripe Charges to HubSpot Contacts</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing of Stripe charge data with HubSpot contacts using Stripe API to fetch charges and customers, then updating/creating HubSpot contact fields with total spend via HubSpot API. Includes scheduling, deduplication, and field management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VCt2zZllJHRjRw7whhDA2MIwwii4mLwG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R185" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">186</div></th><td class="s6">URL &amp; IP Threat Intel Scan and Report</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating VirusTotal and Greynoise APIs to scan URLs and IPs for threat intelligence. It accepts URLs/IPs via webhook or form, performs DNS lookups, submits to VirusTotal for URL scanning, queries Greynoise for IP context, merges results, and sends detailed reports via Slack and email.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hb4fcOFPfYuohkoVdmUDTrq8BpI2F-Px">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R186" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">187</div></th><td class="s6">Google Maps Data Scraper with SERPAPI &amp; Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automate scraping of Google Maps data using SERPAPI API in n8n, processing results, removing duplicates, and updating a Google Sheets document with detailed place info like phone, website, ratings, and reviews. Includes scheduling and error handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18M46FtQPRAX7x3uFNwngtljIR4NwCZSY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R187" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">188</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Scoring and Outreach Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates lead collection via an n8n form, validates emails using Hunter API, scores leads with MadKudu, manages contacts in HubSpot, and sends personalized Gmail outreach emails. Integrates MadKudu, Hunter, HubSpot OAuth2, Gmail OAuth2, and n8n Form Trigger nodes to streamline lead qualification and engagement.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TIvKeMjJ9l7MaMicm2VeAptmQ8wI0IgW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R188" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">189</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Social Media Insights for Meetings</td><td class="s7">Daily fetches Google Calendar meetings, enriches attendees via Clearbit, retrieves LinkedIn and Twitter posts via RapidAPI, summarizes social activities using OpenAI GPT-4, and emails personalized summaries via Gmail. Tech: Google Calendar, Clearbit, RapidAPI LinkedIn &amp; Twitter APIs, OpenAI GPT-4, Gmail.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1b7jdrVfHf_iUw-xcEK51rPaaT699Hncu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R189" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">190</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Capture &amp; CRM Enrichment Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates lead capture via n8n Form Trigger, validates emails with Hunter.io, enriches lead data using Clearbit API, and manages contacts and organizations in Pipedrive CRM. Streamlines lead collection and data enrichment for sales pipelines.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1g33wbxM26UjZxxxLxLkLV0d5Aud9wJot">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R190" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">191</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce Order Support Chatbot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating WooCommerce API, DHL tracking, and OpenAI GPT-4 to provide secure, AI-driven customer service chat. Supports encrypted user email, order lookup, shipping status retrieval, and interactive chat embedding for WooCommerce stores.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=121qQ0Gvdpgrp5GHEaSrqi2k0nHBabQlN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R191" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">192</div></th><td class="s6">GitLab Merge Request AI Code Reviewer</td><td class="s7">Automates code review for GitLab merge requests by analyzing diffs and providing AI-generated feedback using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini. Integrates GitLab API, n8n workflow, and LangChain for automated, high-quality code review comments.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-BSX5gWmkFXlaeRX7KZ92fnv0Lr1RNSc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R192" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">193</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive PDF Auto Translator with DeepL</td><td class="s7">Automates translation of PDF documents in a specified Google Drive folder using the DeepL API. It downloads PDFs, sends them to DeepL for translation, polls for completion, and uploads translated PDFs back. Uses Google Drive OAuth2 and DeepL HTTP APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1y2L7jI63kKhVlsrp7Yc44LRR6YC1yvCh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R193" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">194</div></th><td class="s6">AI WordPress Post Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates creating SEO-friendly WordPress draft posts using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for article and chapter generation, Wikipedia for fact verification, and DALL-E for featured image creation in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Gmf2QBwi9RGvwz8Bf0v6T5Bqon_2gVyR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R194" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">195</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Email Reply Draft with OpenAI</td><td class="s7">Automates drafting email replies in Gmail by using OpenAI Assistant. It fetches emails with specific labels, sends message content to OpenAI, generates reply drafts, converts Markdown to HTML, creates RFC-compliant encoded drafts, and adds them back to Gmail threads. Utilizes Gmail API and OpenAI API within an n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uu8C8I_caj6D3hlz4FACTn5SkWl6iNPU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R195" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">196</div></th><td class="s6">Email Promo to Podcast Audio Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates conversion of Gmail CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS emails into concise audio podcasts. Uses Gmail API to fetch emails, OpenAI for text summarization, TikTok TTS API for speech synthesis, and Telegram API to send audio messages. Streamlines promo content consumption.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1m1HUDaOalmth_-nzAF1VDflYP6-705-W">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R196" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">197</div></th><td class="s6">Email Validation and CRM Lead Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates email verification via CaptainVerify API, creates leads in SuiteCRM with validated data, syncs contacts with Brevo, and sends notifications to NextCloud Discussions about lead creation, invalid emails, and low credits. Triggered by Tally Forms submissions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_UmjQ8P-eKgMeV6L8fG-Q6FeClmRyQyl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R197" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">198</div></th><td class="s6">AI Event Banner Generator with BannerBear</td><td class="s7">Automates creating event banners by capturing details via n8n form, generating images with OpenAI DALL·E 3, optimizing uploads on Cloudinary, designing banners using BannerBear templates, and posting to Discord channels. Uses n8n workflow for seamless event promotion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wjJWvlLFVfzzzXo3ENlO2EeQ_CDl1FEV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R198" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">199</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Company Data Enrichment Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates company research by leveraging OpenAI GPT-4, SerpAPI, and web scraping (ScrapingBee). It enriches Google Sheets rows with structured info like domain, LinkedIn URL, pricing, API availability, market type, and integrations, running on schedule or manual trigger.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EV2MoZvEuvtztysJDPPROl7bNyxvdyc-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R199" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">200</div></th><td class="s6">Slack to Google Calendar Event Automator</td><td class="s7">Automates event creation and attendee management by monitoring