s, extracting content from PDF/DOCX/TXT, summarizing and vectorizing using Mistral Cloud and Qdrant, then generates study guides, timelines, and briefing docs via AI agents.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kmD42T3fso-D624Nt_f298M1cPdKnxAf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R203" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">204</div></th><td class="s6">AI Competitor Research &amp; Report Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates competitor analysis by finding similar companies via Exa.ai, scraping Crunchbase, WellFound, LinkedIn, and review sites using Firecrawl and SerpAPI. Uses OpenAI GPT-4o for extracting structured company, product, and review data, and compiles detailed reports into Notion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Nje-3g2k6fPsxRxpaJbkGFSRjC4rS6CU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R204" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">205</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered PDF QA &amp; Appointment Scheduler</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that integrates OpenAI GPT-4, Anthropic, Pinecone vector store, and Google Calendar API to load PDFs, create embeddings, enable Q&amp;A over documents, categorize emails with AI, and book calendar appointments via chat-based interface.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LByZ4CuA6a78Oi66_KpGioZNfdlEYMm-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R205" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">206</div></th><td class="s6">Survey Response Insights Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates detailed insights generation from Google Sheets survey data by vectorizing responses with OpenAI embeddings, clustering with K-means in Qdrant vector store, and summarizing groups via GPT-4. Outputs enriched insights sheet with sentiment analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nWk5okVahx7-x1HieH1HzRMrZzhQqi97">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R206" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">207</div></th><td class="s6">Trustpilot Reviews Insight Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction, clustering, and summarization of Trustpilot reviews using n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4, Qdrant vector store, and K-means clustering for actionable customer insights. Outputs results to Google Sheets for analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kPBwKgqHC324BB1BTmWOEr5-R6E2FGzM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R207" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">208</div></th><td class="s6">IT Support Slack AI Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates IT support in Slack by integrating Slack Events API, OpenAI GPT-4o, and Confluence KB via n8n. It filters bot messages, acknowledges queries, uses AI with memory buffer, and fetches contextual info from Confluence for precise IT assistance.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZF9idj79Xr6KcXuzj_ONoIHBpdP2Crxb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R208" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">209</div></th><td class="s6">Notion AI Assistant Workflow Generator</td><td class="s7">Generates an n8n AI Agent workflow to query any Notion database using the provided URL. Utilizes Notion API, Langchain AI nodes (Anthropic and OpenAI), JSON validation, and chat triggers for interactive assistant creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12hEpr9lj5ObMFslsc7ct-5xaqHNmeiQS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R209" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">210</div></th><td class="s6">AI Image Caption Generator with Overlay</td><td class="s7">Automates generating descriptive captions for images using Google&#39;s Gemini AI model and overlays them on images with n8n&#39;s Edit Image node. Utilizes HTTP requests for image fetching, Langchain AI nodes for captioning, and code nodes for positioning text, enabling streamlined visual content creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AD3mIIU5n3f_U3C7aq_mrDZM34MRZ6Bq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R210" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">211</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Visual Regression Testing Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates website visual regression testing using Google Sheets for URLs, Apify for screenshots, Google Drive for storage, and Google Gemini AI Vision model for comparing changes. Results generate detailed reports in Linear.app.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1scYnINOdkEuUg1XzCZrV2NJG8yBPAUjQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R211" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">212</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Podcast Summary Email Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval of top US podcasts by genre from Taddy API, crops audio via Aspose API, transcribes with OpenAI Whisper, summarizes using GPT-4o-mini, and emails summaries via Gmail for easy daily podcast insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MH4SLL_zTRd74IwmV4LJsUXEi9tAUCbB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R212" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">213</div></th><td class="s6">AI Calendar &amp; Notion Task Manager</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4, Google Calendar, and Notion APIs to automate scheduling events and managing tasks. It uses LangChain agents, chat triggers, and memory buffers to route user chat inputs to appropriate tools for calendar and task operations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SJrmE5CFz_DLyzElzF3ttTXtZvwjJV7W">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R213" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">214</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Telegram Bot with Memory</td><td class="s7">Automates Telegram conversations using OpenAI assistant with context memory via Supabase. Integrates Telegram Bot API, OpenAI Threads &amp; Assistants API, and Supabase database for user session tracking, enabling personalized, context-aware chatbot replies.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_YD077L52USpNwTsmhIyOKSckO0l01yl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R214" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">215</div></th><td class="s6">AI Personal Assistant via Telegram</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered Telegram assistant integrating OpenAI GPT-4o, Google Calendar, Gmail, and Baserow APIs for voice/text input processing, event and email summarization, task and contact management, enhancing productivity via conversational interface.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CIpRARMtuek69uW1-BGWPokBU6chlDU3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R215" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">216</div></th><td class="s6">Slack-ServiceNow Incident Lookup</td><td class="s7">Automates incident retrieval from ServiceNow via Slack slash command using n8n workflow. Integrates Slack Webhook, ServiceNow API (Basic Auth), and conditional responses in Slack blocks, enabling seamless incident details inquiry and notifications directly in Slack channels.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XxhbT1N0CQ7uuCaKA7yXw6w2s2qXU-zE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R216" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">217</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail AI Auto Labeling Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Gmail API and OpenAI GPT to automatically read, categorize, and label incoming Gmail messages. It polls Gmail every 5 minutes, analyzes emails using OpenAI, matches or creates Gmail labels accordingly, and assigns labels, optimizing inbox organization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HfdX3b0LVqYGwPp0e9oIrRvxQmlMVPtj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R217" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">218</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Metadata Auto Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates YouTube metadata creation using n8n, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, Google Docs API, and YouTube API. Generates SEO-optimized video titles, descriptions, tags, hashtags, affiliate and promo links for enhanced audience engagement and channel growth.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dP4onUOLbo8iRhHybnIWeir2XfjtrNAh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R218" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">219</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered JIRA Stale Issue Auto-Assignment</td><td class="s7">Automates assignment of stale JIRA issues using OpenAI embeddings and Langchain. Utilizes Supabase vector database to find similar resolved issues and identifies best suited team members by workload, auto-assigning and commenting in JIRA to keep backlog manageable.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ARx_piG4h1XP-7yEUbbCLS0UIgL0Fpbe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R219" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">220</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice Extraction from Outlook Emails</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of invoice data from Outlook emails using Microsoft Outlook API and Google Gemini 2.0 for AI-based document classification and OCR. Extracted invoice details are saved to Microsoft Excel, streamlining accounts receivable processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mgn9eQT1ePBI4ul6sC3--FI2HXthEDaz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R220" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">221</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Personalized Sales Email Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates personalized sales email drafting using HubSpot CRM data, Gmail email correspondence, and Google Gemini AI models. It analyzes customer emails to build detailed personas, then crafts tailored outreach emails saved as Gmail drafts for review.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1O99oo4FdiQM6PvQgJP0cgLT-mwIvW-KQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R221" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">222</div></th><td class="s6">Voice AI Appointment Scheduler with Google &amp; Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates appointment booking, rescheduling, and cancellation via a voice AI receptionist using Vapi, Google Calendar, and Airtable. Includes availability checks, event management, and logging call recordings and details for HVAC service scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UybDCD91x4RpGp2C1CZxwcHYL38JGNlD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R222" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">223</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Outlook Calendar Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automate Outlook calendar management via Slack with an AI agent using OpenAI for natural language understanding and Microsoft Outlook API for calendar event search, creation, and retrieval. Enables conversational calendar assistance and event handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OlfxPasEFhlwSMCOeAAXaILQT6DEPh_k">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R223" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">224</div></th><td class="s6">Instagram Auto Posting via Google Drive &amp; AI</td><td class="s7">Automates Instagram Reel posting using Google Drive triggers, OpenAI for generating 