<td class="s7">Automates daily auditing of recently modified Google Drive documents using Google Drive API, Google Sheets for reporting, and Gmail for sending alerts. Identifies files shared publicly or with external users, logs details in a new Google Sheet, and emails a summary report for improved access control.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1h_AwmYjj4orn9vhmYgiEVBAESAzF8dwT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R227" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">228</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Profile Enrichment &amp; Ice Breaker Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates LinkedIn profile enrichment using Bright Data API, generates personalized ice breakers with Anthropic Claude LLM, and updates results in Google Sheets. Uses n8n nodes like HTTP Request, Google Sheets, LangChain LLM, scheduled/manual triggers for seamless workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HneMewkqysR8Chxif5Q3OrH45D7jT66g">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R228" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">229</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Job Scraper to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping of live LinkedIn job posts using Bright Data Dataset API. Cleans and flattens job data, then appends it to Google Sheets for easy use in job hunting or sales prospecting. Tech stack: Bright Data API, Google Sheets API, n8n nodes (Form, HTTP Request, Code, Wait, If).</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1W5QZscpaWk6oYzaDJBBf8qAEnZs8XEVj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R229" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">230</div></th><td class="s6">Monthly Financial Performance Report Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates monthly financial reporting by querying MySQL ERP data, analyzing budgets vs actuals, projects, employees, and departments. Uses Google Gemini AI and Langchain tools for advanced financial analysis and generates styled HTML reports sent via Microsoft Outlook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19pKa-P8-cPrCzf0l2ojXz2wrsQ-fQG8u">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R230" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">231</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram-AI Task Manager with Google Tasks</td><td class="s7">Automates task management via Telegram using AI to interpret messages and voice notes. Integrates Telegram Bot API, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for NLP and transcription, LangChain MCP for AI orchestration, and Google Tasks API for task creation and updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AZHC2m1myUXop27S11d1-JIuo9C1cCXT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R231" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">232</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Gmail Email Organizer via Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates Gmail inbox management by retrieving emails, filtering processed emails, and using OpenRouter GPT-4.1 AI to categorize each email as necessary or unnecessary. Archives unneeded emails, applies labels to others, and reports results via Telegram. Integrates Gmail API, Telegram Bot API, and OpenRouter GPT-4.1.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gfa1EwbqXUdqR1cxHFMBwNge8ulU_S-E">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R232" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">233</div></th><td class="s6">Client Feedback Routing &amp; HubSpot Logging</td><td class="s7">Automates client conversation processing with OpenAI summarization, routes feedback to departments via email, and logs meeting notes in HubSpot using OAuth2. Uses n8n, Langchain, Gmail API, and HubSpot API to streamline client issue management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1A87nQqo3pMeAUHgHgc-tYAhiu55WGgfA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R233" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">234</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Email Parsing &amp; HubSpot CRM Update</td><td class="s7">Workflow automates email parsing using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini model, extracts contact info, searches/updates contacts in HubSpot CRM, and creates email engagement records. Integrates IMAP email, HubSpot OAuth2 API, and LangChain AI nodes for seamless CRM enrichment.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bwRD7KRhC-4vtkbajsn2OWlsw5T5Y0U-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R234" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">235</div></th><td class="s6">MCP Server for Managing &amp; Executing n8n Workflows</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow serving as an MCP server to dynamically manage, list, add, remove, and execute tagged workflows. Uses Redis for memory, n8n API to fetch workflows, and integrates OpenAI GPT-4.1-mini model via Langchain to act as an AI agent that interacts with workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eke8Sh2erVDdb7ekEys0GJLNFz1Zo2X4">Download</a>