.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_Bja3WH5X8prsF_cZjADSn_MQwePwmfS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R238" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">239</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Instagram Content Creator with AI &amp; Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates Instagram post creation by generating unique content concepts, detailed AI image prompts, and captions using Google Gemini LLM, with image generation on Replicate Flux, managing ideas from Google Sheets and publishing through Instagram Graph API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MznupNAbaFkmd1k8_gNhZnnEIF19mXpu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R239" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">240</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered JIRA Support Ticket Triage &amp; Resolution</td><td class="s7">Automates triaging and resolution of JIRA support tickets using scheduled triggers, JIRA API, and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for labeling, prioritizing, rewriting, and suggesting fixes by analyzing new and past resolved tickets with comments.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14W0IQAexDBTLWIv3m9Yz1XYVFRFlS-Z_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R240" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">241</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Support Ticket Creation from Gmail to Linear</td><td class="s7">Workflow automates fetching Gmail support emails, removes duplicates, converts HTML to Markdown, uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to triage and label tickets, then creates issues in Linear.app. Tech stack: Gmail API, OpenAI API, Linear API, n8n automation platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17q3sJJXpHRsIn72TDrKdomrvw0fUQ8_d">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R241" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">242</div></th><td class="s6">Automated HubSpot Onboarding &amp; Calendar Scheduler</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating new customer onboarding using HubSpot CRM, OpenAI GPT-4 for personalized welcome emails, and Google Calendar for scheduling calls. Integrates HubSpot API, Gmail, and Langchain for AI-powered calendar management and email generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15VMC4VvMf4Vm4Hd-qFH9YVlUJ7v-NY_Z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R242" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">243</div></th><td class="s6">MS Teams Weekly AI Team Activity Report</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly summaries of individual and team activities on Microsoft Teams using OpenAI GPT-4.1 LLM. Fetches last week&#39;s channel messages, groups by user, generates personalized and team reports, converts markdown to HTML, and posts back to Teams channel every Monday morning.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gzgkjIkmmeratMvdq8QW7DVYPkIU6ayk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R243" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">244</div></th><td class="s6">Raw Material Inventory &amp; Approval Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating raw material receipt, stock updates, issue requests, and approvals. Integrates webhooks, Google Sheets, Supabase DB, and Gmail to streamline inventory management and send low stock alerts with email notifications.</td><t