nk" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1G4ZMHZf9IBKWgrFBj-aWb2rJBkbTHx8f">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R250" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">251</div></th><td class="s6">AI Exam Question Generator from Google Docs</td><td class="s7">Automates creating open and multiple-choice exam questions from Google Docs content using OpenAI embeddings, Google Gemini LLM, and Qdrant vector database for retrieval-augmented generation and question-answering.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1G2O4_EHsfUtBKaECburzEjkFBYGGcehY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R251" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">252</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Leads Scraper &amp; Enrichment Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates LinkedIn lead generation and enrichment using Apollo.io API for lead data, OpenAI GPT-3.5 for username extraction and profile/post summaries, RapidAPI LinkedIn &amp; Apify for profile/posts scraping, and Google Sheets for storage and workflow triggers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u4Rf5kGZl3P-sqEfSz36hNwpOpBgo2BL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R252" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">253</div></th><td class="s6">API Schema Crawler, Extractor &amp; Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates researching, scraping, extracting, and generating API schemas from service websites using Google Search API, Apify web scraping, Google Gemini LLM, Qdrant vector DB, Google Sheets and Drive integration for managing and storing API documentation data and custom schemas.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1drcclGNNZ_7zRMdKbUgQm-iB4q-2IjHp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R253" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">254</div></th><td class="s6">AI Outlook Email Auto Categorizer</td><td class="s7">Automates categorization of Microsoft Outlook emails using n8n workflows integrated with Ollama&#39;s qwen2.5 AI model. Cleans email content, classifies into categories (action, junk, receipt, SaaS, community, business), updates Outlook labels and moves emails accordingly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ed4PX5vnJmGCsMftnm9wmLJdJWI1xRkg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R254" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">255</div></th><td class="s6">AI Brand Voice Content Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of on-brand blog articles by analyzing existing content from n8n.io blog. Uses n8n nodes with OpenAI API for LLM analysis, HTML extraction, Markdown conversion, and Wordpress draft publishing. Captures article style, structure, and voice.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Fu7QK4CRu6dIoG0uKcXyrlzMXCmOZfX8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R255" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">256</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress SEO Content Automation with DeepSeek &amp; DALL-E</td><td class="s7">Automates blog content creation for WordPress using DeepSeek R1 AI for SEO-friendly articles, OpenAI DALL-E 3 for cover images, and Google Sheets for idea input. Integrates WordPress API to publish drafts and update editorial plans seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17XcRSWhOiFzwDGDagCNu-VWpcrhv6IGL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R256" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">257</div></th><td class="s6">Auto-Resolve Long-Lived Jira Issues with AI</td><td class="s7">Automates detection, classification, and resolution of long-lived Jira issues using n8n workflows integrated with OpenAI GPT-4, Jira API, Notion, and Slack. Supports sentiment analysis, AI-driven knowledgebase search, and team notifications to improve customer support efficiency.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wJyhT-WcEDf18mWJ2FGbZMPzHhFY0uDX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R257" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">258</div></th><td class="s6">Pinterest AI Analysis &amp; Content Suggestion Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates Pinterest pin data collection via Pinterest API, stores data in Airtable, and leverages OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini AI models for trend analysis and content suggestions. Sends summarized marketing insights via Gmail, aiding content calendar planning and audience targeting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Bs2cA0DcaMyC9EtdVw0FOcp5EoDUU1LL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R258" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">259</div></th><td class="s6">AI Pre-Meeting Assistant with Gmail, Google Calendar, LinkedIn</td><td class="s7">Automates pre-meeting notifications by checking Google Calendar for upcoming events, extracting attendee info, summarizing recent emails (via Gmail) and LinkedIn activity (via Apify scraper), then sending concise, AI-generated WhatsApp reminders using OpenAI GPT models.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1p2fZdASmKw1gcbMJhd7_iPWQONfB6bx2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R259" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">260</div></th><td class="s6">Cybersecurity Ticket Enrichment with MITRE &amp; AI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that enriches Zendesk tickets using MITRE ATT&amp;CK data by embedding it into a Qdrant vector store and querying with OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4 and embeddings. It automates extraction of TTPs, remediation steps, and historical context from SIEM alerts using LangChain agents and structured parsers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ev-ZThhkEP3MeaE4FjvHBzA_xgDfs3RK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R260" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">261</div></th><td class="s6">Automated RFP Response Generator</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates RFP processing by extracting questions from PDF RFP documents using LLMs, generating answers via OpenAI Assistants enriched with company data, and compiling responses into Google Docs. Notifications are sent via Gmail and Slack upon completion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1q1xox_uXrEaYZGtTjyvBkn1UlNOn2mgk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R261" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">262</div></th><td class="s6">Local File AI Sync &amp; Q&amp;A with Qdrant &amp; Mistral</td><td class="s7">Automates local folder monitoring and syncs file data as vector embeddings to Qdrant vector database. Uses Mistral Cloud AI for embeddings and chat model, enabling AI Q&amp;A on updated files. Stack: n8n, Local File Trigger, Qdrant API, Mistral Cloud, Langchain nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Va05a7ASxaDA_jN67rknCImxdaW3k8nv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R262" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">263</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Quote Video Creator with PiAPI &amp; ElevenLabs</td><td class="s7">Automates creating cinematic vertical videos with quotes. Uses Google Sheets for input, PiAPI for AI image &amp; video generation, ElevenLabs for ambient audio, FFmpeg for video merging, and uploads final clips to YouTube.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10ulSwaVilw92xdykd0LgFs-yg5d4fpf6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R263" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">264</div></th><td class="s6">Automated 9:16 AI Image &amp; Video Content Creator</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates creating 9:16 aspect ratio short-form video scripts and AI-generated images using Airtable for content management, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for script generation, and Leonardo.ai for prompt improvement and image generation. Perfect for branding and social media content production.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12P0_10W1ujlcNQ5q2IaW2rsDgk9cUl8z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R264" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">265</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Driven Instagram Trend Content Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates Instagram content creation by scraping top trending posts with RapidAPI, analyzing images with OpenAI GPT-4 Vision, generating unique AI images via Replicate Flux AI, and posting with Facebook Graph API. Sends Telegram notifications on status updates. Ideal for creators leveraging AI for engaging posts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15i_d0-wWq6Hmlu0Z8XXOYGz0Th2YrL5i">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R265" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">266</div></th><td class="s6">AI SQL Query Generator from DB Schema</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using MySQL, OpenAI GPT-4o, and LangChain to convert database schema into executable SQL queries via AI chat. It extracts schema from MySQL, stores locally, then generates SQL on chat input, executing queries and returning results seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wmtHHn-yz9j4VUwj5WlHRCGSK5nrU2iA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R266" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">267</div></th><td class="s6">AutoClip: Auto Video Clip Creator &amp; YouTube Uploader</td><td class="s7">Automates creating motivational video clips by combining random quotes, video backgrounds, and music stored on Google Drive and Sheets. Uses n8n with Google Drive, Google Sheets, FFmpeg for video processing, and YouTube API for upload. Perfect for creators automating content production.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17WzN7D5eW8E0PkWf_SeFstpHqcdddpZF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R267" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">268</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chatbot for YouTube Video Summarization</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered n8n workflow that fetches YouTube video details and transcripts via YouTube Data API &amp; youtube-transcript package, then uses OpenAI GPT models for interactive summarization and analysis of video content through chat.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZUNZNC2P0Jw5wj7yKUNRP9A6_RYvhfdD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R268" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">269</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Company AI Scoring &amp; CRM Update</td><td class="s7">Automates LinkedIn company search via Ghost Genius API, scores leads with OpenAI GPT-4.1 AI based on customized criteria, and updates a Google Sheets CRM. Ideal for targeted B2B lead enrichment and qualification with batch processing and deduplication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ivg8JMrjqCk6TuvYOiKbnRSRX9FiWu4w">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R269" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">270</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Weekly Reddit Trend PR Report</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly discovery of trending Reddit posts on chosen topics. Extracts top comments, performs sentiment and content analysis with Anthropic Claude AI, enriches with article content via Jina API, then generates and uploads comprehensive PR story reports to Google Drive and shares via Mattermost. Tech stack: Reddit API, Anthropic Claude, Jina AI, Google Drive, Mattermost webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jszhkC_ub6a5moyznQZIlvf_voV69BQo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R270" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">271</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Instagram Trend Content Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates Instagram content creation by scraping top trending posts via RapidAPI Instagram Scraper, filtering images, analyzing with OpenAI GPT-4 Vision, generating captions, creating images using Replicate Flux AI, and publishing via Facebook Graph API with Telegram notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1z4J5B7mYlqOeSYEOegrdnh8Jb0PE7ddw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R271" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">272</div></th><td class="s6">Hacker News AI Video Content Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates creating AI-generated video summaries from Hacker News articles using OpenAI for analysis, Leonardo.ai for images, RunwayML and Creatomate for video creation, with uploads to cloud storage and posting on social media platforms.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XHW-HspmyVYXfXv5pKHKmp5GFKCTxPTL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R272" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">273</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered SMS Appointment Scheduler</td><td class="s7">Automates PC/laptop repair appointment scheduling via SMS using Twilio, Airtable, OpenAI&#39;s GPT, and Cal.com API. Manages sessions, handles booking actions (create/reschedule/cancel), and sends follow-ups with STOP opt-out support.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ctveg4KYo-zyK6UMonXbGFG3eSbXHZPs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R273" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">274</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Job Application with CV Parsing</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates job applications by processing PDF CV uploads via form triggers, classifying documents with OpenAI, extracting relevant data using LLMs contextualized by job posts, and storing details including PDF in Airtable ATS. Includes multi-step user form with AI-assisted pre-fill.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bU3tFM07N3aLN2_R4SXlsH2YwaRhcwJC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R274" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">275</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Multi-Format Chatbot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates a Telegram chatbot using OpenAI GPT-4o for conversational AI with memory buffer. It handles text and voice messages, transcribes audio with OpenAI API, and responds dynamically via Telegram API, enabling rich multi-format AI conversations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15J72V9SFb4YN10teT3ppOPJpljsm8uWA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R275" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">276</div></th><td class="s6">Gemini AI Video Content Analyzer</td><td class="s7">Automate video analysis using Google&#39;s Gemini 2.0 API in an n8n workflow. Downloads video from URL, uploads it to Gemini cloud for AI-based detailed visual description generation, useful for marketing, content moderation, accessibility, and cataloging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sPsBgEag5ljqY7AVeS2quYx-e_o1VnZf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R276" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">277</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Lead Tracking &amp; Notification System</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates lead tracking by integrating Google Sheets, HubSpot CRM, Slack, and Gmail. It triggers on new Google Sheets entries, logs leads into HubSpot, sends alerts via Slack and Gmail, and includes follow-up reminders for hot leads to improve sales efficiency.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1p24BaM3NJu6U3Ve6xSjiC11m0tKNfz-G">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R277" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">278</div></th><td class="s6">HR &amp; IT Helpdesk Chatbot with Audio Transcription</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that builds an AI-powered HR &amp; IT helpdesk chatbot using OpenAI GPT for text and audio transcription, Telegram for messaging, PostgreSQL with PGVector for vector storage, and LangChain tools for knowledge retrieval and chat memory.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eQo-jASygYzBDsYL70bMUvV9aaLvKIkh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R278" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">279</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered HR Job Application &amp; Interview Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates job application intake, CV storage, AI-driven candidate scoring, questionnaire generation, interview scheduling, and communication using n8n, Airtable, Google Drive, Google Calendar, and OpenAI GPT models.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tZPj-WBI6CPdcqgoA6QOCAQyzEfkXeFu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R279" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">280</div></th><td class="s6">Voice RAG Chatbot with ElevenLabs &amp; OpenAI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating ElevenLabs voice agent, OpenAI GPT language model, Qdrant vector store, and Google Drive for Document Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG). Automates voice Q&amp;A using AI embeddings, vector search, and real-time audio responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uBflRU8n_fqYxB4MVIigUM64g9NztrXO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R280" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">281</div></th><td class="s6">CrowdStrike Detection to Jira &amp; Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates cybersecurity alert handling by fetching new CrowdStrike detections, enriching them via VirusTotal API, creating Jira tickets, and notifying teams on Slack. Built with n8n featuring CrowdStrike, VirusTotal, Jira, and Slack integrations for streamlined incident management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10QGM9ciFWmEqxOFucSrolMmsihicWnsY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R281" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">282</div></th><td class="s6">Semantic Web Search Query &amp; Results Re-Ranker</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates intelligent web search query generation and semantic re-ranking of results using Brave Web Search API and advanced language models (Google Gemini, Anthropic Claude, OpenAI GPT). It refines user questions, ranks top search results, and extracts key info for precise answers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18QaU76FVuE1-qgdH0A5Fup-hokj4yoT9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R282" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">283</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice Data Extraction &amp; Reconciliation</td><td class="s7">Automates invoice processing by watching Gmail for PDF invoices, uploading them to LlamaParse API for parsing, extracting structured invoice data using OpenAI GPT-3.5, and appending results to Google Sheets for reconciliation. Incorporates label management to avoid duplicate processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nhBDlMWlY2iNmX8wrwfs-omkw_zg6IL1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R283" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">284</div></th><td class="s6">Slack IT Support AI Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Slack API, OpenAI GPT-4, and Confluence API to automate IT support queries via Slack. It verifies webhooks, filters bot messages, acknowledges user queries, fetches knowledge base results, and uses AI to generate tailored IT responses, improving IT helpdesk efficiency.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KTGhy5D06fvbwrZBobL_GTWiZFi6uas6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R284" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">285</div></th><td class="s6">AI WhatsApp Customer Support Assistant</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered customer support chatbot for WhatsApp that dynamically crawls and extracts real-time website info using Langchain tools (list_links, get_page), OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and Postgres memory. Enables brands to deliver on-demand, accurate support directly on WhatsApp.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Lt0WLfDpum6ikQOmaceF57yMef_pBIP2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R285" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">286</div></th><td class="s6">Zoom AI Meeting Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automates Zoom meeting transcription processing to create summaries, action items, and schedule follow-ups using Zoom API, Anthropic Claude AI, ClickUp, and Microsoft Outlook integrations with n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1StzVSJQgpyWq66YJ_jkm1YnWmJGH_KPj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R286" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">287</div></th><td class="s6">Notion RAG Chatbot with OpenAI &amp; Supabase</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that enables retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) from live Notion data. It uses Notion API to fetch updated content, OpenAI GPT-4 for embeddings and chat models, and Supabase as a vector store to index knowledge base for context-aware Q&amp;A chatbot.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17Y8JenblAb1DBWcP8no1-LNcgeoG87ng">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R287" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">288</div></th><td class="s6">GitLab Merge Request Auto Review &amp; Risk Assessment</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating GitLab MR review by fetching diffs, using Anthropic Claude AI for risk assessment, issues, recommendations, and test case generation, then posting comments and emailing relevant dev &amp; QA teams. Integrates GitLab API, Anthropic AI, and Gmail.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fZvJtItRhUKjMc5MnDz0KWu8OYbvbrqZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R288" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">289</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Summarizer &amp; Telegram Q&amp;A with GPT-4o-mini</td><td class="s7">Automates extracting YouTube video transcripts, segmenting and summarizing them using GPT-4o-mini, storing transcripts on Google Docs, and enabling interactive Q&amp;A about the video via Telegram chat. Uses n8n with YouTube Transcript API, Google Docs API, Telegram API, and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1x8I3HPS45b9KwvwN_ESlb0EE_cq-bZnK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R289" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">290</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Personal Assistant with Google APIs</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Google Gemini Chat AI, Google Calendar, Gmail, and Google Sheets to create an AI personal assistant. It manages calendar events, emails, contacts in Sheets, and supports conversational interactions via an MCP server and client setup.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aguVE460N02Zhdfe77JjBK5Z3yYw1qU2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R290" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">291</div></th><td class="s6">AI Invoice &amp; Document Parser with LlamaParse</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction, classification, and summarization of documents from Gmail using LlamaParse API, OpenAI GPT models, and Google Drive/Sheets. Extracts invoice details as JSON, saves files, sends Telegram notifications, and organizes data for streamlined accounting and insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NWR8uK5cnzN1sV2CdtxTdzmAk3CZqBok">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R291" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">292</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Online Marketing Report Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly retrieval, analysis, and reporting of online marketing data using Google Analytics, Google Ads API, Meta Ads (Facebook Graph API), and OpenAI GPT-4 for AI-powered insights and summaries. Sends detailed HTML email and Telegram report.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15grtqRC9Xml-vZaqZiZ3_oukIA6k2xD_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R292" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">293</div></th><td class="s6">AI Job Hunt POV Video Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of short-form job hunting videos using OpenAI for captions &amp; scripts, PiAPI Flux for image generation, Kling for video, ElevenLabs for voiceovers, Creatomate for final rendering, Google Sheets for ideas, and uploads to TikTok, Instagram, YouTube, Facebook, LinkedIn via upload-post.com.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OREZAwWmWaVbWl1LwdcFkSWAJ2Sc4Vtz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R293" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">294</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Ultimate Selenium Web Scraper</td><td class="s7">Automates advanced web scraping with Selenium and OpenAI GPT-4 integration. Uses Selenium Chrome container, residential proxies, Google search, cookie injection for session-based scraping, and AI-driven info extraction from screenshots and text for data on dynamic or login-protected websites.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Lz1Qup3QBtrZB8oMD1_vcuW7ztU4IugU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R294" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">295</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Analysis with Google Gemini AI</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that analyzes YouTube videos using Google Generative Language API (Gemini-1.5-flash) to create summaries, transcripts, timestamps, scene descriptions, and viral clip suggestions. It fetches video metadata via YouTube API and stores outputs in Google Drive and email.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VK2EBfclDag7y6KpBUukQgHMCc5MR1fm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R295" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">296</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Document Chatbot with Supabase &amp; Gemini</td><td class="s7">No-code Telegram bot using n8n that lets users upload PDFs, extracts text, creates embeddings with Google Gemini, stores them in Supabase vector DB, and answers document-based queries. Integrates Telegram API, Google Gemini LLM, Supabase, and optionally OpenWeatherMap.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yhvglRDge5sW23dsvVj1K4h-zvNIRtbp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R296" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">297</div></th><td class="s6">Daily AI Email Summary and Action Extractor</td><td class="s7">Automates daily email retrieval from Gmail, uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to summarize key email info and extract action items, then emails a styled HTML report. Tech stack: Gmail API, OpenAI API, n8n workflow automation, with scheduling and aggregation nodes. Ideal for teams needing concise daily email digests.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14dTvRBqb-Rv_bIeipM5c_e24kew9dYwP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R297" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">298</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered WordPress Blog Post Optimizer</td><td class="s7">Automates WordPress blog content creation and SEO optimization using Google Sheets, OpenAI (DeepSeek), WordPress API, and Langchain. Generates titles, articles, images, drafts posts, and SEO meta tags, updating all data back to Google Sheets seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FJkvh_3BpMo08OMVlKus_23oAxiAus-T">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R298" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">299</div></th><td class="s6">CoinMarketCap AI Crypto Analyst Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n AI workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o Mini with CoinMarketCap APIs via modular agents for real-time crypto market analytics, token data, exchange insights, and decentralized DEX liquidity. Outputs interactive replies through Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sgGN2ukK8W5YEgUh6yrAqjEYRSdp5p25">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R299" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">300</div></th><td class="s6 softmerge"><div class="softmerge-inner" style="width:417px;left:-1px">Animated Story Creation with GPT-4o-mini, Midjourney, Kling &amp; Creatomate</div></td><td class="s7">Automates creation of animated story videos using GPT-4o-mini for story prompts, Midjourney for images, Kling for video generation, and Creatomate for final video editing. Ideal for generating engaging animated content from text prompts via APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wLLQtIFiMoEGYIBPIkZzAhF1h1y-M50L">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R300" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">301</div></th><td class="s6">Outlook AI Email Categorizer &amp; Prioritizer</td><td class="s7">Automates email categorization and prioritization in Microsoft Outlook. Integrates Microsoft 365, Monday.com CRM, Airtable, and OpenAI GPT-4 AI to analyze, categorize, and set priorities on incoming emails based on custom rules and contact data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jAfOt8wa_qCIm5tlqm8yjkHSVablbfVf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R301" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">302</div></th><td class="s6">Voiceflow Chatbot &amp; Calendar Integrator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Voiceflow conversational agents with Google Calendar and Qdrant RAG system. Uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for LLM tasks, Qdrant for vector search, Google Drive for document handling, and webhooks for multi-channel chatbot, appointment, and order tracking automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hZKzIEB0b_KSfOv6JU6JqDI07GbXKHHO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R302" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">303</div></th><td class="s6">Monthly Spotify Track Archiving &amp; AI Playlist Classifier</td><td class="s7">Automate monthly archiving of Spotify liked tracks and playlists into Google Sheets, then use Anthropic Claude 3.5 AI to classify tracks into playlists. Utilizes Spotify API, Google Sheets, and Anthropic AI for advanced music management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nJIOj72BwTQLFSUHnD-S4WyECXvYXLul">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R303" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">304</div></th><td class="s6">Video Frame Extraction and AI Narration</td><td class="s7">Automates video downloading, frame extraction using OpenCV, script generation with GPT-4 multimodal LLM, and text-to-speech audio creation via OpenAI API. The workflow batches image frames, creates narration scripts, synthesizes voiceovers, and uploads results to Google Drive.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_R_k9xGuJcDQ1X9a7dtUFAnD_4TgToZG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R304" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">305</div></th><td class="s6">AI SEO Keyword Research Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates SEO keyword research using OpenAI GPT for topic expansion and competitor analysis, integrates DataForSEO API for keyword metrics, and manages workflow with NocoDB and Slack notifications. Generates actionable SEO strategies and content briefs for targeted content creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10NDnIkKQVhWKwzf0yc7KCgKlBzCkz1_H">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R305" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">306</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Weekly Tech Newsletter</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching tech news from multiple RSS feeds, processes with OpenAI embeddings and GPT-4 summarization, and sends a personalized weekly newsletter via Gmail. Uses n8n, OpenAI API, RSS feeds, and Gmail integration to deliver curated tech updates based on user interests.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18kj6f0FKRdmliMlNQoaTrgapBy13E37g">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R306" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">307</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Email Summarization &amp; Reply Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating IMAP email triggers, Gmail, OpenAI GPT models, and Qdrant vector DB to summarize incoming emails, generate context-aware professional replies, classify human feedback, and send emails after review. Supports Gmail, Outlook, Google Drive docs, and uses LangChain components for advanced AI processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iixnrkoTuhKbJXUS7xzs1QIyp_SSihYm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R307" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">308</div></th><td class="s6">WhatsApp AI Chatbot with RAG Knowledge Base</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating WhatsApp Business API, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, Langchain agent, Qdrant vector DB, and Google Drive to build an AI-powered chatbot for electronics stores. It uses a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system to provide accurate product info &amp; support via WhatsApp.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14AQ1r8bL_kUgFGqbY-lmbaHax3hhzuh2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R308" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">309</div></th><td class="s6">Notion DB AI Assistant Generator</td><td class="s7">Generates an n8n AI Agent workflow to query any Notion database using URLs. Utilizes Notion API, Anthropic and OpenAI language models, LangChain agents, and advanced JSON validation. Automates creating custom AI chatbots for dynamic Notion DB schemas.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13ZEpIYxgdgX0-R8Okx90S4gKAriqdpPX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R309" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">310</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Daily n8n Workflow Backups to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates daily backup of n8n workflows by fetching workflow JSON via n8n API, saving to timestamped Google Drive folders using Google Drive API, retains only last 7 days backups with auto-deletion, and sends completion notifications via Telegram API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AyprKKV5yAv-wKe3h6mNV_y6m-CavXAe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R310" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">311</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress Content Chatbot with OpenAI &amp; Supabase</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating WordPress API, OpenAI embeddings &amp; GPT-4o-mini, and Supabase vector DB. It fetches, filters, converts WP posts/pages to markdown, embeddings for search, and enables AI chat with website content using stored vectors and Postgres memory.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RrdS1QDqLicZdzlYiL_2JCe9pACjFd_8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R311" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">312</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce AI Chatbot for Post-Sales Support</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered chatbot workflow integrating WooCommerce, OpenAI, Qdrant vector DB, and Google Drive for secure, verified post-sales support. It automates order and tracking inquiries, FAQ answers, and escalates complex issues via Telegram for a seamless customer service experience.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14sNWkQyGOy4_BpEwM-ctXnvVG3swVpj2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R312" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">313</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Autonomous Research Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating deep research by generating multiple search queries with LLMs, fetching data via SerpAPI and Jina AI, extracting relevant info, and compiling comprehensive markdown reports. Integrates OpenRouter LLM, SerpAPI, Jina AI, and Wikipedia.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1F8hVXmAlyLhgF_1I5XJYm6L_Y4jO92B7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R313" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">314</div></th><td class="s6">AI Email Auto-Responder with Approval Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates email processing by reading IMAP messages, converting to Markdown, summarizing content, retrieving data from Qdrant vector DB, composing replies with OpenAI GPT and DeepSeek models, and sends responses after a YES/NO approval via Gmail. Tech: IMAP, Qdrant, OpenAI, DeepSeek, Gmail API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=166r28OalhbFoeXe3tMn4RZ7LqyI7Py-C">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R314" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">315</div></th><td class="s6">AI SQL Query Generator from Database Schema</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses MySQL to extract database schemas, stores them locally, and combines with OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o via LangChain AI Agent to generate SQL queries based only on the schema and user chat input. It automates SQL generation without executing queries directly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ad-ku5dMksj-zGqkONfOZwHqk6zwxZl3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R315" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">316</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress Automated SEO Content &amp; Image Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates SEO-friendly WordPress blog posts creation using Google Sheets for ideas, DeepSeek AI for article and title generation, OpenAI DALL-E 3 for cover images, and WordPress API for publishing and media uploading. Ideal for blog content managers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XkCbFIhnMBArMBh0vIgXnNqaLvLcESY2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R316" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">317</div></th><td class="s6">AI Agent with Long-Term Memory &amp; Tools Router</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Google Docs for AI agent long-term memory storage and retrieval. It dynamically routes tasks like saving memories, retrieving them, and sending notifications via Gmail and Telegram to enhance AI chatbot contextual understanding and multi-channel communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1t0zH3uISdmxbUDfw4YP3wco-IgDTmzKP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R317" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">318</div></th><td class="s6">Parents Smart Assistant Bot</td><td class="s7">An intelligent personal assistant for busy parents using Telegram, OpenAI (GPT-3.5, embeddings, audio transcription), Qdrant vector DB, Tavily web search, and Wikipedia API. It routes requests to specialized agents for calendar, email, contacts, content creation, and calculations, responding warmly in Hebrew.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yxgP0stqaHoFCQx16XLRL5aJghitRMoF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R318" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">319</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Lead Automation &amp; Enrichment</td><td class="s7">Automates LinkedIn lead generation, data enrichment, and outreach using HDW LinkedIn API, OpenAI GPT-4 for ICP parsing and content summarization, and Google Sheets for data storage. Includes lead scoring, company research, and automated messaging workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1C_KqEMGnCHI9IEU7etsJYoxKRzByi5QI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R319" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">320</div></th><td class="s6">Vision-Based AI Webpage Scraper with Sheets</td><td class="s7">An advanced n8n workflow integrating Google Sheets, ScrapingBee API, and Googl