MCP (multi-command processor) for Gmail. It integrates Gmail OAuth2 API with multiple nodes to perform email operations (get, search, reply, delete, label management, drafts, threads) via a webhook SSE server, enabling AI-driven email management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12qZWQqhgWpRVqjCF-WupIcOcrbmzWEaR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R323" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">324</div></th><td class="s6">AI Lead Generator: Google Maps &amp; Website Scraper</td><td class="s7">Automates business lead generation by scraping Google Maps and business websites using Apify actors, enhanced by OpenAI GPT-4o and SerpAPI for fallback data enrichment. Stores organized contact info and business data into Google Sheets for easy access and analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QsWIYMCdesS-zpNdVyNxpDJdVgFlpoOP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R324" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">325</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chatbot with Long-Term Memory &amp; Telegram</td><td class="s7">An advanced AI agent chatbot using OpenAI and LangChain in n8n workflow. It integrates Telegram for messaging, Google Docs for storing long-term memories and notes, and uses context windows for personalized, contextual conversations with memory management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1slg3VAFy__UYs-klNZ-2HJcdkV6ugsvl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R325" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">326</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Appointment Scheduling with Approval</td><td class="s7">Automate appointment requests with multi-step n8n forms, AI enquiry classification and summarization (OpenAI), Gmail approval workflow, and Google Calendar event creation. Enhances user experience with terms acceptance and conditional scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OMyQY_W7-WGlglAf_Nj0CPlkbwFPf593">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R326" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">327</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered n8n Workflow Credential Explorer</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that extracts credentials info from all workflows via n8n API, stores them in SQLite, and enables querying via an AI agent using OpenAI&#39;s Chat API. Simplifies searching which workflows use specific app credentials.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iWHLbjL7eP4arw0UmZmVjkSEAdmogQ1H">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R327" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">328</div></th><td class="s6">Social Media Multi-Platform Publisher</td><td class="s7">Automates posting photos/videos on TikTok, X, Facebook, YouTube, Instagram, Threads, LinkedIn via Upload-Post.com API. Uses n8n form trigger for uploads, then posts media with captions. Includes success/error feedback forms to users.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bJEWmLkTW8o-cbwBybm689srj9yIkUSK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R328" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">329</div></th><td class="s6">Company Docs RAG Chatbot (Google Drive + Pinecone)</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) for company documents stored in Google Drive. Uses Google Gemini (PaLM) for embeddings and chat, Pinecone for vector storage, and n8n workflow triggers for live updates. Enables AI chat assistant to answer HR queries from internal docs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JgwkBuoWvAOszTgDT0xI6fq_495KSdd8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R329" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">330</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive to Pinecone RAG with OpenRouter &amp; Gemini</td><td class="s7">Automates document ingestion from Google Drive, splits text contextually, generates embeddings using Google Gemini, and stores vectors in Pinecone. Uses OpenRouter chat model and Langchain for AI context-aware chunking to enhance retrieval-based generation workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jJYr0GL4eo_6uC2_JaleTuEDkbL0pBsF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R330" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">331</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Outlook Email Categorizer</td><td class="s7">Automates email categorization and prioritization in Microsoft Outlook using OpenAI GPT-4 model, Monday.com CRM, Airtable for rules and categories, and n8n workflow automation to organize and flag emails intelligently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qYCTYJTY9Nd-apB2NtUEkDQ857YeHCG4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R331" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">332</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered WhatsApp Chatbot Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates an AI chatbot for WhatsApp using WhatsApp API, Google Gemini (PaLM) for multimodal AI (audio, video, image), Langchain AI Agent, and Wikipedia tool integration. It processes and responds to varied message types intelligently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bp52F_cQYVRkjKF33B4j0Y3TlWitgdu_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R332" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">333</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Email Reply &amp; Feedback Logger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on receiving emails from specific senders, generates AI-powered replies using OpenAI GPT, sends email responses via Gmail, and logs both original emails and replies into Google Sheets. It also collects user feedback through webhooks to improve response quality.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Hyr0h5_lgwSyNAIULKgstr2XNc1a-_XI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R333" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">334</div></th><td class="s6">Automated YouTube &amp; Google Keyword Research</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating NocoDB, DataForSEO API, and Social Flood API for automated multi-source keyword generation, filtering, and monthly search volume tracking for YouTube and Google. Ideal for SEO and content marketing automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ml4Kos947LYULtfa0FT8R4gleLBiK9jR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R334" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">335</div></th><td class="s6">Slack AI Chatbot with RAG for Staff</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered Slack chatbot for company staff that uses OpenAI and Anthropic models with Qdrant vector search to retrieve and answer employee queries from internal documents. Integrates Slack API, Google Drive, and Langchain nodes for seamless RAG support and real-time help.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1twVFmcjEkTcdPsDktYCMmKbk0gn2yo-S">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R335" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">336</div></th><td class="s6">Google Ads Keyword Generator with Search Volumes</td><td class="s7">Automates generation of SEO keywords with monthly search volumes using Google Ads API v18. Integrates n8n with Google Sheets for data storage. Helps SEO and marketing teams find valuable keywords for campaigns with competition and bid metrics.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HBXa6hnwPuBXAvd97sPNIpsJ1vV4-M0R">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R336" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">337</div></th><td class="s6">AI Auto-Tagging for WordPress Posts</td><td class="s7">Automate blog post tagging in WordPress using n8n with OpenAI for AI-generated tags. Uses RSS feed triggers, WordPress REST API, and Langchain nodes for content analysis to enhance SEO and content categorization without manual input.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11TMT_VJ5_RS_iNpGB2lu_ygq7NmDH4In">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R337" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">338</div></th><td class="s6">UTM Link &amp; QR Code Generator with GA Reports</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of UTM tagged links and QR codes, stores them in Airtable, and schedules Google Analytics reports analyzed by OpenAI GPT-4. Integrates n8n with OpenAI, Google Analytics, Airtable, and QuickChart APIs for streamlined marketing campaign tracking and executive reporting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pubxgpLhD_c4JwKSKlduhAzUgqFiNJ41">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R338" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">339</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Social Media Lead Outreach</td><td class="s7">Automates social media analysis from LinkedIn and Twitter via RapidAPI, uses OpenAI GPT-4 for personalized cover letter and subject generation, integrates Google Sheets for lead management, and sends customized emails via SMTP. Ideal for marketers and lead gen pros.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XNJijzb7C_99oA1gJ4PcYfWVvqqXiMrP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R339" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">340</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Google Calendar Reminder via Telegram</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches upcoming Google Calendar events (1 hour ahead), uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for generating friendly reminder messages, and sends them via Telegram. Prevents duplicate alerts for stress-free, personalized appointment notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Wi940FMRgphh0sUDyArrQxleunBwVl2M">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R340" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">341</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chat &amp; Dall-E Image Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram API with OpenAI GPT-4 and Dall-E 3 for conversational AI and image generation. It uses Langchain modules for context memory and tool execution, enabling interactive chat with image creation inside Telegram chats.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sQjCocPVvfZmQkJG-yN-CbTi10FXvIL4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R341" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">342</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive Audio Transcription &amp; Summary to Notion</td><td class="s7">Automates transcription of audio files uploaded to a Google Drive folder using OpenAI Whisper, summarizes content with GPT-4 Turbo, and sends structured summaries to Notion. Integrates Google Drive, OpenAI API, and Notion for efficient audio documentation workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eQLyVyqwNNokyJe48ycrQ6KGSx0aeVE_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R342" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">343</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Telegram Voice Message Translator</td><td class="s7">Telegram bot workflow translating voice messages between 55 languages using Telegram API, OpenAI&#39;s speech-to-text and chat models, n8n automation. Converts speech to text, auto-detects and translates languages, replies with text and audio in Telegram chat.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1J4TP_44LvwKq6YIzaPJvO4jUH9-sZD1p">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R343" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">344</div></th><td class="s6">AI Voice Chatbot with Memory &amp; TTS</td><td class="s7">An AI voice chatbot workflow integrating OpenAI for speech-to-text, Google Gemini for contextual chat, LangChain memory for conversation context, and ElevenLabs for text-to-speech audio generation. Enables real-time voice interactions with maintained conversation memory.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1t5wmeln-e8mhcmjnT8eO7Mkf6_P6th-d">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R344" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">345</div></th><td class="s6">Slack to Linear AI Ticket Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates support ticket creation by scanning Slack #n8n-tickets channel for messages tagged with 🎫, uses OpenAI to generate ticket title, summary, priority, and suggestions, and creates tickets in Linear. Utilizes Slack API, OpenAI GPT, and Linear API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Vv8BU6hCRwfdmczGRGICRxui2OCQcFek">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R345" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">346</div></th><td class="s6">WhatsApp AI Sales Agent with Product Brochure</td><td class="s7">Automate customer support on WhatsApp using n8n integrated with OpenAI GPT-4 and vector search. Extracts Yamaha product brochure PDF, creates an in-memory vector store knowledge base, and runs an AI Sales Agent to answer customer queries via WhatsApp text messages.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MZnwYb8ZVs0gsAVh3YbdADDVCzgLGHyU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R346" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">347</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered WhatsApp Chatbot Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating WhatsApp API with Google Gemini AI and Langchain tools to handle, analyze, and respond to various message types (audio, video, image, text) in WhatsApp chats using AI transcription, summarization, and multimodal content description.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1a0MPTtxltX-t6uRTzzmt-NWad9b5b0uC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R347" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">348</div></th><td class="s6">Video Frame Narration &amp; Voiceover Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates video narration by downloading a video, extracting frames using OpenCV in Python, generating a script with OpenAI GPT-4 Vision LLM, creating TTS audio, and uploading results to Google Drive. Integrates HTTP, Python, Langchain, OpenAI APIs, and Google Drive.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AZC2E6gtFD7ybkRTwtVUhJxgkm_vc3oG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R348" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">349</div></th><td class="s6">AI SQL Agent with Dynamic Charting</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o, Langchain SQL Agent, and Quickchart.io to answer SQL queries and generate dynamic charts. It extracts user questions, runs SQL queries on PostgreSQL, classifies if charts are needed, and creates visualizations using OpenAI structured output and Quickchart.io.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mA5Ctd0iPWOhvewrj41klcWAAb9qzzfh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R349" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">350</div></th><td class="s6">Automated CV Screening with OpenAI &amp; Supabase</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to download CV PDFs, extract text, and analyze candidate fit using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini with a structured JSON schema. Stores results in Supabase. Ideal for recruiters to automate initial resume screening and generate fitting scores and insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oJM0tqAguapIv76iz1qeYXhSsJW8wDWi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R350" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">351</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Job Application Automation</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates job applications by accepting CV PDFs via form upload, using OpenAI LLM and text classification to validate and extract relevant candidate data based on a job posting, and saving to Airtable ATS. It enables a two-step form process with AI-assisted prefill and validation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1phb6-UT8tOGEu-SJfTxoPjWzCAoUArQY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R351" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">352</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Appointment Scheduling with Approval</td><td class="s7">Automate appointment requests processing with n8n multi-step forms, OpenAI AI text classification and summarisation, Gmail approval workflow, and Google Calendar integration for scheduling events. Provides user-friendly form UX and admin approval via email.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16KTLf7_u3jC6NSpsw-inN-5zYByBdtqZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R352" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">353</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered On-Brand Blog Article Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates generating brand-consistent blog drafts using n8n workflows. It scrapes latest articles from a blog, converts content to Markdown, analyzes style and voice with OpenAI LLMs, and creates new drafts saved to Wordpress for review.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1usGO_TgrP1-n9hLIwCZUeXUyTu2GVJhj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R353" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">354</div></th><td class="s6">Real-Time AI Meeting Transcription System</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates joining virtual meetings (Zoom, Google Meet) using Recall.ai API for real-time transcription, processes dialogue via OpenAI API, stores structured data in Supabase/Postgres, and creates AI-generated notes for meeting insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12mk-p62Ab-UDtZfQnJo9Ku0qTvIgCFAq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R354" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">355</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Phishing Email Detection &amp; Jira Reporting</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Gmail and Microsoft Outlook triggers to capture emails, uses hcti.io API for HTML screenshot generation, OpenAI&#39;s ChatGPT-4 for phishing analysis, and auto-creates detailed Jira tickets with email data and screenshot attachments for streamlined phishing incident management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fKfdPlJ-ecW_uChAUQT4p0KOlUDK7_jF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R355" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">356</div></th><td class="s6">Email Phishing Detection &amp; Jira Reporting</td><td class="s7">Automates detection of phishing emails from Gmail and Outlook using ChatGPT AI, captures email content and headers, generates email screenshots via hcti.io API, and logs detailed tickets with attachments in Jira for security review.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1DQIs1ow86fc1VEoO3sfvzBdy_6gOLNCm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R356" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">357</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Meeting Task &amp; Event Manager</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of tasks from Fireflies.ai meeting transcripts using OpenAI GPT-4o, stores tasks in Airtable, sends email notifications via Gmail, and schedules Google Meet events. Streamlines post-meeting follow-ups and client communications with AI-powered processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZBgHfzlud48fBxLEwkxdpjX5lbyM7fnC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R357" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">358</div></th><td class="s6">Cybersecurity Incident Analysis with MITRE &amp; AI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4, MITRE ATT&amp;CK data from Google Drive, and Qdrant vector DB to analyze and enrich Zendesk security tickets. Automates TTP extraction, remediation advice, and historical pattern detection using Langchain agents and embeddings.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1X31Pc1x8vcZYgZfvRH7M3pXZPg_RCQq6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R358" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">359</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Backup to GitHub</td><td class="s7">Automates backup of all n8n workflows to a GitHub repository using GitHub API, HTTP requests, and internal subworkflows. It compares existing backup files with current workflows, creates or updates JSON files named by workflow ID, supporting version control and easy restore.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BAe6kLXbg6qfOSh3DEB-Bj1ds4oxogom">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R359" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">360</div></th><td class="s6">AI Agent for Automated CV Screening &amp; Sorting</td><td class="s7">Automates screening, sorting, and rating of candidate CV resumes against job descriptions using n8n with Google Drive, Google Docs, Google Sheets, Gmail, and Groq Llama 4 AI model integration. Moves CVs to folders, updates trackers, and sends notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16ngd7jNowZDFcrcQ5THgm6afXXOMJTOd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R360" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">361</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Zoom Meeting &amp; Stripe Payment Setup</td><td class="s7">Automates event creation by integrating Zoom for meeting scheduling, Stripe for secure payment processing, and Google Sheets for data management. Sends email notifications via Gmail for presenters and participants, streamlining event setup and participant tracking with no-code automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Yz_H7lRwQC5-MtOjxAmWJtddEB1_B6Vc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R361" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">362</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Voice/Text to SEO Social Content AI</td><td class="s7">Automates Telegram incoming messages (voice or text), transcribes voice via OpenAI Whisper, researches topics with SerpAPI, generates SEO-optimized social media posts and photorealistic image prompts, then creates images via HuggingFace Stable Diffusion integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1a6S05kXrrsFO7q4o0C75bRa6iQhxG8_4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R362" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">363</div></th><td class="s6">Chinese Vocabulary Flashcard Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates vocabulary learning by translating English words to Chinese, generating pinyin and example sentences via OpenAI, retrieving images from Pexels API, and updating Google Sheets and Drive. Uses Google Translate, Langchain AI, Pexels API, and Google Workspace APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16PrR6ayEJb3Vi9SwiL5Jzaatd7tNDE03">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R363" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">364</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Subscription Video Email Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automate email notifications for new YouTube videos from your subscriptions. Uses YouTube Data API v3 for subscriptions, YouTube RSS for latest videos, filters out shorts, and sends thumbnail-rich emails via SMTP. Runs hourly by default.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1irlXSlQdPvpsLSTV8qS-g8iUZco3u2-g">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R364" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">365</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Pomodoro Productivity Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates Pomodoro technique sessions via Telegram bot. Uses n8n workflow integrating Telegram API for commands, Google Sheets API for tracking sessions, and JavaScript code for managing user states. Helps schedule focused work and breaks, logging data for productivity insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Za-BD94SrV9bnW2-Ronwr6gXrQHIQu6s">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R365" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">366</div></th><td class="s6">Discord AI Spam Moderation Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates spam detection and moderation on Discord using AI text classification (Langchain) and OpenAI GPT model. Retrieves messages, groups by user, flags spam, notifies moderators with human-in-the-loop decisions, and executes moderation actions with Discord bot integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yOpjPJ-QYIDGzrXogxc6p4itN5zDTOqd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R366" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">367</div></th><td class="s6">SEO-Optimized WordPress Blog Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates SEO-optimized blog post creation for WordPress using Perplexity.ai for research, OpenAI GPT-4 mini for writing and HTML generation, WordPress API for publishing, and Telegram for success notifications. Ideal for content marketers and bloggers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1env-9mtY2qtVufwJNnyyCn65tG_RgmJb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R367" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">368</div></th><td class="s6">CoinMarketCap Crypto AI Agent</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered n8n workflow integrating CoinMarketCap APIs with OpenAI GPT-4o Mini for live cryptocurrency data analysis, including prices, metadata, market rankings, conversions, and global metrics. Enables advanced crypto queries using natural language and session memory.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18MCSRbi7rgnYfBUj-HT9-dIEtX_ysY_0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R368" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">369</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Email Appointment Scheduler</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates detection and management of appointment requests from unread Gmail messages using OpenAI GPT-4 and Google Calendar APIs. It classifies emails, checks calendar availability, proposes meeting times, and replies, streamlining email scheduling tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VvebfU7bxnikRUI5Zt5u6xARyjmH_9lT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R369" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">370</div></th><td class="s6">Extract PDF &amp; Image Text to CSV via Vertex AI</td><td class="s7">Automate extracting text from PDFs and images stored in Google Drive, using Google Vertex AI (Gemini) and Openrouter LLM APIs, converting data into categorized CSV files, then uploading results back to Drive for streamlined data processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xctq_6BTIBBaUY9rhJBzyNlzRzThAhwj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R370" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">371</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Backup to GitLab</td><td class="s7">Automates backup of n8n workflows to GitLab repository using n8n API and GitLab API. Supports manual and scheduled triggers, compares existing files, and updates or creates workflow JSON files tagged for backup.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Bcd7vo_4C0OMWIpqUm_1XFz-CNYKlJQD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R371" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">372</div></th><td class="s6">Line Chatbot with CBT AI Therapist</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Line Messaging API with Azure OpenAI to create a conversational CBT (Cognitive Behavioral Therapy) chatbot. Uses Langchain AI Agent powered by Azure OpenAI, handles text messages, provides therapy guidance, and sends replies via Line API with user-friendly loading animations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZsTAxQ5g4eb1Zqhq6XmfUgHC0HVRtS9v">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R372" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">373</div></th><td class="s6">Gumroad Sales to MailerLite &amp; CRM Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates post-purchase workflows by capturing Gumroad sales, adding customers to MailerLite email groups for automated sequences, and logging sales data to Google Sheets CRM. Uses Gumroad webhook, MailerLite API, and Google Sheets API to streamline customer onboarding and sales tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1N0uDK4YQFf7HmfeP5HVlzFDzKR_CJQBh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R373" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">374</div></th><td class="s6">ConnectWise New Ticket Alerts to Teams</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching new tickets from ConnectWise API, filters out previously sent tickets using Redis, groups them by company, and sends alert messages to Microsoft Teams chat. Uses n8n, ConnectWise API, Redis, and Microsoft Teams integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1k2D2hGLJVHvib5V5YGrbwNWUQYPtdyNG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R374" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">375</div></th><td class="s6">HN &#39;Who is Hiring&#39; Job Scraper</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow scraping Hacker News &#39;Ask HN: Who is hiring?&#39; posts using Algolia Search API and Hacker News API. It cleans and structures job posts with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, then stores them in Airtable for easy job listing. Requires OpenAI and Airtable accounts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Gk925YAQ3d_Mxupo4sKYgYGIytZlaDqN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R375" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">376</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform Feedback Collector</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on Typeform feedback submissions, filters responses by usefulness score, and logs positive and negative feedback separately into Google Sheets using OAuth2 for authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14ZYgCl1p2ADGNTP7Y_Ir0py3xdKSqoBC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R376" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">377</div></th><td class="s6">ISS Position Updates via ActiveMQ Every Minute</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching the International Space Station&#39;s real-time position every minute using WheretheISS.at API, processes the data with n8n nodes, and sends updates to an ActiveMQ topic via AMQP protocol for real-time tracking workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PIerhwnpAmA6fVDyMqUqPQKHiN9oJVwn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R377" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">378</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Profile Finder with Boolean Search</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that generates Boolean search strings using OpenAI GPT-4O-MINI from job descriptions, performs authenticated Google searches, extracts LinkedIn profile URLs, and appends results to Google Sheets for sourcing candidates efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=196x0Ves4-GLYqIEwG4SS6f43VUgPPX6t">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R378" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">379</div></th><td class="s6">ISS Position to AWS SQS Queue</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching real-time ISS location using &#39;wheretheiss.at&#39; API every minute and sends latitude, longitude, timestamp, and name details to AWS SQS queue. Tech stack: n8n, HTTP Request, AWS SQS, Cron node for scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PisITKuYufoT1sbwQzwCWltNCBlOZLUl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R379" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">380</div></th><td class="s6">ISS Location Logger to BigQuery</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching ISS real-time position via &#39;wheretheiss.at&#39; API every minute, formats data, and stores name, latitude, longitude, and timestamp into Google BigQuery. Built with n8n workflows using HTTP Request, Cron, Set, and Google BigQuery nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1N53Gi7Mn0vp1t-HKfZn7ZzuZa3RBRFZ3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R380" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">381</div></th><td class="s6">Website Screenshot Capture &amp; Email Sender</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing website screenshots (full and partial) via Uproc API, uploads them to Dropbox, and emails them using AWS SES. Triggered manually, it efficiently combines web automation, cloud storage, and email services for easy screenshot sharing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QFGhTLCjTWEdZVk3W2n8EunW7Fl6H729">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R381" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">382</div></th><td class="s6">Calendly to Notion Contact Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing new Calendly invitee info and logs it into a Notion database. Uses Calendly API webhook to trigger on invitee creation and Notion API to add pages with invitee name, email, and status for streamlined contact management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12QJ9BCcseEqxygz_F5ngFJXgdXuVNduJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R382" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">383</div></th><td class="s6">AWS S3 to Transcribe Audio Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates transcription of audio files stored in AWS S3 using AWS Transcribe with automatic language detection. Built in n8n with AWS S3 and AWS Transcribe nodes, triggered manually to process all files in a specified bucket.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18y6V_uq3GwBsyD8byXq-W8fxHLWxjF5o">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R383" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">384</div></th><td class="s6">Notion-SIGNL4 Alert Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates alert handling by integrating Notion database monitoring with SIGNL4 incident management. Uses n8n to process incoming alerts via webhook, update Notion status fields, and send or resolve SIGNL4 alerts accordingly. Tech stack: n8n, Notion API, SIGNL4 API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cuCl6pwLfQ_iYuU5iY5HD88g0Px-b09u">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R384" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">385</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Weather Updates via LINE Message</td><td class="s7">Automate sending daily weather updates at 9 AM via LINE messenger using OpenWeatherMap API and n8n Cron trigger. Fetches Berlin temperature and sends a personalized notification via LINE Notify OAuth2 integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=107kixvZPHp2mI2McyGE6SMqZVALCZceX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R385" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">386</div></th><td class="s6">Fetch &amp; Merge Multiple RSS Feeds</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow fetches RSS feeds from specified URLs (Medium and Dev.to for n8n content), reads and batches them, checks completion, and merges all feed items into a single dataset. Tech stack: n8n native nodes (RSS Feed Read, Function, IF, SplitInBatches) to automate RSS aggregation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iUo3aGuYsIrB1FP1f6WwTuIaY1X6fZvt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R386" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">387</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Contacts Pagination Fetcher</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to fetch HubSpot CRM contacts with automatic pagination handling using HubSpot API. It manages API keys, handles rate limiting by waiting between requests, and combines all paged results into a single dataset for further processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17xBaQGonN3t0Yb9bA-am8E8vfJ3ztchn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R387" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">388</div></th><td class="s6">Google Calendar Sync to Slack &amp; Philips Hue</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Google Calendar events to update Slack status and Philips Hue lights in real-time. Uses Google Calendar API, Slack API, and HTTP webhooks for Philips Hue integration. Ideal for visual and status-based meeting notifications in teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1R0wO47_YVlJYZorJd_gT_S0K8dyOv7Mb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R388" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">389</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Recipe Finder and Email Sender</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses Edamam API to fetch recipes based on customizable criteria like diet, health, calories, and cooking time. It runs daily at 10am, selects random diet/health filters if set to random, compiles recipes, and emails them using Gmail SMTP.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gFtgSfLBmuLD7SvS0p41G8Un8UAIo6Bx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R389" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">390</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Dropbox XLS Exporter</td><td class="s7">Automates exporting Google Sheets data to an XLS file and uploads it to Dropbox every 15 minutes. Uses Google Sheets API, n8n spreadsheet conversion, and Dropbox API to keep backups or share spreadsheet updates seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1e2WAMFcOH3mT-_V1G0ZBO7yloOLVF8y6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R390" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">391</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Shopify Sales Report Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly extraction of Shopify orders, calculates total orders and revenue, records data in Google Sheets, and posts a summary to a Slack channel. Uses Shopify API, Google Sheets API via OAuth2, Slack API, and n8n Cron trigger.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=195eUAmAUW84hq92A4sFbRQ64sedXwsgp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R391" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">392</div></th><td class="s6">Calendly to Pipedrive + Slack Follow-up</td><td class="s7">Automates meeting logs and follow-up reminders by triggering on new Calendly invites, creating Pipedrive activities, scheduling a feedback reminder after the meeting, and notifying the sales team in Slack. Integrates Calendly API, Pipedrive API, Slack API, and n8n for workflow orchestration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=120Zo01Wc3SYSYpLwrbwi3gOz4ghKhkeA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R392" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">393</div></th><td class="s6">n8n GitHub Workflow Backup Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates daily backup of n8n workflows to a GitHub repository. Uses n8n HTTP Request nodes with basic auth to fetch workflows, GitHub API nodes to create/edit JSON files, and cron scheduling. Ensures versioned workflow backups with commit metadata.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-vwYJUj0eebo67Ni4sZtDIe9KKTlcRre">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R393" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">394</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform to HubSpot Lead Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates lead capture from Typeform surveys into HubSpot CRM, updating contact info and lifecycle stage, then sending a personalized Gmail follow-up. Uses Typeform API, HubSpot API, and Gmail OAuth2 for streamlined lead management and nurturing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1p4OxmZes1HUWxXHWx0JEzq-8MnpmS0Qd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R394" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">395</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Deal Automation &amp; Notification</td><td class="s7">Automates HubSpot deal processing using HubSpot API triggers, categorizes deals by stage, creates tickets with priority in HubSpot, logs lost deals in Airtable, sends Slack notifications on deal closure, and generates Google Slides presentations for scheduled demos.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wB3bKC31zdNNAkjSOJz2ekNVgLgu6Xts">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R395" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">396</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Issue Auto-Assignment</td><td class="s7">Automates assignment of GitHub issues using GitHub API and OAuth2. Listens to issue and comment events, assigns issues to creators or commenters who request assignment via keywords. Built with n8n workflow automation, improving GitHub repository management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bIaBS8ujvMDmPbka_p4gPDqX6ojGqLU3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R396" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">397</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk Ticket Creator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to create Zendesk support tickets manually. Uses n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger node to initiate and the Zendesk node to create tickets via Zendesk API. Ideal for quick ticket generation in customer service automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Un-yuEis2uE2r34T8DF1TuwLOpOPQAw4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R397" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">398</div></th><td class="s6">YCombinator News Scraper &amp; Emailer</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching latest news from YCombinator using HTTP Request and HTML Extract nodes, merges data, exports to spreadsheet, and sends via email. Built with n8n workflow automation, utilizes web scraping and SMTP email delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YnG143B9CxhxfT5KMxoTQ8-SaoS_7Dtq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R398" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">399</div></th><td class="s6">Netlify Form Submission to Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing Netlify form submissions and appends extracted name, email, and role data to Airtable. Uses Netlify Trigger webhook, n8n&#39;s Set node for data mapping, and Airtable API integration for database storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PahFU1cvpyk8uh_ywHxCWLs6OuqT58it">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R399" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">400</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Issue Auto-Assignment Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates GitHub issue assignment using n8n with GitHub OAuth2 API. Listens to issue and comment events, assigns issues based on &#39;assign me&#39; comments, and adds labels/comments accordingly to streamline issue management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1boEF3mfYZv_RJ7NsejrClKsjspueeJWV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R400" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">401</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Google Calendar to Slack Reminder</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches all events from a Google Calendar, filters events for today&#39;s date in Asia/Qatar timezone, formats event details, and sends a daily summary message to a specified Slack channel. Uses Google Calendar API and Slack API with timezone and date/time manipulations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yEKjDS9d0nMDQk0KwZ46TOJSSlIaUDqt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R401" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">402</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive File Creation Email Alert</td><td class="s7">Workflow monitors a specific Google Drive folder for new files and sends an email notification upon creation. Uses Google Drive Trigger and SMTP email nodes in n8n to automate instant alerts for file updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ykaUtzSDy5rZpKuiapJYNgQZoSO-B433">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R402" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">403</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Contact Enrichment with Clearbit</td><td class="s7">Automates enriching HubSpot contacts using Clearbit API. When a HubSpot contact event triggers, it fetches contact details, retrieves extra data from Clearbit (job title, company, city), and updates the HubSpot contact. Uses HubSpot OAuth2 &amp; Clearbit APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wyPhRGcwuf4hqQmjxMDtOK6zABjgZuiH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R403" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">404</div></th><td class="s6">Product Hunt Top 5 Posts to Discord</td><td class="s7">Automates hourly fetching of the top 5 Product Hunt posts via GraphQL API, processes post data, and sends formatted summaries to a Discord channel using webhook. Uses n8n automation with Cron, GraphQL, Item Lists, Set, and Discord nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Bg7A6R31sgarF1_vXHf33ELDfltFs1PR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R404" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">405</div></th><td class="s6">Onfleet Task Creation from Spreadsheet</td><td class="s7">Automates creating Onfleet delivery tasks using data from Excel spreadsheets. Utilizes n8n nodes for reading binary files, parsing spreadsheets, and Onfleet API integration. Ideal for logistics teams to streamline task imports from customer or delivery data sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vKLTq1ksB90_UjpLkVPwhvDuGwH4OsmS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R405" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">406</div></th><td class="s6">Email Enrichment &amp; Lemlist Lead Import</td><td class="s7">Automates lead enrichment using Dropcontact API with data from Google Sheets, then imports enriched leads into Lemlist for email campaigns. Uses Google Sheets OAuth2, Dropcontact for contact verification, and Lemlist API to streamline B2B outreach.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gAe4F9lrJXZko-DGRjSoG_zBlv5KvzeT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R406" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">407</div></th><td class="s6">Calendly Leads to Notion via Dropcontact</td><td class="s7">Automates lead capture from Calendly invitees, enriches data using Dropcontact API, and logs detailed lead info in Notion database, including contact, company, and scheduling details. Integrates Calendly webhook, Dropcontact API, and Notion API for streamlined CRM.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zBEBwiwuk1kQUuWdr9I1Rx0_GU9unqo4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R407" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">408</div></th><td class="s6">CRM Contacts Sync Pipedrive &amp; HubSpot</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing and updating contacts between Pipedrive CRM and HubSpot using n8n automation platform. Utilizes Pipedrive and HubSpot APIs to fetch, compare, and update person/contact records based on email and name data on a scheduled basis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nHDSnzdrKhbvJBg-F0Oi4YRQpwH3isvC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R408" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">409</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Contacts from Pipedrive to HubSpot</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing of contact records from Pipedrive CRM to HubSpot CRM using n8n workflow. Utilizes Pipedrive and HubSpot APIs to fetch all contacts, merge them by email to avoid duplicates, and update HubSpot contacts every minute via a cron trigger.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-V5zaWSF5tBfwJZSF9txDL-c75v9dO4w">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R409" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">410</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Receipt OCR to Airtable</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates receipt processing by uploading images from Telegram to AWS S3, extracting text via AWS Textract, and appending the data to Airtable. Integrates Telegram Bot API, AWS S3 and Textract, Airtable API to digitize and store receipt info seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19xfdjzWB_cH4yzFGqxNNPiaYEGY-O5Q_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R410" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">411</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive to AWS S3 Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on Google Drive file updates in a specific folder and syncs files to an AWS S3 bucket with AES256 encryption. Uses Google Drive API, AWS S3 API, and n8n nodes for seamless cloud file synchronization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12U8qepIM0wvrq8OoarwCSQ9nDKGSuC1b">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R411" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">412</div></th><td class="s6">Image Labeling &amp; Cataloging Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates image search via Google Custom Search API, analyzes image content with AWS Rekognition, and saves image titles, links, and detected labels to Google Sheets. Utilizes HTTP Requests, AWS Rekognition, and Google Sheets APIs for efficient image metadata extraction and storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1emeOsE8N3eKiCgYwWVnFVmi_Vu7pmqBR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R412" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">413</div></th><td class="s6">Readwise to Telegram Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow syncing Readwise articles updated after last sync to Telegram. It reads last sync time from a file, fetches new articles via Readwise API, filters articles, sends summaries to Telegram, and updates sync time. Uses Readwise API, Telegram Bot API, file system.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tr_2WcVW7qJ9lCmaN50k-9d_HG5ECfKl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R413" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">414</div></th><td class="s6">Webhook JSON to XLSX Exporter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that accepts JSON data via a POST webhook, splits items in the JSON body, converts them into an XLSX spreadsheet file, and returns it as a downloadable binary response. Uses n8n built-in nodes: Webhook, Item Lists, Spreadsheet File, Respond to Webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1H__Drq81KdLwYPnQzIuiFe-FQQ9GwARM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R414" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">415</div></th><td class="s6">Slack-Triggered GDPR Data Deletion</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating GDPR data deletion requests via Slack slash commands. It validates tokens, parses &#39;delete &lt;email&gt;&#39; commands, triggers deletion workflows for Paddle, Customer.io, Zendesk, logs results in Airtable, and responds back on Slack. Integrates Slack API, Airtable, and custom workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1leQY39nDkcgxptDPRbKHofvMvZQzmAcX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R415" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">416</div></th><td class="s6">Monthly Financial Metrics to Mattermost</td><td class="s7">Automates monthly retrieval of financial metrics from ProfitWell API and posts key data (active customers, recurring revenue, growth rate) to a Mattermost channel using n8n workflow triggered by a cron schedule.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1DsvQ-id-yKTPLOwqBvdc-KJUE3d1i7_G">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R416" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">417</div></th><td class="s6">Crypto Portfolio Value Updater</td><td class="s7">Automates hourly updates of cryptocurrency prices and portfolio values using CoinGecko API and Airtable. Retrieves portfolio data, fetches current prices, updates records, and calculates total portfolio value for easy tracking and reporting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gkN1ganoyzSk-GYc_-8-hSLfytIdIFXW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R417" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">418</div></th><td class="s6">Tweet Generator with Hashtag &amp; Airtable Logging</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that generates short tweets featuring random hashtags (#techtwitter, #n8n) using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-3 API, and then logs the tweet and hashtag into Airtable. Utilizes manual trigger, function node, HTTP Request to OpenAI, data set, and Airtable integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qjD8fXvt7IVsDxrypkVqnGKoCTRs4szZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R418" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">419</div></th><td class="s6">Onfleet to QuickBooks Invoice Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates invoice creation in QuickBooks Online upon new Onfleet task creation using Onfleet Trigger and QuickBooks API integration. Streamlines billing by triggering an invoice every time a delivery or task is initiated in Onfleet.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ERgoHvZ7AWULf3NVTqoFhTfBBsp-P8iu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R419" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">420</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive File Update to Onfleet Task</td><td class="s7">Automate task creation in Onfleet when a specific Google Drive file is updated using Google Drive Trigger and Onfleet API in n8n workflow. Useful for seamless delivery or service task management linked to file changes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fBUa1HUC6jPeIbLRXdcx4_LsB2uh78Ep">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R420" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">421</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Tech RSS to Telegram Alerts</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches multiple tech-related RSS feeds every 10 minutes, filters out new entries, categorizes content by keywords and URLs, and sends tailored alerts to distinct Telegram channels using Telegram API credentials. Automates timely tech news delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ee5XNW4_qJ-iWf18bSJh7JlHGBJvGnnE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R421" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">422</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Channel Video Alerts to Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching latest videos from a specific YouTube channel using YouTube API every 30 minutes, filters new videos, and sends notifications with video title and URL to Telegram via bot. Utilizes n8n, YouTube API, and Telegram API for workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gEcq-WlrjLGNOHF518Lddq4hm0vG4ejC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R422" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">423</div></th><td class="s6">Manage Cases in TheHive via n8n</td><td class="s7">Automates creation, updating, and retrieval of cases in TheHive using n8n workflow. Utilizes TheHive API to handle case lifecycle from creation to modification and fetching detailed info, ideal for cybersecurity incident management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pdtuBAJaLFxNmGR7zLGHlHQ9PbBEE-wq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R423" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">424</div></th><td class="s6">GitLab Backup Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates backing up n8n workflows and credentials by exporting them, then committing and pushing changes to a GitLab repo using command line and cron scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1R2UqJ3tWmMmXlj9Vjrhu9zFSrkblc6T-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R424" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">425</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Channel Setup and Messaging Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates Slack workflow: creates a channel, invites users, posts a welcome message with attachments, and uploads files. Utilizes Slack API via n8n Slack nodes and HTTP Request node for fetching files. Ideal for team onboarding and communication setup.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EaMPpQS_UtzB0nkVglsnXSNFceB1hiJQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R425" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">426</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Timesheet Report Generator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to generate timesheet reports with user avatars and task summaries. It fetches data, sorts tasks, retrieves avatars via HTTP, creates a styled Markdown report converted to HTML, and optionally emails the report. Uses n8n nodes: Function, HTTP Request, Markdown, and Email Send.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1X6gJTzduFwxJSL3YcBFGMO0JR6sLqy1E">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R426" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">427</div></th><td class="s6">User Request Management via Typeform &amp; ClickUp</td><td class="s7">Automates workflow for managing user requests by integrating Typeform forms with ClickUp task management. It routes request types (document, presentation, update, workflow) to corresponding ClickUp lists using OAuth2 API. Enhances task tracking and team collaboration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xyBYimGhxsg5uhWg22M2z1lMaJ571CY1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R427" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">428</div></th><td class="s6">HTTP Requests &amp; Pagination Demo Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating common HTTP request use cases: fetching data from APIs (GitHub, Wikipedia, JSONPlaceholder), handling pagination, scraping HTML content, and splitting response bodies for easier data handling. Tech stack: n8n nodes (HTTP Request, HTML Extract, If, Set), GitHub API, Wikipedia, JSONPlaceholder REST API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ud_Nx6IcQNHBQ6MaM52i3lqOIEWbnmjX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R428" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">429</div></th><td class="s6">Daily NASA Astronomy Picture to Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates daily sending of NASA&#39;s Astronomy Picture of the Day to a Telegram channel using NASA API, n8n Cron scheduling, and Telegram Bot API for photo delivery with captions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qWsHIqgNzE211mxtlzKap4UoD71HMl1S">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R429" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">430</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Customer Data to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching customer data via n8n&#39;s Customer Datastore node, transforms fields using Set node, and upserts records into Google Sheets with OAuth2 API. Ideal for keeping customer info updated and organized in spreadsheets effortlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kvzBzkc4HfEnfQTL8eJyBO-CSgWCxqQV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R430" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">431</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Google Sheets to MySQL Importer</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly data import from Google Sheets to MySQL using Cron scheduling, Google Sheets API with OAuth2 for authentication, and MySQL node for insertion. Ideal for syncing spreadsheet data into a database automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tV8g3FO6LSu0F67OKcNpKC0Lnx_bWKwR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R431" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">432</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to HTML Table via Webhook</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow reads data from a Google Sheets spreadsheet using Google Sheets API, converts the data into a Bootstrap-styled HTML table using a custom function, and serves it as an HTML response via a webhook. Ideal for dynamic table generation from sheet data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1q-xhDhcdbturDozG_9wiWHDYIVdPFD1k">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R432" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">433</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform to Pipedrive Lead Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing Typeform survey responses to create and map leads, organizations, persons, and notes in Pipedrive CRM. Uses Typeform webhook trigger, JavaScript mapping for company size, and Pipedrive API nodes for CRM data entry.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JW_Xu5hhcrn5G066pr870VH4mdJ13I-r">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R433" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">434</div></th><td class="s6">Asana to Notion Task Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing tasks from Asana to Notion via their APIs using n8n. Triggered by Asana updates, it creates or updates Notion database pages with task info and deadlines, ensuring task data consistency across both platforms.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18cEiMfHCEGoDaboyiDc1L56RYu2dJTwz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R434" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">435</div></th><td class="s6">Company Logo and Info to Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching company logos, icons, and details via Brandfetch API and stores them in Airtable. Includes n8n manual trigger, Brandfetch integration for company data, and Airtable append operation for database storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZnJsvnXX6f2C7NJigegmJ3EcwFFpU8aB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R435" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">436</div></th><td class="s6">Daily HubSpot to Mailchimp Contact Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates daily syncing of new HubSpot contacts (created in the last day) to a Mailchimp mailing list using OAuth2 authentication for both APIs, triggered every day at 07:00 via n8n&#39;s cron node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19tHU1cj8w2i0JkupYuo63BcBP7Jxi7P7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R436" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">437</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Mailchimp Contacts to HubSpot Daily</td><td class="s7">Automates daily synchronization of updated Mailchimp members to HubSpot contacts using Mailchimp and HubSpot APIs. Tracks last execution timestamp to fetch only recent changes. Built with n8n workflow automation tool and cron scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uM5d88UAZmtc-PJYQ97zi1LeicVW5COb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R437" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">438</div></th><td class="s6">Pipedrive to Stripe Customer Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing updated Pipedrive deals with Stripe by checking deal won time changes, retrieving organization details, searching Stripe customers, and creating new customers if needed using Pipedrive and Stripe APIs in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1k9znq-JJuiTTe2vWFBHNSicufXTGNSRE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R438" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">439</div></th><td class="s6">Stripe to Pipedrive Charge Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates logging of successful Stripe charges to Pipedrive CRM by fetching charges since last run, enriching with customer and organization details via Stripe and Pipedrive APIs, then creating notes in Pipedrive. Scheduled daily at 8 AM using n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17fUkMxGyR10PGnIbytuxR5OJax22h21I">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R439" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">440</div></th><td class="s6">Sync New Pipedrive Products to Stripe</td><td class="s7">Automates product sync from Pipedrive CRM to Stripe. Uses Pipedrive trigger node, processes product data with Function and Set nodes, and creates products and prices via Stripe API calls. Ideal for streamlining e-commerce product management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kjLFnF1XdyaLrcqmpvenTxJETDE4m17E">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R440" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">441</div></th><td class="s6">Pipedrive Lead Enrichment &amp; Email Finder</td><td class="s7">Automates lead enrichment and email discovery using Pipedrive CRM and Datagma API. It enriches new organizations with funding, traffic, and industry data, finds ideal sales contacts, verifies emails, and updates Pipedrive records for streamlined sales prospecting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1srGiRSHcMSpe_IFp7Ol-EnfPs4Lkd06f">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R441" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">442</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Weekly Stock Portfolio Reporter</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow fetches stock data from Baserow, scrapes live prices from Tradegate.de, calculates portfolio value changes, builds an HTML report, and sends it via SendGrid email. Integrates Baserow API, HTTP requests, HTML extraction, and SendGrid for automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LjyfnOpWmjRWq_JY47DUw_CglNWpFlZr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R442" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">443</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive to Pipedrive Lead Importer</td><td class="s7">Automates importing leads from Google Drive spreadsheets into Pipedrive CRM. Uses Google Drive Trigger, Spreadsheet File parser, and Pipedrive API to create organizations, persons, leads, and notes, streamlining lead management and CRM updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hI3ybNp8ITAIdwN0UzN15B7afT-LEQCe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R443" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">444</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Salesforce Account &amp; Contact Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing companies and contacts from a Google Sheet into Salesforce. Uses Google Sheets API and Salesforce API to read, search, create, and update accounts and contacts based on sheet data, ensuring no duplicates. Ideal for CRM data automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GKwM5VuoKm_9zj-42FpbfaMoA9DNMyEa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R444" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">445</div></th><td class="s6">Excel to Salesforce Account &amp; Contact Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing company accounts and contacts from Microsoft Excel to Salesforce using n8n. It reads Excel data, searches Salesforce for existing accounts, merges data, creates new accounts, and upserts contacts via Salesforce API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EIKyOI3f60RO74jy4EH_LKBQ7B0rdMSd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R445" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">446</div></th><td class="s6">Excel to Salesforce CRM Importer</td><td class="s7">Automates importing company and contact data from an Excel spreadsheet into Salesforce. Uses HTTP request to download the file, spreadsheet parsing, Salesforce API to search, create, and update accounts and contacts, deduplicating data along the way.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15X0U3oAKGq3G1E-GjJZVsJB941LtbDTW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R446" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">447</div></th><td class="s6">Google Firestore CRUD - Create, Update, Get</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates document creation, updating, and retrieval in Google Cloud Firestore using Firestore API and OAuth2 credentials. Ideal for backend data management and integration scenarios with Firestore database.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RCaz7_jbI-8-VOGb06QVsqvITYeua03e">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R447" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">448</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Issues Notion Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates synchronization of GitHub issues with a Notion database using GitHub webhook trigger and Notion API integration in n8n. It creates, updates, archives, and manages issue states inside Notion, enabling seamless issue tracking within a Notion workspace.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CP1WbujlBgoGlzUQF4oOwtshk6_0jN6J">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R448" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">449</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Shopify Customers to Zendesk Contacts</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing updated customer data from Shopify to Zendesk by matching email addresses, creating new Zendesk users or updating existing ones including phone numbers. Uses Shopify webhook triggers and Zendesk API integration in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BPKm0XdVZ2VGGKDUiITYL1DoUAh49wLS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R449" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">450</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify to Zendesk Order Ticket Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates creation and tracking of Zendesk support tickets for updated Shopify orders using Shopify webhook and Zendesk API. Checks existing tickets by order ID to avoid duplicates, creating new tickets for new orders to streamline customer support workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rS9TEn20wOLU4COiE65n2D8y2nnYfsOY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R450" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">451</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk to Slack Ticket Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing of new Zendesk tickets to Slack threads using Zendesk API and Slack OAuth2. Creates or updates Slack threads with ticket info, keeping support communication organized across platforms.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1POz-aAtzYkEAHibmVkt3fbzf320RUp1b">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R451" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">452</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk to Asana Task Sync Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates creation and updating of Asana tasks from new Zendesk tickets using Zendesk and Asana APIs via n8n workflow. It checks for existing tasks and appends comments or creates new tasks accordingly, streamlining ticket-to-task management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gBkb3gROZ9n-DgwHpkyNlK9T5hx3uqs6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R452" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">453</div></th><td class="s6">Mautic to Monday.com Contact Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates contact creation in Monday.com from new Mautic leads using n8n. Integrates Mautic webhook trigger and Monday.com API to sync lead names and emails as board items, enabling CRM task automation and enhanced contact management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1d4C1QYaYOMKKzDRfXPha-fZG1r7wRtCe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R453" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">454</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify to Mautic New Customer Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing new Shopify customers to Mautic as contacts using Shopify webhook and Mautic API integration in n8n. Ensures first name, last name, and email transfer seamlessly for marketing automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uCTEjc3CIaiS1ublPuqjX6M4nk9UHvV_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R454" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">455</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk to GitHub Issue Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Zendesk tickets with GitHub issues by creating issues or comments when new tickets are received. Uses Zendesk API, GitHub API, and n8n workflows for seamless ticket and issue management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Pft_YPDeaDx0iMSe2a0nemAA--St4xmd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R455" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">456</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk to Jira Issue Synchronizer</td><td class="s7">Automates synchronization between Zendesk tickets and Jira issues using n8n. It creates Jira issues for new Zendesk tickets or adds comments if an issue exists. Integrates Zendesk API and Jira Cloud API to keep data consistent.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1n0vmqPa6hGczxsxPyvlMNkl6pWK4y1g4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R456" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">457</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Email Reply Handling &amp; CRM Sync</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates email reply categorization using OpenAI, managing leads in Lemlist and HubSpot, and notifying teams via Slack. It integrates Lemlist API, HubSpot CRM, Slack API, and OpenAI GPT for lead status updates, unsubscribes, deal creation, and follow-ups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eBMbAIPlFq8t5qi1-ptABrJAfSVs8RJj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R457" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">458</div></th><td class="s6">Sync HubSpot Companies with Zendesk Organizations</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing of recently modified HubSpot companies to Zendesk organizations every 5 mins using HubSpot and Zendesk APIs. Checks if organization exists to update or create. Uses n8n with HubSpot App Token and Zendesk API credentials.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1H3m8XBbtyIPGZsBJyNFBM3Fgfh5tOAa2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R458" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">459</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk-HubSpot Ticket Sync Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates synchronization of support tickets and contacts between Zendesk and HubSpot using their APIs. Periodically updates or creates tickets in HubSpot from Zendesk tickets, manages contact data, and keeps external IDs in sync timestamps to enable seamless cross-platform support management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1i98ONDGdZnHtarZ1LMvqedwZTDecyWKI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R459" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">460</div></th><td class="s6">Company Profile Extractor &amp; Analyzer</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of company info from domains listed in Google Sheets. Uses HTTP requests, HTML extraction, OpenAI for AI-driven value proposition, industry, market &amp; audience classification, then updates Sheet. Tech: Google Sheets API, OpenAI API, n8n nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FS-J-v67NoqnFg7rxAd9C_G1_KC_T3L0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R460" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">461</div></th><td class="s6">RabbitMQ to SMS Alert System</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that listens to a RabbitMQ queue for temperature readings and sends SMS alerts via the Vonage API when a threshold is exceeded. It automates message processing using RabbitMQ trigger, conditional logic, and SMS notification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IeX9L55155gMkURoU97cJL07M4l3RnRp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R461" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">462</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce Product CRUD Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates creating, updating, and retrieving WooCommerce products using n8n&#39;s WooCommerce node and API integration. Enables manual execution to add a product, update its stock, and fetch product details seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ts_BuZsoV4vAtKc1qjwuKyi6j41xZDF_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R462" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">463</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce to Mattermost Order Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates sending a message on Mattermost when a new WooCommerce order is created. Uses WooCommerce API trigger and Mattermost API for real-time order notifications, improving team awareness and response speed for e-commerce operations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lkci-EUiv2b0KRR9yLybP7aOwPvctT5i">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R463" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">464</div></th><td class="s6">Export SQL Table to CSV File</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches data from a Microsoft SQL Server table and saves it as a CSV file. Utilizes Microsoft SQL API for querying, n8n spreadsheet node for CSV export, and supports further automation like emailing or uploading the file.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1U997r-8XcnTNcm6fYQ3QElQfP3lxRlxu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R464" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">465</div></th><td class="s6">Urgent Bug Alert from Linear to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates notifications for urgent bugs by triggering on Linear issue events, filtering by priority and label, transforming data, and sending alerts to Slack channels using Linear API, n8n workflow, and Slack API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wn0sduUMugli32SXjAJ1TixykdtRJzCt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R465" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">466</div></th><td class="s6">API JSON to Google Sheets &amp; CSV Export</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching JSON user data from randomuser.me via HTTP Request, then directly appends it into Google Sheets using Google Sheets API, and also converts selected data fields into a downloadable CSV file using n8n&#39;s Spreadsheet File node. Includes manual trigger and data mapping via Set node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B9zd5ZwwkDet22zjeJO3tzwDsx4dHvh9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R466" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">467</div></th><td class="s6">Outlook Draft Email with Attachment Automation</td><td class="s7">Automate creating, attaching files, and sending draft emails via Microsoft Outlook using n8n workflow. Integrates Microsoft Outlook API and HTTP Request node to fetch attachments, enabling streamlined email drafting and sending.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1DiW8UI2U-4mFOlow8WIb6GQvkJeC2viJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R467" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">468</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Discord Events to Google Calendar</td><td class="s7">Automate syncing of Discord scheduled events to Google Calendar using Discord API and Google Calendar API. On a schedule, fetches events from a Discord server and creates or updates matching events in Google Calendar for seamless event management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1isNfWJTePIpDPd0LvzquFkvdOnwHBxCk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R468" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">469</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Discord Message Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates sending updated Google Sheets rows as formatted ASCII tables to a Discord channel using Google Sheets API, a custom JavaScript code node, and Discord webhooks. Ideal for real-time collaborative update notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1auP2iVufENWDjLKEsnAkghhsoKkHuyA8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R469" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">470</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Outlook Calendar with Notion Database</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates syncing events from Microsoft Outlook Calendar to a Notion database. It fetches calendar events via Microsoft Graph API OAuth2, checks for existing pages in Notion, and creates or updates them accordingly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ll9A64I_BI3iB-ugdPNqc-q5M0fiQ4xl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R470" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">471</div></th><td class="s6">LangChain AI Chat &amp; Wikipedia Research</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via LangChain nodes for AI chat and a custom Wikipedia tool for research. It executes LLM chains and AI agents on manual trigger, enabling natural language queries and knowledge retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZLohQ0nobuhJe84EjF3uf-SGfNTGUYA0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R471" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">472</div></th><td class="s6">LLM Data Parser with Auto-fixing</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow using Langchain with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to parse structured data about US states and cities. Includes prompt setup, validation via a JSON schema, and an auto-fixing LLM output parser to ensure data correctness and reprocess invalid outputs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FqukmllL12EHuJrylpuGoqm0g8fSEIs6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R472" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">473</div></th><td class="s6">Pinecone Vector DB Chat with Google Drive</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that loads files from Google Drive, splits text content, embeds chunks using OpenAI embeddings, and inserts them into a Pinecone vector index. Enables chat interactions by retrieving relevant data chunks from Pinecone and answering via OpenAI GPT-4o-mini model.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UyHAyQsRfXVowHwFTDZ_U-WX44CMpxFg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R473" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">474</div></th><td class="s6">Slack AI Agent with Gilfoyle Persona</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow creating a Slack AI chat agent mimicking Gilfoyle&#39;s blunt persona from Silicon Valley. Uses Slack webhook, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, LangChain AI agent with SerpAPI and Wikipedia tools, plus memory buffer for conversation context retention. Filters bot messages and posts AI replies in Slack channels.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Vo27dyRSvsmNZwCS7D6CYKMsqeD7RIyd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R474" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">475</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive Document Summarizer</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads a document from Google Drive, splits the text into chunks, and uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via Langchain to generate automated summaries. Integrates Google Drive API and OpenAI API for efficient document summarization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Dxtef8jM433Reyq4ebY9XATMQWfKYoaT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R475" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">476</div></th><td class="s6">Customer Feedback Sentiment Analysis</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing customer feedback via an n8n form, analyzes sentiment using OpenAI API, merges results with form data, and appends entries to Google Sheets. Integrates n8n formTrigger, OpenAI sentiment classification, and Google Sheets for streamlined feedback management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lxyzOpqpHuLYEQ1qCEfQwDcqFNHBgGYw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R476" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">477</div></th><td class="s6">Email Validation &amp; Mailing List Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates email capture and validation using n8n with Hunter.io for email verification and SendGrid to add valid emails to a mailing list, streamlining subscriber management via a custom form trigger.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14FYYB2nSCgQ97jnnJCuW8EeqilGzCIpu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R477" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">478</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Airtable Users to Mailchimp</td><td class="s7">Automates user data synchronization by retrieving contact details from Airtable and creating subscriber entries in Mailchimp using n8n automation. Utilizes Airtable API, Mailchimp API, and a Cron trigger for scheduled execution to keep mailing lists updated.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xsuD3qUIxuYUf4Gc3CueuTleM4IFjlfZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R478" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">479</div></th><td class="s6">Google Calendar to Zoom Meeting Scheduler</td><td class="s7">Automates scheduling Zoom meetings from Google Calendar events within the next 12 hours. Uses Google Calendar API to fetch events and Zoom API (OAuth2) to create meetings. Filters out canceled and specific event types to ensure relevant Zoom meetings are created.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10BCDXoDClrbcyOPEoQOhgibIRiq9PxNE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R479" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">480</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Mailchimp Subscriber Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing email addresses from a Google Sheets range to a Mailchimp mailing list. Utilizes Google Sheets and Mailchimp APIs within n8n, triggered at set intervals to keep subscriber lists updated seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jZpurvTK76nyVrhA4-22gRD1uiUEbI4d">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R480" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">481</div></th><td class="s6">SMS Broadcast via Airtable &amp; Twilio</td><td class="s7">Automates sending personalized SMS messages using Airtable to store contacts and Twilio API for messaging. Users trigger the workflow manually in n8n, which fetches phone numbers and names from Airtable and sends custom SMS via Twilio, streamlining bulk communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IOYQiu0HdKvIm5iza6EhFobd2bPdUfxx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R481" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">482</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform Leads to WhatsApp via Twilio</td><td class="s7">Automates sending Typeform survey leads directly to a WhatsApp number using Twilio. Utilizes Typeform webhook trigger, data parsing with n8n Set node, and Twilio API for messaging. Ideal for instant lead notification and follow-up.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1O2yHBUDwotGvAlhAB4AIPUuSDg2Aszi5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R482" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">483</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Mentions to RocketChat Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of @n8n_io Twitter mentions using Twitter API, filters new tweets, and posts notifications to RocketChat. Built with n8n nodes: Cron, Twitter, Function, Set, and RocketChat for real-time social media alerts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Y_kZOrXrnQIzCWdVneivVcACSZqApen0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R483" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">484</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Search to Mattermost Alerts</td><td class="s7">Automates Twitter search for &#39;n8n_io&#39; using Twitter API every minute, filters new tweets, formats data, and sends detailed notifications to Mattermost channels. Utilizes Twitter OAuth1, n8n Cron, Function, Set, and Mattermost API nodes for real-time monitoring and alerting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zrWyh1ZKN1yPkFXHcpbVcgfKzzQbrvPC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R484" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">485</div></th><td class="s6">Bulk Email Verification with Icypeas &amp; Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates bulk email verification using Icypeas API, Google Sheets for input data, and n8n for workflow orchestration. Reads emails from Google Sheets, authenticates via HMAC SHA1, and posts verification requests to Icypeas, streamlining large-scale email validation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eLye4-X_SDLkhuYBI-wr7qyUYfmT9_MS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R485" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">486</div></th><td class="s6">AI Agent for Hacker News Top Posts</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Langchain&#39;s AI agent and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to fetch, clean, and return the top 50 Hacker News posts in JSON. It uses n8n&#39;s Hacker News node and custom tool workflow features for interactive chat queries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u7l0-hhFRK0UcKGhhX344RHlS90NZisa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R486" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">487</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive Folder File Sharing &amp; Link Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates listing files from a specified Google Drive folder, changes their sharing status to public, and generates direct download links. Uses Google Drive API and n8n workflow automation to batch process files and produce shareable URLs efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mNFnaWPbTP3fWONQ9-rBtkQXJIQNvmQV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R487" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">488</div></th><td class="s6">Crypto 24h Price Alert via Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates crypto price monitoring by fetching Binance&#39;s 24h ticker data, filters coins with ±15% changes, and sends aggregated alerts to a Telegram channel. Uses Binance HTTP API, n8n nodes, and Telegram Bot API for real-time market updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KT5wLJD7iLLYVP9AyanMbEsTKBWSrGnO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R488" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">489</div></th><td class="s6">Spotify Discover Weekly Auto-Archiver</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly archiving of unique tracks from Spotify&#39;s Discover Weekly playlist to a user-created Archive playlist. Built with n8n using Spotify API, Cron scheduling, and data merging to prevent duplicates. Enhances music discovery management effortlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Z5LpAWyFqb4puzDND-y0AHJFGxNoZs-i">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R489" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">490</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress to Medium Blog Publisher</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching latest blog posts from a WordPress site (using HTTP Request and HTML extraction), parses post titles and content, and publishes them on Medium via its API. Ideal for automated blog cross-posting and content repurposing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1J7ZTrocq2rs-e3xA6gr3dqbILLqSox6_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R490" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">491</div></th><td class="s6">Strava to Beeminder Activity Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates adding datapoints to Beeminder goals when new activities are created in Strava using Strava Trigger and Beeminder API nodes in n8n. Ideal for fitness tracking and goal monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1S08WvTTNyrJEJyGFlZaqEvv6gNcaX2gT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R491" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">492</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Assistant with Memory &amp; Calculator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI Assistant API with Langchain memory buffer and calculator tool to create a chat assistant supporting contextual memory and calculation capabilities. Enables conversational AI with session persistence and computation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Aez8jkjwz0EUXegVxcSAUC-FWaugJj8z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R492" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">493</div></th><td class="s6">Google Contacts: Create, Update &amp; Get Contact</td><td class="s7">Automates creating, updating, and retrieving a contact in Google Contacts via n8n using the Google Contacts API with OAuth2. Enables workflow automation for managing contacts seamlessly within Google ecosystem.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Pd8iQi2Lqa56ikldGPTEdl_541AirgxB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R493" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">494</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Company News Email Reminder</td><td class="s7">Automates sending daily emails with latest news about companies from your calendar meetings. Uses Google Calendar API to fetch meetings, NewsAPI to gather recent articles, and Gmail API to email formatted news summaries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16IJ47arLHnSWZDOJ1ZxRURL_2uhsNJeF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R494" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">495</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Contact Enrichment with ExactBuyer</td><td class="s7">Automates enriching new HubSpot contacts using ExactBuyer API with OAuth2 authentication. On contact creation, it fetches the contact, uses email to get additional data from ExactBuyer, then updates HubSpot contact with enriched info like social profiles, job, and location.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1elbITEd70EFVmrbIS5SfrILIVPnmsf9y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R495" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">496</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Contact Outreach Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates daily outreach emails to uncontacted HubSpot leads using Gmail and records engagement in HubSpot. Utilizes HubSpot API with OAuth2 for contact retrieval and engagement logging, plus Gmail API for sending personalized cold emails.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lPJJ-SWb-ikN731o38tpsTn110lpGyG8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R496" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">497</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chatbot with OpenAI GPT</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on Telegram messages, processes them using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via Langchain AI Agent, and responds with helpful, emoji-rich replies. It integrates Telegram API and OpenAI API for interactive chat automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JUuDTI8dnrDhx9rmPkzm3GQ9BOLcCZXI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R497" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">498</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Contact Follow-Up Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates follow-up outreach emails for HubSpot contacts using Gmail and HubSpot APIs via OAuth2. Runs daily at 9 am, filters contacts last contacted over 30 days ago with only one prior engagement, sends personalized emails, and records engagement in HubSpot CRM.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TVTp2D_uZujKmaKaOc0cHc2QzT73eOl_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R498" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">499</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Qualification via Email Verification &amp; Scoring</td><td class="s7">Automates lead qualification by collecting business emails via n8n form trigger, verifying email validity with Hunter API, scoring leads with MadKudu API, and sending Gmail alerts for high-fit leads. Integrates n8n, Hunter, MadKudu, and Gmail for smart lead management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EFZA53_BQvdIEMiDWMD_mWVLNMZjVVL5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R499" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">500</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Qualification &amp; Notification via Form</td><td class="s7">Automates lead capture from a web form using n8n Form Trigger, validates emails via Hunter API, scores leads with MadKudu API, and notifies qualified leads through Telegram. Ideal for smart B2B lead management and instant alerts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11kih7G8gAHsr4yZnotMs5RyA7WGyytVT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R500" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">501</div></th><td class="s6">Google Indexing API Sitemap Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates website URL indexing by extracting sitemap URLs, converting XML to JSON, and submitting each URL to Google&#39;s Indexing API with batch control and quota limit error handling. Tech: n8n, Google Indexing API, XML, HTTP Request.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ebAuXm3RRjAdA-q0Il3u-gZDQ2BuehK5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R501" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">502</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Lead Alerts to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates lead monitoring by fetching new companies created in HubSpot within the last 5 minutes, filters those with annual revenue over $5M, and sends detailed Slack notifications to sales reps. Uses HubSpot API, Slack API, and n8n scheduling for real-time lead alerts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10ESUw8X1USyL6Ao1Z5dq0rDy6rSMbdmi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R502" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">503</div></th><td class="s6">Euro Exchange Rate Webhook API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches the latest Euro foreign exchange rates from ECB&#39;s XML API, converts the data to JSON, filters by requested currency via a webhook query, and responds with current exchange rate. Utilizes HTTP Request, XML to JSON conversion, and webhook triggers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Kco2W4BFTzl6NjqvJ0eQ64qfM1J9KrB7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R503" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">504</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Viral Tweet Creator &amp; Scheduler</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating creation and scheduled posting of viral tweets every 6 hours using OpenAI GPT-4 Turbo for content generation and Twitter API for posting. Customizable influencer niche, style, and inspiration ensure on-brand, engagement-focused tweets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mZqx787KXYU6cXPY-NmGx-2QlvTfBm6R">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R504" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">505</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Idea Capture to Notion Logger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow enabling Slack slash command /idea to capture user ideas and log them automatically into a Notion database. It uses Slack Webhooks, Notion API, and n8n automation to streamline idea collection and collaboration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1n_ICSz-JOrurZQUFUqX6sS-5L5B9f5RK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R505" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">506</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Ideas to Google Sheets Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates idea collection from Slack via a slash command (/idea), storing submissions in Google Sheets. Utilizes Slack API for command triggers, Google Sheets API for data storage, and n8n webhook and workflow nodes for integration and automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1De4dHbmk-CEhMXlUBCXtJb9NeQ0D0xSq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R506" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">507</div></th><td class="s6">Hourly RSS Feed Email Notifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that checks multiple RSS feeds every hour for new posts published in the last hour and sends email notifications via Gmail. It uses RSS Feed Read, conditional date filtering, batching, and Gmail OAuth2 to keep users updated on fresh content automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MORPczTOyoQca14TNtxuPq_QAkURppa7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R507" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">508</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Inbox Starred Email Archiver</td><td class="s7">Automates Gmail inbox management by archiving all non-starred emails daily on workdays. Utilizes Gmail API via OAuth2 in n8n workflow to fetch emails, filter starred ones, and archive others, keeping inbox tidy and prioritized.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1X-K75_gIzA-h4WI4RXkYAcqf_Z06HxFB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R508" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">509</div></th><td class="s6">Todoist Daily Task Automator</td><td class="s7">Automates daily task creation in Todoist by copying template tasks with custom due dates from descriptions. Uses Todoist API, JavaScript for parsing, and n8n scheduling and filtering nodes to manage recurring daily tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lAWOO3mIwUca2AFXAWivFNuRvPx_Vk6m">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R509" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">510</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Slack Error Notifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on any error in other workflows and sends a formatted alert message to a Slack channel (#alerts-n8n-workflows) using Slack API. Includes customizable error details and quick setup instructions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Aw1xDy3VceifnmAXn1sR6t_iy1_p5A5S">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R510" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">511</div></th><td class="s6">SEO Keyword Generator Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that generates SEO keywords using Google Autocomplete API, processes XML response, aggregates and formats keyword suggestions into a clean array. Utilizes HTTP Request, XML parsing, and webhook nodes for dynamic keyword research automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oJD8Ma37Gh_i_uXSnmxt0ihm_WV88g7j">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R511" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">512</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Error Alert Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n error handling workflow that sends a Telegram alert with the failed workflow&#39;s name and execution link. Utilizes n8n errorTrigger, Set node, and Telegram API to notify via chat, ideal for monitoring automated workflows effectively.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1D-FdHQCl5zsvj1BGq-mevklPDLN3e8wI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R512" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">513</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Auto-Documenter</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow auto-generates concise documentation for n8n workflows using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4. It accepts workflow JSON and title via a form, crafts a prompt, sends it to OpenAI API, and returns brief, SEO-friendly docs as HTML. Ideal for n8n users needing quick workflow summaries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1br0SsK_fvlTVN559qJ-mM--t3BiawuuV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R513" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">514</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Workflow Failure Reporter via Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly reports of failed n8n workflow executions using n8n&#39;s API and Telegram Bot API. Fetches last 7 days&#39; failed executions, compiles messages, and sends alerts to Telegram chat for prompt monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UEq3mRNZVfMepuqSBDM4dEKsGoGR5xgP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R514" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">515</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Command to ClickUp Task Creator</td><td class="s7">Automate task creation in ClickUp from Slack slash commands. Uses Slack Webhook API, n8n for workflow automation, and ClickUp OAuth2 API to create tasks with command text. Simplifies managing tasks across Slack and ClickUp for teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OofjipiibMqF_MKGmi2fobhYRiOW40EP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R515" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">516</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Tweets Scheduler from Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates posting tweets by fetching texts from a Google Sheets document every 6 hours and posting them on X (Twitter) via API. It uses Google Sheets OAuth2 for reading and deleting rows and Twitter OAuth2 for posting tweets, enabling scheduled social media updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HTGE2xm1Qq86vkPCDA3EKLIOPOoX4-XN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R516" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">517</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Upload &amp; Playlist Management</td><td class="s7">Automates uploading a video to YouTube, creating a playlist, and adding the uploaded video to it using n8n workflow nodes with YouTube OAuth2 API and local file reading.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MafcMQNvbp_hg1QukS_rr2efLQMAvMuW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R517" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">518</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Description Auto-Updater</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates updating YouTube video descriptions by appending custom text. Uses YouTube OAuth2 API and n8n core nodes like Set, If, Manual Trigger to fetch videos, check for description changes, and update descriptions efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cdVvoEgzDgrIGCGeQlNe2hukxSau8ima">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R518" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">519</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Image Processor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram and OpenAI APIs to receive text prompts via Telegram, generate AI images with OpenAI, and send images back to the user on Telegram. Enhances real-time interactive communication with AI-powered image generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kr_WDzD6pJNWJiG5GQreLTzF00wx6ueD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R519" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">520</div></th><td class="s6">Groundhogg CRM Mailing Address Verifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that verifies new contact mailing addresses in Groundhogg CRM using Lob API for US address validation. It triggers via webhook, checks address deliverability, and updates the CRM by tagging verified or unverified addresses to streamline contact data accuracy.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12kQM_M6JEcoD-7L93Lii-opCJ_4q1-Ou">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R520" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">521</div></th><td class="s6">Google Slides Dynamic Image Replacer</td><td class="s7">Automates replacing images in Google Slides via a webhook. Uses Google Slides API and n8n workflow to identify images by alt text and update them dynamically with new URLs. Ideal for updating presentations programmatically with OAuth2 authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qeFT1vgeg_03QiyYKY_6mfXXMOrJ7ADC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R521" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">522</div></th><td class="s6">Elevenlabs Text-to-Speech Webhook</td><td class="s7">API workflow in n8n converting text to speech using Elevenlabs API. Accepts POST requests with voice_id and text, returns generated speech binary. Uses custom HTTP auth and webhook nodes for seamless TTS automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1g60jLNUbbh7B09fh6HiiEW8W9irtqX7w">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R522" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">523</div></th><td class="s6">Keap Contact Address Verification Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates mailing address verification for new Keap CRM contacts using Lob API via webhook triggers. Tags contacts as deliverable or non-deliverable to trigger follow-up actions. Tech stack: Keap CRM webhook, Lob address verification API, n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1m9uMS8RAuKRnQeKSu364SWXDT0hZ8i3-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R523" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">524</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Show HN Trending Email Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates daily scraping of Hacker News front page using HTTP Request and HTML Extract nodes in n8n. Filters for &#39;Show HN:&#39; posts, formats results in a Function node, and sends summary emails via Send Email node every day at 13:00. Useful for tech enthusiasts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1S1wpkRQRVn0IyFXlJ1T2eRtjAENLFuLE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R524" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">525</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable SEO Meta Tag Auto-Fill</td><td class="s7">Automates filling missing SEO title tags and meta descriptions in Airtable by fetching URLs, scraping their HTML title and meta description using Airtable API and HTTP Request node in n8n. Updates Airtable records, streamlining SEO data management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1777IjbPdt97aNhmcSen1H_wDKrPTWF9o">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R525" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">526</div></th><td class="s6">DOCX to PDF File Converter</td><td class="s7">Automates converting DOCX documents to PDF using ConvertAPI. Downloads a DOCX file, sends it to ConvertAPI for format conversion, and saves the resulting PDF to disk. Utilizes HTTP requests, file handling, and ConvertAPI authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-X1Lf2iYy7bQZ8WJCuB4OVbkCEwIw3N2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R526" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">527</div></th><td class="s6">AI Movie Recommender with MongoDB</td><td class="s7">An AI agent using OpenAI&#39;s chat model integrated with MongoDB aggregation to recommend and store favorite movies. It processes chat inputs, queries movies collection, and updates favorites, combining Langchain memory buffer and n8n workflows for seamless AI-driven movie management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cxwimVr8Ak-aot6IlHlW4kQTD0056ADS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R527" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">528</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Default Error Handler Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow for automated error handling: detects workflow failures, fetches error workflow info via n8n API, updates workflows lacking error handlers, and sends failure notifications via Gmail OAuth2 email. Runs daily via schedule trigger.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19tJp5zvTEFPwClgRx7hXgPLlhEV8WpVp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R528" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">529</div></th><td class="s6">AI Web Scraper &amp; API Data Agent</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using OpenAI&#39;s Chat Models, Langchain agents, and Firecrawl API to scrape web content and call external APIs for data. It enables AI agents to fetch, process, and respond with live web and API data in a streamlined manner.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LjR9oUetpc0MFBK-GgCQJ5y6Gq57hp3x">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R529" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">530</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered n8n Workflow Credential Query Agent</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow extracts and stores workflow credential metadata from the n8n API into a SQLite database, then uses OpenAI&#39;s GPT model with Langchain integration to create an AI agent that can query these credentials via natural language. It enables users to find workflows by app credentials via AI-powered SQL querying using n8n, SQLite, and OpenAI APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Yasjpn8TrCmqsayH7VcOwE3CDck8BSSE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R530" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">531</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Save Email Attachments to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow monitors Gmail for new emails with attachments, downloads them, and automatically uploads the files to Google Drive. It uses the Gmail Trigger node, a Function node to manage binary data, and Google Drive API integration to streamline file saving and organization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-uiRFKTQXdP92ke-zT2nvNHyJRoCSx8G">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R531" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">532</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Repo Release Notifier with Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates daily checks of latest GitHub releases for specified repos (n8n-io/n8n, home-assistant/core) using GitHub API, and sends Slack notifications for new releases. Utilizes n8n workflow with HTTP Request, Schedule Trigger, Slack nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1G5BXP0PlT2oLKc1V8xy1t_vpqe7RhOtu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R532" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">533</div></th><td class="s6">Stripe Checkout Sessions Fetch &amp; Filter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves all Stripe checkout sessions from the last 20 days using Stripe API, paginates results, then splits and filters them by custom fields like nickname and job title for easy data processing and visualization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16k0a4FWn1fKyXUiYrJ_Q7oGmL5Unng3N">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R533" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">534</div></th><td class="s6">Confluence Page Creator from Template</td><td class="s7">Automates creating Atlassian Confluence pages using REST API. Fetches a template, replaces placeholders with webhook input data, and posts a new page to a target space. Uses HTTP Basic Auth with Atlassian API keys and supports dynamic content generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lMd-HqX6KFrX3oKF3F4uBfCf-sQQE9m0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R534" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">535</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Backup of n8n Workflows to Bitbucket</td><td class="s7">Automates daily backup of all n8n workflows to a specified Bitbucket repository. Uses n8n API to fetch workflows, Bitbucket API for storage, and handles rate limiting with dynamic wait times to ensure smooth, uninterrupted backups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ErvNTSW3n5A3YcqcjgxMiaMRPLpEKxCV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R535" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">536</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk Unassigned Tickets to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates sending unassigned Zendesk tickets with status and subject to a Slack channel using Zendesk API, Slack API, and n8n workflow automation. Runs daily at 16:30 to keep teams informed about pending support tickets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FVnyXRrAbIv3gNmXUDdiXA2-ikvJvc7u">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R536" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">537</div></th><td class="s6">Candidate Resume AI Qualification</td><td class="s7">Automates candidate resume screening by downloading PDFs from Google Drive, converting them to images via Stirling PDF API, then analyzing with Google&#39;s Gemini multimodal LLM to assess fit for a specific role. Uses n8n, Google Drive, Stirling PDF API, and Google Gemini.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EME7DU8o4cfv6uXdGTY1MXobHOMtWfCc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R537" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">538</div></th><td class="s6">Passport Photo AI Validator Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Google Drive, Google Gemini AI vision model, and Langchain for AI-based validation of passport photos per UK government guidelines with structured output parsing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZN86qPn1Q0U3eEs_1LItBn0iWbGkixBA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R538" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">539</div></th><td class="s6">Google Ads SEO Keyword Volume Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Google Ads API to fetch SEO keyword monthly search volumes, historical trends, difficulty scores, and competition metrics. Ideal for keyword research automation with up to 20 keywords input and customizable database integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kSxthAgR5J6_KCkx5TDdCO4aaRD9YJ4c">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R539" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">540</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Alert to Azure DevOps Task</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates querying Elasticsearch daily at 12:15 to detect alerts and creates work items in Azure DevOps if alerts exist using Cron, Elasticsearch API, and Azure DevOps REST API with Basic Auth.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ekcuaxnvJgTx4C6S8FNxe8fKfdPgSAtt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R540" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">541</div></th><td class="s6">Image Upload &amp; Optimization Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates image hosting on ImgBB with API key, optimizes images via ReSmush.it API, and optionally generates AI images using OpenAI. Converts local image files to optimized URLs for easy web use, combining ImgBB, ReSmush.it &amp; OpenAI in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AVeeKpeIsdN_wH3LogRx8w48x7PlhBgz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R541" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">542</div></th><td class="s6">Sync YouTube Playlist Tracks to Spotify</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to automate syncing tracks from a YouTube playlist to a Spotify playlist, avoiding duplicates. Uses YouTube and Spotify APIs with OAuth2, batch processing, dataset comparison, and track search for seamless playlist updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YDuX3pFoYgyXFnb6GDKNOkjfvlI4v-L5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R542" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">543</div></th><td class="s6">Elastic Alert Email Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of PRISM Elastic alerts and sends email notifications via Microsoft Graph API using OAuth2. Utilizes n8n nodes: Schedule Trigger, HTTP Request, If, and Email API integration for real-time alert management and communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1feC770eRXEKv7jTeW0rjFv8P5kZ31YQG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R543" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">544</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow GitHub Backup</td><td class="s7">Automates backup of n8n workflows to a GitHub repository using n8n API and GitHub API. Periodically fetches workflows, checks for changes, and commits new or updated JSON files to GitHub for version control and safe storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KgCDKTBlaRZRxUNEOUCCUQD46RKovqaQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R544" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">545</div></th><td class="s6">Auto-Update Zoom Meeting &amp; WP Redirect</td><td class="s7">Automates creating Zoom recurring meetings via OAuth2, updates a WordPress page with a meta refresh redirect to the Zoom join URL, and notifies a Slack channel. Uses Zoom API, WordPress API, Slack API and a cron trigger for scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jz8S-thry9yATXzBLKtPCDA-O9fp5Yh9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R545" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">546</div></th><td class="s6">Webflow Form to Google Sheets Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing form submissions from Webflow via webhook, processes data with custom JS, and appends it to Google Sheets. Uses Webflow API, Google Sheets API, and n8n code node for seamless form data archival and timestamping.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fPKNUB7eDNJxUl9UcuqB6njFe9h7dvxa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R546" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">547</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Weekly Dinner Meal Planner</td><td class="s7">Scheduled weekly automation using n8n to create dinner meal plans from Mealie API. It fetches recipes by category, randomly selects configured number, and posts meal plans with configurable offsets. Utilizes HTTP authentication and JavaScript code for randomization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pIh97706b6EeVDhTbLkQbcWIFqwBEuII">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R547" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">548</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Release Notifier via Email</td><td class="s7">Automates daily checks for the latest GitHub repo release using GitHub API, converts the release notes from Markdown to HTML, and sends an email notification via SMTP if a new release occurred in the last day.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QZyeuGJG3aTedZXVVoh5YW9HwCFEscOr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R548" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">549</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Agent for Supabase PostgreSQL</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI and Supabase PostgreSQL to create an AI assistant that dynamically generates and executes SQL queries based on user chat input, enabling conversational database interaction and smart data retrieval without SQL expertise.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1q-8kJ_o-7oy6WgFAl4jnw-GvmzTz6s-S">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R549" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">550</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Transcript Summarizer &amp; Telegram Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieval of YouTube video transcripts, extracts and summarizes the content using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via LangChain, then sends summarized insights via Telegram. Utilizes YouTube API, OpenAI, LangChain, and Telegram API for content analysis and notification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lO5579CFkQZNqCv_F7tP5n3gGmQJXTQD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R550" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">551</div></th><td class="s6">OnThisDay Hacker News Highlights Digest</td><td class="s7">Automates daily collection of Hacker News front-page headlines for the same calendar day across multiple years, analyzes tech trends using Google Gemini LLM, and sends a categorized Markdown summary with source links via Telegram. Uses n8n, HTTP requests, HTML extraction, and Google PaLM API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UC2N3f1E9A0fMT8fUTXuNRQuEvk9Ujf0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R551" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">552</div></th><td class="s6">Jira to Telegram Issue Notification</td><td class="s7">Automates sending Jira issue updates to specific Telegram users. Uses Jira webhooks, processes events like issue creation, updates, and assignee changes, and sends formatted messages via Telegram Bot API. Ideal for teams tracking Jira tasks via Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QEyCMaTMnzFOo1YXf9GqcAfSrIcSY0FQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R552" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">553</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates summarization of YouTube videos by extracting transcripts via Apify API and generating concise summaries using OpenAI&#39;s GPT via LangChain in n8n workflows. Ideal for content creators and researchers to quickly get key insights from long videos.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ig71sLcz28Jvx6WPbYsovKjs1miyK0-A">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R553" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">554</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Data Extraction with Claude &amp; Gemini</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads a PDF from Google Drive, converts it to base64, and extracts data using AI models Claude 3.5 Sonnet and Google Gemini 2.0 Flash. Enables prompt customization to tailor extraction, comparing results from two top NLP APIs seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MV8sy-qHed1sJMBTXFXVxrPnibKXVjKO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R554" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">555</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive PII Remover</td><td class="s7">Automates removal of personally identifiable information (PII) from CSV files in Google Drive. Uses Google Drive API to monitor and process files, extracts data, identifies PII columns via OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, removes sensitive data, and uploads sanitized files back to Drive.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1X8JXS3c7h8jCOVxucmHrBnYJA8zQ-zBJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R555" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">556</div></th><td class="s6">Upwork Job Scraper &amp; Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping of fresh Upwork job posts using Apify API, filters based on working hours, stores unique jobs in MongoDB, and sends notifications to Slack #general channel. Utilizes MongoDB, Slack API, Apify, and n8n&#39;s scheduling for continuous job updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ueVqcn2ecuCcMqdF36Luqq0wk5H_Zd-I">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R556" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">557</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce Rank Math SEO Updater</td><td class="s7">Automates updating Rank Math SEO metadata on WooCommerce products via WordPress REST API. Utilizes n8n workflow with HTTP Request node and WordPress API credentials to set SEO title, description, and canonical URL, improving product SEO efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yMBf9xU9TlERlPPi0cYDTTwPkZRZQmBK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R557" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">558</div></th><td class="s6">GitLab Merge Request Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating GitLab merge request lifecycle: checks, creates MRs, adds comments, closes or merges them. Uses GitLab API via HTTP Requests and includes scheduling, conditional logic, and wait timers for pipeline completion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Qb5wjFnRqT2WueWGuUE81xMlSnCkwKWE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R558" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">559</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive Workflow Backup Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates scheduled backups of n8n workflows by exporting workflow data as JSON files and saving them into date-stamped folders on Google Drive. Utilizes n8n API, Google Drive OAuth2, and scheduled triggers for streamlined backup management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Cmeb6D2kyGq8dQYTs-8pW4EsC-eUrIdp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R559" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">560</div></th><td class="s6">Export WordPress Posts to Google Drive CSV</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow exports published WordPress posts by fetching them via WordPress API, adjusts relevant fields, converts data to CSV, and uploads the file to Google Drive using service account authentication. Ideal for automated WordPress content backups or integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-97A0XhKQY6bQJNb16_kqzvoumduXOIc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R560" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">561</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Server Update Notification Emailer</td><td class="s7">Automates daily checks of upgradable packages on a VPS via SSH, formats the list into HTML, and sends email notifications through SMTP to alert server admins about pending updates. Utilizes SSH node, JavaScript code node, and SMTP email in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TUiwNEDTHiTc09phL72fL_ZnR5dHRdKh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R561" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">562</div></th><td class="s6">VPS Resource Monitor and Alert System</td><td class="s7">Automates VPS resource checks (CPU, RAM, Disk) every 15 minutes via SSH commands. Uses n8n schedule trigger, SSH node for system stats, SQL merge and IF node for threshold comparison, and sends email alerts via SMTP if usage exceeds 80%.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1U1z36MU6j_M3r_ohRQbIIEhYTjeSqPgl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R562" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">563</div></th><td class="s6">Bulk File Upload to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow for batch uploading multiple files via a form to Google Drive. It checks for an existing folder by name, creates the folder if missing, and uploads files preserving original names. Uses Google Drive API, n8n form trigger, and custom JS code for file handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FpEboCAl1CVrV_0RL50rwcNjPv_WEtxt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R563" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">564</div></th><td class="s6">Exponential Backoff Retry for Google APIs</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow implements an exponential backoff strategy to handle rate limits and errors when interacting with Google APIs (e.g., Google Sheets). It uses n8n nodes including Google Sheets API via service account, code node for backoff logic, wait node for delays, and error handling to retry up to 5 times with increasing delays.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HALnQW6rVe-QGJF56fRZgw6Agt0TTHwP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R564" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">565</div></th><td class="s6">Export Postgres Data to Excel File</td><td class="s7">This workflow connects to a PostgreSQL database to run a SQL query retrieving product names and EANs, converts the result into an Excel spreadsheet, and saves it as a binary XLS file locally. Utilizes Postgres node, Spreadsheet File node, and Write Binary File node in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wKwDNJRjQ7UNMCYOxCFPiqlcIiZmWihU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R565" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">566</div></th><td class="s6">AI Linux SysAdmin via SSH Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that enables an AI agent (GPT-4o via OpenAI API) to act as a Linux system administrator. It receives chat commands, interprets user intent for Linux VPS management, generates safe SSH commands, and executes them remotely using SSH node, enhancing VPS management automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UVvs4GE-ClMnTVz7PPXDM8VpCQjEEh6a">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R566" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">567</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress Article Text-to-Speech Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieval of WordPress articles, generates summaries or transcriptions with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, converts text to speech using Eleven Labs API, uploads MP3 to WordPress, and updates the post. Integrates WordPress API, LangChain, OpenAI, and Eleven Labs TTS.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1C6ct2daSiclRJJxUaPgFepgiRI0w9-c3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R567" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">568</div></th><td class="s6">AI Video Generator with HeyGen &amp; n8n</td><td class="s7">Automates AI video creation using HeyGen API within n8n. Input text, avatar, and voice IDs to generate and monitor video status. Utilizes HTTP Request, Wait, and If nodes for orchestration. Perfect for creating customizable AI avatar videos programmatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YTc4fFcGiXzxHSlV_clWLDRHGQbG3FhS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R568" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">569</div></th><td class="s6">Automated n8n Workflow Backup to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automatically backs up all n8n workflows daily at 01:30 by retrieving them via the n8n API, encoding the data into JSON files, and uploading them to a specified Google Drive folder. Tech stack: n8n, n8n API, Google Drive API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fc-FvcY6ve08cZ1TTMYOrBAPMqKJN3H2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R569" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">570</div></th><td class="s6">Google Doc Auto-Fill from Web Form</td><td class="s7">This workflow collects form input via n8n Form Trigger, copies a Google Docs template, and replaces placeholders with submitted form data using Google Drive and Google Docs APIs. Enables dynamic document generation from user-submitted fields.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15Gm-zWApPaXnBgNqCf7-D3zBi7QKTR4F">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R570" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">571</div></th><td class="s6">Real Estate Appointment Voice Reminder</td><td class="s7">An automated workflow using Google Calendar API, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for message creation, ElevenLabs Text-to-Speech API to generate voice reminders, and Gmail for sending MP3 voice appointment reminders. Designed for real estate agents to remind clients professionally.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u_E0pXa8vkMZ8KqIKKsGygkMojBQMuhk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R571" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">572</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Orders to Google Sheets Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieving Shopify store orders using Shopify API, handles pagination with page_info, and appends/upserts order data (id, note, email, processed_at) into Google Sheets via Google Sheets API. Includes scheduling and manual triggers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cxSA5JF-z4NkdQBm7cW_A3QfLmMf_SlG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R572" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">573</div></th><td class="s6">Squarespace to Mailchimp Contact Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates adding Squarespace newsletter signups to Mailchimp audience using Google Sheets and Mailchimp APIs. Scheduled or manual triggers ensure new contacts sync despite Squarespace-Mailchimp limitations, improving newsletter audience management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XkbLeDQd9HMX3oovoDhJWrb1cOdUiogH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R573" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">574</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Chinese Vocabulary Tutor Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating a Telegram bot to tutor users in Chinese vocabulary using Google Sheets for word lists, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via Langchain for interactive MCQs, with session memory and feedback. Ideal for language learners.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eY-AGqfYsNbCvC_n1MCDXzv2rGg9PM9V">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R574" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">575</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Automated Fulfillment Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating Shopify order fulfillment by fetching unfulfilled orders, filtering those older than 24 hours, retrieving fulfillment orders via Shopify API, and marking them fulfilled with customer notification. Uses Shopify REST API and n8n core nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12t4VSx8qwIjVqpfUJ1dQj7zlc4YU3F70">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R575" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">576</div></th><td class="s6">n8n AI Assistant for Tool Discovery</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Langchain chat triggers, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and n8n Multi-Channel Platform API to provide an AI assistant. It interacts with users&#39; chat queries about n8n, dynamically looks up and executes relevant tools, delivering tailored, actionable responses on n8n usage and resources.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1a1xlVlTA1UpICt7VgB1Eb8eCQ5J-cswg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R576" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">577</div></th><td class="s6">MediaMarkt Deals Email Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieval of MediaMarkt Spain deals using BrightData proxy, extracts and classifies deal info with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, generates HTML emails via n8n Document Generator, and emails personalized top deals based on user-selected categories. Tech stack: BrightData API, OpenAI API, SMTP email, n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-PvUZYYq_FqeGVMbCfpi1CqaNChpnEoW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R577" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">578</div></th><td class="s6">AI Supply Chain SQL Assistant with BigQuery</td><td class="s7">Workflow integrates OpenAI GPT-4o-mini with an AI agent specialized in SQL for supply chain analytics on BigQuery. It processes user chat input, generates SQL, executes it on Google BigQuery, and returns structured shipment performance results.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Tmuufmi1lNrb55plbHdzQ-Bh1MzHTTZA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R578" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">579</div></th><td class="s6">Notion To Do to Slack Reminder</td><td class="s7">Automates daily checks of Notion to-dos assigned to a specific user, sending reminders via Slack DMs. Utilizes Notion API for task retrieval and Slack API for messaging, triggered every morning at 8AM to streamline task management and notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GyQ1aCLzljnixa1JKn9hRS3k7WxVPQn3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R579" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">580</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Missing Project Budget Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly monitoring of open external projects with zero budgeted cost from a MySQL database. Uses n8n&#39;s MySQL, Switch node for cost center routing, and Microsoft Outlook API to send tailored HTML email alerts to respective cost center teams for timely budget updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gyzMPDrORMCNREctENJBJafsGR3A756m">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R580" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">581</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Newsletter to LinkedIn Auto Posts</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that reads newsletters from Gmail, uses OpenAI to extract and summarize key news items, then auto-generates witty LinkedIn posts for each item. Integrates Gmail API, OpenAI API (o3-mini-2025-01-31 model), and LinkedIn API for seamless content automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MoirnAU9TWtAUKh5GRWwLV3F-cCdqS4E">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R581" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">582</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Resume Screener from Gmail to Sheets</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates screening resumes received as email attachments in Gmail. It extracts PDF text, uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via Langchain to analyze and score resumes, extracts contact info, and saves results to a Google Sheets document. Tech stack: Gmail API, Google Sheets API, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, Langchain integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1f7O59XRsxDgb0Oq8eCKEjfDuV-Br6GMQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R582" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">583</div></th><td class="s6">Incident Resolution &amp; Notification Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates incident status updates by integrating PagerDuty, Jira, and Mattermost via n8n. Resolves incidents in PagerDuty, updates Jira issue status, and posts closure notifications to Mattermost channels, streamlining IT incident management workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jhnXSIG9Clt2unXsRn0p7PxTld6TepVI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R583" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">584</div></th><td class="s6">Dynamic Line Chart Generator with Google Drive Upload</td><td class="s7">Creates a dynamic line chart from JSON data using QuickChart API in n8n and uploads the image to Google Drive. Includes a manual trigger, customizable input data, and flexible chart options for easy visualization and sharing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eUBmhSuSc57B2vCfkbSkOQWnONLti9XD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R584" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">585</div></th><td class="s6">Error Notification via Mattermost &amp; Twilio</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on errors, sends detailed error notifications to Mattermost, and then sends an SMS alert via Twilio. Utilizes n8n errorTrigger node, Mattermost API, and Twilio API to provide real-time monitoring and multi-channel alerting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gQ-91brhWHZ4av34gETrVKVJxJZXsigf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R585" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">586</div></th><td class="s6">Upload Photo to SharePoint via Microsoft Graph</td><td class="s7">Automates uploading a photo to a SharePoint folder using Microsoft Graph API with OAuth2 client credentials. Utilizes HTTP Request and Set nodes in n8n to authenticate, fetch test image, set destination, and upload binary data securely.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ust-SzUIn0LHMosj0C_L9FldJ8hI_gWB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R586" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">587</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Image Generation and Editing Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-image-1 model to generate images from prompts and edit them by adding elements like masks with horns. Features manual trigger, multipart upload, and conversion between base64 and binary PNG files. Ideal for creative image automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1r_W-08UmlOJMVdC7TMSt-cnzvAOUl_6y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R587" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">588</div></th><td class="s6">Facebook Lead Ads to KlickTipp Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates lead capture from Facebook Lead Ads into KlickTipp CRM. Utilizes Facebook Lead Ads Trigger and KlickTipp API nodes in n8n to sync lead data with mapped custom fields and tags for personalized email campaigns and segmentation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1myepji4ZQFX-t3UYAc3h3i9ZybzWpz3y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R588" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">589</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Capture &amp; WhatsApp CRM Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating lead capture via webhook, logging leads in Google Sheets, adding contacts to FluentCRM via its API, sending welcome emails, and WhatsApp messages using Whinta API, then updating CRM tags. Streamlines lead nurturing for small businesses using Google Sheets, FluentCRM, SMTP, and Whinta.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rluY5ffn2yt63mrRitU9bQG04OAfFD9k">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R589" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">590</div></th><td class="s6">Google Autocomplete Keyword Generator A-Z</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that generates keyword queries by appending each letter A-Z to a base keyword, queries Google Autocomplete API to retrieve popular search suggestions, and aggregates results. Utilizes n8n code nodes, HTTP request node, and batch processing to prevent API blocking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BzAvRT9MOaldmNjuWE_UGE9KKNXTolqN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R590" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">591</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Triaged Support Ticket Creation</td><td class="s7">Automates support ticket creation by monitoring a Microsoft Outlook shared inbox, using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to triage and label tickets, then creating issues in JIRA. Tech stack: Outlook API, OpenAI LLM, JIRA API, n8n automation platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1h85nwCylBuNMBK9bAa2PSNTPSOymJd6C">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R591" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">592</div></th><td class="s6">Web Scraper &amp; Product Extractor with GPT-4</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping product data via Brightdata API, cleans HTML, and extracts structured info using OpenRouter GPT-4.1 and Langchain parsers, storing results in Google Sheets. Ideal for e-commerce and market research workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1F_v0YS_oA3D3XGaB5aeVu7WpsQ__ndlQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R592" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">593</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Email Classifier &amp; Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating email processing: reads emails via IMAP, extracts PDF attachments, classifies emails into categories using OpenAI GPT-4o, and extracts applicant details with LangChain nodes. Ideal for automating job application and inquiry triage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vf7KQa7nrZnjI7OpjvfZCTXhm0E1I9t_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R593" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">594</div></th><td class="s6">Automated PDF to HTML Converter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on new PDFs in Google Drive, uses PDF.co API to convert PDFs to HTML, and saves the HTML back to Google Drive. Automates document conversion using Google Drive and PDF.co API for efficient web-ready file creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1e_ksYE7aSU5GxQTtwOCFV1e9ACrPQ05D">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R594" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">595</div></th><td class="s6">Clockify to Syncro Time Tracker Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates time entry synchronization from Clockify to Syncro MSP using n8n. It captures time tracking data via webhook, matches users, updates or creates timers on Syncro via API, and logs entries in Google Sheets. Tech stack: Clockify API, Syncro MSP API, Google Sheets, n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wn22viWGQYlZ4FmqxNto273-XIQFcVKL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R595" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">596</div></th><td class="s6">NameCheap Dynamic DNS Updater</td><td class="s7">Automates updating DNS records on NameCheap via their Dynamic DNS API. Uses n8n workflow with Cron for scheduling, IP check to avoid redundant updates, and HTTP Request nodes for API calls. Ideal for users managing dynamic IPs on multiple subdomains.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1moau4zF6KaKoPKjaidv7Tz3_NfdI6oEg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R596" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">597</div></th><td class="s6">TheHive &amp; SIGNL4 Alert Automation</td><td class="s7">An automated security alert system using TheHive API for incident management and SIGNL4 for alert notifications and resolution. It includes webhook triggers, conditional checks, and supports efficient security operations automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Z0Y08x6H9Uc7LV37bDp-8o-guvhwYP-3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R597" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">598</div></th><td class="s6">Crosspost Articles to Medium &amp; Dev.to</td><td class="s7">Automates posting of articles received via webhook to Medium (using Medium API) and Dev.to (using their REST API). Uses n8n webhook node for data intake and formats posts in Markdown for seamless cross-platform publishing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GTS9QGsG1AnE0Khh40MazgJ9y9dvwJR2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R598" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">599</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify to Odoo Product Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing of new Shopify products to Odoo ERP by detecting new product creation events via Shopify API webhook and updating/creating matching products in Odoo using its API. Built with n8n using Shopify Trigger, Odoo nodes, and custom JS code.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1d9uAPGKZu2lecY4wOecDTSKnAd4thE07">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R599" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">600</div></th><td class="s6">Google Webpage Entity Extraction</td><td class="s7">Extract named entities from any webpage by sending its URL to a webhook that fetches content and uses Google Natural Language API. Tech stack: n8n, HTTP Request, Google Cloud Natural Language API. Returns structured entity data like people, locations, orgs with salience.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Nb6zlhPvwKmrdFl9hz-TDKVb9hl7y3kr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R600" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">601</div></th><td class="s6">Email Threat Analysis Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates email threat detection by reading IMAP emails, creating cases in TheHive, analyzing attachments with Cortex analyzers, and updating observables like domain, IP, and email using TheHive and Cortex APIs for cybersecurity incident response.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TkUOwZClXspdz41eT67I_gOT9ziMDRCm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R601" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">602</div></th><td class="s6">Zammad Support Tickets Summary</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval and categorization of Zammad support tickets using Zammad API, filtering by status, and sends a summary notification to Zulip chat for customer support teams, scheduled via cron for standup meetings.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13wLgGIClcgu_OHz0REAeg4qIACBO23Z6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R602" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">603</div></th><td class="s6">CFP Submission Selection &amp; Visualization</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Airtable, Bannerbear, and Trello to automate selection and visualization of conference talks scoring above 15. It pulls submissions from Airtable, creates custom banners via Bannerbear API, and organizes selected proposals on Trello boards.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13f3ba0p5Ght4OaQeoSkxmj1YhDSwEeqn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R603" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">604</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Receipt Expense Tracker</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates expense tracking by capturing receipt images via Typeform, extracting details with Mindee&#39;s OCR API, and storing expenses in Airtable for easy management and review.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ia-J4Nhiv3AL27ZsjLIRKIJWoVcdwlNY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R604" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">605</div></th><td class="s6">Workflow Failure SMS Alert via Twilio</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses an Error Trigger node and Twilio API integration to send an SMS notification when any workflow fails. It helps monitor workflow executions by alerting users immediately via SMS, ensuring quick response to failures.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sgFAxg8xbM5XcAk5AivhlEGP5sPmyHxh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R605" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">606</div></th><td class="s6">Figma to Jira Auto Version Commenter</td><td class="s7">Automates updating Jira issues with design version info from Figma using n8n. Integrates Figma webhook (file version updates) and Jira Cloud API to find issues and add version comments. Requires Figma Commit Plugin and Jira credentials configured.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mc_EaNhbvL6gRPN92T5ffHb8mTje_p3A">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R606" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">607</div></th><td class="s6">Perplexity AI Research Assistant</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Perplexity AI&#39;s Sonar model via HTTP API to answer research queries. It formats user prompts, sends them to Perplexity AI, and extracts clean, in-depth responses for knowledge discovery and content research automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16XrH0ou_zkm28nHqIVRrNdaFt-Jpf5VC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R607" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">608</div></th><td class="s6">AI Pizza Order Chatbot with OpenAI &amp; HTTP APIs</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow implements Pizzaro, an AI-powered pizza ordering chatbot using OpenAI (ChatGPT) and Langchain nodes. It manages customer orders by retrieving product info, processing orders, and checking status via HTTP webhooks, enhanced with calculator and memory tools.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1e8Q5UNlok4EBhKvgOorb6Zrj5X2IBYip">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R608" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">609</div></th><td class="s6">Slack GitHub User Info Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches GitHub user details including name, company, location, avatar, and emails via GitHub GraphQL API, triggered by Slack messages using Slack webhook and OAuth2 integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13kF7k9yNpwz17fBR1ip7KB8u_JD6PALT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R609" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">610</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Mautic Contact Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing contacts from Google Sheets to Mautic CRM every 5 minutes using Google Sheets API and Mautic API via n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qoYJfmUcMzQB-ZLXdd8T4LxrWiczvvzj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R610" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">611</div></th><td class="s6">Product Feedback Collector &amp; Manager</td><td class="s7">Automates collecting product feedback via Typeform, stores responses in Airtable, and routes low-score feedback to Trello for team review. Integrates Typeform API, Airtable API, and Trello API to streamline feedback management and prioritize action items efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lPNrDw2QouUtGeOfwIwFFgWGm2psnrXi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R611" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">612</div></th><td class="s6">GPT-4o Chatbot with Brave Search Integration</td><td class="s7">An AI chatbot workflow using n8n, featuring GPT-4o via OpenAI, Brave Search API through MCP Client Tools, and short-term memory. It processes chat queries, executes web searches, and provides enriched responses, ideal for developers integrating AI search chatbots.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bWBhuFABN06qfpOTPs6xJnP46dvZZXlF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R612" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">613</div></th><td class="s6">IoT Sensor Data Logger via MQTT &amp; InfluxDB</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses MQTT to receive temperature and humidity data from a remote ESP32 with DHT22 sensor, processes the data with JavaScript, and stores it into an InfluxDB time-series database via HTTP API. Ideal for IoT sensor monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vC7YD75igSgjAC4hhT2B-okhmneszSCs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R613" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">614</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Text-to-Speech Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts text to speech using OpenAI&#39;s TTS API. It accepts text and voice parameters, sends an authenticated HTTP POST request to the OpenAI audio/speech endpoint, and outputs an .mp3 audio file. Designed for easy manual or automated triggering.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1meSGh34-2pk-yBzeHIaN3my0FOcusHGO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R614" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">615</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Sentiment ETL Pipeline</td><td class="s7">Automates daily extraction of #OnThisDay tweets via Twitter API, stores raw tweets in MongoDB, analyzes sentiment using Google Cloud Natural Language API, saves enriched data in PostgreSQL, and sends positive sentiment alerts to Slack. Built with n8n integration platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_ovcJGqhub68DRp_dB0oKINBK50VxyLR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R615" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">616</div></th><td class="s6">Weather Info Fetcher via Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches current weather data for a specified city using OpenWeatherMap API triggered by a webhook. It extracts temperature, humidity, wind speed, description, and city info, delivering structured weather details. Built with n8n, OpenWeatherMap API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wBZMfO66BmJfcZO4gsQUktxEn5MKbHYt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R616" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">617</div></th><td class="s6">Weather SMS Notification via Webhook &amp; Airtable</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow receives POST webhook with user data, stores it in Airtable, fetches current weather via OpenWeatherMap API for the specified city, then sends weather details by SMS using Twilio. Integrates Webhook, Airtable, OpenWeatherMap, and Twilio APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Tlah-5vCbmU6f7h1BnjqJX3salAwVCyT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R617" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">618</div></th><td class="s6">Receipt OCR to Airtable Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates receipt data extraction using Mindee OCR API from uploaded receipts via webhook, then logs categorized expense details like merchant, date, total, and currency into Airtable. Uses n8n webhook, Mindee OCR, and Airtable API for expense tracking automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1INKX0vHtopSez5SE3GDQjrdkXjNvHu57">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R618" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">619</div></th><td class="s6">Receipt Data Extraction via Mindee API</td><td class="s7">Automates extracting detailed information from receipt images using Mindee OCR API. Retrieves an image via HTTP request, then extracts structured data like totals, dates, and vendor info. Useful for expense tracking and accounting automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WA6qQBPNWSOUWqOzc6niBmyNu0sxZzZV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R619" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">620</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Coffee Group Bot for Mattermost</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly virtual coffee meetups by grouping Mattermost users into random teams of 3 and sending invites via Google Calendar. Utilizes Mattermost API, Google Calendar API, cron scheduling, and JavaScript for dynamic group creation to foster team bonding.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1v__NN5UK-YC6PF0GHToQ0aYzoHdP9Tla">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R620" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">621</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Language Learning with Hacker News</td><td class="s7">Automates daily extraction of top 3 Hacker News article titles, extracts and translates unique words to German using LingvaNex API, stores results in Airtable, and sends a curated vocabulary list via SMS with Vonage API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1M_hMPGLhlJipzDpRynZtiwnv-hR0b4AZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R621" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">622</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce New Product Alert to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates notifications in Slack for new WooCommerce product creations. Utilizes WooCommerce API webhook trigger to capture new product events and Slack API to send detailed messages including product name, price, sale price, link, and creation date to a specified Slack channel.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1k7I6fiAATdp1gCt-siJGnRic-p3UeeQK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R622" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">623</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow GitHub Backup Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates backup and synchronization of n8n workflows to a GitHub repo using n8n HTTP Request, GitHub API, and JavaScript. It detects new, changed, or identical workflows and updates GitHub accordingly. Scheduled to run daily for workflow backup automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uh8TqT-rDSt7pCkZWvzJiKi2Ugz5Q0Mm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R623" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">624</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Image Editing with Chat Trigger</td><td class="s7">Automate image editing using OpenAI ImageGen API triggered by chat messages. Uses n8n workflow with HTTP Request node to call OpenAI, converts response to file, supports image input via chat webhook, enabling seamless AI-based image editing and integration into custom automations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FW7YeCH65RhSndaBVpjRt0oIJ2Rpw2Bl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R624" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">625</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce New Order Alert to Slack</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on new WooCommerce orders over $100 and sends detailed notifications to a Slack channel. Integrates WooCommerce webhook API with Slack API to automate real-time order alerts for efficient sales tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KnJWru-JO2UKae-wwvZswq4dqslqOWmy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R625" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">626</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Orbit Member Sync</td><td class="s7">Sync and upsert member and activity data from Google Sheets to Orbit workspace using Google Sheets API and Orbit API integration in n8n. Automates community metrics management with OAuth2 authentication and data merging by GitHub usernames.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LK-3XQTC2tMIzK2EZlFrOLY1kFhOcGZj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R626" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">627</div></th><td class="s6">Automizy Contact List Management</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses Automizy&#39;s API to create a contact list, add a new contact, update contact tags, and retrieve all contacts in the list. It automates email marketing contact management seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wvcf03-cpJ902mk-snAKNHZM_4E8gcX9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R627" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">628</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Weather Push Notifications via Pushcut</td><td class="s7">Automates sending daily 9AM weather updates for Berlin using OpenWeatherMap API and Pushcut push notifications in n8n. Ideal for timely personalized weather alerts leveraging cron scheduling and No-Code automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MVAgbl_8kFTX2YwtRivqH6vCiNh0RIki">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R628" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">629</div></th><td class="s6">Matrix Room Creation &amp; Invitation Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates creating a Matrix chat room, inviting members from another room, and sending a welcome message. Utilizes Matrix API for room and user management, with conditional logic to avoid re-inviting the creator, enabling seamless community onboarding.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1II3ujJ20qnADJzYWEO98bYUqe_Gg-H_R">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R629" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">630</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce Customer Sync to Mautic</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing WooCommerce customers to Mautic CRM using WooCommerce webhooks and Mautic API with OAuth2. Checks if customer exists in Mautic, then creates or updates contact. Ideal for seamless marketing integration and CRM updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kV1fDAezSZntdq_5NHD66OW3fwpnIYGl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R630" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">631</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Weather SMS via Vonage</td><td class="s7">Automates sending daily weather updates for Berlin at 9 AM using OpenWeatherMap API and Vonage SMS service via n8n workflow with Cron scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1DeLvNlDxOuayd-VBZUjiF9A-i5JlE-4X">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R631" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">632</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce New Product Announcement to Twitter &amp; Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates announcing new WooCommerce products on Twitter and Telegram. Uses WooCommerce webhook trigger, Twitter API, and Telegram API to post customized new product messages instantly, enhancing social media marketing and customer engagement.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JKrOx6faqWfZoMgOr2Hfr6LXL8QdHe05">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R632" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">633</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Mattermost Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of a Google Sheet using OAuth2, checks for new entries every 45 minutes, and sends real-time Mattermost notifications with new data details. Utilizes n8n workflow nodes: Google Sheets API, custom JavaScript function, interval trigger, and Mattermost API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12ALY1zqZlxZTS_8aLeFE5VYWnGuS8cPT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R633" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">634</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Enhancer with Bright Data Search</td><td class="s7">Enhances chat responses by integrating Google Gemini AI with real-time web search via Bright Data MCP Client tools (Google, Bing, Yandex). Automates AI agent queries, uses memory buffering, and sends notifications via webhook. Ideal for informed, dynamic chat assistants.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17SeVI82gVfpShu7FVWfrT2w0QKKWTIMp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R634" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">635</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Messaging Agent (Text/Audio/Image)</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram Bot API and OpenAI to handle Telegram messages via webhook. It processes text, voice (audio), and images with AI models for transcription, classification, and analysis, enabling intelligent interaction and automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wmnRGFgQFZzonyyY--JM5Bymj65hJhyV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R635" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">636</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Google Calendar MCP Server</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow integrates OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o model with Google Calendar API to build an AI assistant managing calendar events via MCP server-client tools. It supports creating, updating, deleting, and searching events, plus additional AI utilities like text case conversion, joke retrieval, and random user data generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CLPV5NWyqygSws1lc9mgqlJzDaXCoqjC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R636" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">637</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform to Airtable with Slack Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates form submission handling by triggering on Typeform responses, extracting name and email, appending them to Airtable, and sending a Slack notification. Uses Typeform API, Airtable API, and Slack API for seamless data flow and real-time alerts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1C6ZRTJqMKV1MYXxxTfIhnB2nFYLa3eYH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R637" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">638</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice Email Alert &amp; Approval Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates invoice detection from Gmail using IMAP, extracts total amounts with Mindee Invoice API, sends Slack alerts, and emails finance manager for high-value invoices above $1000. Integrates Gmail, Mindee, Slack, and SMTP for seamless invoice workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_6Btlju1Y2pC0uQpK1z3DurCJ7lWapk_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R638" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">639</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Weather Push Notification</td><td class="s7">Automates daily weather updates for Berlin via OpenWeatherMap API, sending temperatures as push notifications using Pushover. Triggered by a Cron job running at 9 AM. Ideal for users wanting timely, automatic local weather alerts on their devices.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18QNds0Eo4mk1BXGLLlGvodquOtaPQMFt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R639" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">640</div></th><td class="s6">SecurityScorecard Report Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating the generation and download of full SecurityScorecard reports for a given domain using the SecurityScorecard API. It triggers manually and sequentially fetches, limits, then downloads JSON scorecard data for security insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19lcb94aHrLVBHleygyChosb2XdcxZtru">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R640" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">641</div></th><td class="s6">GetResponse to Airtable Subscriber Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing new GetResponse email subscribers via webhook and appends their name and email to an Airtable base. Uses GetResponse API webhook triggers and Airtable API integration to streamline email list management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10e7u4acSzv_MwCUBRqqlS6LhtpKoSPb_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R641" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">642</div></th><td class="s6">QuickBooks Invoice Automation Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates customer creation, invoice generation, and email sending in QuickBooks using OAuth2 API integration within n8n workflow. Streamlines accounting tasks by chaining customer creation, invoice creation, and invoice emailing efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14KLWwYl6l2zmwEC5Ov48x-wl2DqoD29Q">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R642" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">643</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Mention Alert to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring Twitter for mentions of a specified company every 10 minutes using Twitter API; formats tweet info and posts alerts to Slack channel. Utilizes n8n, Twitter OAuth1 API, Slack API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GAZIHTEVrlc6-FvqgD_sldIHCPJiW3OP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R643" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">644</div></th><td class="s6">MailerLite Subscriber Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrates with MailerLite API to create, update, and retrieve email subscribers. It automates managing subscriber data including custom fields like city using MailerLite nodes triggered manually. Ideal for email marketing automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sZYsqtE1AxEOWGs-odAN1RoXGJKU3BnZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R644" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">645</div></th><td class="s6">Weather Info via Webhook API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that provides current weather data via a webhook. Utilizes OpenWeatherMap API to fetch temperature and &#39;feels like&#39; info based on city query parameters, returning formatted weather details in English.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Fv-hAgkG1-MbYh3bRc2mKd2ky2MXw56W">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R645" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">646</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform to PDF Invoice Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates invoice generation by triggering on Typeform submissions and using APITemplate.io to create customized PDF invoices. Utilizes Typeform API for form data capture and APITemplate.io API for dynamic PDF creation and download.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jI46tr85xECuRtN0V_6vACKPRkx73PJH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R646" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">647</div></th><td class="s6">Wise Transfer Event to Airtable Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates logging of Wise money transfer events into Airtable by triggering on transfer state changes using Wise API, then fetching transfer details and appending structured data (ID, date, reference, amount) to Airtable. Integrates Wise API and Airtable with n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1r9pdzwvUae8T56wP_mTv3q-6z4FE-RER">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R647" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">648</div></th><td class="s6">Google Trends Data Extract &amp; Summarize</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Google Trends data using Bright Data proxy and web unlocker, followed by structured data extraction and summarization via Google Gemini AI (PaLM). Outputs summaries via email and webhook, enabling insightful trend analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Z-VQpP9VkltNs1VW8TG-SaJtL8Ieb3e4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R648" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">649</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Birthday Reminders from Google Contacts to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval of Google Contacts with birthdays, filters for today&#39;s birthdays, and sends reminders to Slack channels using Google Contacts API and Slack API. Scheduled to run at 8 AM daily, ideal for team and personal birthday notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ti1pz9Eu5UVXbf1WXwvkiT4vM3Nb-xK1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R649" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">650</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Assisted Human-in-Loop Email Reply System</td><td class="s7">Automates email handling by using IMAP to read emails, converts content to Markdown, summarizes it with Langchain OpenAI models, generates professional replies via AI, and integrates human approval before sending replies via SMTP. Tech stack: n8n, OpenAI GPT-4, Langchain, IMAP/SMTP.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NNW0ZIn7PylF0KterKbG8P9-DgwHwCA5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R650" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">651</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Files to Google Drive Auto-Saver</td><td class="s7">Automates saving files received via Telegram messages directly to Google Drive using Telegram API and Google Drive API in an n8n workflow. Ideal for backing up or organizing documents sent on Telegram automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15BfTiL9oDsHKpJ19H2YzSQNplUJ-kQyX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R651" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">652</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chatbot with Multi-Session Management</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered Telegram chatbot workflow using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Langchain for conversational AI, integrated with Google Sheets for multi-session management, command handling (/new, /current, /resume, /summary, /question), and context-based memory. Enables robust user chat experience via Telegram API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ff-y2LxdXcrEQdFWE9j6E7rAuBpILL8g">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R652" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">653</div></th><td class="s6">Email Natural Language to SQL Query</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts natural language questions about a PostgreSQL email metadata database into SQL queries using the Ollama language model. It automates schema extraction, enforces strict schema adherence, and returns query results from the emails_metadata table.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fUswOvR4tgEwymrzehNHjpmxnUIzdd_2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R653" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">654</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform Feedback Sentiment &amp; Task Automator</td><td class="s7">Automates processing of Typeform feedback by analyzing sentiment with Google Cloud NLP. Positive feedback triggers entries to Notion and Trello, and notifications sent via Slack. Integrates Typeform, Google Cloud Natural Language API, Notion, Trello, and Slack for streamlined feedback management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ul8IiiRMbIi8PM1Rqkz3c3g30bEZK6C3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R654" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">655</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Agent with LangChain &amp; DALL·E Integration</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow creating a Telegram AI chatbot using LangChain nodes and OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o for conversational AI, with DALL·E-3 for image generation. It listens to Telegram messages, maintains context memory, generates AI responses, and sends text or AI-generated images back to users.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TLSqpuQ3i3Qifhq9xpFmpJCiUtWcrCuD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R655" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">656</div></th><td class="s6">Amazon Ads AI Optimization Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automate Amazon Ads report processing with Google Drive, Excel/CSV data extraction, and GPT-4o AI analysis to generate actionable optimization recommendations. Uses n8n nodes, Google Drive API, OpenAI GPT-4o, and Gmail to email insights for bid, budget, and keyword strategies.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Oa86zCzsDZ8vsCzzRh4pELmAXQphwD_b">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R656" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">657</div></th><td class="s6">AI Summary Generator for WordPress Posts</td><td class="s7">Automates adding AI-generated summaries to WordPress posts using OpenAI (GPT-4o-mini), Google Sheets for tracking, and Slack for notifications. Converts post HTML to Markdown, classifies summarized content, updates posts via WP REST API, and logs activity efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BgXj0rVIm3CcJbYMQxsh3TOvc3Q9oLEj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R657" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">658</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Agent with SerpAPI Search</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow combining OpenAI GPT-4o-mini chat model, SerpAPI for live search, and a window buffer memory to create an AI Agent that responds to chat messages dynamically with up-to-date information from the web.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Mahqvx8HBlOQnIuACG54NQ53_qT7mTXW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R658" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">659</div></th><td class="s6">AI Agent for Webpage Content Extraction</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow combining LangChain AI (ReAct agent) and OpenAI GPT-4 to fetch, clean, and convert webpage HTML content to Markdown. It uses HTTP requests, regex for HTML body extraction, and options to simplify or fully preserve content for intelligent web data retrieval and processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16VvK0DV_ZsWsofevk5-6ozDghpCwHef3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R659" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">660</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable AI Assistant Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Airtable API to process user chat requests, query Airtable bases and tables, and perform data aggregation and visualization. Enables dynamic, AI-driven interactions for managing Airtable data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tIGWI3ViZDE8bUf2UsGZ5fOG4KjUo21U">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R660" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">661</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Agent for Google Search Console Data</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o and Google Search Console API via OAuth2, using Postgres for chat memory. Enables natural language chat to query, retrieve, and display Search Console insights with a friendly AI agent, supporting customizable date ranges and dimensions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zAPDFKFfwNaQf1uB8YqB3tj-V06c_MmZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R661" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">662</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Agent with Wiki &amp; Weather Tools</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Ollama LLM chat model, Wikipedia and Open-Meteo APIs, plus LangChain memory, to create a conversational AI assistant. It uses buffered chat history, fetches weather by coordinates, and retrieves Wikipedia info to answer user queries interactively.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10PCabHVrOFA5qAaBTCQHauD9pMicvNmr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R662" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">663</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered HR CV Processing &amp; Evaluation</td><td class="s7">Automates job application processing: candidates submit CVs via a form, PDFs are extracted, AI extracts qualifications and personal data using LangChain and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, evaluates fit against a company profile, and logs results to Google Sheets. Integrates Google Drive and Sheets APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xQTfHMccT7oUJU6TgzF1JjS3JsEKSyEv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R663" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">664</div></th><td class="s6">AI Agent with Hacker News Data Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating LangChain AI agent with OpenAI chat and Hacker News API to fetch and process top posts data. Enables querying Hacker News popular posts through AI chat, combining AI and real-time data fetch for interactive insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1i77nQ1xdcjyFecNrsAI_c4jwbvhzDLNB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R664" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">665</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat Agent with Wikipedia &amp; Web Search Tools</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow creating a conversational AI agent using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, integrated with LangChain memory buffer, Wikipedia and SerpAPI search tools. It processes manual chat inputs and leverages external knowledge sources to answer queries contextually.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xg0EHI50EbmDWnyZdPTdNF9tVcsuy2b4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R665" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">666</div></th><td class="s6">Stock Market Q&amp;A AI Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow leveraging OpenAI embeddings, Qdrant vector store, and Google Drive PDFs to enable Q&amp;A over stock market documents. It extracts data via Google Drive, processes with OpenAI and LangChain, and answers queries through a webhook API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1z1Ezd1FYI5umPPPjZZgx3AiRYICeFEd6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R666" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">667</div></th><td class="s6">Customer Feedback Sentiment Analysis</td><td class="s7">Automates sentiment classification of customer feedback using an OpenAI API with form input, then logs categorized responses into Google Sheets for easy tracking and analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HAb4zFU2lbEBSEBtbervM81s5wijsw0P">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R667" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">668</div></th><td class="s6">AI Data Extraction for Baserow PDFs</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of data from PDFs uploaded to Baserow tables using dynamic user-defined prompts and OpenAI&#39;s LLM API. It integrates Baserow webhook events, Baserow API, PDF extraction, and LangChain LLM nodes within n8n to auto-fill table fields based on PDF content and field descriptions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13opXQZThBixtdJ7A-EScgjbtrFyxiRx3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R668" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">669</div></th><td class="s6">AI Social Media Caption Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates generating creative Instagram captions using n8n workflow with OpenAI GPT-4 and Airtable. It triggers on new Airtable records with briefing data, enriches context via background info, crafts captions via a Langchain AI Agent, and updates Airtable editorial plans seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18PqF8aBmC9P4N7SmmGlMMqHqRIt5IMAT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R669" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">670</div></th><td class="s6">Children&#39;s Storytelling Automation on Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates creating and sharing children’s English stories on Telegram using OpenAI GPT-3.5 for story and character generation, DALL-E for illustrations, and Telegram API for delivery every 12 hours.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1liCqgrCN90mvhzOgkkkE7B1-zic2g7s0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R670" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">671</div></th><td class="s6">AI Email Auto-responder &amp; Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates email response by reading IMAP emails, converting content to markdown, summarizing with DeepSeek and OpenAI models, classifying, and generating concise replies reviewed and sent automatically. Integrates Google Drive for document vectorization with Qdrant and uses OpenAI and DeepSeek APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gRM_VD0dVCpa4A_hfdw9wxUiAqvKRIgw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R671" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">672</div></th><td class="s6">Stock Earnings Report RAG Analysis Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates financial analysis of Google&#39;s last 3 quarters earnings by loading PDFs from Google Drive, creating embeddings via Google Gemini, storing/retrieving with Pinecone vector DB, and generating detailed markdown reports saved to Google Docs using AI agents.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1I_B2svWFUFNkHBWY67Q6JxHM72CqMBUW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R672" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">673</div></th><td class="s6">AI Social Media Auto-Poster from Hacker News</td><td class="s7">Automates curation and posting of trending GitHub projects from Hacker News to Twitter and LinkedIn using OpenAI GPT-4, Airtable, Telegram, and n8n. Extracts GitHub links, generates engaging content, schedules posts, and prevents duplicates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16UHp1vq8l-F5bdZoNaTKVlgiCMyE0K_s">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R673" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">674</div></th><td class="s6">Podcast Transcript Summarizer &amp; Digest Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates summarization of podcast transcripts using n8n with LangChain, OpenAI GPT-3.5 &amp; GPT-4, and Wikipedia API. Extracts key topics, generates questions, researches explanations, formats as HTML, and emails a comprehensive episode digest.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18rJvXaZK7X4f-51p0PzKufOACR6_fuV_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R674" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">675</div></th><td class="s6">Automated RSS News Aggregator &amp; Trello Notifier</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow aggregating news from multiple RSS feeds, filtering recent articles, formatting them in Markdown, and posting summaries as Trello card comments with email notifications. Integrates RSS, Trello API, and Gmail via OAuth2 for streamlined team updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tbpsm2adUrXL61kEDQo1a0UgCj5qKEZF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R675" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">676</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Travel Assistant with Google Drive Docs</td><td class="s7">Builds a custom OpenAI-powered travel assistant integrated with Google Drive to upload and convert travel agency documents to PDF, updating assistant knowledge. Uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, Langchain memory buffer, and Google Drive API for contextual chat interaction.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1w6ImB3ADYgPZWEJcB8vKobU4n1hdUsTb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R676" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">677</div></th><td class="s6">USDT ERC-20 Wallet Balance Monitor with Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of USDT ERC-20 wallet balances using Etherscan API. Sends Telegram notifications on balance changes. Utilizes n8n workflow with Cron triggers, HTTP request node for Etherscan API, JavaScript code for change detection, and Telegram node for alerts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12136lfm1pfAYhRbkRw0hASsdGWQqk1LJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R677" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">678</div></th><td class="s6">Hugging Face Paper Auto-Import to Notion</td><td class="s7">Automates daily extraction of research papers from Hugging Face, uses HTML scraping, OpenAI GPT-4O for abstract analysis, and stores enriched metadata in Notion. Integrates Hugging Face API, OpenAI API, and Notion API for academic paper management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pZoCnleGnBehCb5vpb7FdHUwLf6xrtkD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R678" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">679</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform Feedback Sentiment to Mattermost</td><td class="s7">Automates sentiment analysis of event feedback submitted via Typeform using Google Cloud Natural Language API, then sends a sentiment score and message to a Mattermost channel. Integrates Typeform, Google NLP, and Mattermost for real-time feedback monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vYGIaR4gnAE2Og4GT9JJrBFQHNwei-08">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R679" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">680</div></th><td class="s6">Bing Copilot Search Results Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and summarization of Bing Copilot search results using Bright Data API for data scraping and Google Gemini AI for natural language processing and structured data formatting. Delivers structured JSON data and concise summaries via webhooks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dd2RUL34gOY2jab_jXF4UZ4J31lAaOf8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R680" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">681</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Image Generator via Web Form</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that generates images using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-Image-1 model. It accepts prompt and size inputs through a web form, calls the OpenAI API, converts the base64 image data to a file, and returns the generated image for download. Uses OpenAI API and n8n form/webhook nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hMjiZXPvagIyKUwYHjPBHlmW_cerlHHC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R681" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">682</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive to Pinecone FAISS Chatbot</td><td class="s7">Automates document ingestion from Google Drive, splits text for processing, generates OpenAI embeddings, stores/retrieves in Pinecone vector DB, enabling chatbot Q&amp;A with LangChain in n8n workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RDEC6tZwb6JgJ8iDPT7EuHOuWcu7o8P5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R682" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">683</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Driven WordPress Post Categorizer</td><td class="s7">Automates WordPress blog post categorization using OpenAI&#39;s language model integrated via n8n. Fetches posts, classifies by predefined taxonomy, and updates categories natively in WordPress. Ideal for content strategists seeking efficient organization and SEO improvements.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1V4CD5J6acUVeqkT08fXfYwT69ik_zPn4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R683" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">684</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Company Review &amp; News Insights</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4, SerpApi, and Notion API to automate gathering and analyzing company reviews, news, and product offerings. It scrapes review sites, summarizes pros/cons, tracks sentiment, and updates Notion for competitive analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1w1-toD1l2ckkVr5C7TsPJrSvBMq4LA1i">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R684" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">685</div></th><td class="s6">AI Passport Photo Validator</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that imports portrait photos from Google Drive, resizes images, and uses Google Gemini AI vision model to validate passport photo compliance against UK government criteria. Includes structured output parsing for automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hqetKvlHJaiPtFwcm64rkhCEoNYGOuyY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R685" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">686</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Sentiment Filter &amp; Strapi Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching recent English tweets about Strapi or n8n.io every 30 mins, filters out retweets/old tweets, analyzes sentiment using Google Cloud Natural Language API, and stores only positive sentiment tweets and form submissions into a Strapi CMS collection.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HDaOkUI3kfxG6eG16XNorBdHOCtR4kGZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R686" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">687</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Fine-Tuning Workflow with Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates fine-tuning of OpenAI GPT models using training data stored on Google Drive. Uses n8n with Google Drive API to download a .jsonl training file, uploads it to OpenAI for fine-tuning, and triggers a custom fine-tuned GPT-4o-mini chat model via Langchain integration for interactive AI responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nzl5ZBjTFauhNrcrycN_YFeogqUYAN08">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R687" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">688</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Remove &amp; Replace Image Backgrounds on Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates background removal and replacement for images in Google Drive using Photoroom API and Google Drive integration. It watches a folder, processes images with customizable settings (background color, padding, output size), and uploads the results back to Drive.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PgDF1ZRSoNy2k14zDiK5lrM8vIV8Lbw_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R688" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">689</div></th><td class="s6">Automated YouTube to X Post Generator</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates fetching the latest YouTube videos, uses OpenAI GPT-4O-MINI to generate engaging X (Twitter) posts under 220 characters, and posts them automatically via the X API. It also logs posts in Google Sheets and supports Slack, Discord, and Gmail notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sWfBawuqPkP9xD5JLSmuL3jdHRXhwgd5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R689" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">690</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail to Telegram Keyword Alert</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow monitors Gmail for incoming emails and forwards only those with specific keywords (e.g., &#39;Urgent&#39;, &#39;Server Down&#39;) in the subject to a Telegram chat. It uses Gmail API for email triggers and Telegram API for messaging, enabling real-time filtered notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Qa57oqizQGPSFyC3t5fgABqDaFkYmG01">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R690" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">691</div></th><td class="s6">Weather Updates via Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching weather forecasts using OpenStreetMap and US National Weather Service APIs, then posts detailed weather info to Slack channels via OAuth2 authentication. Ideal for real-time weather notifications triggered by Slack messages.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jtNfL_cGjqkuL4aJFVuWWQ7ktQPt3PwU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R691" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">692</div></th><td class="s6">n8n AI Creator Leaderboard Stats</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches and aggregates n8n community creator and workflow stats from GitHub JSONs, merges data by username, filters per creator, and uses OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini AI agent to generate detailed Markdown reports on creator impact, workflow popularity, and community trends.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11138fqp03GyFdyAdPqARHayG_FLxivbt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R692" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">693</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Deployment Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates deployment of n8n workflows by monitoring a Google Drive folder for JSON workflow files. Uses Google Drive API, n8n API with authenticated requests to create workflows, apply tags, and move files between Drive folders, streamlining workflow management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mtaN6RHfrQ0OoFUD-jQrt6UyVimhl0up">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R693" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">694</div></th><td class="s6">Bitrix24 Chatbot Webhook Automation</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow implements a chatbot for Bitrix24 using webhook integration. It handles events like message addition, bot joining chat, app install, and bot deletion through Bitrix24 REST API. It validates tokens, processes messages, and registers the bot, enabling custom conversational automations within Bitrix24.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QSq1sQaQ6USueYXq-DiWguie92A9ngcV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R694" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">695</div></th><td class="s6">AI Health Insurance Chatbot System</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates an AI-powered chatbot for health insurance inquiries using OpenAI assistants, PostgreSQL for chat memory, MySQL for product queries, and external APIs. It dynamically personalizes responses based on user data to recommend insurance plans and access knowledge bases.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=161FNoCXS3hXkDY7gyqaPbpu529mbFuey">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R695" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">696</div></th><td class="s6">Line Pay Slip Text Extractor with Gemini AI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating LINE Messaging API, Google Gemini AI, and Google Sheets to extract and classify text from pay slip images or text messages. It auto-analyzes images with Gemini 2.0, parses key payment details, replies via LINE, and logs data into Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jVW57TEUjBrVE4bAbmziJKEJt7R2bhzj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R696" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">697</div></th><td class="s6">OpenSea NFT Marketplace Agent</td><td class="s7">AI-powered n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o Mini with OpenSea API to fetch and analyze NFT listings, offers, orders, and trait-specific data. Enables informed NFT trading decisions with features like best offers, listings by collection, and detailed order lookups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1j_ed72ihFEXTPUONAeg9jCXAmrkoOiL3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R697" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">698</div></th><td class="s6">Texas Tax Code AI Assistant</td><td class="s7">An automated workflow using n8n that downloads Texas tax code PDFs, extracts sections, generates Mistral.ai embeddings, stores them in Qdrant vectorstore, and provides a chatbot powered by OpenAI to answer tax-related questions with precise citations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qGrPeLOSOb1kiln1s4olezYmErkC1fU8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R698" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">699</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Travel Assistant with Google Drive Docs</td><td class="s7">Automates building and updating a GPT-4-powered travel assistant using OpenAI API and Google Drive integration. It downloads travel documents, converts them to PDF, uploads to OpenAI, and enables interactive chat with context memory. Ideal for travel agencies seeking AI support.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pAa_8U6rfe5sG1zYRH3pWeWj6KxTsyBL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R699" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">700</div></th><td class="s6">Image Object Extraction and Elasticsearch Indexing</td><td class="s7">Automates image processing by using Cloudflare Detr-Resnet-50 AI to detect objects in images, crops identified objects, uploads them to Cloudinary, and indexes them in Elasticsearch for advanced image search by object. Built with n8n, Cloudflare Workers AI, Cloudinary, and Elasticsearch.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rXzn9VtVMoi3E9IRfsNDkZmWgGLWR-Ps">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R700" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">701</div></th><td class="s6">WhatsApp AI Sales Chatbot with Vector Store</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating WhatsApp API, OpenAI GPT-4o, and in-memory vector store to build an AI Sales Agent chatbot. It processes product brochure PDFs, creates embeddings and vector store for product catalog, handles WhatsApp messages, and replies with AI-powered responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qW0EJU_j0h8qIuXhhdtbcNuAPat23vis">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R701" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">702</div></th><td class="s6">AI Auto-Categorize WordPress Posts</td><td class="s7">Automate WordPress blog post categorization using OpenAI&#39;s language model with n8n. This workflow fetches all posts, applies AI-based taxonomy classification, and updates categories via the WordPress API, streamlining content organization for bloggers and marketers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1P8oDLXSuHtDBYoIbDzE4KEFseC_zkmjt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R702" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">703</div></th><td class="s6">Document Analysis &amp; Chatbot Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates document submission, parsing (via LlamaIndex API), translation, analysis, and Q&amp;A chatbot interaction using Google Gemini models, Mistral embeddings, Pinecone vector DB, and Gmail for email delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ogTAI33_VssRYidhPzfsIxixfgjE2aKb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R703" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">704</div></th><td class="s6">Webflow Form to Discord Channel Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates sending Webflow form submissions to Discord by creating dedicated channels per form via the Discord Bot API and Webflow API. Dynamically manages channels and notifies #general with links using n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1va1Hiwyk3zJA9wUsVMcgf4dQzsbS8z72">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R704" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">705</div></th><td class="s6">AI Health Insurance Chatbot with Database</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered chatbot workflow integrating OpenAI assistants, PostgreSQL chat memory, MySQL product querying, and external APIs for personalized health insurance advice. Designed to capture user data, maintain session context, query product offers, and respond via chat with dynamic knowledge base access.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fhiqnvpihHtOSycPmHHMaFj1ZbYkDxz6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R705" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">706</div></th><td class="s6">AI Agent for Interactive Google Sheets Chat</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-3.5-turbo with Google Sheets via API, enabling users to query spreadsheet data conversationally. It includes custom tools to list columns, fetch rows, and get column values dynamically, making complex sheet data accessible through natural language.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15lA2YmmOXCaD8Or_Y91m_gVKb2wiyGFH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R706" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">707</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub API Chatbot with RAG &amp; Pinecone</td><td class="s7">An n8n RAG workflow that fetches GitHub OpenAPI specs, generates embeddings using OpenAI, indexes info in Pinecone vector DB, and enables chat queries with GPT-4o-mini. Provides contextual API guidance via conversational AI.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-cjrzo6sR4jvSD1gVlnHzNpaSLZY7_Lk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R707" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">708</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chat with Memory and Calculator Tools</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow enables an AI chat assistant using OpenAI&#39;s API with session memory management and a calculator tool via LangChain nodes, allowing interactive and context-aware conversations with users through a webhook trigger.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TynGkCWNHR6Vvg3LbmgpaeMH0bkpIl6k">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R708" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">709</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Chat with PostgreSQL DB</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow enables interactive chat with a PostgreSQL database using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini model and LangChain agent. It automatically generates and executes SQL queries based on user prompts, fetching schema and table info dynamically for accurate DB responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lIUBOJmCIlA2AK7XYAbNflQN0oJW5lI2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R709" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">710</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Meetup Scheduler</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram bot with OpenRouter LLM and Google Sheets API to provide AI-driven meetup scheduling assistance. It processes chat inputs, retrieves schedules from Google Sheets, converts them to markdown, and responds intelligently via Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VQsO5zy3AQU9NNznLKOAxX7TaFf2g9W5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R710" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">711</div></th><td class="s6">GitLab Merge Request AI Reviewer</td><td class="s7">Automates code review for GitLab merge requests using GitLab API and OpenAI&#39;s LLM. It fetches code changes, parses diffs, and posts detailed, scored review comments directly to merge request discussions, streamlining code quality checks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Fy29phwweJt-EKgP_HM67KORc4UP_ujc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R711" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">712</div></th><td class="s6">Yelp Review Extractor &amp; Summarizer with LLM</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Yelp business reviews using Bright Data API and processes data with Google Gemini LLM for structured analysis and summarization. Integrates web scraping, AI parsing, and webhook notifications for streamlined review insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1R8JulmV1ZP9ENGcIJUch-jSJLJOuD_6v">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R712" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">713</div></th><td class="s6">Lemlist Reply Automation with Slack &amp; OpenAI</td><td class="s7">Automates handling of Lemlist email replies using OpenAI GPT-4 for classification and sends categorized alerts to Slack. Also manages unsubscribe and interested lead statuses via Lemlist API. Integrates Lemlist, OpenAI GPT-4, Slack, and n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QQoKHOBpjN-tUmJY-qb77vgfeDRVhnoL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R713" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">714</div></th><td class="s6">Linear Bug Ticket Auto-Classifier</td><td class="s7">Automates classification of bug tickets in Linear using OpenAI GPT-4. It filters issues that need triage, classifies bugs by team responsibility (customizable), updates Linear tickets, and notifies Slack if classification fails. Tech: Linear API, OpenAI GPT-4, Slack API, n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1C7OKgS4lwtWj7viyIFUZhOFyVFNa12Ov">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R714" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">715</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Text-to-Speech Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts text to speech using OpenAI&#39;s TTS API. It sets input text and voice, then sends a request to OpenAI&#39;s API to produce an MP3 audio output. Ideal for automating TTS tasks with OpenAI&#39;s tts-1 model.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1p8qwoxkSdztt6wmfuHG_DmxnXsC9TpDl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R715" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">716</div></th><td class="s6">Google Calendar to Telegram Event Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates posting new Google Calendar events to Telegram chats using Google Calendar API and Telegram Bot API. Sends event details like name, description, location, and time to keep you updated instantly via Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Eod-OyQHiiDj9Z38ps8JqrkymndOjzl1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R716" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">717</div></th><td class="s6">Google Maps Lead Generation with Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates lead generation by querying Google Maps Places API based on zip codes and subcategories from Google Sheets. It fetches business details, deduplicates results, and updates the sheet. Uses n8n with Google Maps API, Google Sheets, and implements retries with exponential backoff.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18wcMkBcSu5pApyyxCnqjCo3JEkuy5OLO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R717" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">718</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Google Analytics Report Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly Google Analytics data retrieval (last 7 days &amp; same period previous year), AI-generated summary &amp; analysis (OpenAI GPT-4O), and report delivery via email (SMTP) and Telegram. Scheduled every Monday at 7 AM for actionable insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HQy-r-_Aok-8NSjfyEah62fF44blI14Y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R718" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">719</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter New Followers Banner Updater</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching latest Twitter followers, processes their profile images by resizing and cropping into circular icons, composites them onto a customizable banner template, and updates your Twitter profile banner using Twitter API and n8n image editing nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LilszWvm8ChLF64icPXNxIetYdCwBH6d">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R719" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">720</div></th><td class="s6">Squarespace Orders to Google Sheets Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieval of all Squarespace orders using Squarespace Commerce API and logs detailed order info into a Google Sheets spreadsheet via Google Sheets API. Supports filtering, pagination, and updates with an easy editable global config node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JCyket-jMlqO8lV1r90h0BEai1T-ntXz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R720" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">721</div></th><td class="s6">LangChain n8n Workflow with OpenAI &amp; Wikipedia</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow integrates LangChain with OpenAI language models and a custom Wikipedia tool. It demonstrates creating LLM chains, chat interactions, and agent-based queries combining LLM and external knowledge via LangChain tools for flexible AI responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1S5W02U7hKtAYSpEAmBIlxQoypSxF776q">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R721" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">722</div></th><td class="s6">AI Resume Screening with Multimodal LLM</td><td class="s7">Automates candidate resume evaluation by converting PDF resumes from Google Drive into images via Stirling PDF API, then analyzing them using Google&#39;s Gemini multimodal language model to determine candidate fit for a role and detect AI bypass attempts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RbHhvjmU7jVNsslqlZWNZsG8jnjH5b5-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R722" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">723</div></th><td class="s6">Automated CV Screening with OpenAI &amp; Supabase</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates resume screening by downloading CV PDFs, extracting text, sending data with job descriptions to OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini for detailed candidate evaluation, then storing structured results in Supabase. Ideal for recruiters and HR teams to speed up hiring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13Mjqph6X1JbdbvVf6IVLbd6Ie_i2oAlV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R723" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">724</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Statistics Dashboard</td><td class="s7">Generates a detailed dashboard summarizing n8n workflows including nodes, tags, webhooks, and global stats. Uses n8n API, JavaScript, JMESPath, Luxon, XML/XSLT, and Bootstrap for interactive reporting and visualization within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YDMB1dZVNztL3Pf1FDVma4nBNsvI_mqd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R724" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">725</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Profile &amp; Company Scraper with Bright Data &amp; AI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that scrapes LinkedIn person and company profiles using Bright Data MCP API, processes the data with LangChain&#39;s info extractor and Google Gemini AI to generate detailed company stories, and saves results locally and via webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1djYMwayGogLxjSw2sXJ2JkF_tE4gJ1GD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R725" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">726</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Podcast Summary &amp; Email Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval of top US podcasts by genre using Taddy API, crops audio via Aspose API, transcribes using OpenAI Whisper, summarizes with GPT-4o-mini, and emails results via Gmail OAuth2. Provides concise podcast episode summaries delivered to your inbox.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1K5WY0lBBiR30PcvqXPovBM50Yh-nnwmI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R726" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">727</div></th><td class="s6">AI Logo Sheet Extractor to Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of tools and attributes from uploaded AI logo sheets using OpenAI GPT-4o and LangChain AI agent, then stores and updates records in Airtable with hashed IDs and links. Enables easy cataloging of product comparisons from images via form submissions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lge_R6xDKo_rovV_4Umpn7Xz1ZRiGizn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R727" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">728</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered US Grants Tracker &amp; Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching, AI summarization, eligibility analysis, tracking, and emailing of new AI-focused US grants using Grants.gov API, OpenAI, Airtable, and Gmail. Helps organizations quickly discover and review relevant grant opportunities daily.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dsHzGf2cRDucqYQZBpkRMLfILYXqEGUR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R728" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">729</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Fact-Checking Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Ollama LLM models and custom code to split text into sentences, evaluate factual accuracy against provided facts, and summarize errors. Utilizes JavaScript, Ollama API, and LangChain integration to automate fact verification and summary generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sBU8lxlWSqfV5r64xQF8urPQ5rG5GtiH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R729" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">730</div></th><td class="s6">Discord AI Helpdesk Ticket Sorter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Discord Webhooks and OpenAI GPT-4 to automatically categorize user feedback into success stories, urgent issues, or regular tickets for targeted departmental routing, enhancing support efficiency with AI-powered message classification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19BCfGplG-7Nd2NTirKnXnqHtFOkfvql4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R730" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">731</div></th><td class="s6">PDF to Blog Post Automation</td><td class="s7">Transforms uploaded PDFs into SEO-optimized blog posts by extracting text with n8n and generating structured content via OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini. Publishes drafts directly to Ghost CMS using Ghost Admin API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YZgbN65l6Qa5HFx8-CkLn1Uw6jnGWHAP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R731" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">732</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chat with Message Buffering</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow integrates Telegram, Supabase PostgreSQL, and OpenAI GPT-4 to buffer multiple user messages, aggregate them, and reply with a single AI-generated response. It enhances chatbot conversation quality by combining rapid-fire inputs into coherent replies.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HtCl42t1o0tAzQ14x312DesoEaktKrxz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R732" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">733</div></th><td class="s6">Obsidian Note to Gmail Email Sender</td><td class="s7">Automate sending Obsidian notes as emails via Gmail using n8n. Integrates Obsidian&#39;s Post Webhook plugin, parses YAML metadata for email fields, handles attachments with base64 encoding, and sends emails with or without attachments seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tFup2C_ZEVc5BXDqAaYFoYsu2bKJGbFg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R733" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">734</div></th><td class="s6">Dynamically Switch Between LLMs</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that dynamically selects and switches between multiple OpenAI language models (gpt-4o-mini, gpt-4o, o1) to generate polite customer support responses. It validates answers via sentiment analysis and handles errors to improve response quality.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1F6gDhq-zrBf_Yxoa7Q0eYoQuEw1AGm4M">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R734" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">735</div></th><td class="s6">Trustpilot Reviews to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping recent customer reviews from Trustpilot using HTTP requests and Cheerio parsing, then appends or updates data in Google Sheets for analysis or reporting. Utilizes n8n&#39;s HTTP Request, Code, and Google Sheets nodes to extract review details and save structured data automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WqR7pxHsoQYDpsICTBmEAAeIyeZMpvfu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R735" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">736</div></th><td class="s6">Glassdoor Company Summary with Google Gemini &amp; Bright Data</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and summarization of Glassdoor company info using Bright Data Web Scraper API and Google Gemini (PaLM) language model. Retrieves up-to-date company data, checks scrape status, then summarizes with Langchain AI to provide concise insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1y-SKZAa1X3BO21Wrdi4ndJZpQOPtFiu_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R736" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">737</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Study Assistant for Signal Processing</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered Telegram bot for interactive signal processing study help. Integrates Telegram API, OpenAI API, Google Gemini, Airtable, Wikipedia, and LangChain tools like calculator and memory. Guides users through problems, explains theory, and records memory for personalized learning.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HMEpaQrAYfknHMjcKLUZe5H6n5UPkmpx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R737" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">738</div></th><td class="s6">Book Data Scraper to CSV &amp; Email via Dumpling AI</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping book data from web pages using Dumpling AI, extracts titles and prices with HTML nodes, sorts by price, converts to CSV, and emails via Gmail. Integrates Google Sheets trigger, HTTP request, HTML parsing, sorting, file conversion, and Gmail APIs for end-to-end scraping and delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15pE1k1oa5yY19LoDxkpb6dkXZ9eQlTGJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R738" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">739</div></th><td class="s6">OCR Invoice &amp; Receipt Processor with Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates OCR extraction of invoices and receipts from Google Drive using OakPDF OCR API via RapidAPI, integrates with Google Sheets for structured data storage. Enables real-time and manual triggers for seamless document processing and record keeping.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1naHdIUDEMOfZR1TmvYfVJTNVw2fVDKAD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R739" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">740</div></th><td class="s6">Notion to Supabase Vector Storage with OpenAI</td><td class="s7">Automates storing textual content from new Notion pages as vector documents in Supabase using OpenAI embeddings. Integrates Notion (page trigger, content retrieval), OpenAI (text embeddings), and Supabase (vector column storage) to enable efficient semantic search and organization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1y4JCaJ2KetLMB9KClAM_LGa5MnN3t3nD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R740" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">741</div></th><td class="s6">AI Image Caption Generator &amp; Overlay</td><td class="s7">Automates generating descriptive captions for images using Google Gemini AI and overlays them on images via n8n&#39;s Edit Image node. Utilizes HTTP requests, Langchain with Gemini-1.5 Flash model, and custom code for positioning captions. Ideal for content creation and watermarking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zcJ5yTwL1m0ZEm8i0L3bmQWiiixhty2A">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R741" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">742</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Backup of n8n Workflows to Gitea</td><td class="s7">This workflow automates backing up n8n workflows to a Gitea Git repository every 45 minutes. It uses the n8n API to fetch workflows, compares changes, encodes them in base64 using Python code nodes, and manages files via Gitea&#39;s API with HTTP Request nodes secured by Personal Access Tokens.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xS-fsJG-ijptB69u51ZSFpAc-RqeIXaS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R742" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">743</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Custom Presentation Creator for Leads</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates the creation of personalized Google Slides presentations for each new sales lead by integrating Google Drive, Sheets, and Slides APIs. It imports lead data from CSV files, creates new Sheets, copies presentation templates, and customizes content dynamically to streamline sales outreach.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xNgid-SPudhprFcbGIa21szRrwg4nqaX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R743" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">744</div></th><td class="s6">Automated PDF Scans Upload to Nextcloud</td><td class="s7">Workflow automates copying scanned PDF files from a local ScanServJS API to Nextcloud. Uses HTTP Request nodes to fetch file lists and files, Nextcloud node for uploading, and Schedule Trigger for hourly automation. Ideal for managing scanned documents efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MrGvp42a5dD-gJ4EleMYHuKhzqzyDUEc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R744" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">745</div></th><td class="s6">Automated AI-Powered Fact Emailer</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Airtable as subscriber DB, AI agents (Groq llama-3.3-70b, LangChain, OpenAI) to generate unique factoids and images, and Gmail for sending scheduled personalized educational emails with subscription management via n8n forms.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1P4XKiTLZaZfT3509g6M7yJlBn5BPc7VB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R745" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">746</div></th><td class="s6">Twilio SMS AI Chat Buffering Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Twilio, Redis, and OpenAI to buffer rapid SMS messages into a single AI-generated reply. Uses Redis for message stacking, LangChain memory nodes for chat history, and OpenAI&#39;s conversational agent for summarizing user inputs, improving chat flow and response quality.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12O_9_E1B19xcOcuXA2KrKjRDrpNHHSHI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R746" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">747</div></th><td class="s6">Slack-Qualys Vulnerability Scan Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates vulnerability scans and report generation in Qualys via Slack using Slack Events API, modals, and Qualys API integrations. Enables users to start scans and create detailed reports through interactive Slack modals with real-time feedback.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1krgZbYR0lHdnf8m_SbmXVfYA_0qTpdFj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R747" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">748</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Q&amp;A Generator for n8n Integrations</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates the creation of FAQ templates for various service integrations using Google Sheets, OpenAI GPT-4, and Google Drive. It reads integration data from Sheets, generates and enhances Q&amp;A pairs with AI, and saves results to Drive for CMS use (e.g., Wordpress, Webflow, Strapi).</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Oc1Bc-tmHGeMVihqSifHEG5OlHYHuWr9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R748" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">749</div></th><td class="s6">Pipedrive Org Data Enrichment with GPT-4 and ScrapingBee</td><td class="s7">Automates enriching new Pipedrive organizations by scraping their website with ScrapingBee, summarizing company info via OpenAI GPT-4o, creating detailed Pipedrive notes, and sending formatted Slack alerts. Integrates Pipedrive API, ScrapingBee API, OpenAI GPT-4o, and Slack API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NXNFJQ_eTNcXYxZ-XvWOZVGtj-ZLkfHe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R749" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">750</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable Product Data Enricher with AI Vision &amp; Web Agent</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates enrichment of product data in Airtable from photos using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o vision model, SERP API for reverse image search, and Firecrawl.dev for web scraping. It intelligently analyzes images, performs internet research, and updates Airtable records with detailed product attributes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IHojjcN9rWWtJtdq6ccfz-lncZ2bMiAr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R750" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">751</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chatbot for PostgreSQL Database Queries</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4 with PostgreSQL to enable natural language chat-based querying. Uses Langchain agent with AI tools for schema exploration, table definition, and SQL execution to provide intelligent DB insights and responses in real-time.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13dukb8d578jy9WJHn3buNLQlkJ8GrSn8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R751" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">752</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Sentiment ETL Pipeline</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching #OnThisDay tweets via Twitter API, storing texts in MongoDB, analyzing sentiment with Google Cloud Natural Language, saving results in Postgres, and alerting via Slack if sentiment score is high. Built with n8n for daily ETL workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jry0ZbavERqTPRsgkC3zo1DHo8lGaCVO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R752" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">753</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Generation &amp; Enrichment Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow for automated lead scraping and enrichment using HTTP API calls to fetch personal and work emails, filters leads with valid emails, and saves detailed lead info to Airtable. Ideal for marketers and sales teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vFpCI2TaEZJNhtN7iWdjgdPCpF0lPTHS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R753" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">754</div></th><td class="s6">Dynamic HTML Generator with OpenAI Structured Output</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o API with Structured Output to generate HTML pages dynamically from user queries. It converts JSON UI components styled with Tailwind CSS into HTML, then serves it via webhook. Tech stack: OpenAI API, Tailwind CSS, n8n webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hpz7ZJb7FUYvc6v8PreedcBADovg3cmw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R754" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">755</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Data Extraction via Claude &amp; Gemini APIs</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates downloading a PDF from Google Drive, converts it to base64, and extracts data using Claude 3.5 Sonnet and Google Gemini 2.0 Flash AI models with custom prompts. Enables comparison of extraction accuracy, latency, and cost.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AEUqs9K5GIvm-F3UuNKt9sEnx0fLZ1aA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R755" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">756</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Resume Extractor and PDF Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates resume extraction via Telegram using OpenAI GPT-4 turbo-preview for parsing, formats sections into HTML, converts to PDF with Gotenberg, and sends back through Telegram. It integrates Telegram API, OpenAI API, and Gotenberg PDF conversion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gpEsOAyOeI6wlviYjxBdMJwdShf5tPXb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R756" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">757</div></th><td class="s6">Logo Sheet AI Extractor to Airtable</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates extracting product/tool data from uploaded logo sheet images using OpenAI GPT-4 with Langchain AI agent. It parses tools and their attributes, maps similarities, and upserts structured records into Airtable. Ideal for cataloging software tools from visual data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UwRi8g3YJfSKfk48ys9qudFqVMDehP75">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R757" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">758</div></th><td class="s6">Self-hosted LLM Personal Data Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses a self-hosted Mistral NeMo LLM via Ollama API to extract structured personal data from chat messages. It features error auto-correction, structured JSON schema parsing, and real-time chat triggers for reliable data extraction.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Wxgu8gdpFrwtzj2AjRfIf_vClcdIehNc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R758" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">759</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Credit Card Spend Extractor</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates extraction of credit card transaction details from Gmail labeled emails using Gmail API, PDF extraction, HTML parsing, and AI NLP models (Google Gemini, Groq LLaMA, LangChain) to structure spend data, then logs it into Google Sheets for finance tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zbOBtvoDIJg1bJY2D5lH-zpHhRQ_aBr3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R759" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">760</div></th><td class="s6">Google Trends Keyword Tracker &amp; Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching top trending keywords from Google Trends Italy RSS, scrapes related news content using jina.ai API, summarizes combined text, and appends results with metadata to Google Sheets for editorial planning. Uses n8n with Google Sheets, HTTP Request, XML, and Code nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rJcfx7B78L0ktAXYdNAOpKu6RPjCKWo-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R760" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">761</div></th><td class="s6">Umami Analytics SEO AI Report Generator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that connects Umami analytics API with Openrouter AI and Baserow to automate SEO data analysis. It fetches weekly website stats, sends them to an AI model for SEO insights and improvement suggestions, then saves the summarized reports in Baserow for easy management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1frkmVpVZTsvqWWZbVp3S8EUF8yAaaPUa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R761" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">762</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram to Spotify Track Control</td><td class="s7">Automate Spotify playback via Telegram using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini for track identification. This n8n workflow triggers from Telegram messages, fetches track info using OpenAI, searches Spotify, and controls playback (add, next, resume). Integrates Telegram, OpenAI, and Spotify APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zyj_Dx4iKAV-R_6BKey7ljiPHQwi9_iJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R762" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">763</div></th><td class="s6">Agent Access Control with Telegram &amp; Airtable</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow implementing an AI agent access control system using Telegram Bot, Airtable for user permissions, and OpenAI GPT-4 models. It verifies user roles and allowed tools before executing actions and supports sub-agents like a weather assistant with real-time API data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1o38E1Z0E-iCAsovHoMXgWWubIQ4Rw-00">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R763" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">764</div></th><td class="s6">NetSuite SuiteQL API Query Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating NetSuite REST API to run SuiteQL queries via a webhook or manual trigger. It leverages n8n&#39;s NetSuite node to fetch and respond with dynamic query results, enabling automated and real-time data retrieval from NetSuite ERP systems.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1q3OHUY9TB0QkocFLwTfD_EZHxDt90FoJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R764" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">765</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Prompt Loader with Dynamic AI Query</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches prompt templates from GitHub, dynamically replaces variables using set parameters, validates variable presence, and sends the completed prompt to an AI agent (Langchain &amp; Ollama). Ideal for automated prompt management in AI workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xmMqHjp1YGePeqqgZX7X2kVkXtDxcpnS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R765" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">766</div></th><td class="s6">Flux AI Image Generator Webform</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates an AI-powered image generator webform using Huggingface&#39;s text-to-image models (e.g., FLUX.1-schnell), allows users to select artistic styles, processes prompts, uploads results to Cloudflare R2 S3 storage, and serves a styled webpage with recent image renders.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dDQy8qShqeiihHikocNBTnJr96DlvYSB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R766" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">767</div></th><td class="s6">Fal AI Flux Image Generator to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates image creation using Fal AI Flux API with customizable prompts, size, steps, and guidance. Retrieves generated images, downloads them, and saves to Google Drive. Utilizes HTTP requests with header auth and Google Drive OAuth2 in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ncmL0bOZibWKqCN1_2JD_RofA4NoqbHJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R767" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">768</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Enhanced Structured Output Parser</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI Chat models with LangChain for parsing structured data. It processes prompts, validates and auto-fixes AI outputs to extract formatted information like US states and cities with populations, ensuring reliable structured data generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1l4ADzq_EYOXe-aqHy-78CErm3uqo9NKq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R768" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">769</div></th><td class="s6">Auto-Optimize Images Uploaded to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates image optimization by watching a specified Google Drive folder for new images, downloading them, sending them to TinyPNG API for compression, and saving the optimized images back to a chosen Google Drive folder. Integrates Google Drive and TinyPNG APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ehfV3vIMcMZYkOjOIOcpZvn1_O3ysLM5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R769" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">770</div></th><td class="s6">Crypto Price Telegram Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that integrates Telegram, OpenAI GPT-4o mini, and CoinMarketCap API to provide real-time cryptocurrency prices via chat. It uses Langchain agents with memory buffer to manage sessions and respond dynamically to user queries on Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UBAk5KmhXDHN5Uo9bV_mTAEvQpLRdbPS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R770" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">771</div></th><td class="s6">Stock Earnings Report Analysis with AI &amp; Pinecone</td><td class="s7">Automates analysis of stock earnings PDFs using n8n with Google Gemini embeddings, Pinecone vector store, Google Sheets/Drive integration, and AI agents. Generates detailed markdown financial reports and saves to Google Docs, focusing on Google (Alphabet Inc.) earnings over last 3 quarters.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14KwNh-hKDoqjRFXItGs3mnB_zke41lgH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R771" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">772</div></th><td class="s6">AI Personal Shopper with RAG &amp; WooCommerce</td><td class="s7">An intelligent assistant workflow using OpenAI chat models, Qdrant vector store, and WooCommerce API to handle store inquiries and product search. Integrates Google Drive for document storage and uses RAG for general store info and LangChain for memory and tools.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SOLQHe1v6qPM08EBpqSTe-b0r0raEj97">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R772" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">773</div></th><td class="s6">Hugging Face Paper Summarizer to Notion</td><td class="s7">Automates daily extraction of new research papers from Hugging Face, analyzes abstracts using OpenAI GPT-4O, and stores structured summaries in Notion. Tech stack includes Hugging Face API, HTML extraction, OpenAI API (GPT-4O), and Notion API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15Os7XQxa4JzJY5QRrxa013NDIFhmW2Jh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R773" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">774</div></th><td class="s6">QR Code Coupon Lead Gen &amp; Validation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating unique QR code coupon assignment, lead creation, and coupon validation using SuiteCRM API, Google Sheets, SMTP email, and QuickChart API. Designed for managing discounts in lead generation campaigns.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OkfwHqfvvhiZ4mRgzwWakcjO2huqUsXF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R774" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">775</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Image Generation Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates image creation via OpenAI Image Generation API, using prompts, quality, size, and quantity parameters. It converts base64 responses to files, enabling easy image generation automation with HTTP Request and file conversion nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aYj6pWUN-i-Htu9_QnxRQq5Xa6kLqP3Z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R775" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">776</div></th><td class="s6">INSEE Data Enrichment for Agile CRM</td><td class="s7">Automate enrichment of Agile CRM company data with official French company info from the INSEE OpenData API. This workflow integrates Agile CRM and INSEE APIs to update company addresses and add SIREN identifiers, improving CRM accuracy with verified government data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1R0U5MvWyHBaBiqWkbJL5P5K1G9aAodKQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R776" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">777</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Model Fine-tuning Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates fine-tuning of OpenAI GPT models using training data from Google Drive. Integrates Google Drive API, OpenAI file upload, and fine-tuning job creation with n8n automation platform to streamline custom AI model creation and deployment.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Kj5ydx6ZSUfRvnlbRdu80sKqxZCZvGGk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R777" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">778</div></th><td class="s6">Google SERP Extraction &amp; Summarization with Bright Data</td><td class="s7">Automates Google Search scraping using Bright Data API, processes results with Google Gemini AI for extraction and summarization, then sends formatted data via webhook. Utilizes n8n, Bright Data, and Google Gemini PaLM API for advanced search analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17CypbraZt0bPDaPpBrGdUVJVzwDG-VuA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R778" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">779</div></th><td class="s6">Elevenlabs Text-to-Speech API Webhook</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow creates a POST webhook to convert text to speech using Elevenlabs.io API. It checks input parameters, sends requests with custom API key authentication, and streams back the generated audio. Ideal for automating voice content creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yRisbIaF6efjbMVlZRPUDkv7-4bjAbGb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R779" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">780</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Daily Digest Email Creator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that aggregates top news from Times of India RSS, recent Gmail emails, and Todoist tasks into a styled daily summary email. Utilizes RSS Feed, Gmail API, Todoist API, and custom JavaScript for formatting and sends digest automatically via Gmail.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iwlxNQzpvVNemq0ir-qyQ6rW6zvfzL-L">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R780" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">781</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice PDF Generator with JSReport &amp; n8n</td><td class="s7">Automates invoice creation from form input using n8n workflows, JSReport API for PDF generation, and Gmail to email invoices. Integrates form-trigger, HTTP POST to JSReport (document template API), and Gmail OAuth2 for sending, streamlining billing tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aTRK4aqrSL_H49hyi9gZHTbc4TrhOQ9M">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R781" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">782</div></th><td class="s6">Facebook Long-Lived Access Token Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates the retrieval of long-lived Facebook user and page access tokens using Facebook Graph API and n8n. Takes client ID, secret, user token, and optional app-scoped user ID to securely extend token validity for apps and integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BRkmguUaUkG3k3ghG4afXZkqNkHMZz8J">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R782" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">783</div></th><td class="s6">On-Page SEO Audit Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates on-page SEO audits by scraping a landing page URL and using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini model to generate detailed technical and content SEO audits. Outputs a structured audit report and emails it via Gmail. Built with n8n, HTTP Request, Langchain, OpenAI, and Gmail API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1W0Mq0M0iwDpm7qglgN0eiWei3vGaGReb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R783" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">784</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Telegram Image Response</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Telegram API and OpenAI&#39;s image generation to receive text messages, generate AI images from the text, and send these images back via Telegram, enabling AI-enhanced visual communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bpwh2hAHKQO2SXJa5tvn1RsBktKikKbP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R784" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">785</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Weather Forecast with Open-Meteo API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI&#39;s GPT chat model with Open-Meteo geolocation and weather APIs for interactive, AI-driven weather forecasts. Users input a city name via chat, AI fetches coordinates, then retrieves and returns a 7-day forecast using HTTP requests, enabling smart travel planning.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11oMbMYXU016Qk3o9qBS1MoxtJkBv1BoZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R785" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-h