header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">789</div></th><td class="s6">Confluence Knowledge Base Query Tool</td><td class="s7">Automates IT support by transforming Slack user queries using OpenAI GPT-4, then searching Confluence via its API to return relevant KB article titles, links, and excerpts. Integrates n8n, OpenAI, and Confluence APIs for efficient knowledge retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iSWGJFN41HzvCBUFjOJpOrvMH70so_Sr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R789" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">790</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Resume Disabled n8n Workflows</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automatically resumes disabled workflows tagged with &#39;auto_resume:true&#39; every 4 hours using n8n API nodes, schedule triggers, and filters. Ensures continuous automation by activating paused workflows in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16z2sjtLx2SGQMZssiqAjHysnukSXz4yg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R790" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">791</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive PDF RAG with AI Chat</td><td class="s7">Automates Google Drive folder monitoring to download PDFs, extract and clean text, generate embeddings with Google Gemini, store them in Pinecone vector DB, and enable AI chat queries with context via OpenRouter and Langchain nodes for retrieval-augmented generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zIs6ca-jUi9l8LyNKJWS2Bqyb6X8nbyH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R791" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">792</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video AI Summaries to Discord</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching new YouTube videos from a channel&#39;s RSS feed, retrieves English captions via YouTube API with OAuth2, summarizes transcript content using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-3.5, and posts concise bullet-point summaries with video links to a Discord channel via webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1A7iGBhvVS7UBjQLgZrCBsj2nyfe7DdIR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R792" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">793</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Profile URL Finder</td><td class="s7">Automates finding LinkedIn profile URLs from names stored in Google Sheets using Google Sheets API and Airtop&#39;s AI search API. Fetches names, searches Google for LinkedIn URLs, parses results, and updates the sheet, streamlining contact enrichment for recruiters and sales.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1s2WEpRk4_RjjlrTUWXYQQfRvnGfePjjo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R793" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">794</div></th><td class="s6">WhatsApp &amp; Asana Customer Support Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates customer support by capturing form data via n8n form trigger, sending confirmation messages through WhatsApp Business Cloud API, and creating support tickets in Asana task management. Integrates n8n native forms, WhatsApp Business Cloud API, and Asana API for seamless support workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NEOfRBZJVpC4IarzfoAEFqT_l8cAKsgz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R794" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">795</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Automation Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating Gmail operations like sending, replying, getting emails, and waiting for responses using Gmail OAuth2 API. Integrates n8n&#39;s langchain MCP trigger for AI-driven email handling and dynamic message management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Cjd83wiS4tf4x17_-xI7XoNhX7FgUvrT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R795" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">796</div></th><td class="s6">Sync New Clients from Notion to Clockify</td><td class="s7">Automate client management by syncing new clients from a Notion database to Clockify workspace using n8n. Utilizes Notion API as trigger and Clockify API to add clients automatically, streamlining project tracking setup.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ShhGQqLKIcCH7a9JwHwQQd2rVcl2fz7n">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R796" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">797</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Transcript Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates summarization of YouTube video transcripts using SearchApi.io for transcript retrieval and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini model via Langchain in n8n. Converts video_id input into concise video content summaries for easy consumption.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FZABpu8j122y2n22ij1McmvuG4qLKutQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R797" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">798</div></th><td class="s6">AI Movie Recommendation Agent with MongoDB</td><td class="s7">An AI-driven movie recommendation chatbot using OpenAI GPT and MongoDB aggregation. It receives user chat input, queries a MongoDB movies collection with AI-generated aggregation pipelines, provides recommendations, and allows saving favorite movies. Built with n8n, OpenAI API, and MongoDB.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Nt6u61YQlcX-sXz8pk1xtrC-dnFMdSrZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R798" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">799</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Outlook Email Reply Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automates email replies by integrating Microsoft Outlook and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via n8n. Filters emails from specific sender, generates personalized replies in your style, and drafts or sends replies automatically, enhancing email productivity.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-_9_97Z8E8_TT56PEAIVr-pmka6St1Nz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R799" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">800</div></th><td class="s6">Client Feedback AI Summary &amp; Social Post</td><td class="s7">Automates client feedback processing using n8n workflow with Deepseek AI API for analysis, email for report delivery, and Telegram for social media draft sharing. Summarizes positives, suggests improvements, and drafts social posts from feedback.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HeFWt5BZXq6ryEVZd8aDCjeiSfS1iSJc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R800" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">801</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Google Calendar Meetings to Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates sending a daily list of Google Calendar meetings via Telegram using Google Calendar and Telegram APIs in n8n. Triggered every morning at 6 AM, it retrieves today&#39;s meetings, formats details, and messages them to your Telegram user.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gSYh4zx1jZdyYDa3qCCgY5C7XAtm1993">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R801" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">802</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Command to Generate Google Meet Links</td><td class="s7">Automate instant Google Meet link creation from Slack using n8n. Integrates Slack slash commands, Google Calendar API (with Google Meet conferencing), and Slack API for messaging. Creates temporary calendar events, shares meet links in Slack channels, then deletes events automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nL_2BLSr4qpilkH7ffxMJtEbW3-LroLh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R802" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">803</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Post YouTube Videos to X</td><td class="s7">Automates posting new YouTube videos to X (Twitter) every 30 min using YouTube API, OpenAI GPT-3.5 for post generation, and X API for publishing engaging tweets linking the latest video.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19vr-p63SvdmxGbYSuMmPwoeM8_5LHPmO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R803" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">804</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Issues to Telegram Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching open GitHub issues labeled &#39;Bug&#39; from a specified repo every 10 minutes, filters by comments count, and sends new issue alerts via Telegram bot. Utilizes GitHub API, n8n automation, and Telegram API for real-time notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OpXwJuUJ_pyBBp00FJ1NKGQIFhVeiPNm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R804" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">805</div></th><td class="s6">Send Files to Kindle via Telegram Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates sending files received from a Telegram bot to a Kindle device via email using Microsoft Outlook API. Ensures files are present, renames attachments, sends to Kindle email, and notifies user. Integrates Telegram Bot API and Outlook mail services.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LpSe8XqgzCHYL_A0zbOIQknHO8YutmR5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R805" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">806</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Assistant with File Upload &amp; Chat</td><td class="s7">Automates creating a custom OpenAI Assistant by uploading a Google Drive document and enabling chat interaction. Uses Google Drive API, OpenAI API (file upload, assistant creation, GPT-4 Turbo). Ideal for building knowledge-based chatbots from documents.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vjC_Jp7-SS-dYnWAgJ0tnHWXUST5Ln5u">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R806" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">807</div></th><td class="s6">AI Tweet Generator with Hashtag &amp; Airtable</td><td class="s7">Generates short tweets including random tech hashtags using OpenAI&#39;s text-davinci-001 API, then stores results in Airtable. Uses n8n for workflow orchestration with manual trigger, function nodes, HTTP request, and Airtable node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VxH6vsLDvqJki5nwrt1DkIFQtYG6zrBG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R807" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">808</div></th><td class="s6">Text-to-Speech Audio Generator with OpenAI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts text to audio using OpenAI&#39;s text-to-speech API. It features a POST webhook to receive text input, processes it with OpenAI audio generation, and responds with the audio binary. Useful for automating audio content creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iImv9f7C2FbD49wfpnHN-sTZs4jOV4_r">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R808" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">809</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Error Notification for n8n</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to send real-time error alerts via Telegram bot. Uses n8n&#39;s Error Trigger node linked to a Telegram node with bot token and chat ID. Notifies workflow name, execution time, error details, and last executed node for easy monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Gw7_2FTQEn5BhHMg2HAFtBLG2TSJDW5_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R809" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">810</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Web Server Uptime Monitor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that monitors web server availability every minute. It fetches server lists from Google Sheets, checks server status via HTTP requests, logs results in Google Sheets, and sends Gmail alerts on downtime. Uses Google Sheets API, HTTP Request node, and Gmail API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tqA0-csi4Q3sqqeFutvA7BOi0iYwqWUp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R810" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">811</div></th><td class="s6">Slack AI Chatbot via Slash Commands</td><td class="s7">Creates an AI chatbot integrated with Slack using n8n workflows, Slack slash commands, and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini. Handles webhook triggers, command routing with switch nodes, AI response generation via Langchain/OpenAI, and sends messages back to Slack channels for interactive chatbot functionality.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yohkDUz-WLWcECPxmcxfjetoGwe5t4o5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R811" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">812</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Weather Data Fetch &amp; Store</td><td class="s7">Automates daily fetching of weather data using the OpenWeatherMap API and stores temperature, humidity, wind speed, and location info in Airtable for historical tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14HNxG5h1ar5JNnCtC3r4L7MRUN4UcbIb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R812" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">813</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Post New YouTube Videos to X</td><td class="s7">Automates posting engaging tweets about new YouTube videos using YouTube API, OpenAI&#39;s GPT-3.5 for content generation, and X (Twitter) API for posting. Runs every 30 minutes to promote latest video with AI-generated short posts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Rik8onjYj--BpYGnONAPbxigBQ3Vfi_j">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R813" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">814</div></th><td class="s6">Matomo Analytics Visitor Insights</td><td class="s7">Automates gathering of Matomo analytics visitor data (visits&gt;3) via API, analyzes it using Meta LLaMA AI on Openrouter, and stores SEO insights in Baserow. Uses n8n to schedule, process JSON, and integrate Matomo, Openrouter AI, and Baserow for actionable website visitor behavior analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12bTTN04wxv9LONsZQevJZFu4I5ePipRe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R814" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">815</div></th><td class="s6">CSV to Postgres Automatic Import</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates importing CSV files stored locally into a PostgreSQL database. It uses a manual trigger, reads the CSV file, converts it into spreadsheet format, and inserts data into Postgres. Key tools: n8n, PostgreSQL, local file system.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hvhNxXy4PGIuZpr6MPinfirvBhxn2SQT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R815" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">816</div></th><td class="s6">SERPBear SEO Analytics with AI Insights</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching SEO keyword rankings from SERPBear API, analyzes trends and performance with AI via OpenRouter, and saves actionable insights to Baserow database. Utilizes n8n for scheduling, HTTP requests, code processing, and cloud storage integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dQKJefI8M6Nev-H5bNJ8UYGdCrrDh35_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R816" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">817</div></th><td class="s6">AI Email Summarizer to Messenger</td><td class="s7">Automates reading emails via IMAP, summarizes content using Openrouter.ai&#39;s LLaMA 3.1 model, and sends concise, prioritized summaries with deadlines to LINE messenger using HTTP APIs. Useful for managing important email info in chat apps.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17GOtMzVj1pWCvq8lxcqdB-hmAcG2z-zf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R817" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">818</div></th><td class="s6">Form Data Capture &amp; Storage to Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing user-submitted form data via n8n&#39;s form trigger and stores it directly in Airtable. Utilizes n8n workflow nodes with Airtable API integration to streamline data collection for easy structured management and future use.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iKmupXUj-5BV9Bb5wQi9V08PIWdXcVOw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R818" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">819</div></th><td class="s6">Global SMS Sender via ClickSend API</td><td class="s7">Automate sending SMS worldwide using the ClickSend API with n8n. This workflow sets SMS content and recipient, then sends the message via HTTP POST with Basic Auth. Ideal for global SMS notifications with easy setup instructions included.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1DZOjPT87YlLjWpSNifl-ovVA27b-mUbv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R819" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">820</div></th><td class="s6">Instagram ChatGPT Auto-Responder Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating ManyChat and OpenAI&#39;s ChatGPT to automate Instagram messaging. It receives messages from Instagram via ManyChat webhook, processes them with AI using custom prompts and memory context, and replies automatically in the influencer&#39;s style.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1e3rv0NcTBOXohgdNYwdC-1NboRhy5UEH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R820" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">821</div></th><td class="s6">Spotify Monthly Playlist Updater</td><td class="s7">Automates creation and update of a Spotify monthly playlist by syncing liked tracks using Spotify API and storing data in NocoDB. Scheduled with n8n to maintain playlist freshness and database records.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10bldBvz_Kfw7hqS1IacAgVMxvnsJeK0_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R821" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">822</div></th><td class="s6">URL Shortener and Click Tracker with Airtable</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates short URLs by hashing long URLs using SHA256 and stores them in Airtable. It redirects short URLs to the original URLs while tracking click counts. Includes a dashboard displaying total links, clicks, and hosts. Uses Webhooks, Airtable API, and built-in crypto node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rmvRbO3LNdzbNA-VdJZNchE1nt1FPE4T">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R822" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">823</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Google Calendar to Trello Cards</td><td class="s7">An automated n8n workflow that fetches daily Google Calendar events, filters out recurring tasks, and creates Trello cards for each event with relevant details. Uses Google Calendar API and Trello API, triggered every day at 8am to keep task boards current and organized.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13m9zStD0h27wTrTJGUk7Xyek5iVkUkjI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R823" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">824</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub to TravisCI CI Trigger</td><td class="s7">An automated CI workflow using n8n that triggers TravisCI builds on GitHub push or pull request events. Integrates GitHub webhook via OAuth2 and TravisCI API to automate build triggers based on repository activity for n8n-io/n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1X8sTTc-tPAgEa9v88fN1wXmunwCnvtBO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R824" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">825</div></th><td class="s6">Mattermost Standup Bot Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates daily standup meetings in Mattermost using n8n. Utilizes Mattermost API, webhooks, and cron schedules to prompt users with configurable questions, collect responses, and publish summarized reports in channels. Includes config dialogs and direct messaging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fARmIjjJBUUT0-JVBLJOSXXu5YGYZAaJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R825" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">826</div></th><td class="s6">Notion Empty Page Archiver</td><td class="s7">Automates daily archiving of empty pages in Notion databases using the Notion API. Checks all databases and pages, analyzes page content and properties, and archives those with no meaningful content to keep Notion workspace tidy.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PZv2Nxa1_th1yLLgi7D8cEvaKUB4TPEv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R826" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">827</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable Batch Upsert/Insert/Update Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to batch process Airtable records with modes for upsert, insert, and update. Utilizes Airtable API via HTTP requests, handles rate limits with wait retries, supports batching to avoid throttling, and merges outputs for efficient Airtable data management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qhMXOC8REfwzNny1oPXPPe4pklvnp67f">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R827" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">828</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Book Recommendation via Open Library</td><td class="s7">Automates finding and emailing a random book recommendation weekly using Open Library API and n8n automation. Fetches book count, selects a random book, retrieves detailed info, formats the author links, and sends the recommendation via SMTP email.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13wFL3nGlUSQF2ne_C5PK9WwDUitP_znj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R828" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">829</div></th><td class="s6">Notion Team &amp; Project Management Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates creation and management of team members, projects, and semesters in Notion. Uses n8n with Notion API, webhooks, and JavaScript for data processing. Ideal for educational or organizational project tracking and user-semester-project relations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1x8xRGiexiK6h6LGZDVJhxWd7G8jtqHpN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R829" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">830</div></th><td class="s6">Auto AWS Transcribe &amp; Google Sheets Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates transcription of audio files uploaded to Google Drive by saving them to AWS S3, transcribing via AWS Transcribe, then logging results with metadata into Google Sheets using OAuth2 authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iAPxzP3Q9qiggSoigrRBpCFIIJapLFYy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R830" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">831</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI API Text &amp; Image Processing Demo</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating various OpenAI API uses: text summarization, translation, chat completions, HTML &amp; SVG generation, Whisper audio transcription, and DALLE-2 image creation. It integrates OpenAI models (davinci-003, GPT-3.5-turbo, Whisper, DALLE-2) for multi-modal AI tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QTJzIGmL6gqZIFVRxhqnuVmbGYvzdQQ5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R831" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">832</div></th><td class="s6">Smart Factory Sensor Monitoring &amp; Incident Alert</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrating AMQP for real-time factory sensor data, converting °C to °F, conditionally triggering PagerDuty incidents for temps ≥50°C, and storing machine &amp; incident data in CrateDB for smart factory monitoring and alerting automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iTdcmn2FbImeOWEedPs3oQcn8wzxEOHo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R832" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">833</div></th><td class="s6">HelloFresh Recipe Recommendation Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Mistral large language model API, Qdrant vector search, and SQLite to recommend recipes from HelloFresh&#39;s current weekly menu. It processes user inputs, queries recipe data, and provides tailored meal suggestions while excluding off-menu items.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1S5gAOXE5dDYAcCZrWxVyrWAC6ERgY1Tf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R833" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">834</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify to HubSpot Order Deal Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing of Shopify order updates with HubSpot CRM by creating/updating contacts and deals using Shopify API, HubSpot API and OAuth2. Ensures orders in Shopify reflect as deals in HubSpot, streamlining ecommerce sales workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vrXZpscyCuWPlXdsbsG4Eyuk1wegAk2j">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R834" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">835</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk to Pipedrive Ticket Assignee Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates updating Zendesk tickets by assigning them to the Pipedrive contact owner. Uses Zendesk API to fetch tickets and requester data, Pipedrive API for contact and owner info, and merges agent data to reassign tickets every 5 minutes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18nCQEmMS3_QcIffgfHhon0vZIiC6x1lj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R835" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">836</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk-Pipedrive Ticket Comment Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Zendesk ticket comments as Pipedrive notes by checking ticket updates daily at 09:00. Uses Zendesk API for ticket and comment retrieval, Pipedrive API for person search and note creation, handling emails as sync keys.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19_h5uAjXPAzfodukbihm-l9dhOv3yEL6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R836" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">837</div></th><td class="s6">XML to Google Sheets Data Importer</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading XML data from a URL, parses it, and imports the structured data into a new Google Sheets spreadsheet. Uses n8n with HTTP Request, XML, and Google Sheets nodes. Ideal for converting XML feeds to spreadsheets effortlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wd3uCyFD_ryVwJ0X9UQw9bFE16HIn_UO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R837" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">838</div></th><td class="s6">Spreadsheet File Processing &amp; Upload Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow template for loading, converting, manipulating, and saving Excel and CSV spreadsheet files. Utilizes HTTP Request, Google Drive, Microsoft OneDrive, and SFTP nodes to fetch and upload files. Supports local, public URL, and cloud sources. Automates processing and storage of spreadsheet data in various formats.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1W_8mQwma_YEtnkkWciGAWHnJVPehnYg3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R838" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">839</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Gmail Campaign Manager with Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating email campaigns using Gmail API and Google Sheets. It sends sequences of personalized emails with placeholders, follows up based on thread replies, and updates contact status in Sheets. Supports scheduling, weekend skipping, and multi-step email sequencing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NIZdVA0_gItVz64uN86cHw0BwiiVj81J">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R839" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">840</div></th><td class="s6">Todoist Task Snooze Automator</td><td class="s7">Automates moving tasks between Todoist projects based on due dates to simulate snoozing. Uses Todoist API, scheduled triggers at 5am and every 5 minutes, date calculations, and HTTP requests to move tasks back to inbox or snoozed project automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15etaZrYLP4Nbj8I4Iykx2LVtuTbRgyve">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R840" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">841</div></th><td class="s6">Linear Tickets to Google Sheets Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates daily syncing of team tickets from Linear via GraphQL API to Google Sheets. Includes pagination handling, custom field setting, and data flattening for easy filtering and tracking. Requires Linear API auth and Google Sheets OAuth.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vtkH3dNbNCq5yPdzo1FL5_xzix5PHarQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R841" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">842</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Engaging Moments Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that extracts engaging moments from YouTube videos using the YouTube &#39;mostReplayed&#39; API endpoint. It filters moments with intensity above 0.6, removes close timestamps, and returns human-readable links with timestamps. Utilizes n8n HTTP Request, Filter, Split, and Webhook nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SVbGkojF430vcBQ9ntd1OLuvwHWNiioQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R842" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">843</div></th><td class="s6">Slack to Linear Bug Reporting Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates bug reporting by capturing Slack /bug commands and creating detailed issues in Linear via GraphQL API. Utilizes Slack Webhooks and Linear OAuth2 API for team and label management. Ideal for streamlined developer bug tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12CBVPtRinjnpP8-tHo7_lOSCb5VeGh3h">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R843" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">844</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Linear Bug Ticket Team Classifier</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates bug ticket triage in Linear by using OpenAI GPT-4 to classify tickets and assign them to the correct team. It integrates Linear API, OpenAI API, and Slack to streamline issue management and team notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GHyJF15lBvv8SfUeM-japuHaJn-Ex_3a">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R844" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">845</div></th><td class="s6">PDF to AI Q&amp;A with Supabase &amp; Qdrant</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches PDFs from Google Drive, splits and indexes their content into Qdrant vector store via Supabase for fast semantic search, and answers user queries using OpenAI GPT-4o Mini model. Integrates Google Drive API, Qdrant vector DB, Supabase, and OpenAI.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fhWlziDMSLKB_IVzeXcRGjWVmgZEYnNd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R845" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">846</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets Email Validation Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates email validation by monitoring a Google Sheets for new entries, removing duplicate emails, verifying each email&#39;s deliverability through the Effibotics API, and updating the sheet with verification results. Utilizes Google Sheets API, HTTP request node, and email validation service.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yy8k-w3CKDnKJHzXFh2PYEpQZsZTJlYz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R846" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">847</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Image Auto-Analyzer with OpenAI</td><td class="s7">Automates image analysis on Telegram using n8n workflow with Telegram and OpenAI APIs. It triggers on image messages, analyzes images via OpenAI, and sends textual analysis back to Telegram chats, enabling real-time content moderation, categorization, and feedback.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uDfDyHbh8_dSGPBViXKrrQQm8uHYWCKi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R847" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">848</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Deal Line Items Copier</td><td class="s7">Automates copying line items from a won HubSpot deal to a newly created deal using HubSpot API and n8n. It fetches deals, retrieves line items and SKUs, gets product info by SKUs, creates line items for the new deal, and sends Slack notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1O9xK3E67DQkXlYrMZFRXHeCrSZo42aRs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R848" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">849</div></th><td class="s6">S3 Folder Bulk Download and ZIP Compressor</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading all files from a specified AWS S3 bucket folder, aggregates them into one item including binaries, and compresses the collection into a ZIP file using n8n&#39;s AWS S3 and Compression nodes for easy retrieval or further processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VdAvOabEGLKVbwJs1f6_Vncsa9vubqIq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R849" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">850</div></th><td class="s6">Google SERP Keyword Rank Tracker</td><td class="s7">Automates SEO keyword ranking tracking using ScrapingRobot API and n8n. Fetches Google SERP data for custom keyword lists, processes organic results, assigns ranking positions, and prepares output for databases like Airtable. Ideal for SEO research and competitor analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XI8Z-w2o1EA1GzItKRXY8VU5lZYTiA4s">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R850" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">851</div></th><td class="s6">Webpage to Markdown &amp; Links Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses the Firecrawl.dev API to convert web pages into markdown format and extract links. It handles batch processing with rate limiting and outputs data for further use. Integrates with your own URL database and output tools like Airtable.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1d_4KLi932JW6lQnIzLqsk9hnO5Z5u7AL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R851" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">852</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Birthday &amp; Event SMS Wishes</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates daily SMS sending of personalized congratulatory messages using Google Sheets for event data and messages, Twilio for SMS delivery, and a daily cron trigger. It targets automating birthday and event greetings via SMS.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Aj2r1v6p9QJ018XGUCTkbJKZ0Nj-yl5y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R852" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">853</div></th><td class="s6">Notion Task Reminders via Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates daily weekday reminders of incomplete tasks from a Notion database by sending personalized Slack direct messages. Uses Notion API, Slack API with OAuth2, and cron scheduling to match task assignees with Slack users for timely task alerts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tAOGwhi5SF_FDj1wYCkBS93KOqmtN0eL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R853" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">854</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Generated LinkedIn Advice Contributor</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly Google search for LinkedIn advice articles, extracts article info, generates unique AI advice with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, then posts results to Slack and stores contributions in NocoDB. Integrates Google Search, HTML parsing, OpenAI, Slack, and NocoDB.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17HHIoXCtlwghwCPG2myn42Au1AXpLd5L">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R854" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">855</div></th><td class="s6">Google Docs Image Replacer &amp; Downloader</td><td class="s7">Automates replacing images in Google Docs templates using image URLs from a datasource. Utilizes Google Docs and Google Drive APIs to copy templates, replace images by ID, make files shareable, and download as PDF or Docx. Ideal for batch processing dynamic documents.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aGBryJOCcMmsv4Prm6co7VId9mOn93iM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R855" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">856</div></th><td class="s6">Qualys Slack Bot for Vulnerability Scans &amp; Reporting</td><td class="s7">Automates security operations by integrating Slack with Qualys API. Users trigger vulnerability scans and generate detailed reports via Slack modals. Employs Slack API for interactive workflows and Qualys for scanning and report generation, enhancing security task efficiency.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IBpe001HP__5L9OhxMWUYNVLPIfZTd9h">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R856" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">857</div></th><td class="s6">Qualys Report to TheHive Automator</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching finished vulnerability scan reports from Qualys via API, converts them from XML to JSON, filters new reports, creates matching cases in TheHive SOC platform, and attaches downloaded reports. Uses Qualys API, TheHive API, and n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IIQFUBcavnKDvrvC9VhsCrW80KuTl5Jl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R857" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">858</div></th><td class="s6">Parallel Sub-Workflow Execution Manager</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to start multiple sub-workflows asynchronously using HTTP webhooks, wait pseudo-synchronously for all to finish, and coordinate completion tracking with retry. Uses n8n nodes: HTTP Request, Webhook, Wait, Code, Manual Trigger for parallel task orchestration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AKiC81FPdj2WWsC5NTDdayD0oo4D6qqY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R858" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">859</div></th><td class="s6">Webinar Registration to KlickTipp Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates processing of webinar registrations from JotForm, transforms data (phone, date, URLs), and subscribes contacts with custom tags in KlickTipp CRM for targeted marketing. Uses JotForm API and KlickTipp API integrated within n8n for error-free lead management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KKflbuG3_rZKeyh4AhzMGdQ_6FKXnjcy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R859" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">860</div></th><td class="s6">Gravity Forms to KlickTipp Feedback Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates integration between Gravity Forms and KlickTipp using n8n. Captures form submissions, transforms data (phone format, UNIX timestamps, ratings), manages subscriber details and dynamic tag creation in KlickTipp. Ideal for streamlined feedback and contact management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Kj4W0IJoU-j7V4vPaOk74NTsWV2pkAkI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R860" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">861</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform to KlickTipp Quiz Integration</td><td class="s7">Automates quiz submission processing by integrating Typeform with KlickTipp. It formats quiz data, manages subscriber info including tags dynamically in KlickTipp, and supports seamless lead capture and segmentation. Uses Typeform API and KlickTipp API within n8n for workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qgJ-fP95_fbJo3UhEU7g1ujvq8tOvrYC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R861" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">862</div></th><td class="s6">AI Triathlon Coach Using Strava &amp; Gemini AI</td><td class="s7">Automates triathlon coaching by analyzing Strava activity data with Google Gemini AI. It provides personalized, data-driven training insights and motivational feedback for swimming, cycling, and running. Sends structured HTML reports via Email or WhatsApp. Tech stack: Strava API, Google Gemini (PaLM) AI, Gmail, WhatsApp API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WJKQTUMz4xyurfOKgPb0izd5f0HAbjAP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R862" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">863</div></th><td class="s6">Threads to Notion Post Archiver</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching recent Instagram Threads posts and comments using Threads API, filters and formats media and text content, then archives them into a Notion database with media embeds. Uses n8n, Threads API, and Notion API for seamless social media content archival.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hGNhjp2iU5CjECkQzSpa6E_NPrF9flai">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R863" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">864</div></th><td class="s6">Stripe to QuickBooks Payment Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Stripe payment intents to QuickBooks Online sales receipts. Uses Stripe webhooks &amp; API to retrieve customer and payment details, checks/creates customers in QuickBooks via its API, then posts sales receipts. Tech: Stripe API, QuickBooks Online API, n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13KInfYRTxe-Pb5rW_vprxS-vDn1BNQZl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R864" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">865</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Profile Enrichment via RapidAPI &amp; Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates enrichment of LinkedIn profiles listed in Google Sheets. Uses RapidAPI&#39;s Fresh LinkedIn Profile Data API to fetch detailed profile info and updates the sheet. Ideal for recruiters, sales, and marketers to streamline lead and talent data collection.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zCddxmmu7xhcVDvJWyDNEkeiCSxNHB8H">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R865" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">866</div></th><td class="s6">Email Attachment Organizer to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates saving unread Gmail attachments from a specific sender (ray.thomas@charter.com) to a designated Google Drive folder. Utilizes Gmail Trigger, file size switch-based filtering, and Google Drive API, helping to manage and categorize attachments efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MIDXyRNFSCQKiGHWtMS6-cHsJYg9Y-LP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R866" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">867</div></th><td class="s6">HTML to PDF Conversion via Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that receives HTML content through a webhook, converts it to PDF using the CustomJS HTML to PDF API, and responds with the PDF file. Tech stack includes n8n automation, CustomJS PDF toolkit, and webhook handling for dynamic PDF generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1r6KKShtvgVK-Sua7s8z_tgb1Ze03xnYJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R867" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">868</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice PDF Generator via Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts invoice data into a styled HTML invoice and generates a PDF. It uses custom JS for HTML-to-PDF conversion, processes invoice details, and responds via webhook. Ideal for automated invoice creation using n8n and a custom JS PDF toolkit.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11oEXHmVel0oXqvhle4nQPs3EtQrhMnv4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R868" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">869</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Refund &amp; Complaint Automator</td><td class="s7">Automates customer refund and complaint handling via Telegram, Freshdesk, and Monday.com. Uses Telegram trigger, Freshdesk API for ticket creation, conditional branching for refund or complaint, and Monday.com for task organization. Enables quick response and tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xmmw41R0YHKj8WdjVwWQynf3R6Pjk-vo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R869" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">870</div></th><td class="s6">RSS to Telegram Media Broadcaster</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching Instagram and Weibo RSS feeds, filters duplicates, extracts images from posts, and sends them as photos or text messages to Telegram channels. Uses n8n with RSS Feed, Function, If, and Telegram nodes integrating RSSHub API and Telegram Bot API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YhE0c2d5KX7VUMN1xPf6JVOVOeVY5pK6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R870" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">871</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform Issue Reporting &amp; Notification</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing user feedback from Typeform, logs entries to Google Sheets, filters high-severity issues (severity &gt;7), then sends alerts via Slack and email. Integrates Typeform API, Google Sheets API, Slack API, and SMTP for notifications, simplifying issue tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YSKKHIzfqensoY7LQ4ZPi7xkCcnZkI6a">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R871" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">872</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Image Metadata Tagging via Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates tagging of images in a Google Drive folder using AI image content analysis via OpenAI. Downloads new images, analyzes content, writes descriptive keywords into EXIF metadata, and updates files. Utilizes Google Drive, OpenAI API, and n8n EXIF community node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KoH4eONnHWvldVKtnJAg4W-EB9sPisC-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R872" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">873</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Backup to Nextcloud</td><td class="s7">Automates backup of all n8n workflows by fetching them via n8n REST API every 6 hours or on manual trigger, then saving JSON backups to Nextcloud cloud storage. Utilizes n8n HTTP Request, Function, Merge, and Nextcloud nodes for seamless workflow export and cloud backup.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fzRplvRS3Xw-TC0lNlA-nTQy_xhjm0UO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R873" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">874</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets Data Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Google Sheets API via OAuth2 to append, lookup, update, and read spreadsheet data. Automates managing rental info by city, modifying rent values, and returning formatted results for streamlined Google Sheets data handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_F9G9Y5hJ44HBxa9Ysf5G648YeOHwTj-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R874" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">875</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Webhook Signature Verification</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to securely verify Slack webhook signatures using HMAC SHA256 and Slack&#39;s signing secret. It ensures received requests are authentic by reconstructing the signature from headers and body, preventing forgery or unauthorized bots.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zy1cEWxx52CDqG60GrSOunJpxi4s8bE5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R875" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">876</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Email Validation &amp; Alert Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates validation of new HubSpot contact emails using HubSpot APIs and OneSimple API; sends Slack alerts for suspicious emails. Ensures contact email quality by checking deliverability, domain validity, and disposability, improving CRM data integrity.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TE2qaTRAoh-colGNheVxHZHPj4xXaA7v">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R876" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">877</div></th><td class="s6">Daily RSS to Slack Post</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching yesterday&#39;s RSS feed posts from a blog and posts them as formatted messages to a Slack channel every morning at 8 AM. Utilizes n8n workflow with RSS Feed Read, DateTime, Slack API, and custom JavaScript for message building.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1z7B6EtavWu_2ZmfFVp6FB2zXon_ihm_A">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R877" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">878</div></th><td class="s6">Notion Duplicate Page Archiver</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Notion API and custom JavaScript to identify and archive duplicate pages in a Notion database based on a specified property. Triggers daily or upon page creation to maintain a clean database automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1POJonxtM0XeMQ-EPj7NSuA8hh-mcEIjC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R878" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">879</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive Doc Summarizer to Sheet</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching the latest Google Docs file from a specified Drive folder, summarizes its contents using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and appends the summary with metadata to a Google Sheet for easy organization and quick reference.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=107BWmnFxxZmd5nth1DdqCjUGyIOMf6Pn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R879" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">880</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Image Analyzer with OpenAI</td><td class="s7">Automates image analysis in Telegram chats using n8n, OpenAI for image processing, and Telegram API for communication. Detects received images, analyzes them with OpenAI&#39;s base64 image capabilities, and sends back insightful text responses. Enhances moderation, tagging, and feedback workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1E28ojStJWq_bpS3inwZR03Mak0fJGjAv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R880" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">881</div></th><td class="s6">Email to Google Sheets Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates saving incoming Gmail emails into Google Sheets as new rows, capturing sender, subject, and snippet. Uses Gmail Trigger and Google Sheets API via OAuth2. Ideal for email logging, lead tracking, and structured email record-keeping.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CoOdsGGZiaR0cbhA8CWTkHzWiqh8yWC8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R881" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">882</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Error Notification via Line</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow triggers on flow errors and sends detailed notifications via the Line Messaging API using HTTP requests and header-based authentication. It enables real-time error alerts for efficient monitoring and quick response.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XNxEt7kNu6M94bEHw8u7hIQVjhLh4yG1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R882" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">883</div></th><td class="s6">Daylight Saving Time Change Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates detection of Daylight Saving Time changes for specified timezones. Uses n8n with JavaScript code for timezone handling, Slack API for notifications, and SMTP for email alerts. Helps users adjust schedules by notifying upcoming DST shifts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IVUbLXI6aClcBQXL_8hGUoEMWAfaBL3C">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R883" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">884</div></th><td class="s6">HN Learning Resources Recommender via Google Gemini</td><td class="s7">Automates finding top learning resources by scraping &#39;Ask HN&#39; posts on HackerNews, analyzing comments with Google Gemini AI, categorizing by resource type and difficulty, then emailing recommendations. Uses HackerNews API, Google PaLM API, and SMTP for email delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iDfrU64RDftsUUD8M-4Vn0JDiND2jraK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R884" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">885</div></th><td class="s6">Lemlist &amp; HubSpot Email Reply Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates lead reply categorization and follow-up creation using Lemlist API, HubSpot CRM, and OpenAI GPT-3 for reply analysis. It unsubscribes, tags replies as interested or out-of-office, and creates deals/tasks in HubSpot, enhancing sales workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1upH6VtuCMuH8BG-KOHZMlGPhJGSvE0XY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R885" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">886</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Image Extraction &amp; GPT-4o Analysis</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of images from PDFs via ConvertAPI and Google Drive, then analyzes images with OpenAI GPT-4o. Combines image URLs and AI analysis into a text file for easy review. Uses n8n workflow with ConvertAPI, Google Drive API, and OpenAI GPT-4o model.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uX4XkEmOtvOpiBadYAfN-Qz71rAG5CRf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R886" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">887</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Weather Forecast Chatbot via Open-Meteo API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI&#39;s GPT-based AI agent with the Open-Meteo geocoding and weather APIs. It enables users to chat and receive accurate, multi-day weather forecasts by city name through AI-managed sequential API calls, ideal for travel planning and weather info retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1p6uRKPYQT-sIcWgn6gzpbd4RM6o72szn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R887" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">888</div></th><td class="s6">Fal.ai Flux Image Generation to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates AI image creation using Fal.ai Flux API with customizable prompts, dimensions, steps, and guidance. Downloads generated images and uploads them to Google Drive. Utilizes HTTP requests, manual triggers, wait nodes, and Google Drive API integration in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EH-QtFuyNTtbm0APSd03FnpNJcBlppbJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R888" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">889</div></th><td class="s6">Email Sales Opportunity Summarizer &amp; Odoo Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing sales emails via Gmail API, summarizes inquiry details using OpenAI GPT-3.5, and creates sales opportunities in Odoo CRM. Integrates Gmail, OpenAI language model, and Odoo ERP to streamline lead management and enhance sales pipeline efficiency.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1e7x2mCE8hZ14SRwc95K4YMK1GsQvm_bc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R889" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">890</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video URLs Sync to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching YouTube video URLs from channel IDs stored in Google Sheets using YouTube Data API, then updates another Google Sheet with video titles, URLs, and publish dates. Built with n8n, Google Sheets API, and YouTube API for streamlined content tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12ECMsA9UPbp1-7zJX2hNiJ_cVX4-vLfN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R890" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">891</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Upload Multiple Files to GitHub Repo</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automating simultaneous file uploads to GitHub repos using GitHub REST API. It bypasses the native single-file limitation by creating a new git tree, commit, and updating the branch. Uses GitHub Personal Access Token for authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1b2wS1mJyMoF8ebQsybn3zXb4WfI6W8kr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R891" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">892</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered CV Screening Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates CV submission and screening for Software Engineer roles using n8n, Google Gemini (PaLM) AI for resume analysis, Gmail for notifications, and Google Sheets for candidate tracking. Streamlines HR processes with AI-driven candidate compatibility ratings and email alerts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TMnbPZfAGxTjkM4waIAitaNVXLPxniD6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R892" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">893</div></th><td class="s6">Wikipedia Data Extraction &amp; Summarization</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Wikipedia content using Bright Data API and summarizes it using Google Gemini AI models. Utilizes HTTP requests, Langchain chains for data extraction and concise summarization, and webhook for notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=120WKaU3tuKmY85Y5Edee7cV4_899aSXH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R893" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">894</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Vegan Recipes Telegram Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates sending one random vegan recipe daily via Telegram using Spoonacular API. Integrates Airtable to manage subscriber chat IDs, n8n cron for scheduling, and Telegram nodes for messaging. Welcomes new users and sends recipe image and URL automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10No1Ge3_kMriZHz9IWUIyzFhc_FHLgVR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R894" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">895</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Videos AI Summary &amp; Discord Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates summarizing YouTube video captions using YouTube API and ChatGPT (OpenAI), then posts engaging summaries to Discord via webhook. Triggered by new videos from a channel&#39;s RSS feed, it fetches English captions, converts them, creates bullet-point summaries, and shares them instantly to Discord.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15vPZeormcmyfbfETtqSqcqjdYN6F9RvV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R895" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">896</div></th><td class="s6">AI Expense Tracker with Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow leveraging OpenAI&#39;s GPT via LangChain to parse natural language expense entries from chat, convert them to structured JSON, and append them to a Google Sheets expense tracker. Integrates AI chat triggers, memory, and Google Sheets API for seamless expense logging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18q2BevceGBslyiAH-UX7JpfdlV4icSkC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R896" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">897</div></th><td class="s6">Slack AI Chatbot with n8n Slash Commands</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow enables creating a Slack AI chatbot using slash commands, integrating Slack Webhook and Slack API with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini through LangChain nodes. It automates command handling, AI response generation, and posting messages back to Slack channels.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1O1QS9dkEND9ZtZHfISEeDUAQ3pmvB8sh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R897" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">898</div></th><td class="s6">Notion Pages to Supabase Vectors with OpenAI</td><td class="s7">Automates storing Notion page texts as vector embeddings in Supabase using OpenAI API. Triggers on new Notion pages, fetches and filters content, summarizes text, generates embeddings, and saves them in a Supabase vector column for efficient semantic search.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rUPMLMFnzQePafVccOknJ8_3drSNmkZ_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R898" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">899</div></th><td class="s6">Summarize Google Sheets Feedback with GPT-4</td><td class="s7">Automates feedback summarization from Google Sheets form responses using n8n workflow. Integrates Google Sheets API to fetch data, OpenAI GPT-4 to generate summaries, Markdown-to-HTML conversion, and Gmail API to send summary reports via email.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IfbloZ0XktEUaztgbDXplnmmZ9hIjkgs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R899" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">900</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail to Notion Automated Email Processing</td><td class="s7">Automates converting Gmail emails into structured Notion pages using Gmail API, Airtable for route management, OpenAI GPT-4o for email summarization and task extraction, and Notion API. Filters and labels emails to prevent duplicates, sends error notifications, and manages active workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ig_s7TwDTo-8q1v7Z4TkZxsjA7zBwd7V">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R900" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">901</div></th><td class="s6">Audio Transcription &amp; Summarization to Notion</td><td class="s7">Automates transcription of audio files from Google Drive using OpenAI Whisper, summarizes content via GPT-4 Turbo, and stores structured summaries in Notion. Utilizes Google Drive Trigger, OpenAI API, and Notion API for seamless audio content management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WiQ1M-j2Awi7XeJCICfEU7e0A0hrtEqG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R901" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">902</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Viral Tweet Scheduler for X</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates tweeting every 6 hours with randomized posting times using OpenAI GPT-4 Turbo to generate viral tweets tailored by niche, style, and inspiration. It validates tweet length and posts to X via OAuth2 API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1E13ueNB_kbgWqQkdX2MnMH9Ae5KmHZwi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R902" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">903</div></th><td class="s6">Jira Epic Retrospective Report Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of Agile retrospective reports by fetching Jira Epic issues and comments, summarizing with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and generating actionable lessons learned documents in Google Docs. Uses Jira API, n8n workflows, Langchain AI agent, and Google Docs integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RBv5wAz__D-OCBofWd4UWDM3ewnVn2WN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R903" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">904</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Web Scraper with Bright Data &amp; Google Gemini</td><td class="s7">An automated web scraping system integrating Bright Data&#39;s MCP SDK for data extraction, Google Gemini AI for query understanding, and n8n workflows. It scrapes webpages as Markdown or HTML, triggers webhooks with results, and saves data locally for analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eQ2JMLR_sFkoNe_76ib6MLRx7EmGeqY_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R904" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">905</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chatbot with LangChain &amp; Dall-E</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered Telegram chatbot using n8n with LangChain nodes, OpenAI GPT-4o for conversation, Dall-E-3 for image generation, and Telegram API integration. It handles user chat, generates images on request, and replies with text or images, maintaining session context.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10iweJyVyAAUcZtb0rLGwBzxq-MjaaIfw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R905" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">906</div></th><td class="s6">Jira Ticket Creator from Splunk Alerts</td><td class="s7">Automates creation and updating of Jira tickets based on Splunk alert webhook data. Uses Splunk webhooks, Jira Cloud API, and n8n workflow automation to search for existing tickets, create new ones, or add comments to avoid duplicates, improving SecOps incident management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1k8iJNGphpGzUxRv7XgLfeZDnNrfvGFme">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R906" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">907</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive to Airtable File Sync &amp; Share</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing new files from a specific Google Drive folder by sharing them via email and logging metadata (file ID, name, timestamps) into Airtable. Uses Google Drive Trigger and API plus Airtable API for streamlined file management and tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1omCQiZo6gTijbCZ-sAv2lCLJOh_PPUPl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R907" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">908</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Visualizer with Mermaid.js</td><td class="s7">Visualize and explore your n8n workflows as interactive flowcharts using Mermaid.js. It uses the n8n API to fetch workflows, aggregates data, and dynamically renders diagrams with custom node shapes via Mermaid.js and Bootstrap for UI.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1la02EpkxEB_-ooFwaAqr83HohePUEJlk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R908" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">909</div></th><td class="s6">[OPS] Restore n8n Workflows from GitHub</td><td class="s7">Automates restoration of n8n workflows backed up on GitHub. Uses GitHub API to list and fetch workflow JSON files, compares with existing n8n workflows via n8n API, and creates missing ones. Ideal for workflow backup and recovery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qvFkdK9dsh-Q0y6QTCvq7e6izrKpSEiK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R909" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">910</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Notion Task Updates with ClickUp</td><td class="s7">Automates two-way synchronization between Notion and ClickUp task statuses using Notion API triggers and ClickUp webhooks. Ensures task updates in Notion reflect in ClickUp and vice versa for seamless project management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11ue-lYHJ8DiB6XzIvg4PiBharH9TNzmc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R910" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">911</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Image Upload to S3 via Modal</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates Slack interactions to upload images (.jpg, .png, .pdf) to an S3 bucket. Uses Slack Events API and Modals for user input, downloads files from Slack, uploads to S3, and posts links back to a Slack channel, enhancing file sharing efficiency.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hkUNAvaiNUYjvOSu5usDzIdhwEtWUEJb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R911" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">912</div></th><td class="s6">Dynamic Form Builder for Airtable &amp; Baserow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that dynamically generates web forms from Airtable and Baserow table schemas using their APIs. It converts database fields to n8n form fields, handles form submissions to create/update records, and manages file uploads separately.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Kel_gfl9b-XM2L6O2LBCNm2kZ80AOZaa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R912" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">913</div></th><td class="s6">Smartlead Campaign &amp; HubSpot Data Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching and synchronizing campaign and lead data from Smartlead API with HubSpot CRM, storing enriched data in Postgres, and reporting via Google Sheets. Integrates Smartlead API, HubSpot API, PostgreSQL, and Google Sheets to provide up-to-date campaign analytics and lifecycle stage tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1thnckqv7mPCgYq7M_JAbYnH1rbkJqm5i">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R913" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">914</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered US Grants Tracking &amp; Alerts</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching, AI summarizing, eligibility analysis, and tracking of latest US AI grants from Grants.gov. Uses n8n workflows with OpenAI API for summaries, Airtable as database, and Gmail for email alerts to subscribers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19KM5nVxC9GpuyNHxevKjVtVVyimQaAnt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R914" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">915</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Email Header Authentication Analyzer</td><td class="s7">Automates email header analysis using Gmail webhook or trigger in n8n. Extracts originating IP, queries IPQualityScore and IP-API for reputation and geolocation, evaluates SPF, DKIM, DMARC headers, and compiles authentication results for webhook integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GCeymqj3581vIjjAXFn9YlbK4y86jUgd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R915" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">916</div></th><td class="s6">Proxmox API AI Agent Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Proxmox VE API with Google Gemini LLM for conversational management of virtualization tasks. Utilizes Proxmox API, Gemini AI, HTTP requests, and structured output parsing to convert natural language into valid Proxmox API commands for VM lifecycle and cluster management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pYBA41CQnRIhjGHVo6Jzcb5jiT6wFrq7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R916" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">917</div></th><td class="s6">Baserow PDF Data Extraction with AI</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of data from PDFs into Baserow tables using webhooks, Baserow API, n8n workflow, and OpenAI language models. Supports dynamic prompts per field and updates rows on events like row updates and field changes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ee9E-5D4iG-MOgn7DXkmXHfEMFu81K77">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R917" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">918</div></th><td class="s6">CallForge AI Sales Call Data to Notion</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and organization of AI-processed sales call data into Notion. Integrates Gong AI transcripts, Notion databases, and handles product feedback and AI use cases with rate limiting and data validation for streamlined CRM insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1DEr1HsBDVw3n8VEPsPW13vVB9Z_QzHZq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R918" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">919</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Voice/Text to Todoist Task Creator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts Telegram voice or text messages into structured Todoist tasks. It uses Telegram API for input, OpenAI Whisper for voice transcription, GPT-4o-mini for AI task decomposition, and Todoist API for task creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13NaUqWHQ--piN7ej8Ka-y1BKAC1MtiKt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R919" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">920</div></th><td class="s6">Startup Funding News Data Extractor</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and structuring of funding news data from TechCrunch and VentureBeat sitemaps using n8n with Langchain AI (Anthropic Claude, OpenRouter Perplexity), HTML/XML parsing, and Airtable for storage. Enables comprehensive company funding research.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Uw4M9W-K--_qcFrL4vH8wN-xI69-6DXx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R920" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">921</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Telegram Survey Bot with Redis &amp; Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Conducts structured product satisfaction surveys via Telegram bot. Uses Redis for session state, Google Sheets for questions and answers storage, and OpenAI GPT models for generating follow-ups and conversational AI. Enables guided, multi-turn survey chats with dynamic follow-up questions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1p2UVKQsQfwydFPtGYH-h7JHmN4uKO_Rh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R921" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">922</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram-Based Delivery Tracking Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automates shipment tracking via Telegram bot integration, guiding drivers through delivery number input, GPS location sharing, photo uploads, and sends confirmations via Gmail. Uses Telegram API, Google Drive, Google Sheets, and Gmail within n8n workflow for logistics management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Wa0yBKpigaSf82gUfqm6dMshpZ-vkN__">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R922" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">923</div></th><td class="s6">EDI Order Email Processor with Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates processing of EDI order emails via Gmail API, parses EDI messages using JavaScript code, filters orders by type, and appends detailed order data into separate sheets in Google Sheets for return and outbound orders. Utilizes n8n, Gmail Trigger, JS parsing, and Google Sheets API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1THanfs5m-NAnAcDBDGusmDcihW_MRPap">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R923" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">924</div></th><td class="s6">Website Security Scanner &amp; Audit Report</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to scan a given website URL for client-side security vulnerabilities and misconfigurations. Uses HTTP Requests to fetch page and headers, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini models for detailed security analysis of HTTP headers and page content, merges AI insights, and emails a comprehensive, HTML report via Gmail. Ideal for developers wanting automated website security assessments.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lCLS2_SQm6pHTHvNOhwlDrBalIN6AzhU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R924" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">925</div></th><td class="s6">AI Workplace Discrimination Pattern Detector</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses ScrapingBee to extract Glassdoor reviews, employs OpenAI&#39;s LLMs to analyze demographic rating disparities, calculates statistical measures like z-scores &amp; effect sizes, and visualizes results with QuickChart, helping identify workplace discrimination patterns.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1krc9ZnDrE38AUcyGS_Ga5XoOD3_ia4Fe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R925" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">926</div></th><td class="s6">Bitrix24 Open Channel RAG Chatbot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Bitrix24 Open Channels with a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) chatbot. It uses Bitrix24 APIs, Google Gemini chat model, Ollama embeddings, Qdrant vector store, and LangChain nodes to process messages, manage chatbot lifecycle, handle files, and answer queries based on uploaded documents.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1I9D9ZDBBkHPbL-FSaGKlsQEQvEBWhUKU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R926" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">927</div></th><td class="s6">AI Telegram Bot with Supabase Memory</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram Bot API, OpenAI Assistants (via HTTP API), and Supabase database to create a context-aware AI chatbot. It stores user sessions and conversation threads to maintain memory for personalized, continuous conversations in Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LNma4q-64hzHJyBZZHngFumtyKdLGkB5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R927" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">928</div></th><td class="s6">Reddit Business Opportunity Analyzer with AI</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching and filtering Reddit posts from r/smallbusiness, analyzes business-related content using GPT-4o-mini (OpenAI API) for sentiment, summarization, and solution ideation, then categorizes results into Gmail drafts and logs insights to Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zzE6kJAnNexucf5yQCiv3X7hPssniUiy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R928" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">929</div></th><td class="s6">Etsy Data Mining Automation with Bright Data &amp; AI</td><td class="s7">Automates Etsy product data extraction using Bright Data&#39;s Web Unlocker API for scraping, enriched by Google Gemini and OpenAI for AI-driven information extraction and pagination handling. Outputs structured product info and supports webhook notifications and disk storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11-DCSKZaL2zDZABP1K07B5-tRMV0WsJg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R929" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">930</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Digital Certificate &amp; Signing Service</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automating PDF digital signing with key generation using node-forge and @signpdf libraries, plus API endpoints for uploading, signing, and downloading PDFs securely. Supports PFX cert creation and handles file management in a server environment.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rMYaRuIdIw3S7j5C__wyVD1G08FSkWuZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R930" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">931</div></th><td class="s6">AI News Summary &amp; Auto Post to X</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching the latest AI news using Perplexity AI API and posts concise headlines with article links to X (formerly Twitter) every 21 hours. Uses n8n for scheduling, HTTP requests, and Twitter OAuth2 API integration for social media automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=130rejG3SMYnIZIpMWC7PLZD9APHc4hJo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R931" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">932</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Chatbot AI Assistant Integration</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating HubSpot Conversations with OpenAI Assistants to automate chatbot interactions. It handles message retrieval, OpenAI thread management, action execution, and response posting using HubSpot API, OpenAI API (assistants v1), Airtable for thread mapping, and external company data APIs (listafirme.ro).</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pkejDS8pYKkFmxyAqnz0n64HfJ7b26fy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R932" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">933</div></th><td class="s6">Billbee Address Validation Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates address validation for Billbee orders using Endereco API. Fetches shipping data from Billbee, validates and corrects addresses via Endereco service, updates Billbee, and applies tags for validation status. Uses Billbee API, Endereco API, and n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Xj8Ddz_kWPveBS9YftSwMMQ24y6GNAkx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R933" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">934</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Upload Images and Embed to Qdrant</td><td class="s7">Automates batch importing of crop images from Google Cloud Storage, creates multimodal embeddings via Voyage AI API, and uploads them to Qdrant vector database with cluster and payload indexing setup. Ideal for anomaly detection using agricultural crop datasets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bpDFnYIlDs3xvyN10SAMBitYTgULJpft">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R934" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">935</div></th><td class="s6">KNN Image Classifier for Land Types</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that classifies satellite land-use images using KNN. It embeds images via Voyage AI&#39;s multimodal embeddings API, queries Qdrant vector DB for nearest neighbors, and applies majority voting with tie resolution to output land type classes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1G9Qmw5TqbGABAf_emsABs5PLuDGMLECk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R935" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">936</div></th><td class="s6">Medoids Setup for Crop Anomaly Detection</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow sets cluster centers and thresholds for anomaly detection in agricultural crop data using Qdrant vector DB, Voyage AI multimodal embeddings, and Scipy. Enables precise identification of cluster representatives and scoring for anomaly detection with Qdrant Cloud API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1R32QYNjogTAxnzc_fGL28SKB0XaWTmtF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R936" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">937</div></th><td class="s6">Crop Image Anomaly Detection Tool</td><td class="s7">An anomaly detection tool for crop images using Qdrant Cloud for vector search and Voyage AI multimodal embeddings API. It identifies if an input image URL depicts a known crop or an anomaly against a prepared agricultural crops dataset. Built with n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1G4g5xsy05HO-KrijtOg95ZFRSXIzPENj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R937" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">938</div></th><td class="s6">Venafi Slack CertBot: Automated Cert Requests</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Slack API, Venafi TLS Protect Cloud, VirusTotal, and OpenAI to automate Certificate Signing Requests. Uses Slack modals for inputs, VirusTotal for domain risk analysis, AI for report generation, and conditionally auto-issues or requests manual approval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_pewj2rrmXPLKpOYLDgy4hhoXaj1qXEg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R938" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">939</div></th><td class="s6">OpenRouter LLM Chatbot via LangChain</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating multiple LLM models through OpenRouter API using LangChain nodes to handle chat triggers, memory, and agent logic. Enables customizable large language model interactions with session memory and dynamic prompt input.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dcF6rzUa6paIKH5wXrrizRwL4L_g-jtA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R939" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">940</div></th><td class="s6">Todoist Weekly Completed Tasks Review</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly retrieval of completed Todoist tasks using Todoist API. Filters out unwanted projects, formats tasks by completion date into an HTML email, and sends a summary every Friday. Built with n8n automation, HTTP Request, JavaScript code, and email nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18jTyuuqvSgveYj8lzH6cWXLoWkYfjdnU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R940" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">941</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Gmail Error Notification Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on workflow errors (execution and trigger-level) and sends detailed error notification emails via Gmail. Includes error details, stack traces, and direct links to workflows and executions. Uses n8n Error Trigger and Gmail nodes for robust error handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10GLZHWYvAQSxYDLreRn8Cs5MmSnAatFa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R941" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">942</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Shodan IP &amp; Port Security Monitor</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that weekly checks specified IPs and ports via Shodan API for unexpected open ports, formats results in Markdown tables, and sends alerts to TheHive security platform. Uses HTTP Request, Markdown, and TheHive nodes for automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WpZ3eIxxoUbCGkbZrUYfhMicfwvXSuda">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R942" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">943</div></th><td class="s6">3D Model to Spinning Video Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of 3D spinning videos from AI-generated images using PiAPI&#39;s Midjourney, GPT-4o-image, and Kling APIs. Workflow includes image generation, transformation to 3D figurines, and final video rendering with status checks and waits, all orchestrated in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nMrepg2i7-HZaZ4TrkkBWzn1q0KwP2HV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R943" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">944</div></th><td class="s6">SRT Subtitle File Translator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating SRT subtitle file translation using Google Translate API. It extracts text from uploaded SRT files, processes subtitle blocks, translates content to selected languages (e.g., EN, JP), then rebuilds and returns the translated SRT file. Utilizes n8n form triggers and file processing nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RxO6279XqthZyMCT826OiFqmSCe0dHeD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R944" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">945</div></th><td class="s6">ParquetReader File Converter to JSON</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts uploaded Parquet, Avro, ORC, and Feather files to JSON format using the ParquetReader API. It uses a webhook to receive files, sends them via multipart/form-data to the API, and parses the JSON response, enabling easy data transformation and integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1T8YYdr81xOLd-w_Xvt7jrA7U8EkvODAO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R945" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">946</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Online List Builder</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates building curated online lists by querying Google search with Airtop API, extracting people info from web pages, deduplicating results, and appending to Google Sheets. Uses Airtop API, Google Sheets, and custom JavaScript.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14yXTYvacS-1CpqyKDzl3N1QmsPpMa0_o">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R946" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">947</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Documentation Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates documentation for n8n workflows using OpenAI GPT-4, Mermaid.js for diagrams, and Docsify for Markdown rendering. Supports viewing, editing, auto-generating, and saving workflow docs stored as Markdown files.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Wq_Tw9xGUQ3M8gFIDWTlSeb5ChhB9wFh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R947" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">948</div></th><td class="s6">Gumroad to Beehiiv Newsletter &amp; CRM Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates adding Gumroad sales to Beehiiv newsletter subscriptions and Google Sheets CRM, plus Telegram notifications. Uses Gumroad API webhook, Beehiiv HTTP API, Google Sheets OAuth2, and Telegram bot. Ideal for creators syncing sales with newsletter &amp; CRM.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Tu8WW13G0XoBFfJejCE5QEnhaHFSfN-E">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R948" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">949</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Profile Lead Collector via SerpAPI</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of LinkedIn profiles by keyword and location using SerpAPI for Google search, OpenAI API for data enrichment, and NocoDB for storage. Outputs an Excel file and database-ready lead list for sales or marketing use. Ideal for lead generation with no-code tools.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10prYIw8ebnh4VQii3_Svqj_jbZLZbNZ0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R949" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">950</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive to PGVector Loader</td><td class="s7">Automates loading of documents from Google Drive into a Postgres PGVector database with OpenAI embeddings. Supports PDF, text, and JSON files, uses Langchain nodes for processing, enabling vector search-ready storage and management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xpmwWO2Jy8eNudR0xUC6Gka9XXVXnVKR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R950" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">951</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Thread Generator with AI Agent</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses Langchain&#39;s chat trigger, OpenAI GPT-4o model, and Twitter API to create engaging Twitter threads. It employs a conversational AI agent that drafts informative, friendly tweets and replies, forming coherent, natural threads with memory context for flow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kRhct0WAsNvPjAUQYjLkPAuBicvbCBI9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R951" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">952</div></th><td class="s6">AI Website Screenshot Analyzer</td><td class="s7">Automate website screenshot capture using URLbox API, then analyze the image content with OpenAI&#39;s vision capabilities in n8n workflow. Combines URL capture, AI image analysis, and data merging for concise website summaries. Requires URLbox &amp; OpenAI API keys.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10pzRPd1DILdtX-smpMbEgifIBuhrxTB4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R952" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">953</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Postgres Sync Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates synchronization of data from Google Sheets to a Postgres database using n8n. Utilizes Google Sheets API and Postgres nodes to retrieve, compare, insert, and update rows on a scheduled hourly basis, ensuring database consistency with spreadsheet updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tQTkvRzHePBSlweloKXY-Sz3dX17mOaq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R953" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">954</div></th><td class="s6">Backlink Live Status Checker</td><td class="s7">Automates backlink verification by reading URLs from Google Sheets and checking their live status using DataForSEO&#39;s On-Page API. Updates sheet with backlink statuses (&#39;Live&#39;, &#39;Lost&#39;, or &#39;Lost (Nofollow)&#39;). Integrates Google Sheets, DataForSEO API, and n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qs54mPFMCEczNYG63y6Ohop-WXOJpRV4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R954" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">955</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Metadata Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching latest YouTube videos, extracting transcripts via Apify API, generating SEO-optimized descriptions and tags with OpenAI GPT-4 and Google Gemini models, and updating video metadata. Enables scheduling and batch processing of videos using YouTube OAuth2 API within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18MXHdCu_tgm9QG4ecg0dp4UC95vML9pu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R955" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">956</div></th><td class="s6">MAIA Health Check URL Monitor</td><td class="s7">Automates website health monitoring by fetching URLs from Google Sheets, checking their HTTP status, and sending alerts via Telegram. Utilizes Google Sheets API, HTTP Request node, and Telegram Bot API, enabling easy scheduled uptime notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Oxm5O9xwIJ9PlSV32DgnUXAb6YHxhsUU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R956" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">957</div></th><td class="s6">Brand Content Extraction &amp; Sentiment Analysis</td><td class="s7">Automates brand content extraction from websites via Bright Data Web Unlocker API, uses Google Gemini AI for textual data extraction, summarization, and structured sentiment analysis, and sends results through webhooks and files.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FEySkzRXFNB71V42P1s2tDM3i1DktNu3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R957" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">958</div></th><td class="s6">Multi-LLM Testing &amp; Analysis with LM Studio</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to test multiple local LLMs via LM Studio API, analyze readability and language metrics, and save results to Google Sheets. Uses LM Studio server API, n8n LangChain nodes, and Google Sheets integration to track and compare LLM outputs effectively.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_LYVWLleMKwp4R-0fyVTcIcZi-H_qaEf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R958" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">959</div></th><td class="s6">Email to Todoist Task Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates converting Gmail emails into Todoist tasks using n8n workflow with Gmail API, Todoist API, and OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4 mini model. Summarizes email content, proposes actions, and manages task lifecycle for efficient email-task integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1n2Iy6lL8tT4PwTT2jxEe1DAEzcwhQacc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R959" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">960</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Comment Sentiment Analyzer</td><td class="s7">Automated workflow to extract YouTube video URLs from Google Sheets, fetch video comments via YouTube Data API v3, analyze sentiment using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini model, and log results and timestamps back to Google Sheets for tracking and analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tnhVW_BKMN0aRevTxSJ7cX80FCz1ay_u">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R960" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">961</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Image Metadata Tagging</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automatically tags images uploaded to a specific Google Drive folder by analyzing their content with OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o vision model and embedding keywords into the image&#39;s metadata. Integrates Google Drive and OpenAI APIs for seamless image content analysis and metadata updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1y8CrST-VpHHRYifcgj-uBgfvcFAP2j5t">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R961" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">962</div></th><td class="s6">Meeting Booking to Newsletter &amp; CRM Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates adding meeting attendees from Cal.com to Google Sheets and Beehiiv newsletter, with Telegram notifications. Integrates Cal.com webhook, Google Sheets API, Beehiiv API, and Telegram bot for seamless CRM and newsletter management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oO7F2lZLd2jGBJrKixMASdrrYAU_XnXO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R962" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">963</div></th><td class="s6">Multipage Website Scraper with Jina.ai &amp; Google Drive</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow scrapes multipage websites using sitemap XMLs, processes content with Jina.ai&#39;s no-API-key web scraper, extracts titles and markdown, and saves them to Google Drive. It automates website content collection and organization efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1shsRrjYRx4-rK5Fg7tjVfNDDZrfbrA3n">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R963" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">964</div></th><td class="s6">Line AI Chatbot with Groq &amp; Llama3</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating LINE Messaging API with Groq&#39;s Llama 3.3 AI model for conversational AI responses. It handles user messages from LINE, sends them to Groq&#39;s API, and replies with AI-generated content. Uses HTTP webhook and REST APIs for automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fdN7DebIFtv6A7nTvvKaUFRdCPpU5Xq9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R964" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">965</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly News Scraper &amp; Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly scraping of news posts from Colt&#39;s website without RSS feed. Uses CSS selectors for extracting titles, dates, and links, then summarizes and extracts keywords via OpenAI GPT-4 API. Stores results in a NocoDB SQL database for further processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16hbOiFj1KCo5lBw2u56ljrW3588z28m1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R965" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">966</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Invoice Attachments to Google Drive &amp; Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates processing of unread Gmail emails with PDF invoices by saving attachments to Google Drive, extracting invoice data using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4, and appending results to Google Sheets for reconciliation. Integrates Gmail API, Google Drive API, Google Sheets API, and OpenAI GPT-4.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1l7YrSJ_4IPcLxk7HxmMPiZnspO6vNGMm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R966" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">967</div></th><td class="s6">360° Virtual Try-on Video Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of 360° virtual try-on clothing videos using Kling API via PiAPI. Integrates HTTP requests, status checks, and wait nodes in n8n workflow. Ideal for fashion e-commerce and content creators seeking immersive try-on experiences.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wq9vJYISCf3byDuHXVU_n_YBJ3K9FZu5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R967" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">968</div></th><td class="s6">Discord AI Chat Agent with MCP Integration</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that enables natural language chat interaction in Discord via MCP protocol, using OpenAI GPT-4o model as AI agent. It listens to chat messages, processes with Langchain AI agent, and interacts with a customizable MCP server for powerful Discord bot capabilities.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ycWfQA_pSXZkExBYGx6amTznX1deTdTJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R968" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">969</div></th><td class="s6">Colombian Electronic Invoice Processor</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and organization of Colombian electronic invoices from Gmail ZIP attachments. Uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via LangChain to parse PDF and XML invoice data, validates totals, saves PDFs to Google Drive, and logs details in Google Sheets for easy tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nX9raf9K27JJ17gbhl_0mx0ns0CmG4Il">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R969" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">970</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Trending Content Insight Generator</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered n8n workflow leveraging OpenAI and YouTube APIs to help creators find and analyze trending YouTube videos by niche. It uses Langchain agent, YouTube Data API, and OpenAI language models to provide insightful, data-driven content trends from recent videos.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rVRf7cvzIP2Ae5TeQH6I0dleg7c4-661">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R970" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">971</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Transcript Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that extracts and cleans YouTube video transcripts using the YouTube Transcript RapidAPI. It takes a video URL input via a form, fetches transcript data through API, processes and cleans the text for easy use. Stack: n8n, RapidAPI, HTTP Request Node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13bm8zGdCvzxD6wmiEpQAbZKbXuHtNzI6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R971" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">972</div></th><td class="s6">Competitor Pricing Monitor &amp; Alert System</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring competitor pricing by fetching URLs from Google Sheets, using Airtop AI to summarize and compare pricing plans, filters changes, updates the sheet, and sends Slack alerts. Integrates Google Sheets API, Airtop AI, and Slack API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=167A64n4Ryp0qyXoNDJTIMouUarZo4NDP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R972" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">973</div></th><td class="s6">ICP Company Scoring Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates Ideal Customer Profile scoring by extracting company data from Google Sheets, analyzing LinkedIn data via Airtop AI, and updating scores back to the sheet. Tech stack includes Google Sheets API and Airtop AI for detailed LinkedIn company profile analysis and scoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13cFeHnvercZkv9e18kyBZuuYijHMAGMX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R973" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">974</div></th><td class="s6">Restore n8n Workflows from GitHub Backup</td><td class="s7">Automates restoring n8n workflows by fetching JSON backup files from a specified GitHub repository path using GitHub API and n8n native nodes. It requires GitHub API credentials and n8n API to recreate workflows seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15QnXY9c4Hzw4bwlQ0NK6wU4JT9Hv0Ywz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R974" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">975</div></th><td class="s6">Airflow DAG Run Trigger &amp; Monitor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to trigger Apache Airflow DAG runs and monitor their state using Airflow REST API with HTTP Basic Auth. It supports waiting with retry logic until the DAG run succeeds or fails, returning task results via XCom. Useful for automating Airflow DAG execution and status retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eBn-fNYM5dAGxXU0jjGkqDWrMwFYipGv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R975" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">976</div></th><td class="s6">Custom AI Chat Agent with LangChain &amp; Gemini</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates a self-hosted AI chat agent using LangChain and Google Gemini API. Features include conversation memory buffer, custom prompt engineering for a Chinese-speaking persona, and webhook-triggered chat interface.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13IL3Rkurdf3cC6PmLdEesU7OXD85P_7A">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R976" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">977</div></th><td class="s6">Sync Jira Issues &amp; Comments to Notion DB</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Jira issue events (created, updated, deleted) with a Notion database, updating issue details and statuses in real-time. Utilizes Jira Webhooks, Notion API, conditional logic (IF, Switch nodes), and JavaScript for data transformation in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zjq5sbWKZMBG6_eUO_GvrvtgXfAOf2mU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R977" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">978</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Auto Post from Medium Articles</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automatically fetches Medium articles by tag twice daily using RapidAPI, filters out posted ones tracked in Airtable, posts new articles with images to LinkedIn, and sends Telegram notifications for each successful post. Utilizes Airtable, LinkedIn API, RapidAPI Medium API, and Telegram bot.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JSKB4pxe2r0vDk6pG5u2oKvuEcP_QIec">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R978" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">979</div></th><td class="s6">Qdrant Vector DB Embedding Pipeline</td><td class="s7">Automates embedding of JSON documents from FTP into Qdrant vector DB using OpenAI embeddings. Uses FTP for file retrieval, OpenAI &#39;text-embedding-ada-002&#39; for embeddings, Qdrant Vector Store for storage, and Langchain nodes for splitting and loading. Ideal for semantic search setups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SQGJWVtyAaM8NmS_oN8ICNs24_bhZwI7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R979" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">980</div></th><td class="s6">OpenSea NFT Analytics Agent</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and the OpenSea API to fetch and analyze NFT collection stats, wallet events, and market trends. Provides real-time NFT insights, supports multiple endpoints, and ensures compliant, structured NFT data retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1o74K896ZeNyVvTZLQANi9kFywwruqblS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R980" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">981</div></th><td class="s6">Palo Alto Security Advisory Monitor</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of Palo Alto Networks security advisories via RSS feed, filters for relevant products, creates Jira issues for critical alerts, and emails customers. Utilizes RSS Feed, Jira API, Gmail API, and dynamic filtering for streamlined security alert management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qnHL9yc933e9BNZpTXYYpqPhVBEHXcSY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R981" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">982</div></th><td class="s6">Stripe Payment Order Sync &amp; Customer Info Extraction</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Stripe payment events, auto-retrieves detailed customer info and product purchased from Stripe API using webhook triggers and HTTP requests in n8n for seamless order data handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JuZ0kRP7zLKz8iAwv5tpuih08jJVx1hh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R982" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">983</div></th><td class="s6">Error Logging with Rate-Limited Alerts</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that captures workflow errors, logs them into a PostgreSQL database (via NocoDB schema), and limits alert notifications (email and push) to one every 5 minutes to avoid overload. Includes manual cleanup and extensible error handling hooks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cbywIlHzN8S959svDi5mUx9Z-0yvraUb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R983" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">984</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Capture &amp; Validation Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing form leads with n8n Form Trigger, validates emails via Hunter API, updates Google Sheets, and notifies via Gmail and Discord webhook. Ensures authentic lead data management with seamless integration of form, email verification, spreadsheet, and messaging services.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AuZqMVAedEnbTDzu92yOpkDM7qXIug93">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R984" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">985</div></th><td class="s6">Google Maps Lead Extraction to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of business leads from Google Maps using Dumpling AI API and logs them into Google Sheets. Includes place details like name, address, rating, website, phone, and booking links. Uses n8n HTTP Request, Split Out, and Google Sheets nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zTq5185KwBtE9QXUjvkukinUzZFDfeyi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R985" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">986</div></th><td class="s6">Email To-Do ➔ Google Tasks Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates task creation by capturing Gmail emails labeled &#39;To-Do&#39; using Gmail API and creating Google Tasks via Google Tasks API. Utilizes n8n workflow with OAuth2 credentials for seamless integration, helping users turn emails into actionable tasks effortlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Wx_HGCiuHUhMVC9pR0__DrCe8i_hG38M">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R986" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">987</div></th><td class="s6">LINE Chatbot with Google Calendar &amp; Gmail AI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating LINE messaging with Google Calendar and Gmail using OpenAI &amp; LangChain AI. It enables conversational AI responses, calendar event creation/reading, and email reading via LINE chatbot, enhancing productivity and user assistance.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BJZtGKqSmSrpeO1SM4qoBczLj1bP2FqP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R987" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">988</div></th><td class="s6">OpenSea NFT Data AI Agent</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered n8n workflow integrating OpenSea API and GPT-4o Mini to retrieve, analyze, and process NFT collections, user profiles, contracts, NFTs, payment tokens, and traits. Enables real-time structured NFT insights with advanced query support and session memory.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ot41RyskgESEhvVPzr-5LcS7pug7-MyS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R988" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">989</div></th><td class="s6">Web Data Search &amp; Summarization with Gemini AI</td><td class="s7">Automates web data retrieval and summarization using Bright Data&#39;s scraping API, Perplexity search, and Google Gemini AI models. Extracts data snapshots, processes and summarizes content via LangChain integration, then sends results to webhooks for notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LgTjQfGPen0RTqCFtM5EODzQ3fJRkk9Z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R989" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">990</div></th><td class="s6">OpenID Connect (OIDC) Authentication Flow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow implementing OpenID Connect client login using OAuth2 with PKCE. Utilizes webhook, HTTP requests to auth, token, and userinfo endpoints, and dynamic HTML responses for login and welcome pages. Supports Keycloak and similar providers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oYgY01eMI2IT18DtA4HKfcViSl95LRNL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R990" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">991</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Orders UTM Data to Baserow</td><td class="s7">Automates daily extraction of Shopify orders with UTM parameters using Shopify GraphQL API. Transforms and filters data, then stores enriched order details in Baserow database. Utilizes n8n integration workflows with Shopify API and Baserow API for marketing attribution tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17PO09MTM-HEuP2ngB0zeaV7vLoWl8Kz7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R991" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">992</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Import CSV Files to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates importing multiple CSV files from a folder into a Google Sheet using n8n. It reads CSVs, removes duplicate users, filters only subscribers, sorts by subscription date, and updates the sheet via Google Sheets API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ur5mC1T6rzAGfZEQoQHR3E7R5hqwAiYw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R992" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">993</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Dynamic Clarification Form</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini model to analyze open-ended form responses and dynamically generate follow-up questions to avoid redundancy, optimizing data capture. It combines n8n forms, Langchain output parsing, and filtering to create adaptive multi-step forms for AI consultancy lead qualification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gec_Tj70kD8mdoy9Lu-SlYDlQNbSqhUE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R993" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">994</div></th><td class="s6">AI Travel Planner with MongoDB &amp; Google Gemini</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered travel assistant built with n8n using Google Gemini for chat, MongoDB Atlas for chat memory and vector search, and OpenAI embeddings. It ingests points of interest, enabling intelligent travel recommendations based on up-to-date vectorized data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12p4SGk1asBRQH9f7HitEcM6rda2YlXau">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R994" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">995</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify to Odoo Customer Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing of new Shopify customers to Odoo CRM contacts using Shopify webhook trigger and Odoo API integration for contact creation and deduplication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OY5BBrrc6pmFORY-0lKFx-EtClL5-wlx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R995" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">996</div></th><td class="s6">AI T-Shirt Design Redesign from Image URL</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses OpenAI APIs (GPT-4o, image analysis, and image generation) combined with Langchain AI Agent to analyze a T-shirt mockup image URL, creatively refine its design prompt, and generate a new high-quality T-shirt artwork image. Automates apparel redesign with AI.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wDe2OnrZdJZZFdzDgrU_sxrPAnQWeLWS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R996" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">997</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Channel Video Stats Tracker</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching and storing YouTube channel videos data using YouTube API and PostgreSQL. Retrieves recent videos, filters shorts, calculates average views, and tracks best-performing videos from last 2 weeks. Built with n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KMD4lz3xD4DVZNDtlbpN8tOD82CwwFK3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R997" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">998</div></th><td class="s6">Thai Line ChatBot with Google Sheets Memory</td><td class="s7">An automated Thai-language chatbot for LINE using Google Gemini AI and Google Sheets to store and retrieve user conversation history as context memory. Built with n8n, integrating LINE Messaging API, LangChain AI Agent, and Google Sheets API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ican02udD8Alcrg6POh1Iqtd0OccQAoD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R998" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">999</div></th><td class="s6">LLM Output Comparison with OpenRouter &amp; Sheets</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to compare outputs of two language models via OpenRouter API, displaying results side-by-side in chat and logging them into Google Sheets. Features isolated model memory, supports OpenAI and Vertex AI, enabling manual or automated evaluation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dDZ3GgtT5-Vs6hDWPmOgGVda7MyGfU04">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R999" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1000</div></th><td class="s6">Pipedrive Organization Data Enrichment</td><td class="s7">Automates enrichment of Pipedrive organizations by scraping their website using ScrapingBee, summarizing company info with OpenAI GPT-4o, adding a detailed note in Pipedrive, and sending Slack notifications. Utilizes Pipedrive API, ScrapingBee API, OpenAI GPT-4o, and Slack integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17DSYqsbQYQN6BHyGS5fXtn_VAVPxye3q">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1000" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1001</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Contact Manager with Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates contact management combining OpenAI GPT-4o and Airtable APIs. Uses AI agent for intelligent querying, adding, and updating contacts seamlessly, ideal for CRM automation and productivity enhancement.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nUCJDHzorvbDZzIpPoaceG5w_PgXnnxC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1001" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1002</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Transcript Summarizer &amp; Telegram Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction, summarization, and analysis of YouTube video transcripts using YouTube API, a custom YouTube transcripter, and GPT-4o mini. Sends structured summaries and video info to a Telegram channel. Built with n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GsLnfN_PDRzwMgf1m1va2O2iOPzv-iek">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1002" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1003</div></th><td class="s6">Vision-Based AI Web Scraper with Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses Google Sheets, ScrapingBee API, and Google Gemini-1.5-Pro AI model to extract structured e-commerce data from website screenshots. It falls back to HTML scraping converted to Markdown for accuracy, outputting organized JSON results to Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-ebYzwaby3kowcwxpCy3enVdT__uCpik">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1003" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1004</div></th><td class="s6">FLUX Image Inpainting Editor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating FLUX-Fill API for advanced image inpainting. Provides a web-based editor using Konva.js and img-comparison-slider to edit images with mask and prompt inputs, then processes via FLUX-Fill, returning edited images seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cVvhmUk9pw3j8JAAy6aUkJlcJl-9O0qZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1004" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1005</div></th><td class="s6">DeepSeek Chat &amp; Reasoning Agent</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating DeepSeek&#39;s AI models (deepseek-chat &amp; deepseek-reasoner) and Ollama local model for advanced conversational AI with reasoning. Uses Langchain nodes, HTTP requests, memory buffer, and OpenAI-compatible APIs to manage chat interactions and multi-turn memory.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1i_rvjRfBKmfS-T61vgT6MbIPoWHm-NRN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1005" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1006</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chatbot with Long Term Memory</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram Bot API with DeepSeek AI (compatible with OpenAI API) and Google Docs for long-term memory storage. It validates Telegram user identity, routes message types, processes chats with AI, and saves user-specific memories to enable personalized, context-aware conversations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1O7tUqn-O9c5PyP_e5zm7OtXxR-T5nTH3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1006" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1007</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Documentation System</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow generates, views, edits, and saves Markdown documentation for n8n workflows using Docsify, Mermaid.js, and OpenAI GPT-4 API. It auto-creates workflow docs with interactive Mermaid diagrams, live Markdown editor, and serves HTML/Markdown content via webhooks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1s3SIWfr8JidJbpouJc89INi74vqddNcj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1007" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1008</div></th><td class="s6">Perplexity AI Article Formatter</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrating Perplexity.ai API with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to convert structured article data into professional, single-line HTML content. Uses AI for research, content enhancement, and HTML formatting to automate article generation with rich metadata and hashtags.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lGg8UoywydSUqQKWfobKc3aYY5fJONvS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1008" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1009</div></th><td class="s6">n8n AI Agent for Creator Leaderboard Stats</td><td class="s7">Aggregates n8n community data from GitHub JSONs to generate detailed AI-powered Markdown reports on top creators and their workflows. Utilizes n8n HTTP Request nodes, merges datasets, filters by username, and employs OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for insightful community analytics and trending workflow stats.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VR6A8VnnEM2QNtRRrBgQX4_fvxLvqU68">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1009" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1010</div></th><td class="s6">LM Studio Multi-LLM Testing &amp; Analysis</td><td class="s7">Automates testing and comparison of multiple local LLMs via LM Studio server. Uses HTTP requests, LangChain nodes, OpenAI API credentials, and Google Sheets for logging. Analyzes response metrics like readability, word count, and timing for informed LLM evaluation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TVk-T1QKdH7gFtbiDYnhJKOfL8uXuzof">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1010" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1011</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Bot: AI Text, Audio &amp; Image Handler</td><td class="s7">An automated Telegram bot workflow using n8n. It sets up Telegram webhooks and processes incoming messages with AI capabilities: transcribes voice to text, analyzes images with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, classifies text messages, and routes them accordingly. Integrates Telegram API, Langchain OpenAI nodes, and n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yMXpeMaLZSVJSEIaaFhFoOYFw4Mn9jUI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1011" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1012</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Creators Leaderboard Reporting Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates daily reporting of the top n8n community creators and workflows using GitHub data sources, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Google Gemini LLM for insights. Generates markdown reports, saves to Google Drive, and distributes via Gmail and Telegram, highlighting community trends and top contributors.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iCONYwtV3gN-bYAwQ65eqyBS6nmp3E5x">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1012" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1013</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot &amp; Lemlist Hiring Lead Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates hiring lead management by integrating Lonescale job intent webhook with Dropcontact enrichment, HubSpot CRM for company/contact handling, Lemlist campaigns, and Slack notifications. Tech stack: HubSpot API, Lemlist API, Dropcontact API, Slack API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TkAPPeMImGNksvDGH7iNsrmx8uBsELv_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1013" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1014</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail PDF Attachment Filter &amp; Google Drive Upload</td><td class="s7">Automates filtering PDF email attachments by text content using OpenAI, then uploads matched PDFs to a Google Drive folder. Integrates Gmail, OpenAI, and Google Drive via n8n. Ideal for processing invoices, payslips, or contracts received by email automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hmjK15J2-UMFdtkgc7wwiYs1TJK5OEjR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1014" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1015</div></th><td class="s6">AI Email Auto-Reply and Feedback Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates email replies using OpenAI GPT via Gmail trigger; stores incoming emails, generated replies, and feedback in Google Sheets for fine-tuning. Utilizes Gmail OAuth2, OpenAI API, and Google Sheets OAuth2 for seamless AI-driven email handling and feedback recording.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hh5KwutgDWPPj-ITgMVMMdhFUj3yucfD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1015" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1016</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Notion Ideas Summary to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly aggregation of new product ideas from a Notion database, filters by UX-related ideas, counts unique entries, and posts a summary message to a specified Slack channel. Utilizes Notion API, Slack API, and n8n&#39;s scheduling and data processing nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1y2mSMN0b1KMywuz0X3bbbBomvKnS3jBr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1016" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1017</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail to Notion Email Archiver</td><td class="s7">Automates archiving labeled Gmail emails to a Notion database by creating pages for new emails and removing labels when marked done. Uses Gmail API and Notion API, triggered every minute for timely email management and productivity.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ogPnEmpy1MmZNDfBNCH_mlMi0Mh9UQqH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1017" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1018</div></th><td class="s6">Podcast Transcript Summarizer &amp; Digest Sender</td><td class="s7">Automates summarizing a podcast transcript with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, extracts key topics and questions, enriches them via Wikipedia research, formats the content in HTML, and emails a digest using Gmail. Utilizes n8n, LangChain modules, OpenAI API, and Wikipedia tool.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1g63_Uk0Njly-J6EkYXj2MF_ipuHwqtQc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1018" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1019</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Driven Personalized Marketing Emails</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates personalized marketing email campaigns using LangChain and OpenAI GPT-4-mini. It analyzes customer purchase and feedback data, generates tailored email content, and conditionally adds coupons. Includes email HTML templating and SMTP sending via n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zjWWcsGzdLRMesA6lbGCW3sVrhV-a2kx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1019" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1020</div></th><td class="s6">Nextcloud Folder &amp; File Move Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates moving folders and all their files/subfolders within Nextcloud using Nextcloud API. Supports recursive subfolder processing, folder structure replication, and sequential file moves to handle rate limits in external storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=111wx9CX5zGzDQ3K_fa02ZLvh1EK_gkEO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1020" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1021</div></th><td class="s6">TTS Voice &amp; Email Verification Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates sending TTS voice calls via ClickSend API and email verification through SMTP for secure user verification. Features form input, code generation, voice &amp; email code verification, and user feedback. Tech: n8n, ClickSend API, SMTP, JavaScript.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iH_kcVs7UuGOI9407IuljcN1oLrBdwW_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1021" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1022</div></th><td class="s6">Structured Data Extraction &amp; AI Analysis Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow for structured data extraction using Bright Data Web Unlocker API, processed by Google Gemini PaLM AI models for topic extraction, sentiment analysis, and trend clustering by location and category. Saves results to files and supports webhook notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KJQ1HTUgNYbzrOxb5yAMrfkjs2cnfCE5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1022" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1023</div></th><td class="s6">Printify Product Title &amp; Description Updater</td><td class="s7">An automation workflow integrating Printify API, Google Sheets, and OpenAI to update product titles and descriptions. It uses AI to generate engaging ecommerce content following custom brand guidelines, syncing updates when sheet rows change.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CLs_YWZ6uKke6XUyHdzNGMAbK31ISced">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1023" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1024</div></th><td class="s6">Blockchain DEX Screener Insights Agent</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to provide real-time insights on decentralized exchange (DEX) data via DexScreener API endpoints. It processes user queries from Telegram, fetching token profiles, boosts, pairs, orders, and pools to deliver detailed blockchain DEX analytics.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZZYLORIPvlja7HepQtOHVomWpRljTi7w">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1024" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1025</div></th><td class="s6">Dialpad Call to Syncro Ticket Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that integrates Dialpad webhook events with Syncro MSP API to sync call data and create/update support tickets automatically. Uses HTTP Request nodes for Syncro API, processes contact/customer data, and logs activities into Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Hz1zKFaoBNvo6tiGXLo2OWxuWLWrbR8P">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1025" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1026</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Webpage Fetch and Markdown Converter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Langchain AI Agent with OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini and HTTP requests to fetch, sanitize, simplify, and convert webpage HTML content into Markdown. Handles errors, limits length, and offers a simplified or full content mode.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1P2LTrYWmJW3lLMFE1W_rq_JlGmzjy0rf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1026" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1027</div></th><td class="s6">Icypeas Bulk Domain Scan from Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automate bulk domain scans using Icypeas API by reading company data from Google Sheets. Uses Google Sheets node, custom JavaScript for API auth with HMAC-SHA1 signing, and HTTP POST request for domain search tasks. Ideal for bulk domain research and verification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mEB7F2eGJ1ZltnAlNdsuRgXjYRG4xcsj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1027" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1028</div></th><td class="s6">G2 Competitor Review Monitor</td><td class="s7">Automates daily monitoring of competitor reviews on G2 using ScrapingBee API for scraping, extracts and converts review data to Markdown, stores results in Google Sheets, and sends new review alerts to Slack for real-time team updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Oy5ODvTIsnDVMMTWsD-2Ms0ol-Un-Jcr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1028" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1029</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Inventory Alert to Discord</td><td class="s7">Automates Shopify inventory monitoring via webhooks and GraphQL API. Sends low stock or out-of-stock alerts with product info and images to Discord channels using Discord Bot API, enabling timely inventory management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Efx0PT45vdQIGxzUuivwmFUSkZ30LjfK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1029" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1030</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Support Ticket System via n8n</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram Bot API and Redis to convert Telegram messages into a support ticket system. It manages user data, creates unique forum topics in a Telegram support group, forwards messages, and broadcasts announcements to users. Enables team collaboration and message preservation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14b8mGwxfuQTocZrwU5-xf_Q3S0WdQGFx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1030" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1031</div></th><td class="s6">Cloudflare KV Namespace Manager</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Cloudflare KV storage API to manage namespaces and key-value pairs. Supports creation, deletion, renaming namespaces, plus read/write/delete of KV pairs with metadata. Utilizes HTTP Request nodes, Cloudflare API, and n8n&#39;s set and manual trigger nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TPtz2k4wFT6PeCnPB2G9sdvW_BnDDy5o">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1031" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1032</div></th><td class="s6">Meraki Network Latency &amp; Loss Alert System</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of Cisco Meraki networks by fetching orgs, networks, and uplink latency/loss data via Meraki API. Calculates 5-min averages, filters problematic sites, avoids duplicate alerts using Redis, and notifies teams through Microsoft Teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1REQJe46MzPu0IkadfYyq08rkksvd9HId">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1032" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1033</div></th><td class="s6">Switchy.io URL Shortener with Meta Parsing</td><td class="s7">An advanced n8n workflow integrating Switchy.io API, OpenGraph.xyz, Dub.sh, Norton, Bitdefender, and PhishTank to parse URL metadata, check safety, generate screenshots, and create or update short URLs with rich preview images and branding options.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=186a8ahSJSE6Id0s7NSxnFe5ORMqD3A_I">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1033" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1034</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable Automated Recurring Task Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates recurring task creation using Airtable API in n8n. It retrieves task templates, assignees, clients, calculates task dates, creates new tasks, updates automation records, and optionally notifies assignees via Slack.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19Hb5myoohiXNYSY_0sdz1WGvlRDG31kU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1034" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1035</div></th><td class="s6">Bulk CSV Contact Upload to Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates bulk upload of contacts from CSV files into Airtable using Airtable API, CSV parsing, and file download. Tracks upload status (Processing, Uploaded, Failed) and integrates with Airtable Interface and Google Sheets templates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13C-JWv8ktTE4na2Dd-kC3HHwARTrUs0o">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1035" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1036</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Crunchbase Fundraising to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval of recent Series A, B, and Seed fundraising data from Piloterr API (Crunchbase data) and enriches with company info. Data is processed and updated in Google Sheets. Uses n8n, Piloterr API, and Google Sheets integration for startup funding tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13gNy7EA8fTvT20aq8LiwNOqQv_L0nvK2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1036" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1037</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Transcript Summarizer with LangChain</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses searchapi.io to fetch YouTube video transcripts and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via LangChain to generate detailed summaries and example Q&amp;A, helping users quickly understand and interact with video content.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MxlrVwJHmMhn-fgzTxfk6kgwfejZrZ2j">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1037" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1038</div></th><td class="s6">AI Agent for Google Sheets Customer Queries</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Google Sheets API to create an AI agent that answers complex customer data queries by selectively retrieving column names, column values