s for it if missing, or alerts a Slack channel for human support. Integrates chat triggers, memory buffer, and conditional logic for support escalation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YZeQpAOqT9IeEHFVEylOTlGI7EyaKjtq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1041" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1042</div></th><td class="s6">B2B Lead Qualification &amp; Email Response</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to capture business leads via a form, enrich contact and company data using Clearbit API, filter for B2B companies with over 499 employees, then send tailored Gmail responses. Tech stack includes n8n, Clearbit API, and Gmail SMTP.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gVGbGb2yj19AMQg2I3JSipihkRp9M_N_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1042" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1043</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Email Finder &amp; Enricher via Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates enriching LinkedIn profile data by fetching contact details using Prospeo.io LinkedIn Email Finder API, triggered on schedule, reading/writing Google Sheets for scalable contact info updates with fields like email, name, gender, job title, skills, education, and picture.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gFpIMv4BwvzTYF_FDK6kTMm73GYel7LG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1043" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1044</div></th><td class="s6">Intercom User Enrichment with ExactBuyer API</td><td class="s7">Automates enriching new Intercom user profiles by receiving webhook events, fetching detailed contact info from ExactBuyer API, and updating Intercom contacts with social profiles, phone, location, and avatar data via HTTP requests.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bpeOJSLcrpFRXN-c0mJX7Tfn4liL1-fW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1044" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1045</div></th><td class="s6">Discourse Lead Enrichment &amp; Slack Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates enrichment of new Discourse community members using Clearbit API, filters common personal emails, evaluates company data for lead value, and posts high-value lead info in Slack. Utilizes Discourse webhook, Clearbit enrichment, and Slack API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rcxS0CpuvZ3hEJ1bRXtoIswgRV1Xhsty">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1045" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1046</div></th><td class="s6">Leadfeeder Leads Enrichment &amp; Google Sheets Export</td><td class="s7">Automates lead retrieval from Leadfeeder API, enriches company data using Clearbit API, filters leads by employee count and engagement, and appends or updates results in Google Sheets. Utilizes Leadfeeder, Clearbit, and Google Sheets APIs for B2B lead management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ETpDnhOB1EdlSypnIkNbL5LE-wvClwLD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1046" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1047</div></th><td class="s6">Email Lead Validation and Enrichment</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that triggers from a form submission, verifies email validity using Hunter API, enriches person and company data via Clearbit, and adds valid leads to HubSpot CRM. Integrates Form Trigger, Hunter, Clearbit, and HubSpot with OAuth2 for smart lead collection.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rXhhPhyzYLmDOlOYUNs4CrG6pIZIdqYT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1047" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1048</div></th><td class="s6">Automated HubSpot Deal Assignment</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates the assignment of unassigned HubSpot deals to sales reps based on deal region (US, Germany, others) and company size using HubSpot CRM API. Runs on scheduled trigger every 2 days. Includes data fetching, filtering, and updating HubSpot deals via OAuth2.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BrF5ATgMUCXTilXr0SYtgeqMALVVpzQg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1048" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1049</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Social Media Digest for Meetings</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches attendees&#39; LinkedIn posts and Twitter tweets using RapidAPI, enriches company data via Clearbit, and emails a daily digest before meetings. Integrates Google Calendar, Gmail, LinkedIn and Twitter APIs to streamline meeting prep with social insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JVJSlQAXMX4pZXVcorY84pPKdTok4aK8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1049" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1050</div></th><td class="s6">CRM Auto-Update from Calendly with Clearbit &amp; HubSpot</td><td class="s7">Automates CRM updates by triggering on Calendly bookings. Uses Clearbit API to enrich contact and company data, filters personal emails, then upserts leads and companies in HubSpot CRM via OAuth2. Streamlines lead management and data accuracy.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gh0z1nXBaMZsSxoEGxTjOogrSdrRZBq4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1050" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1051</div></th><td class="s6">CRM Lead &amp; Company Enrichment Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates lead enrichment and management by integrating ConvertKit form subscriptions with Clearbit for email and company data enrichment, and HubSpot CRM for searching, creating, updating companies and contacts. Filters out personal emails for targeted B2B outreach.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OJEE5BxDpHSerXgrufiJe2IA_GHh6Jy7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1051" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1052</div></th><td class="s6">Pipedrive Lead Enrichment &amp; Slack Alerts</td><td class="s7">Automates the enrichment of Pipedrive leads with Clearbit data and sends filtered high-value lead alerts to Slack. Utilizes Pipedrive API, Clearbit API, and Slack API, running every 5 minutes to update and notify sales teams about potential B2B leads with revenue and employee criteria.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PEsh9PvIBXiCi18qOzmXCVGBZTOjDpvd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1052" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1053</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Command Handler with Dynamic Workflow Calls</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Slack API to process slash commands, validate incoming requests securely, and dynamically trigger sub-workflows based on commands. Uses Slack API, HTTP requests, and conditional logic to provide customizable bot commands and threaded conversations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u1GvEoHi_dfKl8PQObz4U3dNz59ddRck">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1053" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1054</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive PDF Chat with Pinecone &amp; OpenAI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads a PDF from Google Drive, splits it into chunks, inserts embeddings into Pinecone vector DB, and enables chat queries with citation-based answers using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini model. Integrates Google Drive, Pinecone API, and OpenAI API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1toxtv6TsV_VlZJmnoxP4Zd_2eNRFdcM4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1054" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1055</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Resume Extractor &amp; PDF Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates resume processing via Telegram: downloads PDFs, uses OpenAI GPT-4 to parse resumes into structured JSON, formats data into HTML, converts to PDF using Gotenberg, then sends PDF back to users. Integrates Telegram API, OpenAI API, and Gotenberg.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qhOiDCqU0fsFmKLj6GXi0mQMV2bGOHr8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1055" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1056</div></th><td class="s6">Stripe Payment Link Creator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates Stripe product creation and payment link generation. Utilizes Stripe API via HTTP Request nodes, with an input form trigger and automatic webhook redirect. Ideal for simple product monetization setups using Stripe.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eTG1nx3lTRY1oKEcR9J9cKUplqKaAydT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1056" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1057</div></th><td class="s6">AI Gmail Auto Labeler</td><td class="s7">Automates Gmail email labeling by analyzing message content with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via LangChain in n8n. It triggers on new emails, fetches content, assigns AI-driven labels like &#39;Inquiry&#39;, &#39;Partnership&#39;, &#39;Notification&#39;, and updates Gmail labels accordingly for organized inbox management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Q2i2aX4kbsXifsHOybYkIi9zu5Be9ZU_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1057" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1058</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Weekly Google Analytics Reporting</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates weekly Google Analytics reporting by fetching and comparing this week vs prior week data on page engagement, country views, and Google Search Console metrics. Uses Google Analytics API and Gmail to format and email HTML reports.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ft09HGEZd1tvaPZXWroEAd589OE0qG52">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1058" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1059</div></th><td class="s6">Zalando Price Monitor &amp; Alert System</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that monitors Zalando product prices by scraping product pages, logging price history, updating product info in Google Sheets, and sending email alerts via Gmail when prices drop below user-defined thresholds. Uses Google Sheets API, HTTP Request, and Gmail API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12hrjy0wBkPAEo78YgaJL-EGDEOIj3Jez">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1059" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1060</div></th><td class="s6">[n8n] YouTube Channel RSS Feed Generator</td><td class="s7">Generates multiple RSS feed formats for any public YouTube channel or video using n8n workflows, without needing Google API keys. Integrates with commentpicker.com APIs and RSS-Bridge.org to fetch channel IDs, video IDs, and produce RSS in XML, JSON, ATOM, MRSS, and more.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jLHxHWC7KsGNFLPTtqBz1IPfVXfDO0dt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1060" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1061</div></th><td class="s6">AI Children’s Storytelling on Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates creation and sharing of children’s stories on Telegram using OpenAI GPT-3.5 for story and image prompts, DALL·E for images, and OpenAI-generated audio. Scheduled to run every 12 hours, integrates Telegram API for direct story, audio, and image delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vqfv2n-WaS2lnA1uIarHf8WNoAI3fZY-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1061" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1062</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Arabic Kids Story Generator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses OpenAI GPT-4 Turbo for crafting, translating, and summarizing kids&#39; stories to Arabic, generating DALL·E images and audio narration, and distributing content via Telegram. Ideal for educational content creators and language learning apps.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11pqTUqJcRsytkH5GLLGg0isdDTTMAgML">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1062" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1063</div></th><td class="s6">Dropcontact Bulk Profile Enrichment</td><td class="s7">Automates enriching LinkedIn profiles without emails using Dropcontact API, PostgreSQL for profile data storage, Python for data transformation, and Slack notifications. Processes profiles in batches asynchronously, ideal for large-scale contact data enrichment.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10v6oQnNV6DhectiLZ3KUJZ5KiGETTqMM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1063" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1064</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Release Email Notifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that daily fetches the latest release info from a GitHub repo, converts release notes from markdown to HTML, and emails the formatted update via Gmail. Utilizes GitHub API, markdown conversion, and Gmail OAuth2 for automated release notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MgGUyySz52xlH7luwPC8XgSK6Zk4p0zR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1064" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1065</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress Blog Post Automation from Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates posting AI-generated markdown blog posts from Airtable to WordPress. Converts markdown to HTML, uploads featured images from Pexels API, and updates Airtable status. Utilizes n8n, Airtable, WordPress API, Pexels API for seamless content publishing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YBL4161FUSFPUmCBx1HA2y3TfjEWF84c">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1065" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1066</div></th><td class="s6">Spotify Downloads Playlist Automator</td><td class="s7">Automates Spotify by creating and maintaining a &#39;Downloads&#39; playlist with the latest liked tracks. Uses Spotify API via n8n nodes, scheduled triggers, and code filters to sync and limit songs, optimizing offline listening with defined limits.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1g84HElZeRZSH81pAjd1KEG2UGNCzGNz0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1066" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1067</div></th><td class="s6">Lemlist Reply Auto-Categorizer &amp; Slack Alerts</td><td class="s7">Automate classification of Lemlist email replies using OpenAI GPT-4o and send structured Slack notifications. Features include auto-unsubscribe and marking interested leads via Lemlist API integration. Workflow uses n8n with Lemlist, OpenAI, Slack APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fb8qESYUM0F1jjLNvWMKlowKp4fRc9Ww">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1067" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1068</div></th><td class="s6">Notion to Webflow Blog Post Sync</td><td class="s7">Automate syncing blog posts from Notion to Webflow using n8n. Converts Notion rich text blocks to HTML, manages slug uniqueness, updates or creates posts in Webflow, and sends Slack notifications. Integrates Notion API, Webflow API, Slack, and n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1May_Vy0eGMlc4_CK2kkYOd9bwJnzxTdK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1068" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1069</div></th><td class="s6">n8n GitHub Credential Backup Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates backing up all n8n instance credentials to a GitHub repo by exporting decrypted credentials via CLI, formatting JSON, and saving/updating files in GitHub using GitHub API nodes. Scheduled to run every 2 hours.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kC3e7IvGLvh9vd-6Ijniq8itMZ8CDa64">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1069" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1070</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Social Media Link Scraper</td><td class="s7">An autonomous AI workflow using n8n, OpenAI GPT-4o, and Supabase to crawl websites from a database, extract all social media profile URLs, and store them in a structured format. It leverages HTML parsing, HTTP requests, LangChain tools, and data cleaning.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ilmHzAA-6ZSoXEdmzumTT42pu_ykf2j6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1070" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1071</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Invoice Data Extraction &amp; Reconciliation</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of invoice data from Gmail PDF attachments using LlamaParse PDF parser, OpenAI GPT-3.5 LLM for structured data extraction, and exports results to Google Sheets. Workflow manages email labeling to prevent duplicates and handles processing status polling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-Wo3qbLH-JOEsnllmV1-DLfgsWFdzrio">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1071" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1072</div></th><td class="s6">Automated RFP Q&amp;A Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates RFP responses by extracting questions from PDF RFPs using n8n with Langchain AI (OpenAI), creates Google Docs for answers, and sends notifications via Gmail and Slack. Enables efficient, AI-powered RFP answering and improves sales team productivity.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1h5YaAVcbiVASqJpGwrMU9MIgzQVSZKcr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1072" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1073</div></th><td class="s6">Scheduled Website Uptime Monitor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that checks website statuses every 6 hours using HTTP requests, reads target URLs from Google Sheets, logs uptime events back to Sheets, and sends alerts via Gmail and Slack upon downtime. Uses Google Sheets API, HTTP Request node, Gmail and Slack integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cJHpq5fH6k1VQ-Emu6WtoNhP0CVpDQws">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1073" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1074</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Product Photo Data Enrichment</td><td class="s7">Automates enrichment of product info from photos in Airtable using OpenAI vision &amp; chat models, SERPAPI reverse image search, and Firecrawl web scraper. Designed for building surveyors to identify and update product attributes efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QsFApEDPZE50-Hyk7afhpaP5MChjkpCs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1074" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1075</div></th><td class="s6">Image Object Detection &amp; Elasticsearch Indexing</td><td class="s7">Automates image processing by detecting objects in a source image via Cloudflare&#39;s Detr-Resnet-50 AI model, cropping detected objects, uploading them to Cloudinary, and indexing metadata in Elasticsearch for granular image search.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18SSCFNXbZEfRwpH8olRp-cgOQHo6svN7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1075" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1076</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Driven Local Folder Organizer</td><td class="s7">Automates local folder organization by monitoring changes and using Mistral AI to suggest file categorization into subdirectories. Utilizes n8n Local File Trigger, shell commands, and Mistral Cloud Chat Model to intelligently move files, enhancing file management efficiency.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cXm73q6f0BkRzkNI9X-F3LY-HwRuUsg1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1076" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1077</div></th><td class="s6">Local Folder to Qdrant AI Bank Statement Expert</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of a local folder for file changes, syncing bank statement files with Qdrant vector store using Mistral AI embeddings, and provides a Q&amp;A AI agent for querying the documents. Uses n8n workflows, local file trigger, Qdrant API, and Mistral Cloud AI.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KEaxamo_W21ZOVL-lPVjmtbrU9GcATIN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1077" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1078</div></th><td class="s6">AI Rental Payment Reconciliation</td><td class="s7">Automates reconciliation of rental payments by watching local bank statement CSV files, querying tenant and property data from an Excel file, and using OpenAI GPT-4 to identify payment discrepancies, generating actionable reports all within n8n self-hosted workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19thP9aTkeMDoeH2tO0gN0920d2GThvpD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1078" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1079</div></th><td class="s6">AI Texas Tax Code Assistant Chatbot</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and querying of Texas tax codes using n8n. Downloads tax code PDFs, extracts sections, creates Mistral.ai embeddings, stores in Qdrant vector database, and enables an AI chatbot via OpenAI and Langchain to answer tax-related queries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fP4LfLgvTcQyZYGH_zUot1jHCAAWXJAH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1079" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1080</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered SMS Appointment Scheduling Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates SMS-based appointment scheduling for PC/Laptop repairs using Twilio SMS, Airtable for session management, OpenAI GPT for conversational AI, and Cal.com API for booking. Includes follow-ups and STOP command handling to manage engagement effectively.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UPoyCi24hUIGsOmTWwni2uM5NIHF5fJR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1080" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1081</div></th><td class="s6">Image Embedding for Vector Search</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads an image from Google Drive, extracts color channel info, generates semantic keywords using OpenAI Vision model, combines data into an embedding document, and inserts it into an in-memory vector store for efficient image vector search.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PKCQuIwPYhdELuWM9wDp3NI2q-Jw1b7T">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1081" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1082</div></th><td class="s6">Twilio AI Chat with Redis Buffer</td><td class="s7">Automates SMS chat replies using Twilio for messages, Redis to buffer incoming texts, and OpenAI&#39;s Chat Model via LangChain agent to generate a single aggregated AI response after a 5-second pause, improving conversational flow for bursty user input.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rKOWIJiS3Pro249Yo6Y6F-0V3vyXrENe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1082" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1083</div></th><td class="s6">HN Comments Insight Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates extracting, vectorizing, clustering Hacker News story comments using HN API, OpenAI embeddings, Qdrant vector DB, and K-means in Python. Summarizes clustered feedback with GPT-4 and exports insights to Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OFPZoyRWS-Q3XPMYDt6YUqfIkNXR3eJ_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1083" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1084</div></th><td class="s6">IKEA Remote to Spotify Control</td><td class="s7">Automates Spotify playback control via MQTT messages from an IKEA 5-button switch using n8n workflows. Integrates Spotify OAuth2 API and MQTT to handle play, pause, volume, track navigation, and playlist actions on a specified playback device.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uJ9A2f291J4qeTzRNa6lVt-UpQtjPP5j">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1084" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1085</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Version Control with GitLab</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates version control of n8n workflows by syncing them with GitLab. It retrieves all workflows from n8n, compares each with corresponding JSON files in a GitLab repo, and creates or updates files accordingly. It uses n8n API and GitLab API for integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1awyKg55hOK3C_TYcat3W4Ij1JiDctngM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1085" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1086</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Paddle Invoice PDF Saver</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates processing Paddle invoice emails received in Gmail. It filters Paddle invoices, extracts invoice URLs from emails, converts them to PDFs using pdflayer API, uploads to Google Drive, renames and organizes files in specified Drive folders.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rQgZOkjYIn7ezl_Hu4whfMBAk-34Ngnd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1086" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1087</div></th><td class="s6">Supabase Vector DB Q&amp;A Chatbot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Google Drive, OpenAI embeddings and chat models, Supabase vector database for embedding storage/retrieval, and LangChain for recursive text splitting and QA. Enables document upload, vector embedding insertion/updating, and conversational Q&amp;A on custom knowledge bases.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u5r7HnYDKIjdazMxz2SyBpJAok2IFVCi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1087" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1088</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Bot Integration with Payment &amp; Registration</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram Bot API to handle various message types (text, photo, file, voice), commands, user registration, and payments via Google Sheets and sub-workflows for registration and payment processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15VqiaS7j6jyv8TdFF76K5WdAKM4EmjmE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1088" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1089</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Airtable Order Summary Email</td><td class="s7">Automates collecting orders stored via webhook into Airtable, then sends a daily 7PM email summary with all today&#39;s orders in HTML table format using Airtable API and Gmail. Helps businesses track and review daily sales efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LRzRRz5ew-rPKc7sI3WyETD9XPOMHjJS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1089" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1090</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Notion Task Summary Email &amp; Push</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly retrieval of tasks from Notion, filters and sorts by deadlines, generates styled HTML emails grouping overdue and upcoming tasks, and sends updates via email and Pushover push notifications. Uses Notion API, SMTP, and Pushover within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ICf0t4UsqGB8bBmVMUxatgxlBIC3mD-e">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1090" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1091</div></th><td class="s6">Notion Knowledge Base AI Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automates search and summarization of knowledge from a Notion database using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o model. Utilizes Notion API for querying database contents and LangChain for managing AI agent memory and tool integration, enabling concise, fact-based Q&amp;A from company knowledge bases.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12wCGMWTg65Z6U80mHWaU34NPnkJn39aA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1091" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1092</div></th><td class="s6">AI Style-Based Image Generator</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrating Huggingface FLUX API and Cloudflare R2 for AI-driven image creation. Users submit prompts and select artistic styles (e.g., Neon Fauvism, AI Dystopia). Images are generated, uploaded to S3-compatible storage, and served with recent renders showcased.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17tRLKp0dsv88EeXOcc9mPadYeKrNoG63">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1092" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1093</div></th><td class="s6">Bank Statement OCR to Markdown with Google Gemini</td><td class="s7">Automates bank statement processing by downloading PDFs from Google Drive, converting PDF pages to images via Stirling PDF API, transcribing images to markdown with Google Gemini Vision LLM, and extracting deposit data as structured JSON. Uses n8n automation with Google Drive API, Stirling PDF, and Google Gemini (PaLM) API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AOMQjWuso-AxCU6rExcuQQIQCgHt9as6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1093" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1094</div></th><td class="s6">Venafi Slack CertBot Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates SSL certificate requests via Slack using Venafi TLS Protect Cloud, VirusTotal for domain risk analysis, and OpenAI for risk summarization, enabling auto or manual CSR issuance with Slack modal interactions and security validation workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yMndI85UV0wmcvMLkdnP3CA0yv8Cb9B6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1094" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1095</div></th><td class="s6">Adobe PDF Services API Automation</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates Adobe PDF Services API to authenticate, upload a PDF, process it (e.g., extract text and tables), and download results. Integrates Dropbox for fetching test PDFs. Uses HTTP Request nodes with OAuth2 and Header Auth for Adobe API calls.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tl45-vKVt10Tun7TgqWdP2mLlIBrIX9X">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1095" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1096</div></th><td class="s6">n8n AI-Enhanced FAQ Generator from Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates FAQ creation by reading service data from Google Sheets, generating Q&amp;A templates, enhancing answers using OpenAI GPT-4, and saving results as JSON in Google Drive. Supports native, credential-only, and non-native integrations for CMS publishing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XhrRZm6gf8PUsYhHDVF15lS48HcerZiI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1096" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1097</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Multi-Repo Webhook Monitor</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of multiple GitHub repositories using GitHub Webhooks and n8n. Registers/deletes webhooks programmatically, listens to push and pull request events, and sends notifications via Telegram (Slack optional). Uses GitHub API and n8n HTTP, Webhook, and Telegram nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1i40yfBsUVnVCOiNjxjUulDSGAT5_MDhs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1097" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1098</div></th><td class="s6">Fastmail AI Email Draft Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automates drafting email replies for Fastmail using OpenAI GPT-4. Monitors IMAP inbox for new emails, extracts content, generates replies with GPT-4, and uploads drafts via Fastmail&#39;s JMAP API. Integrates IMAP, Fastmail API, and OpenAI in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SNNiuT97htIJkwXkcgndESf2zmhwkqzR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1098" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1099</div></th><td class="s6">Stripe Invoice PDFs to AWS S3</td><td class="s7">Automates monthly exporting of Stripe invoice PDFs to an AWS S3 bucket with configurable folder structure by year and month. Utilizes Stripe API, n8n workflow automation, and AWS S3 for cloud storage. Scheduled trigger ensures monthly syncs or manual runs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NLnC-G8o20bxe5gBqkNENpEGceo0byqR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1099" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1100</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Outlook Email Auto Categorizer</td><td class="s7">Automate Outlook email management by categorizing and organizing emails into folders using Ollama AI&#39;s qwen2.5:14b model with n8n workflow. Employs Microsoft Outlook API, Markdown conversion, and advanced AI parsing for efficient inbox sorting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yNKkGpadueuqJ2k2skXUJCcFks-9hLFL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1100" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1101</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Based SEO Seed Keyword Generator</td><td class="s7">Generates 15-20 targeted SEO seed keywords based on an Ideal Customer Profile using AI (Anthropic Claude 3.5). Utilizes n8n workflow nodes, Langchain AI agent, and requires user-defined ICP data and AI/database connections to automate SEO focus keyword creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hm44qVojZvh7gyALYkx6lzn9obzbM5sm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1101" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1102</div></th><td class="s6">Luma AI Text-to-Video Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates video creation from text prompts with randomized camera motions using Luma AI API and stores results in Airtable. Uses HTTP API, JavaScript for randomness, Airtable integration—enabling quick generation and tracking of creative short videos.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ihAf8ylYnyRKvaVJ1Q_-ISOxjNtgmYmS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1102" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1103</div></th><td class="s6">RSS Feed to Telegram Alerts</td><td class="s7">Automates sending new RSS feed items to Telegram chats using n8n with RSS Feed Read and Telegram API nodes. Checks latest items and posts updates automatically on schedule, ideal for real-time content alerts or monitoring feeds in Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SmV4dTz6jQu81qhKnnf9P8IgBjOIKojW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1103" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1104</div></th><td class="s6">Squarespace Order Fulfillment Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching and fulfilling Squarespace orders using Squarespace Commerce API with OAuth2 and API key authentication. Supports filtering by fulfillment status, pagination, and automated notification sending to customers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AC4sVbjppk-udZBsjdhtN6e4pTimn-P3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1104" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1105</div></th><td class="s6">Inbound Order Email Parser to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of purchase orders from Gmail emails using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini via n8n LangChain AI Agent; parses PO number, delivery date, SKUs, quantities, then stores structured data into Google Sheets for order management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rT0ZbiIO_FKOcCOoNOfvG0R6ksJyLK-z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1105" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1106</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Processing with Anthropic Claude API</td><td class="s7">Automates sending and retrieving multiple batched prompts to Anthropic Claude AI via its Batch API. Uses n8n with HTTP Request nodes, JavaScript code processing, and Langchain memory management for parallel prompt execution and result aggregation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xNYN7u0cNMxWIy8AbT_9f_jo_iOyKqtj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1106" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1107</div></th><td class="s6">CSRD Email Audit &amp; Summary Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates review of CSRD XHTML report emails received in Gmail. Uses Gmail API to trigger, extracts XHTML attachments, audits content for sustainability disclosures, and employs AI (LangChain + OpenAI GPT-4o-mini) to generate professional audit summary emails. Improves ESG compliance communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eop8RP2Uv2eTNEX2INsHKvdFrhL00OI_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1107" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1108</div></th><td class="s6">AI Resume Parsing &amp; Client Usage Billing</td><td class="s7">Self-hosted n8n workflow using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via Langchain Code node to parse uploaded resume PDFs into structured JSON. Tracks token usage and costs per client, logs data to Google Sheets, and auto-generates monthly invoices via Gmail. Enables cost monitoring &amp; billing automation for AI document extraction services.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QlneHHhTmZJICalLLUgTCVH0APqXHbVv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1108" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1109</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Digest Email for n8n.io Templates</td><td class="s7">Automates daily email newsletters by fetching the latest n8n.io workflow templates from selected categories stored in Excel. Uses Microsoft Excel, HTTP Request for n8n API, OpenAI GPT-4 for summaries, and Microsoft Outlook to send personalized digests to subscribers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Kk3EKif_mRrJSzCeYEQC8yS2-vLdOQJD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1109" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1110</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Attachments to Organized Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading attachments from filtered Gmail emails, checks and creates company and date-based folders in Google Drive using Google Sheets for whitelist verification. Tech stack: Gmail API, Google Drive API, Google Sheets API via n8n nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bAc8Qsbnxg9H9A0LfkOq8mQceYLvfJmV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1110" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1111</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Profile ICP Scoring Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and scoring of LinkedIn profiles using Airtop AI API and Google Sheets. Extracts detailed personal, professional info and calculates ICP score based on AI interest, technical depth, and seniority. Updates scores back into Google Sheets for easy lead management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1d4j9uWgFzQcxZiit5Zox6jNnqA6bluC_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1111" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1112</div></th><td class="s6">AcuityScheduling Support Chatbot with RAG</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates a support chatbot for AcuityScheduling.com using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and LangChain agent. It integrates with Acuity&#39;s support search API for retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) to provide accurate, up-to-date answers by querying existing knowledgebase articles, optimizing token usage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17l8ARz82MIjZtGFcS-VYF-jD3vID-JAZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1112" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1113</div></th><td class="s6">SMS Course Assistant with Twilio &amp; Airtable</td><td class="s7">An automated SMS chatbot workflow using Twilio for SMS triggers, OpenAI (GPT-4) for natural language understanding, and Airtable as a course database. It fetches and answers course queries, logs interactions, and provides up-to-date academic info for Northvale Institute students.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=129dYHFnuxZcXdsHkWI2d1guSUzflComJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1113" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1114</div></th><td class="s6">Ghost Blog to LinkedIn Post Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates extracting latest blog posts from Ghost CMS, cleans content, and uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via LangChain AI agent to create professional LinkedIn promotional messages. Outputs results to Google Sheets for easy tracking and sharing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MLmywVqZFunWmGdJB4XBdX8lozwPGb1L">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1114" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1115</div></th><td class="s6">Retell Call Data Auto-Saver</td><td class="s7">Automates saving Retell AI call analysis data from webhook into Airtable, Google Sheets, and Notion. Utilizes Retell webhooks, Airtable API, Google Sheets API, and Notion API to store call transcripts, summaries, sentiment, and cost details in structured databases.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=120jsLoJCnJ3n2QdxEgWiavke7RclFolQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1115" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1116</div></th><td class="s6">University Term Dates to Calendar ICS</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of term dates from university Excel files using Cloudflare Markdown Conversion, Google Gemini LLM for event extraction, and Python code to create ICS calendar files, then emails the calendar via Gmail for easy import to calendar apps.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11_G6yON4mL61ZNhhTsxlaicb-ga3aLzf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1116" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1117</div></th><td class="s6">Google Keep Notes to Google Sheets via AI</td><td class="s7">Automates exporting Google Keep notes stored as JSON files in Google Drive, filters, processes content with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini model via LangChain AI, and appends extracted data to Google Sheets. Uses Google Drive, Google Sheets APIs, and OpenAI for text extraction and data structuring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oXAOpEfi40WtcWzGImHGfiUEAYjj8wpq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1117" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1118</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Exchange Rate Updater to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval of USD currency exchange rates via ExchangeRate-API, formats data, and updates &amp; archives it in Google Sheets. Utilizes n8n HTTP Request, Code, Google Sheets, and Schedule Trigger nodes for seamless financial data management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=103baqHXWa8TneBKQ7AnASNYKS_ybIfFc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1118" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1119</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Daily Israeli News Digest</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching and processing of Israeli news from Calcalist and Mako RSS feeds, uses GPT-4o to select top 5 executive-relevant articles, and generates a formatted HTML email digest sent daily via SMTP.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IxRq0RYvfgF77usvXsAUr3is2ZIccr3L">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1119" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1120</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Product Hunt Data Fetcher to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval of today&#39;s top Product Hunt posts using Product Hunt GraphQL API, processes product details, resolves website redirects, and stores enriched data into Google Sheets via service account. Built with n8n, HTTP requests, JavaScript code, and Google Sheets integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eFNKbTKJC63DwLhwE41A1G_oZVd8LZ-N">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1120" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1121</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Meal Nutrient Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates logging meal nutrients from Telegram messages (text or voice). Uses Telegram API, OpenAI (GPT-4o-mini) for transcription and nutrition analysis, Langchain for structured parsing, and stores data in Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QOGytVMBax9SkY3EXubaeBQqlsSUxXto">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1121" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1122</div></th><td class="s6">Indeed Job Listing Scraper with Bright Data &amp; LLM</td><td class="s7">Automates job search by scraping Indeed listings using Bright Data API. Integrates n8n for workflow, Google Sheets for storage, and OpenAI GPT-4 mini model to assess applicant-job fit. Uses form trigger for search parameters and polls for data readiness.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qsfepujY7bLRhMoK1COV-tsbLVrAVbxd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1122" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1123</div></th><td class="s6">Glassdoor Job Listings Scraper with Bright Data</td><td class="s7">Automates job prospecting by scraping Glassdoor job listings via Bright Data API, processes data with OpenAI GPT-4 and LangChain, and stores results in Google Sheets. Includes customizable queries via form triggers for targeted job search automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Fps4oZi2o723MoOx_TcCyLv2TXAb9owz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1123" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1124</div></th><td class="s6">Trustpilot Review Scraper &amp; Ad Copy Generator</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow scraping Trustpilot competitor reviews via Bright Data API, storing results in Google Sheets, filtering negative reviews, summarizing with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and emailing ad copy suggestions for marketing campaigns.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1J2RUxME8OE4NL4CCIBDkSWqBB2oOOicH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1124" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1125</div></th><td class="s6">Hourly Crypto Market Summary to Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching hourly 24h price data of BTC, ETH, and SOL USDC pairs from Binance public API, analyzes key market metrics (volatility, momentum, spread), and sends a formatted HTML summary message to a specified Telegram chat via Telegram Bot API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18fHHFa2sX8e_CW0CXxyoMWKjR-0MQCgm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1125" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1126</div></th><td class="s6">Amazon Reviews Analysis &amp; Creative Generator</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates scraping Amazon product reviews using Bright Data API, stores data in Google Sheets, summarizes reviews with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, generates Ads images, and emails media buyers. It leverages Bright Data API, Google Sheets, OpenAI GPT, and Gmail for competitive review analysis and marketing creative generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dIZAwCsYmJWTCVEzl-sRGaze5v-eoakD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1126" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1127</div></th><td class="s6">PostgreSQL MCP Server for DB Management</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow acting as a PostgreSQL MCP server enabling secure database management operations (select, insert, update) via MCP clients like Claude Desktop. Uses n8n nodes (Postgres, LangChain MCP Trigger/Tools), avoids raw SQL for security and supports schema introspection.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uaTph2yD_n8o93qkGOtXdoNkkC6Z5jiG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1127" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1128</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive File Search &amp; Content Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow acting as a Google Drive MCP server to search, download, and extract content from files (PDF, CSV, images, audio, video) using Google Drive API and OpenAI. Enables AI-rich file understanding and text extraction for MCP clients.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15TY9kEvQiHg8cha4F7tGI91EBq6qtJeA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1128" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1129</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Issue Management via MCP Server</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow implementing a custom MCP server to manage GitHub issues and comments. It uses n8n MCP Trigger, GitHub API nodes, and custom tool workflows to get latest issues, fetch issue comments, and add comments. Secure, extensible, and ideal for interactive GitHub repo support.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10tUMsDkt-XH1OZgrBC_ICUe6GL2ODkze">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1129" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1130</div></th><td class="s6">Qdrant MCP Server for Review Analysis</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow implementing a customized MCP server to extend Qdrant&#39;s vector database features with review database management. Utilizes OpenAI for embeddings and Qdrant API for advanced search, grouping, and recommendation functionalities to handle, search, compare, and recommend customer reviews.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QbvVm3Zt-lWnJLMROGgmIJvIcoqDbu2n">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1130" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1131</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Search and Transcript MCP Server</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow using Apify API for YouTube video search, transcript retrieval, and usage metrics via an MCP server trigger. Enables integration with MCP clients like Claude Desktop to automate YouTube content research with no official rate limits.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CxmWISARgojPyNUC2cVZxBVDubR1kSSD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1131" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1132</div></th><td class="s6">PayCaptain Employee MCP Server</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow creates an MCP server for PayCaptain payroll, enabling employee search, lookup, and updates via the PayCaptain API. Uses MCP Server Trigger, HTTP Request, Google Sheets (for logs), and LangChain tool workflows. Ideal for payroll automation with audit logging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16p782YB6KKt0_GiZNORfJvHfiecLHhAy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1132" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1133</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Alt Text Generator for Web Images</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow extracts images and alt texts from a webpage, then uses OpenAI GPT-4O to generate improved alt text for images with short descriptions. Results are stored and updated in Google Sheets for accessibility enhancement and SEO improvement.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10jUlBGYqBBJ9fNqAKaVekMXHlJBP5hzo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1133" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1134</div></th><td class="s6">EU Sustainability Legislative Scraper &amp; Tracker</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that scrapes EU parliamentary legislative procedures from an official site, uses OpenAI GPT-4 Turbo to classify sustainability-related items, records filtered results in Google Sheets, and creates Google Tasks for study reminders. Tech stack: HTTP request, HTML parsing, OpenAI API, Google Sheets, Google Tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1x5llhr6GObGsFhsRZ7FHTRUVgkwRaekP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1134" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1135</div></th><td class="s6">EU Sustainability News Daily Digest</td><td class="s7">Automates daily scraping of EU news, classifies sustainability articles using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via LangChain, records results in Google Sheets, and sends a curated HTML email digest via Gmail. Integrates HTTP Request, HTML parsing, AI classification, Sheets, and Gmail nodes for sustainable news curation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RJ75A5A43h90VuRdYYaOl_QNEG0BlQse">Download</a></