://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1n9y2v31WEIIcnCXTbHMkDP_qufiyyOzV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1138" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1139</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Backup to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates scheduled backups of all n8n workflows to a specified Google Drive folder using n8n API, Google Drive API, Gmail for notifications, and Discord for status alerts. Enables reliable versioned backups and timely notifications on success or failure.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BKfF-PxXzPBVrU4-ViZpnDV2W7YlJrih">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1139" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1140</div></th><td class="s6">Chat Message Batch Consolidator with LangChain</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow buffers chat messages per context using Redis, waits for inactivity or message count thresholds, and uses OpenAI GPT-4.1-nano via LangChain to consolidate messages into a single summary paragraph. Ideal for chat apps needing batch processing and deduplication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zCAgMKy-aL3bTiAMb5hqNCdPjiRgTz7b">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1140" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1141</div></th><td class="s6">Reddit Business Lead Finder &amp; Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Reddit posts from Entrepreneur subreddit using Reddit API, filters posts by engagement and recency, uses OpenRouter GPT-4.1 AI to identify business opportunities and summarize them, then appends results to Google Sheets for lead management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10_Q9Yiy8oCuEoN-gOD5a3BPvKVOI2BC7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1141" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1142</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Client LinkedIn &amp; Post Monitor</td><td class="s7">Automates tracking of HubSpot owners&#39; clients by fetching client data via HubSpot API, searching LinkedIn profiles through RapidAPI, monitoring LinkedIn posts and positions, and updating a Google Sheet. Sends email alerts using Gmail when client updates occur.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rYby4HfsqzmhebQCojIiExdt5HJJDlAd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1142" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1143</div></th><td class="s6">Voice-to-Email Reply Assistant</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating email reply drafting by analyzing incoming Gmail messages, assessing response need via OpenAI GPT chat, sending email details to Telegram, accepting voice note replies on Telegram, transcribing audio with OpenAI Whisper, and drafting polished replies in Gmail threads.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nMp8T1_aGdTEvGXnbI9ixHstRNtM4IGk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1143" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1144</div></th><td class="s6">WhatsApp Campaign Automation with KlickTipp</td><td class="s7">Automates personalized WhatsApp outreach using WhatsApp Business Cloud API integrated with KlickTipp for subscriber-triggered campaigns. Features message filtering, template messaging, opt-out management, and dynamic content insertion via n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pHtJvv-UCYp1ElD84osLlXD2YdIswFzb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1144" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1145</div></th><td class="s6">Restaurant Order Chatbot to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates restaurant order taking via AI chat using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Langchain. Extracts item names, quantities, and table numbers from chats, verifies input, then logs each order item with timestamp into Google Sheets for POS integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WBwwAZv7qZzhKpjGdfsU67oKhtOc4wkM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1145" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1146</div></th><td class="s6">AI Style Transfer Image Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates image style transfer using Google Gemini 2.0 for visual style analysis and Imagen 3.0 for image generation. Inputs taken via a form, images uploaded to Cloudinary, optional email delivery via Gmail. Enables creative AI-driven logo and image remixing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VcSu4PU1kVgJZ8soOcrIijHe6Ysqgc60">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1146" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1147</div></th><td class="s6">Secure Webhook with Auth &amp; Payload Check</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that protects a webhook endpoint by verifying a Bearer token and validating required fields in the JSON POST body. Uses native n8n nodes for webhook, conditional checks, JavaScript code, and structured JSON responses for 200, 400, and 401 HTTP codes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=145wt8q8UmbG6HpmvgqtWa7MXbMgRTDW9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1147" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1148</div></th><td class="s6">Prevent Concurrent Runs with Redis Lock</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to prevent concurrent executions using Redis for distributed locking. It uses Redis keys to track workflow states (set, get, unset) and manages workflow concurrency by erroring if already running. Useful for critical or long-running tasks to avoid overlaps.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BGtewfcmuVS2t1SjujVdyqYUUfLoqzCg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1148" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1149</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Automated Error Analysis &amp; Email Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates error detection in n8n workflows via n8n API, analyzes errors using OpenAI GPT-4o with LangChain, generates detailed diagnosis and resolution, and sends formatted email alerts via Gmail. Ideal for improving workflow reliability with AI-powered insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1T2nSalTHI2wpZPMJv_9NySXNeyb9icvO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1149" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1150</div></th><td class="s6">Email Header IP &amp; Spoofing Analyzer</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow analyzing email headers for IP reputation and spoofing threats using IP Quality Score and IP-API, plus SPF/DKIM/DMARC authentication checks via JavaScript. Provides 