rocesses webpage content via chained and parallel LLM calls for detailed insights and humor generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ltI49C0KtaKhVKsJ6csARFzdjfdxZr44">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1153" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1154</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Management &amp; Backup Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates listing, detailed retrieval, file backup, and metadata updating of n8n workflows using n8n API, Airtable, Dropbox, and Cron. Supports batch processing and triggers; ideal for managing and backing up workflows systematically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PeBc42AJSiOu8GKhGIC95kPp8lU_aTPb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1154" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1155</div></th><td class="s6">Odoo Product Image Importer from Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates importing product and template images from Google Drive into Odoo ERP using Google Drive API and Odoo API integration in n8n. Filters image files, updates records in Odoo, cleans up old files, and sends Google Chat notifications for completed updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XlahEndAjZgzfjpa6YNOyc8F1YImUgez">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1155" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1156</div></th><td class="s6">Instagram AI Comment Responder</td><td class="s7">Automates Instagram comment replies using Instagram Graph API, OpenRouter AI (Google Gemini 2.0), and n8n workflow. It filters comments, generates context-aware responses in Brazilian Portuguese for AI/automation content, and posts replies automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_fQbjVRtgaARsU0z0kjKf-Z3sAUbfx6v">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1156" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1157</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI File Retrieval with Citation Formatter</td><td class="s7">Automates citation-rich content retrieval using OpenAI assistant with vector store for file search. Integrates OpenAI API, HTTP requests, and n8n Langchain memory nodes to format text with dynamic citations in Markdown or HTML, enhancing accuracy and traceability.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Xt-xBb7jegVHVAVtUZ_BK4rpbG3QrX1r">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1157" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1158</div></th><td class="s6">Google Calendar MCP Server Integration</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating MCP Server with Google Calendar API to manage events via create, read, update, and delete operations. Utilizes Google Calendar OAuth2, n8n MCP Trigger &amp; Client tools, and OpenAI GPT-4o model for AI-driven calendar management workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JrrrDS5O1AyFDLRu4mVHuDp7HfoVQ22U">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1158" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1159</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram PDF Q&amp;A with Pinecone &amp; AI</td><td class="s7">Automates Telegram document handling by converting PDFs to vector embeddings using OpenAI, storing them in Pinecone, and enabling AI-powered Q&amp;A with Groq and LangChain, providing instant responses within Telegram chats.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1v-IPKMVwuhZYWhwxm7xD9nK5UB5VUlBJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1159" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1160</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Transcript to Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates extracting YouTube video transcripts via a RapidAPI service, summarizes content with LangChain LLM, and updates Airtable entries with main ideas and key takeaways. Keeps content ideas fresh using Airtable, RapidAPI, and n8n scheduling for workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XvDqyLCIbMGddZwgRn3U7ZZptIu0V8Qw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1160" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1161</div></th><td class="s6">Clinic Appointment &amp; Reminder Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automates clinic appointment management and reminders using OpenAI GPT-4, Google Calendar, Google Tasks, Telegram, WhatsApp (Evolution API), and Postgres. Handles patient rescheduling, confirmation, shopping lists, and escalations for a streamlined healthcare workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zu1cIIqfdralHYRNl673JP8XH5eVYmEg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1161" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1162</div></th><td class="s6">Sports Betting Data Automation with TheOddsAPI &amp; Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval and updating of sports betting events and results using TheOddsAPI for data