ment metrics from GitHub, Docker Hub, npm, and Product Hunt APIs to a custom dashboard using n8n workflow automation with HTTP Requests, GitHub node, and JavaScript functions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1r-Toanu0Jq0q1xDIaySBfGQP3R23olZm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1165" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1166</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sitemap Index URL Re-indexing</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching and parsing sitemap.xml URLs, checks indexing status via Google Indexing API, and updates Google with new or modified URLs for faster re-indexing. Uses HTTP requests, XML parsing, Google OAuth2 API in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Rz20HpJ5oYF9L1VCzOLgUCyJeIN4Fayu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1166" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1167</div></th><td class="s6">Auth0 OAuth2 User Login Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates user authentication via Auth0 OAuth2. It uses Auth0&#39;s OAuth2 API to authorize users, exchange authorization codes for access tokens, and retrieve user info. Includes webhook triggers and HTTP Request nodes for secure login flow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uRG-gnlqHyo_9CvOqJpKyQLu3znS4TPK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1167" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1168</div></th><td class="s6">DMARC Report Email Parser &amp; DB Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates processing of DMARC reports by monitoring IMAP email for XML attachments, unzipping and parsing them into JSON, mapping the data into a MySQL database, and sending notifications via Slack/email on SPF or DKIM failures. Uses n8n automation with email, compression, XML, MySQL, and Slack nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1g_AQZ5SCuwWmQw7rNUxvSKXFlibJ3_-U">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1168" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1169</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Blog Post Creator for WordPress</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Google Sheets, OpenAI (OpenRouter), and WordPress XML-RPC API to automate blog post drafting, updating, and publishing based on a scheduled spreadsheet. Uses dynamic prompts and manages status logs for seamless content creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MC1UTGPNWJ5ruAwEa8x0d91wnZZRAf2X">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1169" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1170</div></th><td class="s6">AI-powered Gmail Auto-labeler</td><td class="s7">Automatically categorizes Gmail messages into labels (Partnership, Inquiry, Notification) using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4 Turbo and n8n automation. Integrates Gmail API for triggers, label management, and message updates. Enhances inbox organization with AI-driven content classification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hyCOYyBVNRQy5RfYFpnaczPCmYohxC3D">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1170" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1171</div></th><td class="s6">Autonomous Social Media Profile Crawler</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow leveraging OpenAI GPT-4, LangChain, Supabase DB, and built-in HTTP/HTML nodes to autonomously crawl company websites, extract and standardize social media profile URLs into JSON format, and store results back to a database. Highly customizable multi-page crawler.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HbKVAQEHxCIVZg7Fr0_nBk8avfIZhEzz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1171" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1172</div></th><td class="s6">PUQ Docker NextCloud Deployment API</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates deployment and management of NextCloud instances in Docker for WHMCS/WISECP through an API backend. It uses Docker, docker-compose, SSH, nginx-proxy, and PowerDNS API to manage containers, DNS records, NGINX config, user accounts, and disk mounts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17GyfXQBAo_CWWQv0x7Hcc5vmpiIV25Ul">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1172" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1173</div></th><td class="s6">OAuth2 Configuration Finder AI</td><td class="s7">AI-powered n8n workflow to identify OAuth2 settings (authorization URI, token URI, audience) for APIs from a service name. Uses OpenRouter Chat Model with Llama 3.3, LangChain AI integration, and structured JSON parsing with confidence scoring for reliable API OAuth2 setups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tXsTTFxFvRFQ0GICgTo_k0MZOUnsOYL-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1173" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1174</div></th><td class="s6">Form Data to Google Sheets &amp; Airtable Pipeline</td><td class="s7">Automates data collection from an n8n form, extracting date/time, formatting inputs, saving to Google Sheets and Airtable, and sending personalized emails via Gmail. Utilizes n8n workflow with Form Trigger, Code node, Google Sheets, Airtable, and Gmail integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17EtQNR06gMEW28AoKKHl_CwXHnIkBsKT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1174" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1175</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Transcript Analyzer &amp; Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates YouTube video analysis by extracting transcripts via youtube-transcript.io API, summarizes content using AI models (OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, DeepSeek, OpenRouter), and emails a structured summary. Ideal for creators and marketers to quickly digest video content.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1t5NWsHxjLQBfBpWxOdUEoSShi8kAF-ZP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1175" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1176</div></th><td class="s6">Spotify Liked Songs to Playlist Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates syncing Spotify Liked Songs to a specified playlist by adding missing tracks and removing unliked ones. Utilizes Spotify API for data fetch and modification and Gotify for notifications. Runs on a scheduled trigger, ideal for music playlist management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1otjivSScKEMtsv6ehatkc6-HJEdmvYMt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1176" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1177</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Driven SEO Seed Keyword Generator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses AI (Anthropic Claude model) and Langchain to generate 15-20 SEO seed keywords based on an Ideal Customer Profile (ICP). It aggregates ICP data, prompts the AI agent, and outputs keywords for SEO strategies. Requires connection to AI API and database.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XArCtoQCzotGQNCYJicPMQKehaOObzlA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1177" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1178</div></th><td class="s6">Image Analysis &amp; Embedding from Google Drive</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow downloads an image from Google Drive, extracts color data, generates semantic keywords using OpenAI vision models, creates a combined embedding document, and stores it in an in-memory vector store for image search. Utilizes Google Drive, OpenAI API, and n8n LangChain nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GugHGZ1VsoNyHDDRICF-EY1DFINwREiD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1178" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1179</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Auto Upload &amp; Metadata Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates uploading new videos from Google Drive to YouTube, generating SEO titles, detailed video descriptions, and relevant tags using OpenAI GPT-4.1 and Google Gemini models. Also scrapes video transcripts via Apify for content context and updates YouTube metadata automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OB4Tx5XYGMXe_o3UnKiRhdMnUWcuhSq6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1179" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1180</div></th><td class="s6">Pinterest Data Analysis &amp; AI Content Suggestions</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly Pinterest data retrieval via Pinterest API, stores it in Airtable, and uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for AI-powered trend analysis and pin content suggestions. Summarized insights are emailed to marketing managers to optimize content calendars.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XEzIgZxMpndE88d9fG30_ycDhE3L9a_Q">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1180" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1181</div></th><td class="s6">Google Calendar Event Manager</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Google Calendar API for creating, reading, updating, deleting, and checking availability of calendar events via automated webhook triggers. Utilizes Google OAuth2 for authentication and Langchain MCP trigger for AI-driven interactions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mDoiXWB4uUzVk77m1Y741lPcsCCqjH3-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1181" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1182</div></th><td class="s6">Landing Page Conversion Rate Optimizer</td><td class="s7">Automates analysis of landing pages by scraping URLs, then uses OpenAI&#39;s GPT-powered Langchain Agent to roast and provide 10 personalized, creative, and actionable Conversion Rate Optimization recommendations. Ideal for marketers and founders wanting data-driven CRO insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-PI2CBPKYMIwuWnNQWYCWrrvmRGMsN8R">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1182" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1183</div></th><td class="s6">AI Research Reports via Jina DeepSearch</td><td class="s7">Automates deep research using Jina AI DeepSearch API and n8n. Users input queries via chat, triggering the API to generate structured, fact-based reports. Includes automated Markdown formatting and cleanup for readable, insightful analysis. No API key needed.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pTxFbdq32kekgmjMo1cZm-goHeMm3SiD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1183" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1184</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable Multi-Method API Endpoint Template</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow providing a RESTful API for Airtable with full CRUD operations via multi-method webhooks. It uses Airtable API and n8n webhook/respond nodes to create, read (single/all), update, and delete customer records in Airtable.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pLDm6lnodh0evHGXyeJL8w_odsrpzTyu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1184" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1185</div></th><td class="s6">Amazon Best Seller Electronics Data Extractor</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Amazon Electronics best seller data using Bright Data API for scraping and Google Gemini LLM for structured information extraction, delivering product rankings, ratings, and offers as structured JSON.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uhe8hFoQIi8PsY5NLBZVLCqDglYf3-Es">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1185" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1186</div></th><td class="s6">HN Who is Hiring Job Scraper</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of &#39;Ask HN: Who is hiring?&#39; posts from Hacker News using Algolia Search API and Hacker News API. Leverages OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to structure job listing data and stores results in Airtable. Ideal for tracking tech job opportunities monthly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-kjogBS1kQVmtPI_ZEgBa7dGev5KSXnR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1186" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1187</div></th><td class="s6">Hacker News Historical Headline Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching Hacker News front-page headlines from multiple years on the same day, categorizes and summarizes key tech trends using Google Gemini (PaLM) LLM, and publishes markdown reports via Telegram. Utilizes HTTP requests, HTML parsing, date calculations, and Langchain LLM integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zZFBgxuUb69lPZVxmQlCwY8fnVgHouXg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1187" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1188</div></th><td class="s6">Line MiniBear Bot: Namecard &amp; Task Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates Line messaging by processing texts, images, and audio. Uses Line Messaging API, OpenRouter GPT-4o model, and Microsoft suite (Teams, To Do, OneDrive) to extract namecard info, create tasks, save messages, and manage files with AI-driven content recognition.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MLx6H3w47I7vcfldNvqB-XZcnG7iZAj