com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PN5VlCA99xHHArie8WwujFRAgWsnbP13">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1194" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1195</div></th><td class="s6">Indeed Company Info Extract &amp; Summarize</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and summarization of company data from Indeed using Bright Data&#39;s Web Unlocker API and Google Gemini LLM. Converts markdown data to text and HTML, formats results via AI agent, and sends summarized insights via webhook for HR and engineering use.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1o9lQkw-OvhvZImKMUXhxNKy_0_ZgJ_Rd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1195" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1196</div></th><td class="s6">Line Bot Chinese Translator</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrating Line Messaging API and OpenRouter.ai LLM to translate text and image content to Chinese with pinyin and English. Supports text, image input via Line webhook, uses OpenRouter&#39;s qwen models, sends replies back via Line API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18tzJr4lF7xJ9vfEBRGMA3NpTJzElbna5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1196" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1197</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Likes to Airtable Content Hub</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of insightful LinkedIn post likes from the last 7 days via RapidAPI, filters and formats them into content ideas, then stores these ideas in Airtable for content planning. Uses LinkedIn API (via RapidAPI) and Airtable integration with n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19no0iuafsgCa20EUQCVlKGFrO6MfCVr8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1197" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1198</div></th><td class="s6">AI Travel Planner with Couchbase &amp; Gemini 2.0</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered travel planning assistant using Google Gemini 2.0 Flash for chat, OpenAI text-embedding-3-small for embeddings, and Couchbase vector search for storing and retrieving points of interest. Enables conversational trip planning with vector similarity search.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-1MY2qDiu-YJiY2w4rSp0062vyvMV6TP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1198" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1199</div></th><td class="s6">Entra Contacts to Zammad User Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to synchronize Microsoft Entra contacts with Zammad user accounts. It uses Microsoft Graph API to fetch contacts and Zammad API to create, update, or deactivate users. Automates user management by merging, filtering, and comparing datasets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oE1EieMRH8c8H26SI0x1hIhZWFjmMdbz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1199" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1200</div></th><td class="s6">CoinMarketCap DEXScan AI Agent</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrating CoinMarketCap&#39;s DEXScan API with GPT-4o Mini AI to provide real-time and historical data on decentralized exchanges, including liquidity, trading volume, OHLCV, spot pairs, and trades. Uses HTTP requests, OpenAI API, and memory buffers for intelligent query handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TkGiX570EyT1IczGSoRTTbgzwr3jouxB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1200" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1201</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Resume Review &amp; Google Sheets Logging</td><td class="s7">Automates resume submission, extraction, and evaluation using a form, Google Drive, PDF text extraction, OpenAI GPT-4, and Google Sheets for record keeping. It extracts personal info and qualifications, summarizes candidate profiles, assigns HR ratings, and logs results for streamlined hiring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ywuSP6FwxLogqkNdqvAt4OJR1Y1cBkKX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1201" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1202</div></th><td class="s6">KNN Image Classifier for Land Use</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that classifies satellite images into land use types using Voyage.ai for image embeddings and Qdrant vector search for KNN classification with majority voting and tie resolution loops.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cK_ukNc85isWOmgzADj41Rk2AbXWKHjX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1202" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1203</div></th><td class="s6">Auto-Create Airtable Tables from Webflow Forms</td><td class="s7">Automates creating Airtable tables dynamically for each Webflow form submission using Webflow API trigger and Airtable API (Personal Access Token). Organizes submitted form data efficiently without manual table setup, ideal for Webflow sites needing structured data storage in Airtable.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17hNNCrs5tiuoAqLpiwbUWxvofjS_MXNz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1203" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1204</div></th><td class="s6">JPG/PNG to WEBP Image Converter</td><td class="s7">Automates conversion of JPG and PNG images to WEBP using APYHub API. Retrieves image URLs from Google Sheets, converts images, uploads results to Google Drive. Tech stack: APYHub API, Google Sheets and Google Drive integrations, n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1s4S83VtDHNtXC9AdrgejR2NX-5QbIrD4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1204" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1205</div></th><td class="s6">Pipedrive OAuth2 Token Refresh Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates OAuth2 token refresh for Pipedrive API using n8n, Supabase DB for token storage, and HTTP/webhook nodes. Enables secure storage and refreshing of access tokens for reliable API calls with Pipedrive integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ljS5ulriRhoOJZtbJlzA-D2JhUCPOphc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1205" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1206</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Transcriber Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates transcription of YouTube videos via Supadata API and OpenAI GPT-4O for punctuation and formatting. Validates YouTube URLs, fetches raw transcripts, and refines text for easy reading in Portuguese, streamlining video content consumption and study.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1abhbJbmyIDQNQenNacWrOJYvGz5jzxWo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1206" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1207</div></th><td class="s6">SSL Certificate Expiry Alert System</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly monitoring of SSL certificates for URLs listed in Google Sheets using SSL-Checker.io API. Updates sheet with validity and expiry info, and sends alerts via Gmail and Telegram for expiring or invalid certificates, ensuring proactive SSL management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_yr2WYofdXC7I0Y9es6WKD3Z8-BuJVOk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1207" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1208</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify-Mautic Marketing Consent Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing customer marketing consent and segment membership between Shopify and Mautic using Shopify webhooks, Mautic API (OAuth2), Shopify GraphQL API, and webhook signature validation for secure marketing preference management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oi6ptLNlpjP0tugk5Y00ZNeUXpsYmQtF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1208" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1209</div></th><td class="s6">Hourly Automated n8n Error Retry</td><td class="s7">Automates retrying failed n8n workflow executions every hour. Uses n8n API for fetching error executions, logs into n8n via HTTP request, filters successful retries, and retries failed executions automatically. Ideal for improving workflow reliability.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vuD4wH9OWMQ5mfYkgoEk99VUYRevf6WO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1209" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1210</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce to Telegram Order Alerts</td><td class="s7">Automates sending Telegram notifications for WooCommerce orders moved to processing status. Utilizes WooCommerce Webhooks, n8n workflow, JavaScript for message formatting, and Telegram Bot API to instantly alert store owners with detailed order info.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10ttCM_sMlGRQkba6L-SQCRe227VAnCpv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1210" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1211</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress Form Lead Capture to Mautic</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing leads from WordPress forms via webhook, normalizes data (name, email, mobile), validates emails, and creates contacts in Mautic CRM. Built using n8n workflow with WordPress webhook and Mautic API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CcvDXy-HidS0xf2VIWbHZ-9sibd9lGei">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1211" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1212</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive AI Document Summarizer &amp; Emailer</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading documents from Google Drive, summarizes content using Mistral AI language model with n8n LangChain integration, and emails the summary via Gmail. Ideal for quick document insights using Google Drive, Mistral Cloud API, and Gmail OAuth2.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YQ7gxtAMUt5QUT2DJXLLnBO_n3iF3nls">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1212" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1213</div></th><td class="s6">Clockify Monthly Report Backup to GitHub</td><td class="s7">Automates backup of monthly Clockify detailed time reports by retrieving data via Clockify API, comparing with existing JSON files in GitHub repo, and creating or updating report files. Built with n8n using Clockify, GitHub API, HTTP Request, and data processing nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QjYLcBTMR_09ZmUeShT9B3gyJKEHKsuF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1213" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1214</div></th><td class="s6">Google Analytics SEO Data Analysis</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly Google Analytics data retrieval using GA4 API, compares current and past week SEO metrics, queries an AI model via Openrouter for SEO insights, and saves results in Baserow. Integrates Google Analytics, Openrouter AI, and Baserow within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_hLcHYRjI7MEQyMZQ2nHKQ77NdCQkd_Q">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1214" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1215</div></th><td class="s6">CoinMarketCap Crypto Exchange &amp; Sentiment Agent</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating CoinMarketCap APIs with OpenAI GPT-4o Mini to provide detailed cryptocurrency exchange data, asset holdings, market sentiment via Fear &amp; Greed Index, and the CMC 100 index. Designed for crypto analysts seeking automated, structured insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MlTcMb1wRajk6yZj57UPiXVWZ58eHnKd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1215" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1216</div></th><td class="s6">Local Ollama Vision Models Image Analyzer</td><td class="s7">Automates detailed image analysis using multiple locally hosted Ollama Vision LLMs, downloading images from Google Drive and saving markdown-formatted results to Google Docs. Ideal for developers needing exhaustive contextual and object insights with Google Drive and Docs integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19S2wWGVaLoX0nZutul68qr1peMz4tqkr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1216" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1217</div></th><td class="s6">Entra to Zammad User Sync Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates synchronization of Microsoft Entra (Azure AD) group users with Zammad user records via Microsoft Graph API and Zammad API. Manages user creation, update, and deactivation to keep Zammad in sync with Entra group memberships.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wu7oZSkFdCctXGLeiCf0QpM_LobWZNNR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1217" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1218</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Airtable MCP Server</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow builds an MCP server integrating Airtable with AI tools from Langchain and OpenAI GPT-4o. It enables chat-triggered intelligent CRUD operations on Airtable records using AI agents, memory buffers, and real-time SSE endpoints. Ideal for automated