r opened suspicious emails. Integrates Sublime Security webhook, Slack user lookup, and Jira Software Cloud for security alert management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rs-4wqVhyx_ejKRSm5UBxhkIO99inUJd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1221" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1222</div></th><td class="s6">AI Business Model Canvas Generator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Ollama LLM (LLaMA 3.1) via Langchain nodes to generate a complete Business Model Canvas from user input. Outputs all 9 blocks plus business title as a downloadable HTML file, automating strategic business planning.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Sb4q2j08jWRfA311XcrY6-Apx25mBnB9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1222" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1223</div></th><td class="s6">Discord MCP Server Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates Discord server management using Discord Bot API and custom API calls. It enables sending messages to channels or users, waiting for replies, managing roles, and fetching servers, channels, and members. Integrated with MCP trigger for flexible event-driven automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kdxxpDVNkHEMsG9Y9rORwRPUNj7M9-5P">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1223" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1224</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Email Classification &amp; Labeling</td><td class="s7">Automate Gmail email classification using Google Gemini and LangChain AI. Categorizes emails into High Priority, School Related, Promotion, or Other, then applies Gmail labels via OAuth2. Ideal for organizing and prioritizing inbox with AI-driven text classification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xWvloRgPjqNQWxSCUA4gTnJlYaZIZyx_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1224" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1225</div></th><td class="s6">Medoid Setup for Crop Anomaly Detection</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow setting cluster centers (medoids) and threshold scores for anomaly detection on agricultural crop images. Uses Qdrant vector database for clustering and distance matrix APIs, Voyage AI multimodal embeddings, and Python scipy for sparse matrix operations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1f9_PnEXhjhU_4DYhq6fOPTS1RZIsDS7C">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1225" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1226</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Citation Formatter for File Retrieval RAG</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using OpenAI assistant with vector store for file retrieval augmented generation (RAG). It retrieves chat thread content and file metadata via OpenAI API, formats text with citations, and optionally outputs Markdown or HTML for clean, referenced AI responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MmJglg3aVpJlvGInenGIAeHlBmx5O_-9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1226" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1227</div></th><td class="s6">Adobe PDF Services API Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that automates Adobe PDF Services API integration for PDF processing. It performs OAuth2 authentication, uploads PDFs, processes extraction/splitting requests, waits for completion, and downloads processed results. Uses Adobe API, Dropbox for test files, and HTTP requests.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PxY5hSbmLTbVR4IvFyyr1mc6ywif3JSc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1227" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1228</div></th><td class="s6">Graphic Wallpaper Generator with Midjourney &amp; GPT-4o-mini</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of cinematic sci-fi wallpapers using PiAPI&#39;s Midjourney image generation, GPT-4o-mini for creative prompts, and Canvas API for final design. Produces visually rich, emotionally resonant graphic wallpapers tailored by user-defined themes, scenarios, and styles.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IrOSkSbM3WQJ_7emMA4rrUAE5ptLF6iU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1228" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1229</div></th><td class="s6">Confluence AI Chatbot with OpenAI &amp; Telegram</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that integrates Confluence REST API (basic auth) to fetch page content, converts HTML to Markdown, and uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini via LangChain for AI-powered Q&amp;A. Supports context memory, responds via Telegram bot.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18x4LYEZYkTLWSxhR9vADoaTZziWEeqCj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1229" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1230</div></th><td class="s6">eCommerce Contact Form Text Classifier</td><td class="s7">Automates classification of contact form messages for eCommerce using n8n, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for text classification, Google Sheets for data storage, and SMTP for email notifications to respective departments (quotes, orders, etc.).</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tVRl8IzpvcqAHhNZ_iGGJrzQKFA4VNw9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1230" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1231</div></th><td class="s6">LINE to Google Drive File Upload &amp; Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates saving files from LINE Messaging API to Google Drive with folder organization by date and file type. Logs file metadata to Google Sheets. Utilizes LINE API, Google Drive API, and Google Sheets API within n8n workflow for seamless file handling and user reply.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hs3fwreO1PVNC7mNL7CY4R93bVq5XqQZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1231" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1232</div></th><td class="s6">Local Ollama LLM Prompt Router</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses local Ollama LLM models to dynamically route user prompts to the best specialized AI model (text, code, vision) for task-specific responses. It ensures privacy by running entirely on local Ollama API with memory buffers for chat context.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MhkkG-fZrMbbvXp74lBsz2zmbaROL0i9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1232" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1233</div></th><td class="s6">Doctor Appointment Booking Assistant</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered virtual assistant workflow that automates medical appointment scheduling for Dr. Hakim using OpenAI GPT-4, Google Calendar, and Google Sheets. It handles patient interaction, checks availability, books slots, and logs data efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hJCxN5FCG5YsferBcDD-Sdw0zrzAIB0K">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1233" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1234</div></th><td class="s6">Odoo Sales AI Chatbot with Opportunity Summary</td><td class="s7">AI-powered chatbot for Odoo sales module using OpenAI GPT-4, LangChain, and Odoo API to fetch, summarize, and interactively discuss sales opportunities with live context and memory management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QoMQtNyfxi37Q0rLfB88EYKPck9j1uCX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1234" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1235</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify to D365 Business Central Order Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Shopify orders to Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central by creating sales orders or invoices via Business Central REST API. Utilizes n8n, Shopify API, and OAuth2-secured Business Central endpoints for customer lookup, order processing, and fulfillment integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1owjpG--5iKfjw5lasUMIoKvCAn9X-BBd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1235" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1236</div></th><td class="s6">Email Invoice &amp; Payment Extractor with LLM</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of transaction details from labeled Gmail invoices and payment emails using n8n. Uses Gmail API triggers, PDF extraction, HTML parsing, Google Gemini and Groq LLMs with structured output parsers, then logs data to Google Sheets for finance management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EUZUa51duvYUNSz0sXLkGe6y1Bwty_6m">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1236" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1237</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Profile Finder with Bright Data &amp; GPT-4o-mini</td><td class="s7">Automates LinkedIn profile discovery by processing user form input with Bright Data for Google scraping and GPT-4o-mini for NLP. Extracts and filters LinkedIn search results, generates personalized outreach emails, and sends via SMTP. Ideal for sales prospecting automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1l7tz1RGHYJRUgu0Ukqtg3K9yRzlSE30n">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1237" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1238</div></th><td class="s6">Notion AI Knowledge Base Assistant</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow creates an AI agent that queries and summarizes data from a Notion knowledge base using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o model. It integrates Notion API for database search and content retrieval, Langchain for AI memory and tool use, enabling concise, fact-based answers from Notion data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cOQxMsKtFpFFAt4ywGvwvYh_qQPodxIB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1238" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1239</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Companies to Airtable CRM Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates searching LinkedIn companies via Ghost Genius API, filters by criteria, checks duplicates, and adds new companies to Airtable CRM. Uses n8n with HTTP requests, batch processing, and Airtable integration for streamlined lead management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vobul71Et3_pgQuf89ur8EQnUMsuBAhG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1239" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1240</div></th><td class="s6">Human-in-the-Loop AI Email Assistant</td><td class="s7">Automates email reading via IMAP, summarizes with LangChain and OpenAI GPT models, drafts replies, and sends emails after human approval. Integrates IMAP, SMTP, LangChain AI nodes, and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for professional business email handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YDkrl-iYbkRHuvcmJ_Ykt6iE4qEbnR-5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1240" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1241</div></th><td class="s6">WhatsApp Business Appointment Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating WhatsApp appointment notifications and user message handling. Uses WhatsApp Business API, Google Sheets, and scheduled triggers to manage user opt-in, send templated messages, receive and reply to messages, and update statuses seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11W38nWZGfizcwhOIXvg0DekIFtP1ll1_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1241" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1242</div></th><td class="s6">Obsidian Notes to Podcast Feed Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates turning Obsidian notes into a podcast feed using OpenAI TTS for audio, Cloudinary for storage, and Google Sheets for episode metadata. Generates an RSS podcast feed compatible with major platforms. Integrates Obsidian, OpenAI, Cloudinary, Google Sheets, and n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1T3AzDfpwrp-ms3vH8HTdqIIh4coXhPxp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1242" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1243</div></th><td class="s6">Amazon Data Scraper with Bright Data API</td><td class="s7">Automates structured bulk data extraction from Amazon using Bright Data&#39;s Web Scraper API via HTTP requests in n8n. Waits for snapshot readiness, aggregates JSON results, writes data to disk, and triggers webhook notifications. Ideal for data analysts and engineers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1w9XpwiMaw4POiIPHs4D80z_hxiSCuEt8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1243" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1244</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive Image Background Remover</td><td class="s7">Automates background removal for images in Google Drive using the PhotoRoom API. Downloads new images, removes or changes backgrounds with padding and size options, then uploads them back to Drive. Built with n8n, Google Drive API, and PhotoRoom API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WNEJOfq3rkML9zazgUjnUt7PghEO9eld">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1244" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1245</div></th><td class="s6">Ahrefs Keyword Research Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates SEO keyword research using Ahrefs API via RapidAPI, Google Gemini AI for query extraction and response formatting, and custom JS for data extraction. Enables chat-triggered keyword insights with detailed metrics on main and related keywords for content optimization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1M-Jel0GQGR6uoS4wKBGORF3WqfsyK0dN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1245" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1246</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI API Usage Examples Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating various OpenAI API integrations: text completion, chat (ChatGPT), text editing, audio transcription (Whisper), and image generation (DALLE-2). Shows prompts for summaries, translations, HTML SVG generation, and quick email replies.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10bABtT4Pc2Xd312hyKxOxAZdBBiJ7Lua">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1246" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1247</div></th><td class="s6">Printify Product Title &amp; Description Updater</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating product title and description updates for Printify shops using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini. Integrates Printify API, Google Sheets for trigger and record keeping, and AI-powered content generation to enhance eCommerce product listings efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Rlmj_0VHIYL1Kx340bYCo8y6_7lq0Tma">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1247" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1248</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Local Folder Organizer</td><td class="s7">Automates file organization in a local folder using n8n. It monitors a target directory with a local file trigger, lists files via shell commands, and uses Mistral Cloud AI to suggest subfolder categorization. Files are then moved accordingly with execute command nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ETqfGmQpzDT_LyuabYuJF14Q26bnXKRn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1248" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1249</div></th><td class="s6">FLUX-fill Image Editor &amp; Inpainting API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating FLUX-fill API for interactive image editing and inpainting. Uses Konva.js and img-comparison-slider in an HTML editor, with webhook-triggered image processing, mask and prompt inputs, and real-time generation via FLUX-fill API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qVHY7LeGmeNZOiLYGjINI2ysTfRFddky">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1249" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1250</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Subworkflow Dependency Graph &amp; Auto-Tagging</td><td class="s7">Automatically builds a dependency graph of n8n workflows to identify and visualize which workflows call others. Uses n8n API, JavaScript code nodes, HTTP Requests, MermaidJS, and chart nodes to provide dependency insights and auto-tagging of sub-workflows for easier management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eyYrUM4qXaIAbC6JmYHKlh6KMsr4jpkC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1250" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1251</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice Parsing &amp; Database Entry Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates invoice processing: triggers on new Google Drive files, sends files to LlamaParse API for extraction, receives parsed data via webhook, then creates invoices and line items in a database. Uses Google Drive, webhook, LlamaParse API, and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for data extraction and structuring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uAjMIMKhH9_TVKNIgeKLZjcSiBzpe9cB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1251" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1252</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Air Quality &amp; Pollen Advisor</td><td class="s7">Automates daily air quality and pollen data retrieval via Ambee API, then uses OpenAI GPT-4 and Langchain AI to generate personalized, easy-to-understand environmental health summaries and care suggestions emailed to users based on location and health profile.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oRsrGct56srns3YGEYcp9vYOI6SE-D6P">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1252" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1253</div></th><td class="s6">Notion Work Time &amp; Break Tracker</td><td class="s7">Automates work time tracking by logging start, break, and end times in Notion using n8n webhook. Integrates Notion API with conditional logic for real-time updates, perfect for personal or team productivity monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BgKDSjcux9-x-R7HWCKMKPU_38WUNNFN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1253" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1254</div></th><td class="s6">Training Feedback Automation with Airtable &amp; Usertask</td><td class="s7">Automates training feedback management using Airtable to trigger workflows, Usertask API for task creation, LinkedIn for positive feedback posting, and SMTP email notifications. It routes poor feedback to urgent tasks and celebrates good feedback on LinkedIn.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QaLi4VEjMy70yShH_t5_gXuFMwyfhPG7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1254" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1255</div></th><td class="s6">AI Personal Shopper with RAG &amp; WooCommerce</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI LLM, Qdrant vector database, Google Drive, and WooCommerce to build a personal shopper chatbot. It extracts user intents and product details from chat, queries WooCommerce for products, and uses RAG with store docs for general queries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ypVFywaD4HE9isVF1W8PMzxtKKtFn99b">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1255" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1256</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Slack Channels for Webflow Forms</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of Slack channels named after Webflow forms, sending form submissions as Slack messages. Utilizes Webflow trigger and Slack API with Bot OAuth token. Also notifies #general channel for new channels, enabling seamless team communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12idckEYmgn0zUWOAW7J6-FeF3sliHin0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1256" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1257</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chatbot for Google Search Console Data</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o and Google Search Console API with Postgres chat memory. Enables conversational querying of Search Console properties and data insights via a secure webhook, providing markdown-formatted responses based on natural language inputs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ePAfqocfNCbueQgqx1PRKzPep8KJ31BE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1257" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1258</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Upload Crop Images to Qdrant with Embeddings</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that imports crop images from Google Cloud Storage, creates embeddings using Voyage AI API, and batch uploads them to a Qdrant Cloud collection. It includes collection management, filtering for anomaly detection, and payload indexing for efficient queries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zntTyhSPpK9_jG634OAdMRKV91-fWu76">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1258" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1259</div></th><td class="s6">Prompt-Based Object Detection with Google Gemini 2.0</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow leveraging Google Gemini 2.0 API for prompt-based object detection in images. It downloads an image, extracts dimensions, queries Gemini for bounding boxes of specified objects, rescales coordinates, and draws boxes on the image using n8n&#39;s Edit Image node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18yPdPrlD7bfMXiYgp1hvhsItZkvAqBtd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1259" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1260</div></th><td class="s6">Proxmox AI Assistant for API Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Google Gemini AI and Proxmox API tools to parse user instructions into validated Proxmox VM management API calls. Features chat, Telegram, Gmail triggers, structured output parsing, and automatic API call execution for managing VMs and clusters.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yX_Kz1RFTQGjF89w4zz0KCnaUHfec6JL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1260" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1261</div></th><td class="s6">Todoist to Notion Task Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing of Todoist tasks labeled &#39;send-to-notion&#39; into a Notion database, updating tasks with Notion links. Utilizes Todoist API (OAuth2) and Notion API, triggered on schedule to keep both apps aligned seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1imz9lZNeUgjiEHs3QSC7tvHKQzY-0MA0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1261" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1262</div></th><td class="s6">Automated n8n Docker Update with Telegram Alerts</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates checking the latest n8n Docker image version via GitHub API, compares it with the installed Docker container version, and if outdated, pulls and updates the container. It uses SSH commands to manage Docker and Telegram API for user notifications and approvals.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Dbv2LcoVXcUHCgL0WEsMNaXbqP7HNtcS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1262" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1263</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Company Story Generator with AI &amp; Bright Data</td><td class="s7">Automates company story creation from LinkedIn data using Bright Data&#39;s web scraping API and Google Gemini AI models for extraction, formatting, and summarization. Combines HTTP requests, recursive text splitting, and AI-driven language modeling for detailed and concise narratives.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wWIuzeF1ql7X2qalJyne1PMOXX-ohJ86">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1263" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1264</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Discord Channel Cleanup</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates daily cleanup of Discord channels by deleting messages older than 7 days. It uses Discord API, scheduled triggers, batching, filtering, and waits to respect rate limits, ensuring efficient and compliant channel management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cEqgPyNSdb1nWbqOVd5fcZt7EOt4c5kY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1264" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1265</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly SSL Expiry Monitoring &amp; Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly SSL certificate checks for URLs listed in Google Sheets using ssl-checker.io API and sends alert emails via Gmail if expiry is within 7 days. Built with n8n, Google Sheets API, ssl-checker.io, and Gmail API for proactive SSL management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rdo4D67LDpUu10TS4ognhi1rB96H_Z3V">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1265" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1266</div></th><td class="s6">RetellAI Automated Lead Call &amp; Scheduling</td><td class="s7">Automates outbound lead qualification calls and inbound appointment scheduling using RetellAI. Integrates Google Sheets (lead tracking), Twilio (SMS reminders), OpenAI GPT-4 (call summarization), and Gmail (email notifications) to streamline call workflows and post-call updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1p7BU1SOt9hXLPMmC6mWlsvNZuzLuttfY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1266" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1267</div></th><td class="s6">Tavily API Search &amp; Extract with AI Summary</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Tavily API for intelligent web search and content extraction, combined with OpenAI to summarize content. Automates fetching relevant web data and summarizing it for research or content enrichment using Tavily&#39;s search/extract endpoints and OpenAI&#39;s LLM.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1m9E39oUFYK99feda2Gi7MxprJn78OT8c">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1267" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1268</div></th><td class="s6">Lead Qualification in Google Sheets via GPT-4</td><td class="s7">Automates lead qualification by monitoring Google Sheets for new entries, using OpenAI GPT-4 (chat model) to evaluate leads based on business criteria, and updating the sheet with a rating. Integrates Google Sheets API and OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4 for seamless lead scoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kUtrcq9G7gBepCt31ehma2YACc58exuX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1268" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1269</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Lead Qualification &amp; CRM Deal Creation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Gmail, Pipedrive CRM, and OpenAI GPT-4 to automatically assess email replies from cold campaigns, identify interested leads, and create deals in Pipedrive. It enables scalable, AI-powered sales pipeline automation with multi-inbox support.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16fMi2An3uY3WIx_e_LHH8OqADNybIUqc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1269" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1270</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Prompt Loader and Dynamic AI Prompting</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow fetches markdown prompts from a GitHub repo, dynamically replaces variables set in the workflow, verifies missing variables, and sends the prepared prompt to LangChain AI agent and Ollama chat model for processing and content generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AU9gvV5pQaGNBQZxPyds32u3FhXZltyc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1270" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1271</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Driven Rental Payment Reconciliation</td><td class="s7">An n8n self-hosted workflow automating rental payment reconciliation by monitoring local CSV bank statements, querying tenant &amp; property data from an Excel file, using OpenAI GPT-4 for AI analysis, and updating reports in XLSX format. Stack: n8n, localFileTrigger, OpenAI API, SheetJS.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xeNd9pjP7AC_8DmkeyouZn4CS7D8Pm8g">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1271" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1272</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Remove PII from Google Drive CSV</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that monitors a Google Drive folder for new CSV files, uses OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to detect PII columns in tabular data, removes those PII columns, and uploads sanitized CSVs to another Drive folder. Integrates Google Drive API and OpenAI API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fIqHv-c-JZLZ-6nmR8JaCkgwZ9tH5_Cd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1272" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1273</div></th><td class="s6">Real Estate Lead Enrichment &amp; CRM Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates property lead discovery by querying BatchData API with custom filters, enriches leads via skip tracing for owner contacts, scores leads, exports to Excel, and pushes to HubSpot CRM with email notifications. Uses n8n HTTP, code, spreadsheet, and email nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16ENy9E4gSQnqtxms9OpaJ6DhQn5bCeqD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1273" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1274</div></th><td class="s6">Asana Task Rescheduler &amp; Cleaner</td><td class="s7">Automates Asana task management by rescheduling overdue open tasks to today&#39;s date and deleting completed tasks. Uses Asana API with n8n scheduling and conditional logic nodes to keep workspace organized and up-to-date daily.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XCwHpPQknroGiE2jjoFwfCczhnnxYdHG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1274" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1275</div></th><td class="s6">NeurochainAI Telegram Chatbot</td><td class="s7">Automates AI-powered chat and image generation via Telegram using NeurochainAI API. Utilizes Telegram Bots and NeurochainAI&#39;s REST API for text and image generation with configurable AI models. Handles user prompts, errors, and sends AI responses directly in chat.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14t9aCgbPVHdTjBS3pTl4l27hUIYEFV7X">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1275" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1276</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chatbot with Long-Term Memory</td><td class="s7">An AI-powered Telegram bot using DeepSeek and LangChain for conversational interaction with long-term memory stored in Google Docs. It validates users, routes message types, and uses DeepSeek&#39;s AI models for context-aware, personalized responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qvXvmVOlyWtW3eFhEvlIuCNsdouPz4oz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1276" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1277</div></th><td class="s6">BambooHR Webhook Testing with PostBin &amp; Slack</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow enables testing BambooHR webhooks without changing webhook URLs by using PostBin for request capturing and Slack for notifications. It integrates BambooHR API, PostBin API, Slack API, and OpenAI to monitor HR data changes and send welcome messages.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JG45pw6TKYTfzUEFvO-UaRxfX6JfjFL7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1277" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1278</div></th><td class="s6">Trustpilot Review Scraper &amp; Sentiment Analyzer</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping of Trustpilot reviews using DeepSeek API, extracts detailed review info, analyzes sentiment with OpenAI, and stores results in Google Sheets. Ideal for companies monitoring customer feedback and sentiment analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1DYaYdcAZ84ydPm7Y5cx6i4niAi9Jk_0i">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1278" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1279</div></th><td class="s6">Google Analytics SEO Insights Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly Google Analytics data retrieval and comparison using GA4 API, processes page engagement, search console metrics, and country views. Uses Openrouter AI (meta-llama model) for SEO analysis and stores results in Baserow database.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-88zeCm655WZpZrRrlOGqBPEsfrcGzwS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1279" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1280</div></th><td class="s6">Email PDF Attachment Filter &amp; Upload</td><td class="s7">Automates filtering of PDF attachments from Gmail using OpenAI to detect relevant documents (e.g., payslips), then uploads matched PDFs to Google Drive. Uses Gmail API, OpenAI API, and Google Drive API within n8n workflow for document management automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BbPaGqAwNXAO_PVAqkSjLDc_Tpynb_XD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1280" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1281</div></th><td class="s6">Linear Issue Sentiment Monitoring &amp; Alerts</td><td class="s7">Automates sentiment analysis on updated Linear.app issue comments using OpenAI, stores insights in Airtable, and sends Slack alerts on negative sentiment transitions, enabling proactive support issue management. Tech stack: Linear GraphQL API, OpenAI, Airtable, Slack, n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tVHgLpUqA54g2sQ8x13QB0ruEd-8jw6g">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1281" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1282</div></th><td class="s6">Hey Siri AI Agent with n8n and OpenAI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Apple Shortcuts with OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini model, enabling voice-driven AI interactions via Siri. It uses webhook triggers, LangChain agents, and responds with voice-optimized AI answers, perfect for hands-free intelligent assistant tasks on iOS/macOS.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KUIC8UTy8jGdsmEq-DWLBMhOQkQhnVbc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1282" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1283</div></th><td class="s6">AI Event Banner Generator with n8n</td><td class="s7">Create event banners using n8n forms, OpenAI DALL·E 3 for AI image generation, Cloudinary for image hosting and optimization, BannerBear for templated design, and Discord for automated event posting. Streamlines banner creation and sharing via automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LC78tnNlO9vhgs_xlAeKuG4tW7eaW6um">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1283" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1284</div></th><td class="s6">SERPBear SEO Rank Analysis &amp; Storage</td><td class="s7">Automates SEO keyword rank monitoring using SERPBear API. Processes ranking data with JavaScript, sends it to Meta-LLama AI for expert analysis, and stores insights in Baserow database. Utilizes n8n for scheduled triggers and API integrations, enabling easy SEO performance tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1meTIob1AJ0P97NsJBMG67cpna10ULh5g">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1284" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1285</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Google Doc Summarizer to Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates summarizing new Google Docs uploaded to a Drive folder using OpenAI GPT-4O-MINI and logs summaries with metadata into Google Sheets for easy management. Integrates Google Drive, Docs, Sheets APIs and Langchain AI tools for streamlined document insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UxxIbTB9Q3XCB2bDbDaPtUmP0wyEbTu8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1285" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1286</div></th><td class="s6">AI Email Summarizer &amp; Messenger Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates reading emails via IMAP, summarizes content using Openrouter.ai&#39;s LLaMA model, and sends concise summaries or important alerts with deadlines to LINE messenger. Integrates IMAP, Openrouter API, and LINE Messaging API for streamlined email management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1In47Mbpt_2ul0WmHIDKlf4uqRvDN63Ht">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1286" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1287</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Video Summarizer with AI</td><td class="s7">Automates summarization of YouTube videos by extracting transcripts via Apify API, then using OpenAI&#39;s language model with n8n Langchain nodes to produce concise summaries. Ideal for content creators, researchers, and professionals seeking quick insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11LXc0RvYOK5Mwwc0rMKDLF5l97ctOwRU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1287" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1288</div></th><td class="s6">SQL Query Agent with Conversational Memory</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that enables conversational AI to query a local SQLite database using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4-turbo model via LangChain. It fetches, extracts, and stores the Chinook sample SQLite DB, then allows interactive SQL queries with memory of previous interactions for better context.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19zte37KIrCZusa6fh9kZ7ImJi2UdS8oo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1288" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1289</div></th><td class="s6">Spotify Control via Telegram and AI</td><td class="s7">Automate Spotify music control by sending messages through Telegram. Uses Telegram API for message triggers, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to parse artist and track info from chat, and Spotify API to search, play, and manage tracks. Ideal for hands-free Spotify interaction.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WfhtUyH_aMDQV6oU3gtN20W_ereYvAQK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1289" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1290</div></th><td class="s6">Location-Based Work Attendance Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates work attendance tracking by logging check-in/check-out times via iPhone location-triggered webhooks to Google Sheets using Google Drive and Sheets APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fB-oowWV2ghb8R3RfWlllunw5m1MJEGk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1290" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1291</div></th><td class="s6">Text Automations for Apple Shortcuts with OpenAI</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow integrates Apple Shortcuts with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini API to automate text tasks: translating (English/Spanish), grammar correction, and content length adjustments. Users select text on iOS/macOS, invoke shortcuts linked to a webhook, and receive AI-processed text updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zY9Es6GkYmVwHLkrhKlhc1-lRg4RxMhr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1291" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1292</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Google Drive Workflow Backup Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates nightly backups of n8n workflows to Google Drive using Google Drive and n8n APIs. It manages backup folders, moves old backups, and purges backups older than 30 days automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gcSiXMHjIY4qSBzMBcITCIDyopkgP0xo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1292" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1293</div></th><td class="s6">Email Verification Waitlist Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates user registration with email verification for a waitlist using n8n. Integrates Google Sheets for data storage, SMTP for sending verification codes, and n8n Forms for user input and validation, ensuring secure and organized waitlist management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fuW1cDgLfUJWVV58pK5tTCF39Y0jjUv7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1293" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1294</div></th><td class="s6">Productboard to Snowflake Data Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating import of Productboard notes, companies, and features into Snowflake data warehouse, using Productboard API and Snowflake DB nodes. Includes Slack notifications for weekly updates and Metabase dashboard linking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TZAnJWrMyE4WSzMtBBzjawOLga7YwSHT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1294" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1295</div></th><td class="s6">Linear to Productboard Sync Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing project status and target end dates from Linear to Productboard features using their APIs. Updates Productboard features&#39; status and timeframe, and sends notifications via Slack. Tech stack: n8n, Linear API, Productboard API, Slack API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-DPgC-8XFCfg8msh-Q_EnLEVR7zxYYOl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1295" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1296</div></th><td class="s6">Multi-Step Newsletter Signup &amp; Survey</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow captures newsletter signups and further user details via chained multi-page forms, storing data in Google Sheets and sending Slack alerts. Tech stack: n8n built-in Form and FormTrigger nodes, Google Sheets API, Slack API. Ideal for onboarding and lead capture.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fURhRAh2MtChmUrea7xnk0Yda9iGSlhg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1296" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1297</div></th><td class="s6">Google Search Console Data to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching Google Search Console data (queries, pages, dates) using Google OAuth2 API, processes it in n8n, and updates Google Sheets reports regularly to track SEO metrics like clicks, impressions, CTR, and position.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vJWaHAk5k6RdSHUFP9GnGWWig0EoJznx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1297" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1298</div></th><td class="s6">Calendly-KlickTipp Booking &amp; Cancellation Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates the sync of booking and cancellation data from Calendly to KlickTipp. Converts Calendly event info, manages invitee and guest subscriptions, handles rescheduling, and updates contact lists in KlickTipp using APIs. Streamlines event-based subscriber management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QkiijaZlc4xTQ0K-KHrX8B7d_by0IdFq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1298" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1299</div></th><td class="s6">Linear Issue Sentiment Monitoring &amp; Alerting</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of Linear app issues using GraphQL, performs sentiment analysis on issue comments via OpenAI&#39;s Chat Model, stores results in Airtable, and sends Slack alerts on negative sentiment transitions. Enables proactive issue management with n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lcfPnHINPq_ZumJKyOerrKnnTlv_QZAy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1299" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1300</div></th><td class="s6">Prompt-Based Object Detection with Google Gemini 2.0</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses Google Gemini 2.0 API to perform prompt-based object detection on an image, detecting specific objects (e.g., rabbits) with bounding boxes. It fetches an image via HTTP, gets image info, calls Gemini 2.0 for detection, rescales coordinates, and draws boxes using n8n&#39;s Edit Image node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HsxEKZwijPUsIjtpI4t6-HHez5x0Y28E">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1300" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1301</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Backup to GitHub</td><td class="s7">Automates backup of all n8n instance workflows to a specified GitHub repo. Uses n8n API to fetch workflows, GitHub API to retrieve and update files, and compares JSON content to avoid duplicates or unnecessary overwrites. Runs on schedule or manual trigger.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nAxmiYIJfCG6x_W8GAy1Dls_4ymEYjvB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1301" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1302</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice Parser: Google Drive to Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates invoice data extraction from Google Drive using LlamaParse API, OpenAI GPT-4 for line item extraction, then stores structured invoice and line item data in Airtable. Utilizes Google Drive trigger, HTTP requests, and webhook integrations for seamless, real-time processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_VTahPtSg1DXeQ6nUdvRfmqISQDm0SW1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1302" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1303</div></th><td class="s6">ServiceNow Incident Alerts to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching new ServiceNow incidents every 5 minutes and posts detailed incident notifications to a Slack channel. Utilizes ServiceNow API, Slack API, and n8n scheduling and sorting nodes for real-time IT incident monitoring and team alerting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1a9-62P1WX-SYINiGrYlTcF32zTDA4eiQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1303" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1304</div></th><td class="s6">CSV to JSON Conversion API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts CSV files or raw CSV text to JSON format using webhook POST requests. It uses n8n nodes for file extraction, CSV parsing via JavaScript code, and conditional branching. Supports error handling with Slack notifications for conversion errors.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10dZhseOZ4X-VI7vX5GC7F94-ygYZ7Qqx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1304" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1305</div></th><td class="s6">Social Media Lead Analyzer &amp; Email Generator</td><td class="s7">Automates lead outreach by extracting LinkedIn and Twitter posts via RapidAPI, analyzes data using OpenAI GPT-4, and generates personalized HTML cover letters sent via SMTP. Integrates Google Sheets for lead data and tracking, ideal for marketers and sales pros.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jARbK-lJy70NTGOpJNF5ejtZ_m0Snv1V">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1305" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1306</div></th><td class="s6">Docker Registry Image Cleaner</td><td class="s7">Automates cleanup of Docker registry by listing images and tags, identifying old tags beyond latest 10, removing them via Docker Registry HTTP API, running garbage collection via SSH, and sending email notifications. Uses HTTP Request, SSH, Code nodes in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1P5neYEWvzYAXTa-A6sfceNXOe4TfmYmy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1306" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1307</div></th><td class="s6">SuiteCRM Drive-To-Store Lead Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates lead generation for drive-to-store campaigns by integrating Google Sheets, SuiteCRM API (OAuth2), and webhooks. Checks duplicates, assigns coupons, and updates leads with custom fields to streamline CRM workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1J--JiqC3xF1l5b_ypp6RlKj4g7VEgIN6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1307" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1308</div></th><td class="s6">Notion Content Blocks Markdown Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing Notion database updates by converting Notion blocks to Markdown and back. Uses Notion API, n8n Notion Trigger, HTTP Request, and custom JS code to preserve rich text formatting including headings, lists, and annotations for seamless content manipulation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wlqIVZnX1IkN0XY1i3dtrrwNHaj2XFD8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1308" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1309</div></th><td class="s6">AI Fact-Checker for Articles with Ollama</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Ollama LLM models and Langchain nodes to split articles into sentences, fact-check each statement against given facts, and summarize factual inaccuracies. Integrates code splitting, merging, filtering, and aggregation nodes to automate article verification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zgzGW9-PpBOZRhUIOs0YAnSXoNvZBzfE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1309" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1310</div></th><td class="s6">BBC News to Podcast Script &amp; TTS</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches BBC news, classifies headlines using Google Gemini LLM, extracts details, and converts multiple news articles into a natural podcast script. The script is formatted for Hugging Face text-to-speech synthesis, enabling automated news podcast creation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hag_dld7akkLCGgLp_QBoSYgi79WoER4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1310" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1311</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube AI News Playlist Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates daily creation of YouTube playlists from AI news channels using Google Sheets for channel management, YouTube API to fetch recent videos, and Telegram for notifications. Deletes previous playlists to keep updates fresh and organized.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BVyC7fzmLoujwG9azhUBIRVcBtWHC1WJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1311" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1312</div></th><td class="s6">Google Form Quiz Certificate Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates certificate generation for quiz takers using Google Forms (quiz mode), Google Sheets, Google Slides, Drive, and Gmail. It triggers on new form responses, evaluates scores, creates personalized certificates from a Slides template, converts them to PDF, and emails them to users.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SNpMsy9jW1BrMEkPl4HVJbX3MsKSyQbu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1312" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1313</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Prompt Generator &amp; Categorizer</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow leveraging Google Gemini (PaLM) LLM to generate, categorize, name, and store AI prompts. Uses LangChain nodes to parse output and Airtable API to save prompts in a structured Prompt Library for seamless AI prompt management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oaP0HGzgxf7qsJfUImongZ2rtgNvKCFq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1313" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1314</div></th><td class="s6">CallForge Gong Call Data Processor</td><td class="s7">Automates processing Gong call data integrated with Salesforce. Uses Salesforce and Gong APIs in n8n to fetch, filter, and format call records by stage and opportunity, then passes them for AI-based call preprocessing, enabling sales insights extraction.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HUvugK39spr0NXqSjUX6_pJL4p41vD9X">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1314" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1315</div></th><td class="s6">CallForge AI Sales Call Processor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Gong API, Notion, Google Sheets, and OpenAI to automate extraction, enrichment, and processing of sales call transcripts for actionable insights and error correction in Gong calls.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12YELlACu0riWrmJ_Q7P3zk43my1qEO3y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1315" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1316</div></th><td class="s6">CallForge AI Gong Sales Call Processor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that extracts and enriches Gong sales call transcripts with Salesforce data using Gong API, Salesforce API, and advanced data transformation nodes. It segments speakers, enriches call metadata, and formats data for AI analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1G2X1b1Q9r9LTUdrCzm6Rfkdg6j1PdkP7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1316" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1317</div></th><td class="s6">CallForge Sales Call AI Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and organization of sales call data from Gong into Notion. Uses n8n with Notion API, Slack API, and AI subworkflows to analyze calls, update databases, and send progress alerts. Ideal for sales teams wanting streamlined call analysis and tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10QjR-N_1ycK8ygFjY7x17J8mohsJuZ4y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1317" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1318</div></th><td class="s6">AI Sales Call Data to Notion DB</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction and organization of sales call insights like competitors, integrations, objections, and use cases using AI-generated data. Utilizes n8n with Notion API, handling data splitting, aggregation, and rate limiting to update multiple Notion databases for sales analytics.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1q-xuT70rWN8wcF785-Bs886KmfU8v-83">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1318" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1319</div></th><td class="s6">AI Sales Call Insights to Notion</td><td class="s7">Automates processing of AI-generated sales call data with Notion integration. Extracts Marketing Insights, Recurring Topics, and Actionable Insights from Gong calls, then organizes and updates them in separate Notion databases. Uses n8n workflow automation with Notion API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1syu7S5R_5C9sOR0STrTS9Dsw54ROG4h7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1319" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1320</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Water Drinking Reminder with AI Motivate</td><td class="s7">Automates water intake reminders via Slack using Google Sheets for logging, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for personalized motivational messages, and iOS shortcuts integration. Encourages healthy hydration with friendly AI-generated advice and tracks drinking habits.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LAW-kGKlqxTja-w42oeRR2r7r38Mac2M">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1320" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1321</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Driven Google Sheets Data Analyst</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4, LangChain AI Agent, and Google Sheets API to analyze and query transaction data via chat. It filters by date, status, and product using Google Sheets OAuth, enabling dynamic, AI-powered data insights and calculations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rZ94Y0GlFMujUKcTiQ2nOan_hrlf7dHm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1321" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1322</div></th><td class="s6">Google Gemini AI Media Analyzer Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating 5 methods to analyze images and PDFs using Google Gemini AI (PaLM API), Unsplash image source, and direct API calls. Automates media content understanding with dynamic prompts, batch processing, and data transformations in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TUTD5xcEVproisGQrMU43hzLsGNVdFh_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1322" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1323</div></th><td class="s6">Dartagnan to Braze Email Template Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating synchronization of email templates from Dartagnan to Braze. It fetches auth tokens, lists and compares campaigns and email templates, processes HTML content including image embedding, and updates or creates templates via Dartagnan and Braze REST APIs. Runs on schedule.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Cm7kQkgAIGYZ2P9GjgxUCg8Eqnd9KRkO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1323" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1324</div></th><td class="s6">Mistral OCR Document &amp; Image Parsing</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Mistral Cloud API for advanced OCR of PDFs and images. It supports public URL input or private file uploads via Google Drive and Mistral signed URLs, offering document parsing, text extraction, and document question answering capabilities.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jyg3BQhDpd8658ORprpQqC8Effgx1MWS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1324" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1325</div></th><td class="s6">HIBP New Breach Alert Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of new data breaches from HaveIBeenPwned API every 15 minutes. Caches last breach info locally, compares for new incidents, and triggers alerts for new breaches. Built with n8n using HTTP Request, file operations, and conditional logic nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oWnUmNMpzAbjZOwkA_0phXWdReuTuQfO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1325" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1326</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Email Categorizer &amp; Responder</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates email handling by triggering on new Gmail messages, classifying them using Google Gemini NLP, and sending tailored responses (guest posts, YouTube inquiries, courses) via SMTP. Contacts are updated in Brevo. Tech used: Gmail API, Google Gemini, SMTP, Brevo API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11QsBvYfHqShnVOztc_dOIQKbjR3gHUp4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1326" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1327</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Customers to Google Sheets Exporter</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching Shopify customers via Shopify API, handles pagination, and appends/upserts customer data (email, first name, last name, ID) to a Google Sheets document. Uses n8n with Shopify API, Google Sheets OAuth2, JavaScript for pagination parsing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kJNNjGpOyOVKe09jfGXiCHsgso0lSLBF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1327" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1328</div></th><td class="s6">Dropbox Folder Watch &amp; New File Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that monitors specified Dropbox folders using Dropbox webhooks and API, filters new files against a NocoDB database to exclude known files, and triggers subworkflows for new files processing. Uses Dropbox API, NocoDB, and n8n automation platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fJBAGFizeMONNJkd63TAonEezFsKi3ms">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1328" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1329</div></th><td class="s6">Webpage Change Monitor &amp; Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of webpage content changes using n8n&#39;s HTTP Request, HTML extraction, Crypto hashing, Google Drive &amp; Sheets APIs, and Gmail. Tracks changes via hashes, logs updates, saves snapshots, and sends email alerts for updated webpages.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1znDyMYL6dzaX8iOcsj-2VMBgmBHvqFC5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1329" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1330</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail PDF Invoice Classifier &amp; Drive Uploader</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow using Gmail, Google Drive, and OpenAI GPT-4.1-mini to scan emails for PDF invoices/receipts, classify via AI, upload matched PDFs to Drive folders by date, and optionally email them. Customizable with token limits and search terms.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yPuNiJLexYW2lCmvbHGSm1C4qqRvXkiN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1330" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1331</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Arabic Kids Story Creator</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates creating, translating, and sharing kids&#39; stories in Arabic using OpenAI GPT-4 Turbo for story generation and translation, DALL·E for image creation, audio generation, and Telegram for distribution. It fosters educational storytelling with visual and audio content.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19yaaRzWj9bm1lvUzTKtDXpis5W4sAIHy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1331" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1332</div></th><td class="s6">Personal Resume AI Chatbot with Google Gemini</td><td class="s7">An AI chatbot that answers questions about a personal resume/CV using Google Gemini (PaLM) for embeddings and chat, Pinecone vector DB for data storage, Google Drive for document triggering, and NocoDB for conversation logging. Sends daily email summaries via Gmail.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10_8ggQJOCsQkexUaho-JAg0nQKGa9Oo8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1332" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1333</div></th><td class="s6">Umami Analytics SEO Insights Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching website traffic stats from Umami analytics API, uses Openrouter AI to generate SEO summaries &amp; improvement suggestions, and stores results in Baserow database. Integrates Umami, Openrouter AI, and Baserow in n8n for weekly reporting and analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WP69oD-444HAhQrNCsLbT9z0vfwTn_Cx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1333" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1334</div></th><td class="s6">AI Chatbot for Kadampa Book Q&amp;A</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads an EPUB of a Kadampa Buddhist book from Google Drive, processes it with LangChain loaders and OpenAI embeddings, stores data in Supabase vector DB, and provides a chatbot for Q&amp;A using OpenAI&#39;s chat model and vector retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11_ClLJORTwl5tX5xom_z-0UgPfMWQPWT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1334" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1335</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered HR CV Processing &amp; Evaluation</td><td class="s7">Automates HR recruitment by extracting candidate info from PDF CVs via LangChain AI, evaluating fit against job criteria, and storing results in Google Sheets. Uses n8n workflow, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, Google Drive, and Sheets APIs for streamlined candidate management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TVNVOp8QMBlLClqp8oQo7GKMCuhzY9Lk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1335" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1336</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered A/B Split Testing Chatbot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that implements A/B split testing for chatbot prompts using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini model, Supabase for session management, and Postgres for chat memory. Enables testing of different prompt variants for chat sessions to optimize AI responses.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1neCRbt9TeXx34zHj6i15naOlsUnEA7-r">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1336" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1337</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chatbot with Voice &amp; Text</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram API, OpenAI GPT-4o, and LangChain to build a multi-format chatbot. It handles text and voice messages, transcribing audio via OpenAI, maintaining conversation memory, and replying with rich HTML formatting on Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1j7POm-Vz8I_-XyPIdCqNWdoi4s9vLTcN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1337" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1338</div></th><td class="s6">NeurochainAI Telegram Bot Integration</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that integrates Telegram bot messages with NeurochainAI&#39;s REST API. It processes user prompts via Telegram, sends them to NeurochainAI for text or image generation (using models like Meta-Llama and Flux), then returns AI-generated responses or images to the user on Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IdH5H1BUGx1j61H9rg7mLwoUUbSOhqGF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1338" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1339</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram AI Chatbot with Image Generation</td><td class="s7">An automated Telegram bot leveraging n8n workflows, OpenAI GPT-4 for chatbot replies, and DALL·E for image creation. It supports multi-language chat, welcome messages, text-to-image commands, and error handling for unsupported commands.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1M5FVgOdJdMeR4P7hRJd_KlRzqz3jspMw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1339" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1340</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram PDF RAG Chatbot with Pinecone</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates processing PDFs sent via Telegram by extracting, chunking, embedding with OpenAI, and storing in Pinecone vector DB. Enables retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) chat using Groq LLaMA-3.1-70b model for precise answers from uploaded documents.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NBN84WE_1w9_apo7ZpbSLDoievApb6Gi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1340" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1341</div></th><td class="s6">Text Automation via Apple Shortcuts &amp; OpenAI</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Apple Shortcuts with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini models to automate text tasks: translate (English/Spanish), grammar correction, and text length adjustments. Sends text via webhook, processes through OpenAI, responds to Shortcut for in-app editing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BrXAbQcXSEi8W__G6ATIqw6lLXuLFTj6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1341" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1342</div></th><td class="s6">Company Data Enrichment with OpenAI &amp; Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Workflow enriches company data from Google Sheets using ScrapingBee for homepage scraping and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini for extracting business insights. It updates sheets with company business areas, offers, models, and ideal customer profiles automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B8ru2DvCRKfUboU3lGp6T7fwK0Kji6-O">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1342" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1343</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Release Updates to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of GitHub repo releases using RSS feeds, caches release IDs in Redis, processes release notes with Google Gemini AI to extract and translate key info to Chinese, and posts formatted updates to Slack channels with error notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dcRJ528x38Q8JVHHZdyqDThX9b3nQtvZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1343" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1344</div></th><td class="s6">Amazon Product Price Tracker</td><td class="s7">Automates tracking Amazon product prices using ScrapeOps API, logging data to Google Sheets, calculating price changes, and sending alert emails when prices cross thresholds. Utilizes n8n workflow with Google Sheets, ScrapeOps HTTP API, and SMTP email integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rZqo5RqYqvjdz-SjSaOCAuwnhdW9LrhV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1344" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1345</div></th><td class="s6">Bank Statement OCR to Data Extraction</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of deposit data from bank statements by converting PDFs to images, then transcribing pages to markdown with Google Gemini VLM, finally extracting structured data. Uses Google Drive API, Stirling PDF API, and n8n nodes for PDF/image processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17eS8fneMny0u6B2GVjg44r-PUfYm05wR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1345" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1346</div></th><td class="s6">French-To-English Audio Translator</td><td class="s7">Automates French text-to-speech with ElevenLabs, transcribes speech via OpenAI Whisper, translates text using OpenAI GPT, and generates English speech again with ElevenLabs. Useful for multilingual audio content creation and language learning.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ToHm3AMLu1w3GzGlynLXWuh9BHZ5nEix">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1346" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1347</div></th><td class="s6">Airtop AI Web Automation Agent</td><td class="s7">An intelligent n8n workflow integrating Airtop browser tooling and Anthropic Claude 3.5 AI to automate complex web browsing tasks. It uses Langchain AI Agent to query, click, type, load URLs and manage browser sessions, enabling natural language driven web interaction and data extraction.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dUcerA8s8hj78UMPtKjqrsvQ9mS-HWPR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1347" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1348</div></th><td class="s6">Indeed Company Data Scraper &amp; AI Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping company profiles from Indeed using Bright Data Web Unlocker, extracts and converts markdown data, then summarizes with Google Gemini AI models. Integrates Airtable for URL input and webhook notifications for processed summaries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bQeAvs7qXKjhI_JnqVjlSYLYcDBShg3y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1348" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1349</div></th><td class="s6">Trustpilot Review Scraper &amp; Sentiment Analyzer</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping Trustpilot reviews using DeepSeek API, extracts detailed review info, analyzes sentiment via OpenAI, and stores results on Google Sheets for easy tracking and analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mFAF3gN6l9MkHnbqQkt_m9nTvhYxHQeS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1349" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1350</div></th><td class="s6">TOTP Code Generator in n8n</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow demonstrates generating Time-based One-Time Passwords (TOTP) using the n8n TOTP node with a configured TOTP account credential. It includes a manual trigger node to test the workflow and is ideal for implementing 2FA code generation within automation processes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1o1CJq_AGCm6D9lMVnXP-PNOO6uEZW6R9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1350" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1351</div></th><td class="s6">Bitwarden Group &amp; Member Management</td><td class="s7">Automates Bitwarden password manager group creation, lists all members, updates group members, and retrieves group members. Uses Bitwarden API via n8n nodes. Ideal for managing Bitwarden user groups programmatically and synchronizing member access.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pdte6f1SAjYBTpwEadiZ_LMYQARVCQHk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1351" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1352</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter New Tweets to Airtable</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching the latest tweets about &#39;verstappen&#39; using Twitter API and appends only new tweets to Airtable database. Uses n8n with Twitter and Airtable nodes to filter out duplicates and update records seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ghe2O194WvdrmDzBg5y2AR7xtCwQS_CM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1352" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1353</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Weather SMS Alert via Plivo</td><td class="s7">Automates sending daily SMS weather updates for Berlin at 9 AM using OpenWeatherMap API for temperature data and Plivo API for messaging, orchestrated by n8n&#39;s Cron node for scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-Od3iT6vQ6J-8h3eCmLxrLyQk-WcLZsn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1353" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1354</div></th><td class="s6">Todoist Task Categorizer with AI Priority Update</td><td class="s7">Automates categorizing Todoist inbox tasks into projects using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini, then updates their priority in Todoist accordingly. Uses n8n workflow with Todoist and OpenAI APIs, scheduled trigger, and filters to streamline task management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1acLoMH16f7ujBsp0XWUPnDG9wBlSTz8A">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1354" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1355</div></th><td class="s6">Copper CRM Person Create-Update-Get Flow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates Copper CRM interactions by creating a person with email, updating phone number, then retrieving the person data, using Copper API and manual trigger node for streamlined CRM data management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ilvc5DMJRkHJGlXE0VuIBCtnAvl3VrWC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1355" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1356</div></th><td class="s6">Email Existence Verification Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that verifies if an email address exists using Uproc&#39;s checkEmailExists API. It triggers manually, creates the email item, checks its deliverability status, and branches accordingly. Useful for validating emails in automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TSZ-eIF-8jfOBozBCjkUk8ZNLILlVGj9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1356" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1357</div></th><td class="s6">Webflow CMS Item Create &amp; Update Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating creation and update of CMS items in Webflow using Webflow API. It triggers manually, creates a new item, then updates it with additional fields including an avatar URL, ensuring content management automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WdL4TJMwTUvit03BKKlwsZvmpIEgaWik">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1357" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1358</div></th><td class="s6">IP-Based Location Email Sender</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow using Uproc API to get geographic location from IP, then sends a customized welcome email in Spanish or English via AWS SES based on user country (Spain or not). Automates localized email outreach using IP geolocation and email automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1107a2ScuGEsC0b_PGgqrWUUvWcASLCPL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1358" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1359</div></th><td class="s6">Clearbit Email Person Lookup</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Clearbit API to fetch and enrich person details by email input. It triggers manually and retrieves person data like name, job, and company using Clearbit&#39;s person resource for streamlined data enrichment.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XiB1cbCQ-GrhJLlPTgfPQ-OX3hk8R3uy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1359" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1360</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable Email Validation Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches email records from Airtable, validates them using Mailcheck API to check MX record existence, and updates Airtable records with validation results. Tech stack includes Airtable API and Mailcheck API integration for data integrity.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iEh8J3A8qC2UsaCCe05MaTe0rRUsekMS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1360" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1361</div></th><td class="s6">Orbit Member Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates creating and updating members in Orbit using its API. It adds notes and posts linked to members in a workspace. The workflow triggers manually and sequentially manages member data, notes, and posts via Orbit API within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oAvFPe7Swxxc65UyiEnaSHZbs_XytRyO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1361" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1362</div></th><td class="s6">ClickUp Task Creator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to automate task creation in ClickUp using ClickUp API. Trigger tasks manually and create tasks in specified ClickUp spaces, folders, and lists. Useful for streamlining project management with no-code automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ebeFKHpXoQtUrWcSqYAqsW3o0AmgnVaK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1362" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1363</div></th><td class="s6">ISS Position Publisher via MQTT</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching the current ISS location every minute using the WhereTheISS.at API and publishes latitude, longitude, and timestamp data to an MQTT topic for real-time tracking. Built with n8n, integrating Cron, HTTP Request, Set, and MQTT nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Mry9h5VK0UnpqTx9mwYqrKjs6qw_drDy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1363" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1364</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Attachment to Google Drive Link</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieving Gmail messages with a specific label, uploads their attachments to Google Drive, and outputs the file link. Uses Gmail and Google Drive APIs within n8n workflow to streamline attachment management and sharing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CxvVNtPWXTOkZxegXLDNs4HkQDfoaSvS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1364" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1365</div></th><td class="s6">Add a Book Volume to Google Bookshelf</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses Google Books API with OAuth2 to fetch a specific book volume by ID and add it to a chosen Google Bookshelf. It automates managing your digital library inside Google Books, simplifying book collection updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14aUxBucYz1hpUfTToJpQW6LofxVh0R1q">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1365" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1366</div></th><td class="s6">Email Invite with iCalendar Attachment</td><td class="s7">Automates sending an email with an iCalendar event invite using n8n. Utilizes n8n manual trigger, iCal node for calendar event creation, and SMTP email node (Outlook). Ideal for sending event invites with calendar attachments.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15aJaF1OXJOPIruJW-Ig47cLrphWUZivE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1366" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1367</div></th><td class="s6">Notion to Mattermost Meeting Alerts</td><td class="s7">Automates notifications in Mattermost when new meeting notes are added to a Notion database for the Marketing team. Uses Notion Trigger node to monitor Notion API, applies conditional logic, then sends formatted messages via Mattermost API to alert team members.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LtPiJL0g3K-7UpG2g3_QJHyH4k5xpxLv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1367" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1368</div></th><td class="s6">Chargebee Event Updates Receiver</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using the Chargebee Trigger node to listen for all Chargebee subscription and billing events in real-time, enabling automated processing and integration with other systems.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zJC1Tkx6bcxks7YyfIg6hZwC5yXxFthu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1368" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1369</div></th><td class="s6">Calendly to Notion Personality Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates the creation of Notion database pages with personality insights by triggering on new Calendly invitees, querying Humantic AI for detailed personality analysis, and storing results in Notion. Uses Calendly webhook, Humantic AI API, and Notion API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KGbAH6UIUZYXl7EIFM6iMuCTPTxXM3v6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1369" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1370</div></th><td class="s6">SSL Certificate Expiry Notifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that checks the SSL certificate validity of a specified domain (default: n8n.io) using the Uproc API and sends an alert to a Telegram chat if the certificate has expired. Integrates manual trigger, function item, Uproc and Telegram nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BqSQID9Oot3TN9M4KdOhC9EOEcsW_Zfm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1370" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1371</div></th><td class="s6">ClickUp Event Updates Receiver</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using the ClickUp Trigger node to receive real-time updates for all events in a ClickUp workspace. Integrates with ClickUp&#39;s API to automate task and project monitoring efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HYTEpMMLpQmalVcsIW-b1hBMiyAaFXbN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1371" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1372</div></th><td class="s6">URL to Notion Link Logger</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses Webhook, HTTP Request, HTML Extract, and Notion API to capture URLs, fetch page titles, and add them as entries into a Notion database. It includes Discord reply confirmation. Automates link organization with webpage title retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18qDjmxXvPTqoCJhw8At5G5n4Q9dkB-qK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1372" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1373</div></th><td class="s6">UptimeRobot Monitor Create-Update-Get</td><td class="s7">Workflow using UptimeRobot API in n8n to create a monitor for n8n.io, update its friendly name, and retrieve monitor details. Ideal for website uptime tracking automation with UptimeRobot API credentials.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17koeaCVD_2x2ZSuBab39tm2WaZ5cTT5p">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1373" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1374</div></th><td class="s6">Microsoft To Do Task Automator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation and status update of tasks in Microsoft To Do using n8n workflow with manual trigger and Microsoft OAuth API integration. Simplifies task management by creating, updating to &#39;inProgress&#39;, and retrieving tasks seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1DwSrkqB5EWFN75u13gtOpR2bj_FhR2AZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1374" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1375</div></th><td class="s6">Get and Update Contacts from GetResponse</td><td class="s7">Workflow to fetch all contacts from GetResponse using its API, check their campaign association, and update the campaign ID if it differs. Built in n8n automation platform, it uses manual triggers, GetResponse API integration, conditional logic, and updates contacts accordingly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XM9LA2ywGX2DrV_gE1PniW3RAcpOiQft">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1375" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1376</div></th><td class="s6">Syncro to OpsGenie Alert Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates alert creation and closure in OpsGenie from Syncro MSP by receiving webhook notifications. Utilizes Syncro webhooks and OpsGenie API with HTTP Request nodes for real-time incident management and status synchronization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pGMcZ5BmZzcON1PyVDKMjRsJd5X0KCw4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1376" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1377</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Product Launch Social Broadcaster</td><td class="s7">Automates social media announcements for new Shopify products by posting customizable messages to Twitter and Telegram using Shopify Trigger, Twitter API, and Telegram API integration in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VAz5D-OHXBQA8VffLlVvxFIpQkLR4bXT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1377" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1378</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Toxic Language Filter</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow monitors Telegram messages and uses Google Perspective API to detect toxic language (profanity, identity attack, threat). Offending messages trigger an automatic Telegram reply warning users. Integrates Telegram API and Google Perspective API for real-time content moderation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-4L5-uYTmNdaxdN0P-YIGnet-OwUR3b7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1378" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1379</div></th><td class="s6">Steam Phishing Domain Reporter</td><td class="s7">Automates detection and reporting of Steam phishing domains via webhook. Uses DNS dig commands to validate domain and Cloudflare nameservers, then sends alert emails via Mailgun API to Steam and Cloudflare security teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10wB5tGBQEMXtaV0MWr0iwFl2PSxNl9vE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1379" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1380</div></th><td class="s6">Segment Event Tracking Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to track custom events in Segment using the Segment API. It triggers manually and sends event data to Segment&#39;s tracking endpoint, enabling user behavior data collection for analytics and marketing automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nwhaoW44CPvlMJEG0gaHXWXJnGheAQFq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1380" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1381</div></th><td class="s6">API Rate Limiter with Airtable Data Fetch</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow implements an API rate limiting system using Redis for per-minute and per-hour limits with secured webhook authentication. It fetches Pokemon data from Airtable and returns it if limits are not exceeded, ensuring controlled API usage and data delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LBnjyofNTsGoTBB1aJhrksSXGbC_VpxV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1381" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1382</div></th><td class="s6">AWS Textract Invoice OCR Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates OCR extraction of invoice data from an image stored in AWS S3 using AWS Textract API. Triggered manually in n8n, processes &#39;Rechnung.jpg&#39; from &#39;textract-demodata&#39; bucket to extract text for further workflows, leveraging AWS cloud services.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BeSaLyhZaqi8KEP_5gNmMte_4OFb-Pfl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1382" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1383</div></th><td class="s6">Slack Error Notification Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on any error event and sends a formatted alert to a specified Slack channel using the Slack API. It helps teams quickly identify failed workflow executions with direct links for troubleshooting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QjFid9jrkKCpJOZTCoi0CT0jQCBjqJcw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1383" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1384</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice Email to Nextcloud Uploader</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching invoices from an IMAP &#39;Invoices&#39; email folder, processes each attachment by sanitizing filenames, and uploads them to dated folders in Nextcloud. Utilizes IMAP Email node, custom JavaScript for filename sanitization, and Nextcloud API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BIPg9hOGcg-_m4u5VctiTCRigE9KPeyq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1384" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1385</div></th><td class="s6">GitLab Issue for New GitHub Release</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly checks of the latest GitHub release of a repo and creates a new GitLab issue if no corresponding issue exists. Uses n8n with GitHub API (releases), GitLab API (issues), and cron scheduler to sync release tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YnClmR2nSOkPwv5X59qcD6m0iEQ-1c-w">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1385" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1386</div></th><td class="s6">ISS Position Tracker to Firebase DB</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches the International Space Station&#39;s geolocation every minute using WhereTheISS.at API, then saves latitude, longitude, and timestamp data to Google Firebase Realtime Database. Automates real-time ISS tracking and storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-sdNbiWtLTggyFqUIJ8xRyrgUr9dTB47">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1386" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1387</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Followers Banner Updater</td><td class="s7">Automates updating Twitter profile banner with latest followers&#39; avatars. Uses Twitter API v2 to fetch followers, downloads and edits avatars and a background image, composites them, and updates banner via Twitter API v1.1 with OAuth1.0 authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=156qKH3GH8ZRqioBhZtPgDtEhb_hzlRZe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1387" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1388</div></th><td class="s6">Product Label Generator with DB &amp; API Integration</td><td class="s7">Automates product label creation by integrating n8n webhook, MySQL and PostgreSQL databases, and a local HTTP API for print configuration. Retrieves detailed product, fabric roll, and composition data to generate comprehensive labels for inventory management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1h9rF9Yd4ShqjbdQnyck3_QNOUvWESOY2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1388" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1389</div></th><td class="s6">Automated MySQL Cleanup with Telegram Alerts</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates the cleanup of old package records from two MySQL databases at 8 AM daily using Cron, then sends Telegram notifications to specific chats. It leverages MySQL, Cron, Telegram API, and a webhook trigger for manual invocations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11rYh58iv8ehUaZ_lCCKPedZDgDRb-Cxe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1389" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1390</div></th><td class="s6">User Signup &amp; Notion Semester Tracker</td><td class="s7">Automates user signup via a secure HTTP webhook, extracts user name and email, checks existence in Notion database, creates new user if absent, and updates their associated semester info. Uses n8n with Notion API and basic auth for secure, streamlined academic user management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-KIYVmGGl3aTHwjyRYSg0zKEyDrFGtdA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1390" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1391</div></th><td class="s6">GitLab Release to Outline Document</td><td class="s7">Automates creating published documents in Outline from GitLab release tag pushes. Uses GitLab Trigger node for tag_push events, IF node to filter release events, and HTTP Request node to call Outline API to create release notes automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tIMWK620Fx8JZnGJQpQ2pANSKhGMfBG7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1391" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1392</div></th><td class="s6">Mautic Form Submission SMS Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates sending SMS confirmations via Twilio when a form is submitted in Mautic. Uses Mautic API for form trigger and Twilio API to send personalized SMS notifications, ideal for webinar sign-ups or lead confirmations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15hX4ZZ8GWmGt985uETh0lVLw-9u8fk6r">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1392" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1393</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Weather Push Notifications with Spontit</td><td class="s7">Automates daily weather updates for Berlin using OpenWeatherMap API and sends them as push notifications via Spontit. Scheduled with n8n Cron node for daily delivery at 9 AM, ideal for keeping users informed about temperature changes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19GVOxnR1YA_bY8y7xNoBrqDXQRe5Jume">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1393" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1394</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot New Company Domain Validator &amp; Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of new HubSpot companies by validating their website domains via HTTP request. Suspicious or unreachable domains trigger alerts posted to Slack. Integrates HubSpot API for company data and Slack API for real-time notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1C6K4OrHz_zyt_OuJkON4WoZfAUkvqiWs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1394" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1395</div></th><td class="s6">News Change Alert via Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of Hacker News front page by fetching the page every 5 minutes, comparing the content, and sending a Telegram alert if changes are detected. Uses HTTP Request nodes, Cron trigger, Wait node, IF condition, and Telegram API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nIiSjTGSVYhTHL-LpqB4pNiVWtm7YDHO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1395" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1396</div></th><td class="s6">SyncroMSP Call Timer Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates call duration logging to SyncroMSP by syncing webhook call data with Google Sheets to find matching tickets, then adds timer entries via SyncroMSP API. Uses n8n, Google Sheets API, webhooks, and HTTP requests for efficient call tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SU8BFOZSd5dX2LVDLfMo7ov8FgFVXujc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1396" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1397</div></th><td class="s6">Strava Activity Reminder &amp; Encouragement</td><td class="s7">Automates daily activity checks using Strava API to track moving time. If activity is below threshold, sends encouragement emails to accountability partners via SMTP. Built with n8n, integrates Strava OAuth2 and email sending.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16aLlfwfWEJZ4JBpbIS-goZC8ccSkOqWe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1397" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1398</div></th><td class="s6">Add Subscriber and Send Email Campaign</td><td class="s7">Automates adding an email subscriber to a Sendy list and sends a welcome email campaign using Sendy API triggered manually in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rDAD00dcc0C_fV3YhgO95mO5M_evC-Pd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1398" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1399</div></th><td class="s6">Onfleet Driver Signup Slack Notification</td><td class="s7">Automates notifications to Slack when a new driver signs up in Onfleet. Uses Onfleet API trigger to detect new driver creation and Slack API to send messages to a specific channel, enhancing team awareness instantly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ysNgJ2_2b1RCMG-CRkcFKyGzE5hbVBNB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1399" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1400</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable to Mattermost Notification</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates notifications by triggering on new data entries in Airtable and sending formatted messages to a Mattermost channel. It integrates Airtable API and Mattermost API for real-time alerts, facilitating team collaboration and data monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13Agnsrbd722dXnxgyk7zjbozM4CyVr83">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1400" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1401</div></th><td class="s6">Download Image and Post to Slack</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads an image file from a specified URL using HTTP Request and then posts it to a designated Slack channel via Slack&#39;s API with OAuth2 authentication. Automates file sharing seamlessly between web and Slack.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17aNqPu10YFho6pN6HELzRgOL7mcE7m49">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1401" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1402</div></th><td class="s6">PagerDuty Incident Create, Update, and Retrieve</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating PagerDuty incident management with create, update, and get operations. Uses PagerDuty API via n8n nodes to streamline incident lifecycle management triggered manually.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1h7u4CIzsbiGvEqjxdjjkOClFMr_tQk2f">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1402" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1403</div></th><td class="s6">City Weather Info via OpenWeatherMap API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that receives a city name via webhook and fetches current weather data using the OpenWeatherMap API. It extracts temperature and weather description to return concise weather info dynamically. Tech stack: n8n, Webhook, OpenWeatherMap API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xyObtn1Ya7rCQsF8KE_4Xev4RwbO85iG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1403" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1404</div></th><td class="s6">URL Job Analysis with Cortex API</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow triggers manually to analyze a URL using Cortex&#39;s Abuse Finder analyzer and retrieves detailed job results. It integrates n8n with the Cortex API to automate URL threat detection and forensic job data collection.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FaVehqklfwZB-WH0rjKiFaTmPinLBIJR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1404" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1405</div></th><td class="s6">TheHive Event Update Notifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using TheHive Trigger node to receive real-time updates for any event occurring in TheHive security incident response platform. Enables automation based on security event notifications via webhooks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1siOX_F5Vn6d5Ml8D4Muf022Xe_7GOqKK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1405" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1406</div></th><td class="s6">Iterable User Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating with Iterable API to create, update, and retrieve user data by email. It automates user profile management in Iterable marketing platform using n8n&#39;s Iterable nodes triggered manually.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GhpZDLUQkn605hq6u-RzNeWsZOxAdE3a">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1406" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1407</div></th><td class="s6">Kafka Temperature Alert via SMS</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that listens to a Kafka topic for temperature readings, checks if the temperature exceeds 50, and sends an alert SMS via Vonage API. Integrates Kafka, conditional logic, and Vonage SMS for real-time temperature monitoring alerts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1z5WM_e3pDB93TBu4Qnujkatu0RuARfpc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1407" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1408</div></th><td class="s6">Shorten URL &amp; Fetch URL Stats with YOURLS</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to create short URLs using YOURLS API and retrieve their statistics. It uses n8n&#39;s manual trigger and YOURLS nodes to automate URL shortening and stats fetching, ideal for tracking short link performance.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CraSPAVesKJaNgzN6n0P_X92OZk9K1g1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1408" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1409</div></th><td class="s6">Factory IoT Data Generator with AMQP</td><td class="s7">Generates synthetic smart factory data including machine ID, temperature, uptime, and timestamp at regular intervals using n8n. Sends data via AMQP to a specified queue for IoT or monitoring integrations. Tech: n8n workflow, JavaScript, AMQP protocol.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rQpfF7XRN_BdbzvS4_0HzCX45uAFtyhm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1409" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1410</div></th><td class="s6">Manage Ghost Posts via Admin API</td><td class="s7">Automates creating, updating, and fetching posts on Ghost CMS using n8n. Utilizes Ghost Admin API and n8n&#39;s Ghost node to streamline content management workflows with manual trigger initiation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CruNQPFDKvY7X5rmIqE9-EbmoPOCrj1B">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1410" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1411</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable Data Insert and Update Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Airtable API to append, list with filter, and update records in an Airtable base. It automates managing data rows programmatically via manual trigger, ideal for streamlined data syncing and updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1waLbGiEuX6p2-CEOskuks1Ar7KgBPqWQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1411" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1412</div></th><td class="s6">Snowflake Table Create &amp; Upsert Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of a Snowflake table and performs insert and update operations using n8n with Snowflake API integration. Ideal for managing and updating data programmatically with no manual SQL needed.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1brpwmrXPCTnIuyh-9PS5UvAdAw7eyEHZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1412" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1413</div></th><td class="s6">Random User Data to Google Sheets &amp; CSV</td><td class="s7">Fetches random user data via the RandomUser API, extracts name and country, then appends it to a Google Sheets spreadsheet using OAuth2 authentication and also exports the data as a CSV file. Utilizes HTTP Request, Google Sheets, and Spreadsheet File nodes in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NNx6kfhrMHDxjnZNOMgz1QOHhVNxzxmt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1413" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1414</div></th><td class="s6">Random User Data to Sheets &amp; Email</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching random user data from randomuser.me API, formats it, appends to Google Sheets via OAuth2, converts data to CSV and JSON files, saves locally, and emails JSON file using Gmail API. Integrates HTTP Request, Google Sheets, File, and Gmail nodes in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZDzESKVsHNr9rM8FEiPeZsaGVIsq8mtY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1414" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1415</div></th><td class="s6">Automate Twist Channel Creation &amp; Messaging</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow using Twist API to create and update channels, add users, and send custom messages with action buttons linking to docs. Integrates Twist OAuth2 for secure access to workspace, streamlining team communications and onboarding.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eRQmxw4wIN0tH3FbXVAiWsK6lwJ1jSko">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1415" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1416</div></th><td class="s6">Customer Data Filtering &amp; Branching Demo</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating conditional filtering and routing of customer data from a custom datastore using If and Switch nodes. Highlights multi-condition logic with AND/OR combos and branching by country (US, CO, UK, others). Ideal for learning data-driven workflow branching.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Dt0sxtqsPCBiS0ob-9FxwP4JN1Uz63RT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1416" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1417</div></th><td class="s6">Customer Messaging Approval Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating batch message sending with rate limiting, waits for external approval via webhook, and simulates sending approval URLs to merchants. Uses n8n core nodes, custom Customer Datastore &amp; Messenger, wait, splitInBatches, and webhook nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nycQH9XOOrERgLt4-wRFridPdwLPXgpm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1417" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1418</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly MySQL to Google Sheets Export</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly data export from a MySQL database to Google Sheets using n8n. Triggers every week at 5am, queries all records from &#39;books&#39; table, and appends them to a specified Google Sheet via OAuth2 authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LikSIcNsQI6-oi8ztAlhr7sd76zEvfuY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1418" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1419</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets Row Processing Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that reads rows from a Google Sheets document every 5 minutes, checks if rows are unprocessed, executes actions on new data, marks them processed with timestamps. Utilizes Google Sheets API with OAuth2 for automatic data management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mo0gROCTGGUfgc53a7B7T3eYdmu7frF-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1419" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1420</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to HTML Exporter</td><td class="s7">Automates exporting data from Google Sheets to an HTML file using n8n workflow. Utilizes Google Sheets API via OAuth2 credentials and n8n&#39;s spreadsheet file node to convert sheet data into an HTML document triggered by a webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-ZXZV-5S6JLv87VQWEpnr_yDYYdafKSx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1420" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1421</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Label Manage: Fetch, Remove, Add</td><td class="s7">Automates Gmail email management by fetching messages with a specific label, removing that label, and applying a new one using Gmail API via OAuth2 in n8n workflow. Ideal for organizing emails automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oMUipHRDgjvEKlFt8fc0Hn-P_Ot9dxte">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1421" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1422</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Fork Leads to Pipedrive Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates lead creation in Pipedrive CRM from GitHub fork events using GitHub API and Pipedrive API. Detects fork, retrieves user info, checks/creates person in Pipedrive, creates lead and note linking GitHub URL. Tech stack: n8n, GitHub Trigger, HTTP Request, Pipedrive nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vhEutRibSPzqFXGub2Gz44XxGbQpup-K">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1422" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1423</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub PR to Pipedrive Note Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates adding notes to Pipedrive persons when a GitHub pull request is created. Uses GitHub webhook trigger, HTTP request to GitHub API, and Pipedrive API. Checks PR sender email in Pipedrive, adds PR URL as a note if person exists.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KsgDfCRGOnlYrQDNrKEMl6nlSsGUyiVV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1423" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1424</div></th><td class="s6">Mattermost Channel Setup and Welcome Message</td><td class="s7">Automates Mattermost by creating a new channel, adding a specific member, and posting a welcome message using Mattermost API within n8n workflow. Ideal for onboarding and team collaboration setup.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mTHwYpu7Qd0dq9nSWctj97xPclH4FM7X">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1424" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1425</div></th><td class="s6">Customer Data Invoice &amp; Email Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching customer data, sorting, generating invoices and customer lists using n8n, a custom Customer Datastore API, Document Generator for templates, and SMTP for email delivery. Enables sending individual invoice emails and summarized new customer report emails.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rTccaAMlfNvRpPpu-9c81X560O7iwVbp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1425" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1426</div></th><td class="s6">JSON to Google Sheets Append</td><td class="s7">Automates reading a local JSON file and appending its data to a Google Sheets spreadsheet using OAuth2 authentication. Utilizes n8n&#39;s Read Binary File, Move Binary Data, and Google Sheets nodes to streamline data synchronization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eaN2JUkh7bVfGnSOnptDiFsr0pg6ILCu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1426" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1427</div></th><td class="s6">Podcast RSS Feed Generator from Web Episodes</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that scrapes podcast episode data from ardaudiothek.de, parses JSON metadata from episode pages, and generates a valid RSS feed. Utilizes HTTP Requests, HTML extraction, JSON parsing, and custom JS code to create podcast RSS XML feeds dynamically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IG9ksLoFI92c0Ty93ROHa2esR84sTWoF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1427" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1428</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform to NextCloud Spreadsheet Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates data flow from Typeform submissions to NextCloud-stored Excel files. Uses Typeform Trigger to capture form responses, merges with existing spreadsheet data from NextCloud, updates the file, and uploads it back to NextCloud.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rVnKyTLWNnEoK-7qEpXwv4Pyy1FDeQvU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1428" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1429</div></th><td class="s6">Google Drive to Notion File Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates logging of newly uploaded Google Drive files to a Notion database. Uses Google Drive API trigger to detect file uploads in a specific folder and Notion API to create database entries with file details and links. Ideal for file management and tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tOH9LjN8m0CRC9-c9QscKMsf3lr_mhsf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1429" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1430</div></th><td class="s6">Calendly to Mautic Contact Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates contact creation/update in Mautic when a new Calendly event is created using Calendly webhook and Mautic API integration. Keeps contact info up-to-date by syncing invitee email and first name upon scheduling events.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CUgop5rCk7Btoefy6rQ8i_ONZ-yNvtz9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1430" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1431</div></th><td class="s6">Clockify Invoice to Notion Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates logging of new Clockify invoices into a Notion database using Clockify webhook and Notion API. Captures invoice number, issue date, due date, and amount for centralized invoice tracking and management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tVmMwXvWaKB1dzaJy1_4Tr6WbrSryYA6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1431" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1432</div></th><td class="s6">Export MySQL Table to XLSX File</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to export data from a specified MySQL table into an XLSX spreadsheet file using MySQL and spreadsheet nodes. Triggered manually, it allows easy saving of SQL table data for sharing or backup.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=151lH2XlehXRLzjri94_U6eTfKj9qJhCM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1432" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1433</div></th><td class="s6">Manage e-goi Subscribers: Create, Update, Retrieve</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using the e-goi API to create, update, and fetch subscriber details. It automates subscriber management by chaining operations with manual trigger, utilizing e-goi&#39;s contact list API for email marketing and audience handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gzp6PJhYYGixin8UYku8Y9F8zjctlYze">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1433" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1434</div></th><td class="s6">Gender Inclusive Language Notifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that listens for messages containing gendered terms via a webhook and sends a Mattermost bot suggestion to use gender inclusive language alternatives like &quot;folks&quot; or &quot;y&#39;all&quot;. Uses n8n Webhook and Mattermost API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dmsCj-u-6uo3gDoOYcZ1gfzt4_Cgdg7G">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1434" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1435</div></th><td class="s6">Website Screenshot to Telegram Channel</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing a full-page website screenshot via uProc API and sends it as a photo to a specified Telegram channel using Telegram Bot API, triggered manually in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13OTPoyeWgy-4V928BCSgp_AKhqEnohiW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1435" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1436</div></th><td class="s6">Postgres to Google Sheets Lead Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing qualified lead data from a PostgreSQL database to Google Sheets, filtering out internal emails. Uses Postgres Trigger, Filter, and Google Sheets nodes in n8n to enable real-time or manual lead data export for easy tracking and contact management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IDGqlgwCEnG0LKwGQfZAiIQDViIgUWuU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1436" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1437</div></th><td class="s6">MySQL Products to XML File Exporter</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of 16 random product records from MySQL, formats data with or without XML attributes, converts to XML, and saves as files. Utilizes n8n with MySQL node, JSON to XML conversion, and file writing for easy product data export.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hoS7lCE1pWVwE-hWrIxoGJJOpikjgWGV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1437" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1438</div></th><td class="s6">Paul Graham Essays Scraper &amp; Summarizer</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that scrapes the latest essays from paulgraham.com, extracts titles and full texts, and summarizes them using OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini model with Langchain nodes. Automates content aggregation and summarization of Paul Graham&#39;s essays.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UgVk67xGa83LjfE5TnB0qZPFMUs9cTBt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1438" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1439</div></th><td class="s6">LangChain Q&amp;A with Workflow Content Retriever</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using LangChain integration with OpenAI (GPT-4o-mini) to perform question-answering on dynamically retrieved workflow data. It uses a manual trigger, a subworkflow retriever, and a set node to input queries, enabling smart Q&amp;A on saved workflow content.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xlyCfUpw4Xs6DVYV6Xaxpvwty1zdXx_f">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1439" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1440</div></th><td class="s6">Chatbot with Mistral-7B via Hugging Face</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on chat message input and generates polite, emoji-rich replies using an open-source Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.1 model via Hugging Face API. Utilizes LangChain nodes to manage LLM chaining for conversational AI.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yJc8qYyr4y6SL2XI9bZtqTOXVZnzJa7V">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1440" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1441</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Controlled N8N Workflow Activator</td><td class="s7">Automates activation/deactivation of n8n workflows via Telegram bot commands. Uses Telegram API for command input and n8n API for workflow control. Enables quick management of marketing and sales workflows remotely through &#39;/start&#39; and &#39;/stop&#39; commands.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13jYVl1VdhGsc4mYHWjCYjBrRPTbYSdg3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1441" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1442</div></th><td class="s6">Snowflake CSV Data Importer</td><td class="s7">Automates importing CSV data from an HTTP URL into a Snowflake database table. Uses n8n nodes: HTTP Request to fetch CSV, Spreadsheet File to parse, Set to map fields, and Snowflake node to insert data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ulnVa6qft3pHBypBScmNyyUsVf8Tw6hn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1442" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1443</div></th><td class="s6">TwentyCRM Event Notifications to Email &amp; Slack</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that receives event triggers from TwentyCRM via webhook, filters and logs event data to Google Sheets, and sends notifications to Gmail or Slack channels based on event type (e.g. deletion events emailed, others sent to Slack).</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Vf_c-Y4omLtuRqPPDIK_kfJ0MLK_RCIZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1443" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1444</div></th><td class="s6">Website Screenshot Capture with Bright Data</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to capture website screenshots using Bright Data&#39;s Web Unlocker API and save them locally. Utilizes HTTP requests with authenticated headers, proxy zone configuration, and file system write operations to automate web page capture.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15HNTbM0h2AZVn7ICyknPteTRTrRrLixt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1444" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1445</div></th><td class="s6">Email to Nextcloud Deck Card</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of Nextcloud Deck cards from emails using IMAP for email retrieval, JavaScript function to strip HTML, and Nextcloud Deck API via HTTP request for card creation. Ideal for task management workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mQodXuxByCfrhsopl9ENKRPkQgdIMRLs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1445" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1446</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Telegram Journal Reminder</td><td class="s7">Automates daily 6 AM journal prompts via Telegram by generating a reminder message with yesterday&#39;s date. Uses n8n Cron for scheduling, JavaScript function for message formatting, and Telegram API for notification delivery. Helps maintain consistent journaling habit.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CivwuUXeteIzDI3Q85td_x4yK61dY6op">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1446" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1447</div></th><td class="s6">Email XML Order Processing and API Submission</td><td class="s7">Automates order processing by reading emails via IMAP, extracting XML attachments, converting them to JSON, and sending data via HTTP POST to a sales order API. Uses n8n nodes: IMAP Email, XML, Set, HTTP Request, and Move Binary Data for seamless integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vIy79DLmugbOMwv-aFoxHxfaD7pL-m7b">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1447" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1448</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Email Sender with CSV and Image Attachments</td><td class="s7">Automates batch email sending using n8n with CSV parsing, batch processing, and SMTP email sending. Reads CSV data, processes in batches of 5, attaches personalized PNGs per recipient, and sends certificate emails via SMTP.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kkG_-gih7NUBLMXMTsMPuD0w0a8dmEFo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1448" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1449</div></th><td class="s6">Website Availability Monitor with Discord Alerts</td><td class="s7">An hourly website content monitor using n8n&#39;s HTTP Request node to check for specific text (&#39;Out Of Stock&#39;), conditionally triggering Discord notifications via webhook. Integrates Cron for scheduling, IF node for logic branching, and Discord nodes for alerting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tNUEDpC-lFNKhiH9VxftQqe0Q98R3fV4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1449" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1450</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress Posts to CSV Exporter</td><td class="s7">Automates exporting all WordPress posts using WordPress API, converts them to CSV via n8n spreadsheet node, and saves a local CSV file. Ideal for non-coders needing quick WordPress content exports as CSV files.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gorF3lwWHJAPprIP-iyYFh4X7P-LJK0v">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1450" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1451</div></th><td class="s6">Icypeas Real-Time Email Search Listener</td><td class="s7">Automates real-time retrieval of email search results from Icypeas via webhook, extracting emails and names. Uses n8n webhook and Set nodes to process data for integration with services like Lemlist. Ideal for bulk email/domain scans with instant notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nxGjK9dov5Y_ksWyfEVOMX6o9xsxibWO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1451" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1452</div></th><td class="s6">Phantombuster Data to Airtable Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieval of data from Phantombuster API and stores structured results (name, email, company) into Airtable. Utilizes n8n workflow with Phantombuster connector, manual trigger, data mapping, and Airtable API for seamless data capture and storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xGkLcv_JT9MyZn5E0eIjI_x5P6Z0gTG9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1452" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1453</div></th><td class="s6">Fastmail JMAP Unread Email Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating with Fastmail&#39;s JMAP API using HTTP requests and header auth to retrieve mailbox info and fetch the latest unread emails. Designed to automate email monitoring leveraging Fastmail&#39;s API and n8n&#39;s HTTP Request nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bw7FNJj32yRr3QnwSniV5jGNrIfhgdqr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1453" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1454</div></th><td class="s6">Azure DevOps PR to DingTalk Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates notifications on new Azure DevOps Pull Requests by sending customized DingTalk messages. Uses Azure DevOps webhook, MySQL for user mapping, and DingTalk&#39;s robot webhook API to notify correct users in group chats.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Pk4fPPK9hFjmW36bM7y5fNTM17T4-GwY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1454" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1455</div></th><td class="s6">Save URLs to Notion via Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses a POST webhook to capture URLs and automatically saves them as pages in a specified Notion bookmarks database, enabling easy bookmarking and organization. Tech stack: n8n, Notion API, Webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MaoWrS-65N2WF0wLpWjq8wq8KEF0TtKD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1455" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1456</div></th><td class="s6">Website Analytics to Airtable Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching Google Analytics data (sessions by country over a date range) and appends it into an Airtable base for easy tracking. Utilizes Google Analytics API, Airtable API, and n8n automation platform for seamless data integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14Xzgkd8oWm_cfTuhC4wcnY-xrAG-1Igf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1456" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1457</div></th><td class="s6">Monday.com Error Logging Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates error detection in n8n workflows by triggering on errors, extracting stack traces via JavaScript, and logging detailed error records into a specified Monday.com board with timestamps. Integrates n8n, Monday.com API, and custom code for workflow error management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=148yi_dcaCwYKXUCuwusqqk_WR53Oh1oN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1457" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1458</div></th><td class="s6">French to English Audio Translation Workflow</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow converts French text to spoken audio using ElevenLabs TTS, transcribes it with OpenAI Whisper, translates to English with GPT-4o-mini, and generates English speech via ElevenLabs. Integrates ElevenLabs TTS API and OpenAI APIs for a full audio translation cycle.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nfKC0NYbWP5M5I4yVwt4wkJkR6-6l966">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1458" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1459</div></th><td class="s6">AI Activity Suggestion Chatbot</td><td class="s7">An n8n AI agent workflow integrating OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Bored API to suggest personalized activity ideas based on user input on activity type and participants. Includes memory buffer for chat context and a sub-workflow for API calls.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fCrnI6oALgjIs0m9NqHCQPapw9gMH5_C">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1459" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1460</div></th><td class="s6">SendGrid Contact Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates creating, updating, and retrieving contacts using SendGrid API within n8n. Utilizes manual trigger, SendGrid node for contact resource operations including adding first and last names, and fetching contact by email. Ideal for managing email lists.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BSkBn7d4CryJi3ezbE8KfNfuG7xK93eV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1460" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1461</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Sync to Notion Database</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing of n8n workflows tagged &#39;sync-to-notion&#39; with a Notion database. Uses n8n API to fetch workflows every 15 mins, then queries and updates or adds corresponding pages in Notion via Notion API. Ideal for workflow management and monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nPfdys3INB1tG6btr-a-NpSay1JkiLfU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1461" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1462</div></th><td class="s6">G Suite Admin User Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automate creation, updating, and retrieval of G Suite users using the n8n G Suite Admin node with OAuth2 authentication. Ideal for managing Google Workspace users programmatically within n8n workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14ntkaZdraImNylpzYfO15aw6VBD7WQTp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1462" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1463</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Error Notification Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on errors in other workflows and sends an email alert via Gmail API with error details. Set up with Gmail OAuth2 credentials and target email to receive notifications about workflow failures for quick troubleshooting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PV4nTE5dGykxT3DdHd00-kkmZcXQAGBK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1463" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1464</div></th><td class="s6">Set Default Error Workflow in n8n</td><td class="s7">Automates updating the default error workflow ID in n8n workflows stored in a Postgres DB. Uses n8n API to fetch workflows, filters by tags, and updates workflow settings via Postgres node. Scheduled every 4 hours or manually triggered.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xIbZLG7ps9wZjaMjITkJzmoP6DzsHY9v">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1464" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1465</div></th><td class="s6">Country Info Lookup via GraphQL API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves country details (name, phone code, emoji) using a GraphQL query to the countries.trevorblades.com API. It accepts a country code from a webhook, processes the response, and returns a formatted summary string.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=102j-4wvARsqJ6iyDnOKfmTB1YtdSBNly">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1465" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1466</div></th><td class="s6">HighLevel Contact Address Verifier</td><td class="s7">Automates verification of mailing addresses from HighLevel CRM contacts using Lob API. It triggers via webhook, verifies address deliverability, and tags contacts in HighLevel accordingly for follow-up or confirmation. Integrates HighLevel CRM, n8n workflow, and Lob address verification API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iYx4Z1VWaITxR-r6h0WBWnDYReu15yjr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1466" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1467</div></th><td class="s6">Grist Record Transfer with Confirmation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses a Webhook and Grist API to transfer records from a source to a destination table only when a &#39;Confirmed&#39; boolean flag is true. It prevents duplicate entries by checking existing records before creating new ones, ensuring manual confirmation triggers the process.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1r7W0hI-6rN2e-mPL3AVg-Yp1w6u_ymdZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1467" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1468</div></th><td class="s6">XML to JSON Conversion API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow webhook that converts uploaded XML files or XML text payloads into JSON. Uses n8n&#39;s Extract From File and XML nodes, supports binary file uploads and text input, sends JSON responses, and logs errors to Slack.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13e1Zy09N4ZSHnJfZl916hQSBKUUywExx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1468" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1469</div></th><td class="s6">Dynamic NASA API Key Credentials</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating how to dynamically set NASA API credentials using form input expressions. Utilizes n8n Form Trigger, NASA API node, and Respond to Webhook to fetch and redirect to NASA&#39;s picture of the day. Great for learning dynamic credential handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Kb4ot55NtPxAGiihMZMdVKc8DcYZdNec">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1469" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1470</div></th><td class="s6">Email Validation &amp; Domain Extraction Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that validates email addresses and extracts domains using native functions. It uses n8n&#39;s manual trigger, random data generator for sample emails, and set node for processing. Ideal for quick email checks in automated processes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12EcdqlRASRxd-5woRB-v55Kb1IXHS1Ms">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1470" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1471</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Mautic Contact Unsubscribe via Gmail</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates unsubscribing contacts in Mautic based on unsubscribe emails received in Gmail. It uses Gmail API to trigger on new emails, parses sender emails, searches Mautic contacts via Mautic API, updates contact segments (unsubscribe and newsletter), and replies with a confirmation message.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hHaf-PPXonCz_X6pbMtbcAbgnQIZBnsz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1471" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1472</div></th><td class="s6">Redis Workflow Lock for Scheduled Runs</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Redis to lock execution status, preventing concurrent runs of a main workflow triggered on a set schedule. It checks and updates workflow state as &#39;running&#39; or &#39;idle&#39; to ensure serialized runs, using scheduleTrigger, Redis, and executeWorkflow nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qSe8yx7sC_vGvA9HzYLtz6l83F70lkdm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1472" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1473</div></th><td class="s6">FlutterFlow Low-Code API Endpoint</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow provides a low-code API endpoint for FlutterFlow apps using webhooks, a customer datastore node, data aggregation, and response formatting. Easily customize with your database and serve GET requests for app data integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vSa0oXHDyINKAzND1QdWg4HVviiNX_oB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1473" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1474</div></th><td class="s6">DOCX to PDF Conversion Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts DOCX files to PDF using ConvertAPI service. It fetches a DOCX file from a URL, sends it to ConvertAPI with query authentication, and saves the resulting PDF locally. Ideal for automated document format conversion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1v4lzLrZ7nac0903G1SUsgSibeICKekin">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1474" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1475</div></th><td class="s6">Scheduled Website Scraper with Scrappey API</td><td class="s7">An automated workflow using n8n that triggers on schedule to scrape any website via the Scrappey API, avoiding anti-bot blocks. It uses n8n&#39;s Schedule Trigger, HTTP Request node with Scrappey API, and customizable URL input for scalable web scraping tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fJ1P-W-85gg2FcOxZIPj8tZtJwB6jIiu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1475" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1476</div></th><td class="s6">XLSX to PDF Conversion Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading an XLSX file, converts it to PDF using ConvertAPI&#39;s API, and saves the PDF locally. Utilizes n8n, HTTP Requests, and file handling nodes to streamline document format conversion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SPV1okec_gGiJ20gFijX8SqAuSMZq-ls">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1476" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1477</div></th><td class="s6">PPTX to PDF Conversion Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates downloading a PPTX file, converting it to PDF using ConvertAPI&#39;s API, and saving the result locally. Utilizes HTTP Request nodes and file system operations with authentication via ConvertAPI query credentials.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RtYBlVJDDhPEJrx4FCxdQQqYaf7EBmiJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1477" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1478</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Password Protect and Save Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n automation workflow that downloads a PDF, applies password protection using ConvertAPI, saves it locally, and uploads to Google Drive. Utilizes ConvertAPI for PDF processing and Google Drive API for cloud storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Sxwouucb-pSEniWtEz6_zS3-k5T09wEx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1478" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1479</div></th><td class="s6">Webpage to PDF Converter</td><td class="s7">Convert any webpage URL into a downloadable PDF file using ConvertAPI via HTTP request, with automated file saving on disk, triggered manually in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pgkXH1SBlGJM-HwNWc5RXKTAx3UtCRe6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1479" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1480</div></th><td class="s6">HTML to PDF Conversion with ConvertAPI</td><td class="s7">Automates conversion of a simple HTML document to PDF using ConvertAPI via HTTP request, with file handling in n8n. Demonstrates use of manual trigger, code node for binary conversion, and authenticated API request to create a PDF file.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1M9er55lSz_D11cVEH1uZKd6IZARgaFE_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1480" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1481</div></th><td class="s6">Image to PDF Conversion Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads an image from a URL, converts it to PDF using ConvertAPI, then saves the PDF locally. Utilizes HTTP Request node with ConvertAPI for file conversion, manual trigger to start, and file system write node for output.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ip7_ymTOjf-GpmKMMAPFAZJhIJqxBssS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1481" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1482</div></th><td class="s6">PDF to PDF/A Conversion Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading a PDF file, converting it to the PDF/A standard using ConvertAPI, and saving the result locally. Utilizes n8n, HTTP Request nodes, and ConvertAPI&#39;s authenticated REST API for file conversion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1F27Qq0g3miAAm4xUFPr2go5REtN4iYj5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1482" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1483</div></th><td class="s6">Systeme.io Contacts &amp; Tags Management</td><td class="s7">Automate retrieval and management of contacts and tags using Systeme.io API in n8n. Includes pagination and rate limiting handling for full data sync, plus batch adding contacts with custom fields via HTTP requests.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1H1F3Gw6IQgWKHHmPMhnwnpL59GblyVNv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1483" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1484</div></th><td class="s6">Zigbee2MQTT Weekly Backup to SFTP</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly Zigbee2MQTT backups by triggering an MQTT request every Monday at 2:45 AM, receiving the base64 backup response, converting it to a ZIP file, and uploading it securely to an SFTP server. Utilizes MQTT, SFTP, JSON parsing, and n8n scheduling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1h_IRRrnffr_a5DI2BXzFoDC_uJXpaelQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1484" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1485</div></th><td class="s6">TOTP 2FA Code Validation Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to validate 6-digit TOTP codes using Python in a function node without creating credentials. It runs a time-based one-time password algorithm for 2FA verification, suitable for secure authentication systems.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14cga8NT8WmqRqbLrHzCwYdrEBr39HxAk">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1485" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1486</div></th><td class="s6">Todoist Task Prioritization with OpenAI</td><td class="s7">Automates task prioritization in Todoist using a scheduled n8n workflow. It fetches inbox tasks, categorizes them to projects via OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and updates their priority accordingly. Utilizes Todoist API, OpenAI API, and n8n automation platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10ijplhAC8R2ECjW-yQlK8ngpSR0ubWXs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1486" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1487</div></th><td class="s6">Image Overlay Watermark Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates overlaying a watermark or logo image onto a background image using n8n nodes like HTTP Request, Edit Image, and Code. Downloads images, extracts metadata, calculates center position, and composites them. Useful for branding and watermarking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YVRYYgJs984VNiX7iojuPQS3AeBB7tiY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1487" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1488</div></th><td class="s6">Fastmail Masked Email Generator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates disposable masked email addresses via Fastmail&#39;s JMAP API. Triggered by a webhook, it authenticates using HTTP header credentials, processes input state and description, generates a masked email, and responds with the details. Ideal for privacy and testing integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GouR1vFfWg0OKO-vYlx_hOVTk5JXF4B6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1488" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1489</div></th><td class="s6">Xero Webhook Verification &amp; FileMaker Sync</td><td class="s7">Automatically verifies Xero webhook payloads using HMAC SHA256 and syncs data to FileMaker. Utilizes n8n&#39;s webhook, crypto, and FileMaker nodes to securely validate and store webhook events with custom script execution.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15x2HWf-O64Aqf2KXE_Wk9g7Ed78n-o4c">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1489" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1490</div></th><td class="s6">Access Token Management with Static Data</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to manage expiring API access tokens using static data storage. Uses Webhook and Schedule Trigger nodes, HTTP Request to fetch new tokens, JavaScript code nodes to store tokens and timestamps globally, and conditional logic to validate token expiry before reuse.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aexc2cVhG3DLlxQMgVIpScdhKAICfb_Z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1490" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1491</div></th><td class="s6">Book Info Scraper to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow scrapes book data from a website using HTTP request with Jina AI, extracts details via OpenAI-powered Langchain, and saves structured info (title, price, availability, image, link) into Google Sheets. Tech stack: n8n, Jina AI, OpenAI, Google Sheets API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jwOwj2VZBNAKFWTd2t-GVgEDUdeuj7ux">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1491" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1492</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Calvin &amp; Hobbes Comic with AI Translation</td><td class="s7">Automates daily retrieval of Calvin &amp; Hobbes comics using HTTP requests to GoComics, extracts comic images with LangChain, translates dialogues to Korean &amp; English via OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and posts results on Discord via webhook. Uses n8n scheduler for daily automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1U1ORGKNTdILlKDJHcZf-VluxMAE6uvT6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1492" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1493</div></th><td class="s6">BlueSky Auto Post from RSS Feed</td><td class="s7">Automates posting new RSS feed items to BlueSky social. Uses BlueSky API (session creation, image upload, post creation) and n8n workflow nodes to download images, upload blobs, and create posts with text, images, and metadata. Ideal for content syndication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nL7Hlz_LD7gu6jxKZhlaABX9YsvqN4-n">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1493" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1494</div></th><td class="s6">ConvertKit Subscriber &amp; Tag Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates adding subscribers to ConvertKit forms, creating tags, and associating subscribers with tags using ConvertKit API in n8n. Enables streamlined email marketing list management by linking subscribers and tags automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AkRyoTKyyHFDEUe_9tYH4DDkgzTRfTBw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1494" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1495</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Cleanup Old Workflow Executions</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses n8n API and scheduling to automatically list and delete workflow executions older than 10 days. It includes manual and scheduled triggers, conditional date checking, and execution deletion to keep the n8n instance clean and performant.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HdVnInBTn_-i2XlOd2ZY7vkuQ0Y8oGmR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1495" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1496</div></th><td class="s6">Line to LEGO Style Image via DALL·E</td><td class="s7">Transforms images sent via LINE messaging app into LEGO-style isometric images using a LINE webhook, LINE Messaging API, and OpenAI&#39;s DALL·E and GPT models for prompt creation and image generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yTz6VtdPwSY8Kn6irWbg7DQSlOCCRS5V">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1496" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1497</div></th><td class="s6">Sentry Release Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates creating a new release and retrieving all releases in Sentry.io using its API. Triggered manually, it integrates with the Sentry API to manage software release versions and track project releases efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18-xv6dp12HPnLpTRR75KN94DsoFeFCc6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1497" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1498</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Welcome and Farewell Bot - Spanish</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating greetings and farewells in a Spanish Telegram group using Telegram API. It detects new or leaving members and sends personalized welcome or goodbye messages in Spanish to the group @comunidadn8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ynjtt082u2m7m-O5bfu8CpwdlAkRZXNT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1498" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1499</div></th><td class="s6">Perplexity AI Q&amp;A with n8n</td><td class="s7">Automates sending system and user prompts to Perplexity AI&#39;s Sonar model via HTTP API in n8n, processing answers and citations. Uses n8n workflows with HTTP Request node and Generic Header Authentication to query AI-driven chat completions for knowledge comparison.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14Mbes_tjLiV6r9_o8qXQ9q0MESALQpy6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1499" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1500</div></th><td class="s6">Keyword IT Service Identifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that reads keywords from a Google Sheet, uses OpenAI GPT-4 via Langchain to identify if keywords include known IT software or services, then updates the sheet with &#39;yes&#39; or &#39;no&#39; results. It features batch processing and rate-limiting wait nodes for API stability.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qjPc95X859iQlbJPVxilNLaCKV0ox6BL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1500" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1501</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Telegram Text Affirmations</td><td class="s7">Automates sending daily positive affirmations at 9 AM via Telegram using n8n with a Cron trigger, affirmations.dev API for content, and Telegram API for delivery to user Daniel.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1n_2XTQfI3OKzs3MYNGGwNRgDJuDE6elN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1501" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1502</div></th><td class="s6">RSS to Mastodon Auto Poster</td><td class="s7">Automates posting new RSS feed items to a Mastodon instance using n8n. Utilizes RSS Feed Read, Cron scheduling, Function node for deduplication, and HTTP Request node to post updates via Mastodon API every 10 minutes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eFXGZXluE-66t5oXzJNMLgn33rZeqP2_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1502" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1503</div></th><td class="s6">SIGNL4 Alert Automation</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow triggers hourly to read alert data from a JSON file, sends or resolves alerts via the SIGNL4 API, and updates the stored alert status. It uses n8n nodes like Cron, file read/write, JSON-binary conversion, and SIGNL4 integration to automate alert management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12tC8g8zC7fRxu7ViNuDW-Vt9nBy2PkwQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1503" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1504</div></th><td class="s6">Syncro Tickets to Clockify Timer</td><td class="s7">Automates time tracking by creating Clockify entries from Syncro ticket data via a webhook. Uses n8n workflow with Syncro webhook POST input and Clockify API to log work sessions efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1k9SUF3JN2np7cHDwZH12lrrPRH21dGtA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1504" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1505</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Insert Text into YouTube Descriptions</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses YouTube API to fetch videos, insert custom text between specified lines in video descriptions, and update them automatically. Ideal for YouTubers managing multiple videos. Tech stack: n8n, YouTube API, JavaScript for description editing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZDyvLIaAzN9r-XW9DqaXWRtI2j5fin8f">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1505" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1506</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Nocode Tool Info Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow creating a Telegram bot that retrieves no-code tool info from a Strapi API and sends translated descriptions and images. Utilizes Telegram API, Strapi REST API, and local translation CLI, enabling multilingual responses for no-code enthusiasts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fB-cS9TGl7en0Oz1prSLPpfzXu1Pkkr3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1506" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1507</div></th><td class="s6">MailerLite Subscriber to Airtable Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing new MailerLite subscriber additions to a group and stores their name and email in Airtable. Uses MailerLite webhook trigger and Airtable API via n8n to keep subscriber data synced in real-time for easy CRM or marketing use.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1q-8LOG4q_Kyju1ZDz4EQ_d9MbeIufbE7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1507" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1508</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Invite Users from Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates inviting users to an n8n instance by syncing email addresses from a Google Sheet with existing n8n users. Uses Google Sheets API, n8n API, and supports pagination and scheduled or manual triggers for updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_PYw6z3fsMe6QiGLhNKnNEZ0XFsP3CDU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1508" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1509</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Downloader and Merger Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates downloading multiple PDF files from URLs, merges them into a single PDF using a custom PDF Toolkit node, and writes the merged file to disk. Uses HTTP Request, Split Out, and file system nodes with custom-js PDF merge API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MhKhflAgnV14GVHjH69BAxYCQaEwdYCV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1509" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1510</div></th><td class="s6">Customer.io: Create Customer &amp; Add to Segment</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Customer.io API to create a new customer with custom properties and add them to a specific segment. Utilizes manual trigger and Customer.io nodes for customer management and segmentation automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1l2eXQ_haXmMrDfWCRpEUJjvv-SUNQM_j">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1510" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1511</div></th><td class="s6">Sensor Alert System with PostgreSQL and Twilio</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of sensor data in PostgreSQL, sending SMS alerts via Twilio for readings above a threshold. Uses n8n Cron to schedule, queries the DB, sends notifications, and updates alert status to avoid duplicates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pdRjUDDyNFrsl6xPxxrWaU0VTCjzGkL9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1511" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1512</div></th><td class="s6">Gumroad Sale Notification Trigger</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow listens to Gumroad sales using the Gumroad API webhook trigger to notify users in real-time when a sale is made. It enables automated updates for sales events, ideal for creators and sellers using Gumroad.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HjD7MYWDBHPoHb88tP5PBq6uaRWm3sI-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1512" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1513</div></th><td class="s6">PagerDuty Incident Acknowledge Notifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that listens for POST webhook calls, acknowledges PagerDuty incidents via their API, and posts confirmation messages to Mattermost channels. Utilizes PagerDuty and Mattermost APIs for incident management and team notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B59vbQa93G5C7nMmMESe6Owut5ovYV9c">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1513" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1514</div></th><td class="s6">HTML to Compressed PDF Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates converting HTML content to PDF and compresses PDFs. Utilizes CustomJS PDF Toolkit nodes for HTML-to-PDF conversion and PDF compression, plus manual trigger and code nodes. Useful for content generation, document processing automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1khdjlvyNGp8LvUAEcOvBZyk22CSzJUwZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1514" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1515</div></th><td class="s6">HTML to PDF and PDF to PNG Converter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using CustomJS PDF Toolkit to convert HTML content to PDF and transform PDFs (from generated output or URL) into PNG images. It automates document format conversions with HTML input, manual trigger, and URL-based PDF input.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QnovzU3w7yCzRA0htFkqPjs1yOy7T8PZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1515" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1516</div></th><td class="s6">Email Open Tracking Transparent Pixel</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow creates and serves a 1x1 transparent PNG tracking pixel via webhook to detect email opens. It uses n8n nodes to decode base64 image data, convert to binary, and respond with the image. Includes logging placeholder and supports capturing userId via query parameter.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12iz6DFSmQnd7bEt_scO6E2AuiucuKOB6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1516" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1517</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Auto-Start Workflows by Tag</td><td class="s7">Automates activation of n8n workflows tagged with &#39;Auto start&#39; via n8n API integration. Runs post-start to ensure tagged workflows are activated automatically, ideal for auto deployment pipelines and containerized n8n setups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1z3do7Z9O_ApO2temzQDavfUUTETziQiz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1517" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1518</div></th><td class="s6">Export PostgreSQL Table Data to CSV</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using PostgreSQL and Spreadsheet nodes to export data from a specified database table (e.g., booksRead) into a CSV file format with manual trigger execution.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SNG0ANg9ydknJ-MtA91ReG8Cmde8GsaE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1518" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1519</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Poem Telegram Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates daily delivery of a random poem via Telegram using Poemist API for poem retrieval and LingvaNex for translation to English. Triggered by Cron at 10 AM, it sends translated poems to a specified Telegram chat. Useful for daily literary inspiration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Hir5avuxsMFnCFvTesd0rXv0NeU4YmTq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1519" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1520</div></th><td class="s6">Orlen Invoice Auto Archiver</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Orlen invoice emails, saves attachments to date-organized Google Drive folders, marks emails as read, and sends Slack notifications. Uses Gmail API, Google Drive API, Slack API, and cron scheduling in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ntImOhKk-5RgUlIxcQgpAVVN3Pmkw062">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1520" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1521</div></th><td class="s6">Webflow Form Submission Trigger</td><td class="s7">Automates receiving updates from Webflow form submissions using Webflow Trigger node with OAuth2 authentication in n8n workflow. Ideal for alerting or processing form data instantly from your Webflow site.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sLNHa_HUequAOd10STQp8-vYXZt91gW-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1521" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1522</div></th><td class="s6">DigitalOcean Droplet Creation via API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates creating a DigitalOcean droplet using HTTP Request node. It sends a POST request to DigitalOcean API with droplet details (name, region, size, image) and requires a personal access token for authorization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PTx-pPCJwqj52bUMHwVZq4Tg3gHKExVN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1522" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1523</div></th><td class="s6">Wit.ai Speech-to-Text from WAV File</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that reads a WAV audio file and sends it to the Wit.ai speech recognition API for transcription. Utilizes the Read Binary File node and HTTP Request node with audio/wav content type to convert speech to text.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GuArk584wQS3EoMsrCaXXwIqsKytvI0y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1523" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1524</div></th><td class="s6">Weekly Cocktail Recipe Poster</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching random cocktail recipes from TheCocktailDB API, generates a custom image with Bannerbear API, and posts it weekly to Rocket.Chat. Uses n8n workflow automation with HTTP Request, Bannerbear, Cron, and Rocket.Chat nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xjxqnalWcIhwK6ynI5lKFdwA4iob-xkC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1524" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1525</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Notifications to Discord Alert</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow fetches GitHub notifications every minute using GitHub API with Basic Auth, processes them to create a summary report, then sends the report as a tagged message to a Discord channel. Utilizes Cron, HTTP Request, Function, IF, and Discord nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IsrMQx0qqJz-leMbD6xs4P8OqzR8RfAH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1525" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1526</div></th><td class="s6">Asana Event Update Notifier</td><td class="s7">Workflow that triggers notifications on updates within Asana&#39;s Engineering workspace using n8n&#39;s Asana Trigger node. Ideal for automating task/event updates by leveraging the Asana API to monitor changes in real-time.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vznzhjjo6OA6ZIr1hwDlToScTV1TjdK6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1526" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1527</div></th><td class="s6">Email Bounce &amp; Open Event Receiver</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Postmark API webhook to receive real-time notifications for email bounce and open events, enabling users to track email engagement and delivery status automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12Mqxz_A-cFzAhf_hnmX8u7ZxFOUfcUqf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1527" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1528</div></th><td class="s6">Wallabag Auto-Starred RSS Importer</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching starred articles from Tiny Tiny RSS and posts them to Wallabag. Uses TTRSS API for authentication &amp; retrieving articles, Wallabag API for OAuth2 token and posting. Enables scheduled article archival every 10 minutes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Vfz51LIB1bcgTVdss0WkHTOX9700lI72">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1528" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1529</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Stars Slack Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates Slack notifications for GitHub star events on n8n&#39;s repository, using GitHub Trigger and Slack API nodes. It alerts the #general Slack channel when someone stars or unstars the repo, showing user info and star count.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uTvT_Huhi6mLpWMir0B1DeDwkDyr_UqR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1529" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1530</div></th><td class="s6">Mailchimp Subscribe Event Listener</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on Mailchimp subscribe events using Mailchimp API credentials. It listens to new subscribers from multiple sources (API, admin, user) for a specific list ID, enabling automated responses or actions on subscriber signup events.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QE-P7sjsC5L2dLH0LxzzOa5QLhVOpChI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1530" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1531</div></th><td class="s6">Email Verification with Hunter API</td><td class="s7">Automates email verification using Hunter API in an n8n workflow. Triggered manually, it validates the format and existence of an email address to reduce bounce rate and improve outreach accuracy.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xnjGbo-N2P4rKbUs4VY_rGILYD9IGpLH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1531" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1532</div></th><td class="s6">MQTT Message Receiver</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using MQTT Trigger node to receive messages from an MQTT queue. It listens to MQTT broker messages and can be extended for IoT, messaging, or automation projects requiring MQTT integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LhswZidsHXqgp2vVEI474w9XkFGTz9vM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1532" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1533</div></th><td class="s6">Hacker News Feed Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches the latest stories from Hacker News using the native Hacker News node triggered manually. It provides a simple way to retrieve news data for automation or integration purposes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OTZ-MwHZ-h2LJGAZ8rS-fpaO_f0p3jAu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1533" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1534</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Repository Event Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that listens to all event types on the n8n-io/n8n-docs GitHub repository using GitHub API via webhook trigger. Ideal for automating actions based on repo activity.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16DkDPedBtavPv1zRjEnmxFZtaFbrkT4q">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1534" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1535</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice Ninja Data Fetcher</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching all invoices from Invoice Ninja using its API triggered manually in n8n workflow. Useful for financial data retrieval and integration with other systems.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uGoeN0cuWkbh6V2zZPBNiZEqgp3dSz1i">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1535" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1536</div></th><td class="s6">Eventbrite Order Event Listener</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to listen for Eventbrite order events (placed, updated, refunded) using Eventbrite API via webhook trigger. Ideal for automating responses to ticket sales and order changes in an Eventbrite organization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TkP_NuqbFrM2hF48UjgFvOkgEREN32YO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1536" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1537</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify New Order Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Shopify API to trigger on new orders creation in a Shopify store. It leverages Shopify webhook to automate workflows based on new order events, useful for order processing and notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19yBPteEAOt3gl9oq1mSJopmKlI4Wtelq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1537" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1538</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Products Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers manually to fetch all products from a Shopify store using Shopify API credentials. It helps automate retrieval of product data for e-commerce operations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ByWZ9vvyATmw1veSgDvMOyVbuJU6x8kL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1538" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1539</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform to Airtable Submission Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates capturing form responses from Typeform via webhook and appends them to an Airtable base for organized storage. Utilizes Typeform API trigger and Airtable API node in n8n. Ideal for streamlined data collection and management workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gKJwlAWpXmEU-bA_OdlHPLOrk9JG-7L6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1539" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1540</div></th><td class="s6">Zoho CRM Data Fetch Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers manually to fetch all records from Zoho CRM using Zoho OAuth2 API. Useful for integrating and automating CRM data retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EihQucJZOYyBVK54S2ls_NqC_c1oEU5t">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1540" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1541</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Cocktail Recipe via Telegram Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates sending a daily random cocktail recipe with image and instructions to a Telegram chat using TheCocktailDB API, n8n HTTP Request node, and Telegram Bot integration triggered every day at 8 PM via Cron node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hC4ZsNvex5uuwFo-K5GtY19T0lLciGlA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1541" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1542</div></th><td class="s6">Facebook Page Comments Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses the Facebook Graph API to fetch latest posts and their comments from a specified Facebook Page. It processes, filters, and organizes Facebook post and comment data, leveraging nodes like Set, Split Out, Filter, Merge, and Code to structure the output.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ivXKNim0RERfXni6turwp76FjEVJSAoa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1542" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1543</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Release Notifier to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates notifications of new GitHub releases from Mesdocteurs/mda-admin-partner-api repository by triggering on release events and sending detailed messages to Slack channel &#39;extranet-md&#39; using GitHub API and Slack API integration in n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1maKvNUAfh_Ei6ftafLQYSMVUD2r57rQn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1543" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1544</div></th><td class="s6">Clockify Ticket Status Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that syncs ticket statuses with Clockify projects via webhook triggers. It uses the Clockify API to archive or unarchive projects based on ticket status updates, automating time tracking project management for support tickets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GRZPI3rQBkvLDR9zM__evSEnv96tsG3z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1544" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1545</div></th><td class="s6">WordPress Post Create and Update Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates creating and updating WordPress posts using the WordPress API nodes in n8n. Triggered manually, it first creates a post with a title, then updates its content. Useful for content management automation with WordPress and n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zZl9lFQ0UjAkxyWOFaUJbqun9-FZwhuw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1545" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1546</div></th><td class="s6">NextCloud Image Download &amp; Upload</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading an image from a URL and uploading it to NextCloud folders using n8n workflow. Utilizes HTTP Request and NextCloud API nodes to manage files seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10qT4v-O2pZu5RN6yeBNUa30jPojCgUbE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1546" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1547</div></th><td class="s6">Contentful Data Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches all entries from Contentful CMS using its API, triggered manually. Useful for automating content retrieval from Contentful for various applications without coding.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B-KXDyZS1dR1zBV5L52itDYGQ1xljRGN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1547" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1548</div></th><td class="s6">Fetch Completed Orders from Unleashed Software</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to manually trigger and fetch all completed orders from Unleashed Software API using the Unleashed Software node. Ideal for inventory or order management automation setups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u2CZK-Q90x-0760tw0eP_5r-P-dCTqZU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1548" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1549</div></th><td class="s6">Download and Upload File via FTP</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading a file via HTTP request and uploads it to an FTP server, then lists files on the FTP. Uses n8n&#39;s HTTP Request and FTP nodes. Enables simple file transfer automation between web and FTP storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1q5YSEIe2U70F5T_HZ_eOhZb-j5qiWs3F">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1549" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1550</div></th><td class="s6">Salesforce Lead Creation and Update Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates lead creation in Salesforce, updates lead details (city), and adds a note marking &#39;Deal Won!&#39;. Uses n8n with Salesforce OAuth2 API integration to streamline CRM lead management tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1loyxmqC8-5qUQgh2X8-Ict7-eBA_dAFn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1550" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1551</div></th><td class="s6">Microsoft Teams Channel Setup &amp; Messaging</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates creating and updating a Microsoft Teams channel and sending a message using Microsoft Teams OAuth2 API. Triggered manually, it integrates Microsoft Teams operations to manage team channels and post messages efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18STO11qP7g4kms6lASCdv_D1YUmULEAr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1551" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1552</div></th><td class="s6">LinkedIn Image Post Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates posting an image with text on LinkedIn. It downloads an image via HTTP request from a URL and then publishes it as a post on a LinkedIn profile using LinkedIn API and OAuth2 authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AUwQ9sWk0ITBkEae3q3yzaQGbOZocoHf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1552" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1553</div></th><td class="s6">Weather Alert SMS Notification</td><td class="s7">Automates sending SMS alerts via Twilio based on current Berlin weather from OpenWeatherMap. Uses n8n with Cron trigger, weather API, conditional logic, and Twilio messaging to notify if &#39;feels_like&#39; temperature is under 18°C.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ej7BejkqRUMHx9g1yxBsMY-hj6fEpKto">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1553" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1554</div></th><td class="s6">Taiga Project Event Update Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers notifications upon events in a specific Taiga project using the TaigaCloud API. Ideal for automating project update alerts and integrations within team workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Zlq9jXQEVRnj6nLy6BlbmmbzfSzpNsqK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1554" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1555</div></th><td class="s6">Session Feedback Reminder via Mattermost</td><td class="s7">Automates scheduled feedback requests by fetching session details from Google Sheets and posting a customized message with a feedback link to a Mattermost channel using n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HfA-8otaSqYdhntuuC2lF3KmMEX-s2ja">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1555" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1556</div></th><td class="s6">Clockify Project, Tag &amp; Time Entry Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates workflow in Clockify by creating a project, adding a tag, creating a time entry with details, and updating it with the project ID. Utilizes Clockify API through n8n nodes for seamless time tracking and project management automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1D3FpGjfAWqLBgCLipxVvI2IZhVYlVrYe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1556" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1557</div></th><td class="s6">Bulk Telegram Message Sender from Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates sending messages via Telegram bot to multiple chat IDs listed in a Google Sheets column. Utilizes Google Sheets API for data retrieval, Telegram API for messaging, batching with SplitInBatches, and timed delays to avoid flooding. Ideal for broadcast messaging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wIxNd3VNKFOuy5W-JglK_Y8qCmv1R7i9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1557" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1558</div></th><td class="s6">BTC Price Alert via SMS</td><td class="s7">Automates BTC price monitoring in EUR using CoinGecko API every minute; sends an SMS alert via Twilio if the price is &gt;= 9000 EUR. Uses cron scheduling, conditional logic (IF node), and Twilio API for messaging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OCmlmFHlbx6mMYp-jBdBC7NpkUhg5tos">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1558" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1559</div></th><td class="s6">Web Page Scraper with FireCrawl API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that takes a URL input and uses the FireCrawl API to scrape the webpage content in markdown format. It automates fetching web page data via HTTP requests and processes it for reuse in AI agents or other applications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NinvG7KTn7-piOvPoLWB_EvsxNQ6_sKe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1559" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1560</div></th><td class="s6">Sitemap Reader and URL Filter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches a sitemap.xml via HTTP, converts its XML to JSON, splits URLs, and filters them by criteria (e.g., PDFs). Main tools used: HTTP Request, XML node, Split Out, and Filter nodes. Useful for automated URL extraction and filtering.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1r_p3E2oFLWRYpZfEoQG63FPrXi4FiW0t">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1560" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1561</div></th><td class="s6">YouTube Playlist to Raindrop Bookmarks</td><td class="s7">Automates saving new videos from a specified YouTube playlist to Raindrop.io as bookmarks every 30 mins. Uses YouTube API with OAuth2, filters new videos via workflow static data, and creates bookmarks with tags and titles in Raindrop via its OAuth2 API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=178nlzvrs5CkfqZ95_77uClzL_ZnsXldC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1561" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1562</div></th><td class="s6">Disk Usage Alert via Twilio SMS</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow monitors hard disk usage on the host machine twice daily using a shell command, and sends an SMS alert via Twilio if usage exceeds 80%. It automates system resource monitoring and alerting with Cron, Execute Command, IF, and Twilio nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cn7BZGIFwOdRJCmeaoN8jkQLGT8n2FVK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1562" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1563</div></th><td class="s6">WooCommerce Refund Alerts to Slack</td><td class="s7">Automates notifications for WooCommerce store refund events over $100 by sending detailed alerts to a Slack channel. Utilizes WooCommerce API as the trigger and Slack API to deliver refund info, streamlining refund monitoring for e-commerce teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aIgnDiSLeRj0pUtKdNKU8e4r8YXMNTjh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1563" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1564</div></th><td class="s6">Zoom Meeting Creation Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates creating a Zoom meeting using the Zoom API. Triggered manually, it leverages the Zoom node with OAuth2 authentication to set up meetings instantly within automation pipelines.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ik1Zmii19gWYtaoYGkHKarned17Vf5zn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1564" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1565</div></th><td class="s6">Mautic Contact Email Validation Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates validation of new Mautic contacts&#39; emails using One Simple API. Triggers on new contact creation, verifies email quality and domain, and sends alerts to Slack for suspicious addresses. Integrates Mautic, One Simple API, and Slack for lead quality control.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IMKAMb5K_a7yUQi2LB5HaKlIVR20MKhw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1565" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1566</div></th><td class="s6">Create Jira Issue on Manual Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates a new issue in Jira Software Cloud when manually triggered. It uses the n8n Jira node connected to Jira Software Cloud API, enabling quick issue creation with specified project, summary, and issue type.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1X7wSDSyTWYnUX_USu8lWyT30j598y_EP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1566" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1567</div></th><td class="s6">ISS Real-Time Position Tracker</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches the current International Space Station (ISS) position using the whereistheiss.at API every minute, filters out duplicate timestamps, and outputs new coordinates with timestamps for monitoring ISS position changes in real time.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_pba0n47uJhnX9cbP5O5rPqGc9oOKTnz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1567" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1568</div></th><td class="s6">New RSS Feed Fetcher with Images</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching of only new articles from The Verge RSS every 5 minutes, extracts titles, authors, publication dates, content snippets, and images using n8n nodes like Cron, RSS Feed Read, HTML Extract, and Function to filter duplicates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Pkicm0ckGZNVGGLOda69o0QVqOCYLcEg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1568" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1569</div></th><td class="s6">Workflow Error Notification via Mailgun</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that captures runtime errors using an Error Trigger and sends detailed error reports via Mailgun email API, including error message and stack trace, to specified recipients for quick debugging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Z5q61a4gNCGxRGlKeekyyaqSB5U2IrW_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1569" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1570</div></th><td class="s6">ISS Position Logger to TimescaleDB</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching the International Space Station&#39;s live latitude, longitude, and timestamp every minute using the &#39;wheretheiss.at&#39; API, then stores the data into a TimescaleDB database for time-series analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1h6Rsm3voEO7DTrquAkIV_T1GX7x9DCvj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1570" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1571</div></th><td class="s6">Reddit Post and Comment Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates creating a Reddit post, fetching it, and adding a comment using n8n&#39;s Reddit node with OAuth2 credentials. Ideal for Reddit content automation workflows using n8n&#39;s automation platform and Reddit API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u9KSy9YsVrdbeSh6ngvnH2v8MkETI8nZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1571" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1572</div></th><td class="s6">Tapfiliate Affiliate Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates affiliate creation and tagging in Tapfiliate using n8n. Includes manual trigger, affiliate creation, metadata tagging, and program assignment via Tapfiliate API integration, streamlining affiliate program management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17VbKzHSIR2FI2El_j5O56izJ-ik68X_O">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1572" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1573</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform to Demio Webinar Registration</td><td class="s7">Automates webinar sign-ups by triggering on Typeform submissions and registering users to Demio events using their APIs. Streamlines lead capture from surveys or signup forms directly into webinar platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WxDXu6Or4wv6Ni2HRh-uyB3cSiVTwY_D">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1573" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1574</div></th><td class="s6">Raindrop Bookmark CRUD Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating bookmark create, update, and retrieve operations using Raindrop API with OAuth2 authentication. It manages bookmark collections and individual bookmarks like creating a collection, adding docs link, updating title, and fetching bookmark details.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lkm38P5AYEGoqxyl5P5MWoW6o-gL7hGu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1574" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1575</div></th><td class="s6">Strava Activity Auto-Tweet</td><td class="s7">Automates tweeting new Strava activities using Strava API trigger and Twitter API. When a new activity is created on Strava, it tweets the activity name and distance automatically using OAuth2 and OAuth1 authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rtyJAk6mExKM8J-b4-E4PkhgZl-H2EEK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1575" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1576</div></th><td class="s6">GoToWebinar Webinar Automation Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating webinar management in GoToWebinar API: creates a webinar, updates its description, and fetches webinar details using OAuth2 credentials. Ideal for automating webinar setups and updates seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1T2lmEHzUg32umWCIiZyJw5UTIfmLNJuW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1576" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1577</div></th><td class="s6">Weather Alert Notification via SIGNL4</td><td class="s7">Automates weather monitoring for Berlin using OpenWeatherMap API, triggers a SIGNL4 alert if the temperature drops below 25°C. Utilizes n8n&#39;s schedule and conditional nodes for timely notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Y6aHuz_oWeaDvN0mp5H7iEJWQwJq2KRx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1577" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1578</div></th><td class="s6">Webhook to PostHog Event Tracker</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that receives events via a webhook and sends them to PostHog analytics using the PostHog API. Useful for real-time event tracking with no-code automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-riGrj3t8_Td8dPmoPnjgtykERMrR_Pv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1578" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1579</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable to Lemlist Lead Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates lead syncing by fetching contacts from Airtable and adding them to a Lemlist email campaign. Utilizes Airtable API for data retrieval and Lemlist API to manage leads and campaigns, streamlining outreach and lead management workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bOe4128FatN7qj3-dIfKfkZiCfUUfRiK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1579" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1580</div></th><td class="s6">Lemlist to Mattermost Reply Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates notifications in Mattermost when a recipient replies to a Lemlist email campaign. Utilizes Lemlist API webhook triggers and Mattermost API to post personalized reply messages to a specified channel, streamlining sales and outreach follow-up.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WnrXwCPfaMmYd1QgqeMmZv27HgRh0hR1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1580" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1581</div></th><td class="s6">Asana Task Creation via Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates Asana tasks triggered by HTTP requests via webhook using Asana&#39;s OAuth2 API. It automates task creation and returns a confirmation URL. Useful for integrating external systems with Asana task management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YzkCChhbJRpu2cqLAJvp56F_E9qw025U">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1581" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1582</div></th><td class="s6">Create Task in Asana</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of tasks in Asana using n8n workflow with manual trigger and Asana API integration. Ideal for streamlined task management within teams.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1A3K3aw2LctYg9R69x0QvtnFq_gg-pNj8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1582" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1583</div></th><td class="s6">Autopilot to Airtable Contact Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on new Autopilot contacts, extracts their first name, last name, and email, and appends them to an Airtable base. Utilizes Autopilot API for contact events and Airtable API to store contact data for easy CRM management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18UAfIG8YaOdoMWKiaOFo8CxtQzwhyYDj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1583" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1584</div></th><td class="s6">Random Cocktail Recipe Translator</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow fetches a random cocktail recipe via TheCocktailDB API and translates the instructions to French using the DeepL API, automating cocktail content localization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16fBTB3m_jeJo5nx7q3aZUXpynUFIW0RL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1584" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1585</div></th><td class="s6">Microsoft SQL Query Executor</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to manually trigger and execute SQL queries on Microsoft SQL Server using n8n&#39;s built-in Microsoft SQL node. Enables easy database querying via automated workflows with manual control, ideal for database admins and developers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1O-iQ7o4oCP8W8iQ56ptvt_F7fdEfhKua">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1585" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1586</div></th><td class="s6">3D Figurine Views Generator with AI APIs</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of 3D figurine orthographic views using Midjourney for initial 3D-style image generation and GPT-4o-Image API to produce front, side, and back views on a turnaround sheet. Built with n8n workflow automation handling HTTP requests and image URL parsing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Y_VV7zH63YdvpSAp1UZkO29asiTf-elT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1586" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1587</div></th><td class="s6">Matrix Virtual Coffee Group Organizer</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly virtual coffee meetups by grouping Matrix chat room members into randomized small groups. Utilizes Matrix API, cron scheduling, and custom JavaScript to fetch members, shuffle, and announce groups in the room every Monday at 10 AM.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=190e3rSjpBLs4eeJj9ILC0H8dUi-F2S6I">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1587" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1588</div></th><td class="s6">Paul Graham Essays Milvus AI Agent</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow scrapes Paul Graham essays, extracts and processes text, loads to Milvus vector database, and enables AI chat with OpenAI GPT-4o mini model. Tech stack: HTTP requests, HTML parsing, LangChain tools, Milvus vector store, and OpenAI embeddings and chat APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ibq_FJMx8_SNF0OdgiHZLYprqQp2pOXy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1588" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1589</div></th><td class="s6">Line Messaging API Auto Reply &amp; Push</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow leveraging Line Messaging API to automatically reply to incoming Line messages using reply tokens and send push messages with user-specific Line UID. Integrates webhook listener, conditional checks, and HTTP requests for interactive chat automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19gijF2j4Gn7bqtlSo-DdzXLABcf8HzyS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1589" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1590</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Image Description with GROQ LLAVA</td><td class="s7">Automates image description by sending photos received via Telegram to the GROQ LLAVA V1.5-7B API for detailed analysis and returns text descriptions back to Telegram users. Uses Telegram Bot API, base64 image encoding, and GROQ AI vision API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CB6KAqWcn6MBMVNpK9vW3HtJFzSXNG58">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1590" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1591</div></th><td class="s6">Book Data Scraper to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that scrapes book details from a website using HTTP request to Jina.ai endpoint, extracts structured info with OpenAI-powered Langchain nodes, and appends data (title, price, availability, image, link) into Google Sheets. Automates product price tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1twhtVHhhi4QnZieNOqXw58rAorGM0zH4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1591" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1592</div></th><td class="s6">LangChain Workflow Retriever with OpenAI QA</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating LangChain and OpenAI API to retrieve and query data from another n8n workflow by ID. It uses LangChain&#39;s Workflow Retriever and Retrieval QA Chain with an OpenAI Chat model to answer questions based on workflow data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mEeATz-fHhQ_gcPsurtkcpDBf9fyxcOO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1592" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1593</div></th><td class="s6">Typeform Feedback Sentiment Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates sentiment analysis on Typeform event feedback using AWS Comprehend and sends negative feedback alerts to Mattermost. Integrates Typeform API, AWS Comprehend for sentiment detection, and Mattermost API for messaging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Zy0DnXGCQsa1XgrtdPm0QLiX2bFnbI2d">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1593" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1594</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Website Change Spy &amp; Email Alerts</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates detecting changes on specified websites using Firecrawl scraping API, compares content over a day, uses OpenAI GPT-4 models to analyze differences, and conditionally sends detailed Gmail alerts. Integrates OpenAI, Firecrawl, and Gmail for spy-like website monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1x7SRjSzJGCPnRX-Yp07FPDCtWWa3vSDO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1594" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1595</div></th><td class="s6">TikTok Video Downloader &amp; Google Drive Uploader</td><td class="s7">Automate downloading TikTok videos without watermarks using HTTP requests and HTML parsing. The workflow scrapes the raw video URL and downloads the file, then optionally uploads it to Google Drive with public sharing. Integrates TikTok website, JavaScript code node, and Google Drive API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Y6noCbqkkkWD6IgpVH7xdkLTL_chfder">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1595" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1596</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Meetup Scheduler AI Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram Bot API, Google Sheets, and OpenRouter AI to provide meetup scheduling assistance. It fetches schedule data from Google Sheets, converts it to markdown, and uses LangChain with OpenRouter for AI-powered chat responses on Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Shug68NOlicGfbVGC0U2kYVTsgpq7GF7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1596" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1597</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Daily Top 13 Trending Repo Scraper</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that scrapes GitHub&#39;s trending page to extract details of the top 13 repositories daily using HTTP Request and HTML Extract nodes. It parses repository info like author, title, URL, description, and language, enabling automation of GitHub trend data collection.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HTlWqeCQEtO8L6OJa66hoJFPkJp27XgT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1597" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1598</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Auto On/Off Scheduler</td><td class="s7">Automates activation and deactivation of an n8n workflow daily at 08:00 and 20:00 using n8n API node and cron-based schedule triggers. Ideal for controlling workflow operation hours in DevOps setups with custom API credentials.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1R21CdeKrtzv8R-Cp-iNDmghsSLyCOQTD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1598" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1599</div></th><td class="s6">Chat with Local LLMs via n8n &amp; Ollama</td><td class="s7">Interact with self-hosted Large Language Models (LLMs) using n8n workflow and Ollama API. This system captures user chat input, sends it to a local Ollama-powered LLM, and returns AI responses seamlessly within n8n, enabling private, customizable AI chats.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Mj_QPhB1yMtKnxkoAgZFHhiMmbkPciZp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1599" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1600</div></th><td class="s6">Webpage to Markdown &amp; Link Extractor</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that uses Firecrawl.dev API to convert webpage HTML into markdown and extract all links. Supports batch processing with rate limiting and integrates with custom data sources for input/output. Ideal for content extraction and AI preprocessing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OViya4XZTMWZbihSGvA-ehQBPZJzsy3p">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1600" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1601</div></th><td class="s6">Docker WHMCS/WISECP API Backend</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow providing an API backend for managing Docker containers via WHMCS/WISECP integrations. Uses SSH to run bash scripts on Docker servers, managing container lifecycle, disk mounts, NGINX config, and user/password operations for containerized n8n instances.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Hga-MMQYIzCU9IZk_N-Z-qdbcC3ECPfx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1601" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1602</div></th><td class="s6">DigitalOcean File Upload via Form</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that accepts file uploads through a web form and uploads them to a DigitalOcean Spaces bucket using the S3 API with public read access. It then returns the public URL of the uploaded file. Uses n8n form trigger, S3 node, and form completion steps.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pTgwEP2XAuLc5FqRg7iu1zWZg-ic3pp6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1602" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1603</div></th><td class="s6">Uber Eats Email Expense Logger</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Uber Eats order details from Gmail emails and sends formatted expense info to Slack with Moze app links, using Gmail and Slack APIs within n8n workflow for seamless delivery expense tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vFGHZNgsH_-ENZG-gdAA6yeGTP-IP-L-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1603" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1604</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Toxic Language Filter</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrating Telegram API and Google Perspective API to detect and respond to toxic language in Telegram chats by automatically replying with a warning message when profanity is detected above a threshold.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zojKDecrCLCT8kvF9Jkfo19_PFf7Kc4k">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1604" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1605</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Merge Automation with ConvertAPI</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates downloading two remote PDF files, merging them into one using ConvertAPI&#39;s PDF merge endpoint, and saving the result locally. It integrates HTTP Request nodes for file download and the ConvertAPI for file merging, requiring API key authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nvj0laK-T3KZTwHOopNmOIbJ-gJt14Lt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1605" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1606</div></th><td class="s6">HTML Page Generator with OpenAI Structured Output</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses OpenAI GPT-4o to generate structured JSON UI components styled with Tailwind CSS from user queries, converts JSON to formatted HTML, and serves dynamic web pages via webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1n_cYfLcEvyFUhSE-_FVK_hPKCSLPI5Cc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1606" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1607</div></th><td class="s6">Squarespace Code Injection Backup to GitHub</td><td class="s7">Automates backing up Squarespace header and footer code injections to a GitHub repository using n8n workflow. Utilizes Squarespace HTTP API, GitHub API, and cheerio for HTML cleaning. Enables scheduled and manual backup to organized repo folders.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ai6wZPSyDqackLx-tr8tU9bRW4J87rOP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1607" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1608</div></th><td class="s6">SQL Dataset Comparison Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to compare two SQL datasets using MySQL queries and the Compare Datasets node. It fetches aggregated payment data for customers from overlapping years and identifies differences based on customerNumber and year fields.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=169byniFp_tXTn6xvlo-e_eSW7Ax_lcJn">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1608" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1609</div></th><td class="s6">Google OAuth2 Credentials Auto-Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of OAuth2 credentials for multiple Google services (Docs, Sheets, Slides, Drive, Gmail, Calendar, Contacts) in n8n using Google JSON client info and user email. Simplifies tedious manual setup with n8n API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PpVCjlxQRpjyZ8PPJMMOL1W7V_GsrMZM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1609" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1610</div></th><td class="s6">Sign-in IPs Report &amp; Email Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieval of sign-in events via SaaS Alerts API, deduplicates IP data, converts to CSV, encodes base64, and emails the report using SMTP2Go. Includes an auth form for API key and email input for last 24h sign-in IP info delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eAJ4bd0fhUa4kwdgeUGur4AIByxiwvr1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1610" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1611</div></th><td class="s6">Daily ProductHunt AI Launch Monitor</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow monitors daily ProductHunt launches related to specified products like AI Agents using Airtop API for web extraction, and sends the curated list via Slack. Automates product discovery using ProductHunt, Airtop API, and Slack integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1J4pXYvq6xL7QLQDPwOSL5MfFFDmG6dJv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1611" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1612</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable Query &amp; AI Response in Obsidian</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow links Airtable data with Obsidian notes using OpenAI GPT-4 through an AI Agent. It automates querying Airtable and sends AI-processed answers back into Obsidian via webhook, enhancing note-taking with dynamic database insights.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1PJ4eydQofR8ElZkXlfsArXHbByh7jpUo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1612" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1613</div></th><td class="s6">GetBible Scripture Retrieval</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches Bible verses from the GetBible API v2 using JSON input with references, translation, and version. It processes scripture references, queries the API, and returns standardized scripture texts for dynamic integration in faith-based apps or projects.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1U3H4fuHOoNaKsWP-68LO0oSqdTrif3_b">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1613" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1614</div></th><td class="s6">Text-to-Speech Voice Call Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates text-to-speech phone calls using the ClickSend API triggered by form submissions. Users input text, recipient number, voice, and language. Built with n8n using HTTP Request and formTrigger nodes for easy voice message delivery and notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Xi0zqMQLy5ztKfL6WteTcc0ISQ_2hAdz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1614" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1615</div></th><td class="s6">Personal Data Extractor with Self-Hosted LLM</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that extracts structured personal data from chat messages using a self-hosted Mistral NeMo LLM via Ollama API. It includes auto-fixing output parser and JSON schema validation to ensure precise extraction of user info like name, contact, and communication details.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15K_tHbdp91tYVxiv9Qk4M6890Ir6605W">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1615" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1616</div></th><td class="s6">Icypeas Email Verification (Single)</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to verify a single email using Icypeas API. It authenticates with API key, secret, and user ID using HMAC-SHA1 signature, then sends a POST request to Icypeas email verification endpoint. Useful for integrating email validation in automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13yV1U4pydPjdp1cNXT_PblGtf4nP54G2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1616" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1617</div></th><td class="s6">Amazon Keyword Suggestion &amp; Storage Workflow</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates fetching Amazon keyword suggestions via Amazon&#39;s Completion API, cleans and aggregates keywords, and stores them in Airtable. Utilizes n8n HTTP Request, Airtable integration, and JavaScript code node for keyword processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-YnjNP-RJyW6TMGxlVEi3IQ3K_oxVD_p">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1617" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1618</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Text Extraction &amp; HTML to PDF</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using CustomJS PDF Toolkit nodes to convert HTML to PDF and extract text from PDFs via URL or direct input. It automates PDF content extraction and generation steps with manual trigger initiation, suitable for document processing tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11tc9890_PSSC_upMnSMBKwQmfyMb6ukW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1618" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1619</div></th><td class="s6">TechCrunch Latest Articles Scraper</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow scraping the latest 20 articles from TechCrunch using HTTP Request and HTML parsing nodes. Extracts post metadata, detailed content, images, and timestamps for use in content aggregation or analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1f-HDUn6PsRMdcpMzaBV0DNyLK9qsZSzR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1619" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1620</div></th><td class="s6">Monday.com Subitem &amp; Linked Items Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that integrates with Monday.com API to retrieve an item&#39;s details, its subitems, and linked pulses by parsing specific columns. Uses JavaScript code nodes, splitOut, and API calls to fetch and merge detailed relational data from Monday.com boards.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZkYGZuyz2PgSF_30X1KZ7X1HYyutwQYM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1620" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1621</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Merge Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading two PDF files via HTTP requests, merges them using a custom JS PDF toolkit in n8n, and writes the merged PDF to disk. Utilizes n8n&#39;s HTTP Request, custom JS node, and file system nodes for seamless PDF processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1y45l4o8AULtqeF8-f7pz4tBPcfVFN7gl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1621" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1622</div></th><td class="s6">Youtube Podcast Discord AI Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates a Discord AI assistant using Google Gemini chat and Langchain memory. It responds to user questions with context-aware answers about &#39;Presting Podcasts&#39; YouTube videos, integrating webhook input and formatting replies for Discord.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YBpZg4vBFb7tNNgC9HJte0nMSkzP-ApP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1622" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1623</div></th><td class="s6">Namesilo Bulk Domain Availability Checker</td><td class="s7">Automates checking domain name availability in bulk using Namesilo API. Supports batches up to 200 domains with rate-limit handling. Outputs results as Excel file. Built with n8n workflow using HTTP Request, JavaScript code, Wait, and Convert to Excel nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1t7GnW8qxsiVQEDOlcIov6RuCGLXQOFQa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1623" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1624</div></th><td class="s6">Forward Netflix Emails via Gmail and Mailjet</td><td class="s7">Automates forwarding Netflix emails from a Gmail account to multiple recipients using Gmail API and Mailjet. Detects Netflix emails via Gmail trigger, splits recipient list, and sends personalized forwards via Mailjet SMTP API for seamless multi-recipient delivery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1s8q0_nCecvDiW5dOHTj_bn6X7ZqTB-A7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1624" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1625</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Posting to X via Airtop &amp; n8n</td><td class="s7">Automatically post text content on x.com using Airtop API and n8n workflow automation. It creates a browser session, opens X, types a post, and publishes it. Triggered via form submission or another workflow for seamless marketing updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AaicB1KSR_beNgpNlgBMHFR4xiPrNW8g">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1625" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1626</div></th><td class="s6">API Uptime Monitor with SMS Alert</td><td class="s7">Automates API uptime checks using scheduled HTTP requests and Twilio SMS alerts when the API status code is not 200. Built with n8n automation, leveraging HTTP Request and Twilio nodes for timely service downtime notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GWtDFvRREpoeNioTudh49F5YGgub0Bom">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1626" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1627</div></th><td class="s6">AI Financial Chart Analyzer Backend</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow backend for a Chrome extension that uses OpenAI&#39;s GPT-4o-mini model to analyze stock or cryptocurrency chart images sent via webhook. It provides simple, novice-friendly technical market analysis with disclaimers. Tech stack: n8n, OpenAI API, webhook integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qGU87sh_tFUXNG5-M7IUikX6fLRssr7v">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1627" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1628</div></th><td class="s6">Conditional Retry Workflow with Known Error Handling</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow for retrying failed API calls up to 3 times, except for specific known errors (e.g., &#39;could not be found&#39;). Uses wait and counter logic with Manual Trigger, If and Set nodes to manage retries and error handling, ensuring robust error flow control.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1y-5ytIBWuPq_l0WZ23ZtObKBHjNp1ZXD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1628" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1629</div></th><td class="s6">Perplexity AI Q&amp;A with n8n</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates querying Perplexity AI&#39;s chat completions API using HTTP requests, setting system and user prompts, and cleaning responses. It uses generic HTTP header authentication and enables retrieval of AI-driven answers filtered by search domains, ideal for dynamic Q&amp;A automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rmIeFhdmL6d_x1XqpgJXDSJjjCfKXqtt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1629" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1630</div></th><td class="s6">Multi-file Zip Compressor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that compresses multiple input files (images, PDFs, CSV/XLSX) into a single ZIP archive. Uses n8n&#39;s Execute Workflow Trigger, JavaScript code node for binary handling, and Compression node to produce a dated zip file as output.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gLfw1HQKFx4bl2N831nlHdSoglzXigBY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1630" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1631</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Keyword-Based Community Topic Tracker</td><td class="s7">Automates tracking of new topics matching a keyword on the n8n community forum using n8n workflows. Integrates HTTP API requests to n8n community search, Google Sheets for data storage, and optional Slack and email notifications. Ideal for monitoring community discussions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u8L6ua7sH8B0ajXDwjK7xluZ0z_tkebb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1631" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1632</div></th><td class="s6">Multi-Image Upload to Instagram &amp; TikTok</td><td class="s7">Automates uploading multiple images to Instagram and TikTok using the Upload-Post API. It fetches images, renames binary data for upload, merges files, and sends multipart-form requests with API key authorization, simplifying cross-platform social media posts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OiXB4WqggrLCZjbjGX6js27PUmlvsEf7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1632" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1633</div></th><td class="s6">Git Commit and Push Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates adding files, committing with a message, and pushing changes to a Git repository using n8n&#39;s Git nodes, triggered manually to streamline version control operations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1v5OAZzF_dne0fZMSk7W4dKiFE7ippgWf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1633" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1634</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Export to Google Drive</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves all workflows from an n8n instance via HTTP API with Basic Auth, processes the data, and uploads each workflow as individual JSON files to Google Drive. Uses n8n core nodes including HTTP Request, Cron, Function, Merge, and Google Drive integration for automated daily export.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CkuglcPT9LxPNUJ1e6zT0mRJEVkkvmTa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1634" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1635</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail Bulk Delete Automation</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that connects to Gmail via OAuth2, retrieves all emails excluding chats and unsubscribe content, and deletes them in batches of 100. Automates inbox cleanup using Gmail API within n8n automation platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cEeLVqCBmn1jFqwp6Gjw6tvMwo3tTwM5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1635" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1636</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Weather Updates via Gotify</td><td class="s7">Automates sending daily weather updates for Berlin at 9 AM using n8n. Utilizes OpenWeatherMap API to fetch current temperature and Gotify API to deliver messages. Ideal for users wanting automated, timely weather notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tFE6klnyjH3a3d0cYr9aKCilsU9Q_Ylb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1636" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1637</div></th><td class="s6">Strapi Entry CRUD Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates creating, updating, and retrieving blog posts in Strapi CMS using n8n. Utilizes n8n&#39;s Strapi nodes with manual trigger, Set nodes for data, and sequential API operations to streamline content management workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KpAetQHe_OYOie2W_UloZGcUUFKMeY0o">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1637" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1638</div></th><td class="s6">Plex Qbittorrent Throttle Automator</td><td class="s7">Automates bandwidth throttling of qBittorrent based on Plex media playback events using n8n workflow. Integrates Plex webhook triggers, qBittorrent API authentication, and speed limit toggling to optimize network usage during media consumption.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TUaBPH-IquFhqBSJQIY2KiMXG4yjcvdf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1638" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1639</div></th><td class="s6">Netlify Deploy Failure Alert to Slack</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on Netlify deploy failures and sends detailed alerts to a Slack channel. Integrates Netlify webhook events with Slack API to notify teams about deployment errors instantly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1s8U06l8Mq2aoiBNf-HMQxnZhh5aFCjir">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1639" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1640</div></th><td class="s6">Image Text Extraction and Logging Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading an image, extracting embedded text using AWS Rekognition OCR, processing the text with custom logic, and appending results to Google Sheets. Uses AWS Rekognition API, HTTP Request node, and Google Sheets API with OAuth2 for easy text extraction and data logging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KcGzBeOpbYLpdfPoeuHrdBbV-OiPceaT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1640" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1641</div></th><td class="s6">Random Cocktail Suggestion to Mattermost</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow triggers via a POST webhook, fetches a random cocktail recipe from TheCocktailDB API, and sends a formatted message with recipe details and image to a Mattermost channel. Integrates webhook, HTTP Request, and Mattermost API for cocktail recommendations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AXnaK8BQ8yfg7SK17hN15wBhYLMIXJYN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1641" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1642</div></th><td class="s6">SWIFT Code Scraper &amp; MongoDB Importer</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating extraction of banking SWIFT codes by country from theswiftcodes.com. Uses HTTP Request &amp; HTML Extract nodes for scraping, uProc API for country normalization, and MongoDB for storing parsed data. Efficiently handles pagination and batch processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JUzX7QfH6iVOqa9mXjmhdc30gFmxDjhv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1642" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1643</div></th><td class="s6">Quick Base Record CRUD Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates creating, updating, and retrieving records in Quick Base using n8n workflows. Utilizes Quick Base API and n8n built-in nodes like Set and Manual Trigger to manage database records efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13Yo4NEFj4vn7cyaTBHIQ-gU2hh4LDLKZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1643" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1644</div></th><td class="s6">Multilingual Telegram Welcome Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram API and NocoDB to manage multilingual user interactions. It welcomes new users, provides help, and updates user language preferences, using Telegram Trigger, HTTP requests, and language dictionaries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LStMqb8Spb085JQd6Y2XgWHQYE3Nd5QQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1644" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1645</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Weather Bot with R Visualization</td><td class="s7">An automated Telegram bot workflow built in n8n that fetches weather data from OpenWeatherMap API for major European cities, processes it into CSV, runs an R script to generate ggplot2 weather charts, and sends the image back to users on Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1DAZrhoH1bpF8szZWpIPe-crO7xLo5Pkt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1645" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1646</div></th><td class="s6">Gmail JSON Email to CSV Exporter</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of the latest JSON email from Gmail using OAuth2, processes its binary data, and exports content into a CSV spreadsheet file using n8n&#39;s Gmail and spreadsheet nodes. Ideal for email-driven data workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=174tAQ4TZQDOhhJX_kNnWSVShbGev19bO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1646" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1647</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram to Facebook Ad Interest Exporter</td><td class="s7">Automates extraction of Facebook ad interests from Telegram messages using Telegram API, Facebook Graph API v17.0, and n8n. Extracts hashtagged interests, queries Facebook, formats data into CSV, and sends back via Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iRYlWb-xwDBv-rFo8-hO9w47ooOvj4lV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1647" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1648</div></th><td class="s6">Send Gmail Email with Embedded Image</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Gmail API, HTTP Request, and base64 encoding to send an email with embedded images. Fetches an image from a URL, converts it to base64, composes MIME email with inline image, and sends via Gmail OAuth2.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1y5imDjlIrFMHh84d4uV5Bds09EVqFzpU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1648" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1649</div></th><td class="s6">DigitalOcean Droplet Snapshot Manager</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates DigitalOcean Droplet snapshot management using the DigitalOcean API. It runs every 48 hours, lists droplets, deletes oldest snapshots if over 4, and creates new snapshots to maintain up-to-date backups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cLbg1dufVcri3ltHNVqy6IcTXa4qAyTy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1649" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1650</div></th><td class="s6">Scheduled SharePoint List Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that periodically retrieves SharePoint list items using OAuth 2.0 client credentials flow. It integrates Microsoft Azure AD for token generation and SharePoint REST API for data fetching, automating secure SharePoint data access.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OvE6M4O_tM1cKRo2pBvVPYRxP9GT3cxT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1650" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1651</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Sticker Info Responder</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating Telegram bot interactions to detect and respond with sticker info. Uses Telegram Trigger node and conditional logic to reply with sticker details or a no-sticker message, enhancing Telegram bot user engagement easily.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZN49QSc1JhxFi0MJ_hVeguIHAkKx4kpt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1651" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1652</div></th><td class="s6">Auto Website Screenshot from Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow triggers on new rows added in a Google Sheets document containing URLs. It captures website screenshots using a custom PDF Toolkit node and stores the images in a specified Google Drive folder. Useful for automated visual content archiving.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14MFVKeX-onbixuzRb9X719Kjkp1dpaFV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1652" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1653</div></th><td class="s6">Postgres Sensor Data Ingestion</td><td class="s7">Automates ingestion of simulated sensor data into a PostgreSQL database every minute using n8n. Utilizes Cron for scheduling, a Function node to generate random humidity sensor readings with timestamps, and PostgreSQL node to insert data. Ideal for IoT data pipelines.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WY9QYSNkTLn-jypQDjkOtTT03Yx9AGdL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1653" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1654</div></th><td class="s6">Zendesk Support Updates Listener</td><td class="s7">Workflow listens for real-time support ticket updates via Zendesk API using n8n Zendesk Trigger node to automate support workflows and notifications. It captures events as they happen to streamline customer support processes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bzp7tCyiFyfO_N0UG4O-4hTMFx8Of1uj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1654" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1655</div></th><td class="s6">BetterStack Log Sender Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to send log messages from other workflows to BetterStack Logs via HTTP POST with header authentication. Supports manual testing and embedding. Utilizes n8n executeWorkflow nodes and HTTP Request node for log forwarding.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ly1VHBA3PHtmSSYxCoSEB8EH0rLavv_2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1655" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1656</div></th><td class="s6">Mautic CRM User Sync &amp; Tagging</td><td class="s7">Automates user management in Mautic CRM via webhook-triggered workflow. Processes student data, finds or creates contacts, updates details, handles subscription tags, and manages marketing email opt-in status using Mautic OAuth2 API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_ByU0VFye4lwnzDAgds3hvLUQ5jBRi_6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1656" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1657</div></th><td class="s6">Brave Search via Telegram Bot</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow integrates Brave Search API with Telegram using MCP community nodes. Users send /brave commands to a Telegram bot, triggering Brave search queries and receiving results directly in chat. Tech stack: n8n, MCP client for Brave API, Telegram node, JavaScript code for query cleaning.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IuIuuPt8k2tlXuKGG3xD7FZ1u54HmqMm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1657" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1658</div></th><td class="s6">Philips Hue Light On &amp; Brightness Set</td><td class="s7">Automation workflow using n8n to turn on a Philips Hue light and set its brightness via Philips Hue API. Triggered manually, it sets brightness level to 90 for light ID 123. Useful for smart home lighting control with Philips Hue OAuth2 integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=168RauzYdk_Gqx67BVSM99Racv3nSoMjG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1658" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1659</div></th><td class="s6">CSV to Google Sheets COVID Data Importer</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading COVID-19 testing CSV data from ECDC, filters for DACH region in 2023, adds unique keys, and uploads to a specified Google Sheets document via Google Sheets API using n8n workflow nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fuXPIbpRjM5AEiYPhUAKjd8R04zBIdsH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1659" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1660</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Tron USDT Wallet Blacklist Checker</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Telegram and Tronscan API to verify if a TRON USDT wallet address is blacklisted. Users send wallet addresses via Telegram; the system validates format, queries the Tronscan stablecoin blacklist API, and replies with the blacklist status.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1t4GczfOwM6Ki8X4f5RlrPIezQS4izpBw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1660" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1661</div></th><td class="s6">Luma AI Webhook to Airtable Video Logger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that captures POST requests from Luma AI&#39;s video generation webhook, extracts video and thumbnail URLs, and automatically updates Airtable records with this data. Integrates Luma AI webhook, Airtable API, and conditional data validation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jd4XWoLEZ_giTHwuN_YmDg3Jgo53_pRr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1661" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1662</div></th><td class="s6">PDFMonkey Callback PDF Downloader</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates PDFMonkey webhook callbacks by receiving PDF generation status, verifying success, and downloading the generated PDF via HTTP request. Integrates PDFMonkey API and n8n webhook for seamless PDF retrieval upon generation completion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B-4KuBN9xCTyBTDd6EjYyrsbAlnmxplO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1662" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1663</div></th><td class="s6">Paul Graham Essays Scraper &amp; Summarizer</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping of Paul Graham&#39;s latest essays from his website using HTTP and HTML nodes, then summarizes the top 3 essays with GPT-4 via OpenAI API and LangChain nodes in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sps28Hdqw3D4ll4mxIlib_iPei1d6QtY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1663" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1664</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Gratitude Reminder via LINE</td><td class="s7">An automated daily reminder system that sends personalized gratitude prompts at 9 PM via LINE. Utilizes Azure OpenAI for varied message generation and reformats output for LINE Push API. Helps build positive habits using n8n workflow and AI.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xD98H5BRr4hU7Sp3njnRry_5Ex73SvYV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1664" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1665</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Calvin &amp; Hobbes Comic Auto Poster</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching daily Calvin and Hobbes comic images via HTTP request, extracts the image URL using LangChain info extractor, translates dialogues to English and Korean with OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and posts the results to Discord daily using a webhook. Uses n8n, OpenAI API, and Discord webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vjTL4ey19Y1rY7PyRbW82EyVsyHsDbX4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1665" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1666</div></th><td class="s6">Squarespace Blog to Google Sheets Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching blog and event collections from a Squarespace site via HTTP API with pagination, and appends or updates the data in Google Sheets using Google Sheets OAuth2. Scheduled or manual trigger allows easy syncing of blog content to spreadsheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hvhsu8A6bq1TJ9QgsvlVu_uaXBC7Lr6R">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1666" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1667</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Video Captioning with json2video API</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates adding captions to videos using the json2video API. It accepts video URL and dimensions, sends a video captioning request, polls for completion, and outputs the captioned video link and details. Uses HTTP Request, Wait, and If nodes for automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1euhq9ra--qhPs-43i33tcxwUMiwPHjMl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1667" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1668</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Banner Auto-Updater</td><td class="s7">Automates updating your Twitter profile banner by downloading an image from Unsplash and uploading it to Twitter using OAuth1 authentication. Utilizes HTTP Request nodes in n8n for image retrieval and Twitter API interaction, triggered manually.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1n24syrYJjT7CWHwUurEXkA2nxGfFYgmb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1668" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1669</div></th><td class="s6">Monthly Absence Summary Email Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates monthly extraction of absence data (holidays &amp; illness) from Google Calendar, summarizes days absent per person, and emails payroll. Built with n8n using Google Calendar API, cron scheduler, JavaScript code nodes, and SMTP email.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eN-QvSqK0Qao1Inwsx76INlUTJpy-8Ut">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1669" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1670</div></th><td class="s6">Nostr #damus AI Report with Gmail &amp; Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates analysis of Nostr #damus hashtag threads using Google Gemini LLM, aggregates themes, and generates detailed AI reports sent via Gmail and Telegram for community insights and engagement.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1S2eXNUmzNmGgOOpRC8zSVnZRBUTuvgwj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1670" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1671</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow: Export Executions to CSV</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves all workflow executions via the n8n API, converts the data into a CSV file for easy parsing, and prepares it for export to a cloud storage or other destination. Utilizes n8n manual trigger, n8n API node, and file conversion tools.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gMjbL6hXCLTSBq78escw-S2ILvCH2BJj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1671" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1672</div></th><td class="s6">YogiAI Daily Yoga Pose Reminder</td><td class="s7">Automates daily yoga pose reminders via Line using Azure OpenAI and Google Sheets. Fetches weighted random poses from Sheets, formats messages with AI, creates Line Flex messages with images, and sends scheduled notifications. Tech: n8n, Azure OpenAI, Google Sheets, Line Messaging API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xOETnVoiW18SJ7X5Zc1g2ucXQgole64p">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1672" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1673</div></th><td class="s6">Web Page Content Scraper via FireCrawl API</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow fetches webpage content in markdown format using FireCrawl API. It accepts a URL as input, triggers an HTTP POST request to FireCrawl, and extracts markdown content for reuse. Ideal for automating web data extraction leveraging n8n and FireCrawl API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1quu88EEGT1CJv88AYV8vl_spVoEJI-2S">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1673" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1674</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets &amp; MySQL Event Inquiry Sync</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating sync between Google Sheets (Google Sheets API) and MySQL database for event inquiries. It compares datasets, upserts new records, updates statuses, and schedules regular 30-min interval checks on weekdays. Ideal for managing event form data efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tx_veBxYhVIAsMW4zGn1b8X4XAq9P6JT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1674" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1675</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Image Generation Webhook</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow exposes a webhook that triggers OpenAI&#39;s image generation API using a user-provided prompt via URL query. It returns the generated image directly in the browser. Tech stack: n8n, OpenAI API, webhook, URL query parameters.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XIMAqj-mozqn8yxfQEP8p0NzhdRnw0sV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1675" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1676</div></th><td class="s6">ProspectLens Company Research Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates company data enrichment by integrating Google Sheets with ProspectLens API using n8n. Retrieves detailed company profiles and updates sheets with firmographic info, funding, traffic, and location, streamlining business research workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LMsHij-48SFesNR7bnuKX3gj5utywzd3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1676" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1677</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Campaign Image Uploader</td><td class="s7">Automates updating Shopify theme assets by uploading campaign images via Shopify GraphQL and REST APIs using n8n. Integrates Baserow webhook for triggers and supports dynamic content injection into Liquid templates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Mn8rnCHPx6gHzClhlvgn-HZGjaT_44hq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1677" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1678</div></th><td class="s6">CSV to Excel Converter from URL</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading a CSV file from a public URL, imports it using n8n&#39;s HTTP Request and Spreadsheet nodes, and converts it to an Excel (.xlsx) file. Utilizes n8n native nodes with no external APIs, ideal for data processing automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UbSqSpMtiScp5584OQNHuS3WpS4G9mFZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1678" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1679</div></th><td class="s6">Bluesky Image Post Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates posting image posts on Bluesky by downloading images from URLs, uploading as blobs via Bluesky API, and creating posts with captions. Utilizes HTTP Request and Code nodes in n8n for session creation, image handling, and feed posting.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YDIUfp_0mcNe5oD17J8tQNfSiTFAgj25">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1679" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1680</div></th><td class="s6">2D Image to 3D Model Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates converting 2D images to 3D models using Fal.run AI API, Google Sheets for input/output management, and Google Drive for storing 3D files. Periodically checks image status, updates results in sheets, and uploads final .glb 3D models.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rUsLlg90931LE_u4c8enDKReQOuBxn2P">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1680" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1681</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets to Shopware 6 Manufacturer Import</td><td class="s7">Automates importing multiple product manufacturers from Google Sheets into Shopware 6 using Shopware&#39;s API. Utilizes Google Sheets API, OAuth2 authentication, and custom JavaScript for multi-language translations and logo uploads for seamless e-commerce management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1a3E09PJTNFquIk--uXPeXGdWTb4dNy-0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1681" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1682</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Nodes Update Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates checking and updating outdated nodes in n8n workflows using n8n API and Gmail for summary emails. Identifies outdated nodes, prepends symbols, optionally adds updated nodes to canvas, and notifies via Gmail. Helps maintain workflow health.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1geh45O1J7t6nMvP5GR3143pW3-6H9T57">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1682" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1683</div></th><td class="s6">Zammad User Role Update via Excel</td><td class="s7">Automates updating user roles in Zammad helpdesk by processing Excel data sourced via HTTP. Utilizes n8n workflow nodes including HTTP Request, Excel extraction, and data merging to sync user roles based on email matching. Requires Zammad API with Bearer token.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VgW5zr6L8y_4CPopNXSDOwh4LJ0Pu1jB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1683" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1684</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Cloner Between Instances</td><td class="s7">Automates cloning of n8n workflows from one instance to another using n8n API and HTTP requests. Syncs workflows and assigns them to projects, leveraging native n8n nodes and API calls for efficient workflow migration between environments.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SB7oAwzbBZvuvu5nV41gAAOZ6Vwgn4op">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1684" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1685</div></th><td class="s6">Post WordPress Blog via XML-RPC HTTP Request</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to post blog entries on Wordpress.com using XML-RPC protocol via HTTP Request node. It uses JavaScript code to prepare XML payload, handles XML response, and supports posting with a manual trigger. Tech stack: n8n, Wordpress XML-RPC API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sfAFCEeQZ4j5WE9qcQd3W9_9flEK_7Qf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1685" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1686</div></th><td class="s6">WhatsApp Echo Bot via Meta API</td><td class="s7">Automates WhatsApp messaging using Meta&#39;s WhatsApp API with n8n. Verifies webhook, listens for incoming messages, checks message presence, and echoes text back to the sender. Ideal for building interactive WhatsApp bots with webhook and API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10IW6FVieMFa2zHLN0Evokd2B9xgdqqMe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1686" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1687</div></th><td class="s6">Monday.com Full Item Data Fetcher</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to fetch comprehensive data for a specific Monday.com board item, including all columns, subitems, and board relations. Utilizes Monday.com API nodes, JavaScript code nodes for data processing, and merging/aggregation nodes for structured JSON output.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sBjVGveJkgSdxBa-Y8lqWDYqgv0puakg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1687" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1688</div></th><td class="s6">Bitrix24 Task Widget with Webhook Integration</td><td class="s7">Automates Bitrix24 task widget app installation and task data retrieval using webhooks, HTTP requests, and file handling within n8n. Integrates with Bitrix24 REST API to manage widget placement, installation responses, and display task details dynamically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1L5_HVAW2lpZUGS0QCSgArfVNFXPQCTgz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1688" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1689</div></th><td class="s6">Taiwan Agricultural Market Data to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching sheep quotation data from Taiwan&#39;s Ministry of Agriculture API (data.moa.gov.tw) for specified dates and markets, then appends parsed data into Google Sheets using Google Sheets API via OAuth2. Aids agricultural data tracking and analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1GKcSzHwrgzJ9iZHMZPLtJACJL99CK2g9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1689" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1690</div></th><td class="s6">Generate llms.txt from Screaming Frog CSV</td><td class="s7">Automate creation of llms.txt files from Screaming Frog website crawl CSVs. Uses n8n nodes, optional OpenAI GPT-4o-mini text classifier, and file processing to filter, format, and generate AI-ready text files describing site content for LLM training or analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B7XmpGKhb_I_P7FOWhCBn3Jo92GbdnTu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1690" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1691</div></th><td class="s6">Ollama Chat Integration with Llama 3.2</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow integrating Ollama API with Llama 3.2 model for chat message processing. Uses LangChain nodes including chat trigger, LLM chain, and structured response formatting to handle and respond to chat prompts as JSON objects.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1L_Vrbpn8qQCqcM40MNFlzSwboOpHD34k">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1691" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1692</div></th><td class="s6">Reddit n8n Posts Classification &amp; Summary</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching recent n8n-related Reddit posts, filters by upvotes and date, classifies relevance with OpenAI, then summarizes content. Uses Reddit API and OpenAI API, aiming to monitor and categorize discussions about n8n.io efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SOm4RcmM58zSAIWmc72JB4Xo-vJmJ7lp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1692" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1693</div></th><td class="s6">Icypeas Bulk Email Search Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates bulk email search with Icypeas API using Google Sheets. Reads names and companies from a sheet, authenticates via custom JS with API key/secret, and triggers POST requests for email search results. Tech: n8n, Google Sheets API, Icypeas API, Node.js crypto.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wHxhC0mpGwg6I2HoE6ZiYSfNg80aoVyc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1693" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1694</div></th><td class="s6">Monthly Event Scraper &amp; Email Newsletter</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping of monthly event listings from a location-specific website using HTTP requests and HTML extraction; processes event data, formats it into an HTML email, and sends via Gmail. Ideal for keeping informed about local events monthly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16zcLaSE-OlKWTynh0QqftEpSkhr5YoB0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1694" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1695</div></th><td class="s6">Automated n8n Workflow Backup to Dropbox</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates backing up current workflows by exporting them as JSON files to Dropbox, organizing backups into folders, and purging backups older than 30 days. It uses n8n API, Dropbox API, and date-time nodes for scheduling and maintenance.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13YPljNEYZcmmFsbknoc7YSmPOTSlhZHY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1695" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1696</div></th><td class="s6">Email to HTML Webpage via GitHub &amp; Telegram</td><td class="s7">Automates converting incoming IMAP emails into private GitHub Gist HTML pages and sends a Telegram notification with a link. Uses IMAP for email, GitHub API for gist creation/deletion, and Telegram Bot API for notifications and message lifecycle management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1C_HToVtENDXkD-pr7bezfEmvzyrnaURt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1696" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1697</div></th><td class="s6">Discord Member Role Filter with Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching Discord server members using Discord Bot API, filters by role, and tracks progress in Google Sheets. Useful for managing member lists and roles with n8n integration of Discord API and Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xHZikVDEGJeXZxty6E2PmLiENkmjgqOa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1697" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1698</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Outdated Node Checker</td><td class="s7">Checks n8n workflows for nodes with outdated versions by comparing each node&#39;s type and version to the latest available via the n8n API. Uses n8n&#39;s HTTP Request, Aggregate, If, and Code nodes with n8n API key authentication to identify nodes needing updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13cZ-WY18ko9PcFdapEteCriJIDOHathL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1698" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1699</div></th><td class="s6">Contabo VPS Snapshot Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates daily backup snapshots for Contabo VPS instances using Contabo API, UUIDGenerator for unique request IDs, and n8n nodes. Handles authorization, instance listing, snapshot checking, deletion, and creation with scheduled and manual triggers.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HeDL_fQO-QZBhkQ8EdfTZLBHIhlGnLFN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1699" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1700</div></th><td class="s6">Webhook.site to Local n8n Relay</td><td class="s7">Automates receiving public webhooks via webhook.site API and forwards them to a local n8n workflow. Utilizes schedule triggers, key-value storage (@horka.tv/n8n-nodes-storage-kv), HTTP requests, and custom JavaScript for filtering and processing. Ideal for testing and local webhook processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bJp3Kl6whwN9Y1Ti8n1ynGuNjUVMNgz5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1700" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1701</div></th><td class="s6">Fastmail Masked Email Management</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow leveraging Fastmail API to manage masked email addresses: create, update, delete, and list. It uses HTTP Request nodes with Fastmail JMAP API, a webhook secured by basic auth, and generates an interactive HTML table for email states.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1u6rqk83YIxnw6idIjKTttYgHgNFsnCuV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1701" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1702</div></th><td class="s6">Customer.io Unsubscribe Event Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses the Customer.io Trigger node to automatically capture and respond to customer unsubscribes in real time via Customer.io API, enabling automated actions upon unsubscribe events.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19pLZRmexUJvKvjiUyqv5rUXhg-ewEHDF">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1702" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1703</div></th><td class="s6">MP4 to Text Transcript with Eleven Labs API</td><td class="s7">Automates transcription of local MP4 video files into text using Eleven Labs speech-to-text API. Uses n8n workflow with local file reading and HTTP Request nodes for audio transcription, enabling seamless offline media processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UC6OIENfon24vWEYk6hzsVoLS1rvWitS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1703" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1704</div></th><td class="s6">Redis Locking Workflow for Webhook Concurrency</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Redis to implement distributed locking for webhook handling, preventing concurrent or duplicate executions. It parses Slack webhook payloads, checks and acquires Redis locks, conditionally executes workflows, and releases locks after completion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kNhZrrlpZtorzcWmXnaCNwxaLKi_mirh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1704" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1705</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Tag-to-Folder Workflow Organizer</td><td class="s7">Automates organization of n8n workflows by converting tags into folders via n8n API. Uses n8n HTTP Request, Form Trigger, and Code nodes to login, fetch tags, create folders, and move workflows. Simplifies project management for personal owned projects.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1saQmQOYoUI3lZG-dd2P0zfGxFW_sTn7J">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1705" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1706</div></th><td class="s6">Automated RSS to Google Sheets Updater</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that periodically reads RSS feed URLs from a Google Sheet, fetches and filters recent news (last 3 days), converts content from HTML to Markdown, updates and deletes entries in a Google Sheet to maintain fresh news data. Uses Google Sheets API, RSS feed reader, and custom JavaScript code.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ycAFNRKF8xrfvg_BWK5HKqwTCtcuqwrl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1706" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1707</div></th><td class="s6">Paul Graham Essays Scraper &amp; QA Chat</td><td class="s7">Automates scraping of Paul Graham&#39;s essays from his website, processes texts using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini, and stores embeddings in Milvus vector DB. Enables QA chat with the indexed essays via LangChain nodes in n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1iesehmoWWdSIkl_ZLszvJUiYAU2f5FKo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1707" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1708</div></th><td class="s6">Linux Filesystem MCP Server</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow implementing a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server for Linux filesystem. It enables remote MCP clients to list, search, read, create directories and files securely on the host machine using n8n&#39;s MCP trigger and Execute Command tools. Ideal for file management automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Qejysp1OHQyqLhERE3zpqC7guK6f1zIv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1708" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1709</div></th><td class="s6">SQLite MCP Server for Database CRUD</td><td class="s7">Self-hosted n8n workflow acting as an MCP server to securely manage SQLite DB via CRUD operations. Utilizes SQLite3 Node.js lib, MCP server trigger, and Code + custom workflow tools for read, insert, update. Ideal for business intelligence tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1elVDlMLwHCpEJK7lvpiGVV39fFdlBh2G">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1709" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1710</div></th><td class="s6">PayPal Payment Capture &amp; Template Delivery</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to handle PayPal NVP SOAP webhook for payment captures, fetch order details using PayPal API with OAuth2, filter specific product purchases, convert JSON template to file, and email the purchased workflow template to customers. Tech stack includes PayPal API, HTTP Requests, webhooks, and email node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1s4rwS_DefnuIDnK-TqcCGf5MvBWiI54_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1710" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1711</div></th><td class="s6">Retell Voice Agent Booking Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that connects Retell AI Voice Agents with custom logic via webhooks. It captures booking requests, processes data, and sends confirmation responses in real-time. Tech stack includes Retell AI, n8n webhook and respond nodes, with potential for API integrations and AI enhancements.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1p8bcYNmmnD6bfreWhTNaX4hlpmDV38OA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1711" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1712</div></th><td class="s6">Encrypted WhatsApp Flow Handler</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow for secure WhatsApp interactions using hybrid RSA-AES decryption. It decrypts encrypted webhook payloads, parses user state (&#39;screen&#39;), applies conditional routing, extracts appointment or seat data, then encrypts and responds via API. Utilizes n8n nodes, Node.js Crypto, and webhook integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-DHHCArNsi2w2zNqR3FLOYJdDEG1KIH3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1712" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1713</div></th><td class="s6">Google News RSS Decoder to Clean Article Links</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that reads Google News RSS feeds (customizable by language), decodes obfuscated Google News URLs via reverse-engineered POST requests, and outputs clean, direct article links. Uses RSS Feed, HTTP Request, HTML extraction, and JavaScript code nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17VzAAArlR0xqlbI_Hrts7JinmpPoni4X">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1713" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1714</div></th><td class="s6">Squarespace to Shopify Customer Sync via Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates conversion of Squarespace profile data to Shopify customer format using Google Sheets for data handling. Uses n8n webhook to receive submissions, processes data in batches, and updates Shopify customers and Squarespace profiles in Google Sheets seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1m012qrPJX_PPcDDBDqY9kF37oICvIj1z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1714" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1715</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Bluesky Thread Creator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that authenticates to Bluesky via API and automates creation of threaded posts (initial post, replies, siblings) on schedule. Uses Bluesky&#39;s xrpc API with HTTP Request and JavaScript code nodes to build and post multi-level conversation threads daily at 9 AM.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KYxs_0umKf1U4CdFLzoWMYKKBPh1pBTU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1715" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1716</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Price Tracker and Notifier</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates monitoring product prices across multiple web pages using HTTP requests and CSS selectors for data extraction. It compares current prices with stored data and sends email alerts via SMTP for price drops or extraction issues.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XNFgle9UYXD0Sz3xpQ4evN_dha9nU73G">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1716" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1717</div></th><td class="s6">Docker InfluxDB WHMCS API Backend</td><td class="s7">Automates Docker-based InfluxDB container management for WHMCS/WISECP. Uses n8n workflow with Webhook API (Basic Auth), SSH for Docker commands, Docker Compose, and nginx-proxy configs to deploy, start, stop, suspend, and monitor InfluxDB containers per client domain.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZwKMi84G3M4yeZwJtaX7YGNVbs7aOlgQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1717" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1718</div></th><td class="s6">Centroid Calculator for Vector Sets</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that receives vector arrays via webhook, validates uniform dimensions, computes their centroid by averaging each component, and returns the result. Uses n8n&#39;s Webhook, Set, Code, and Respond nodes for API-driven vector centroid calculations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dHLYL_040BkmOjK3SNooMwqPGumtx1SV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1718" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1719</div></th><td class="s6">Crop Image Anomaly Detection Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow detecting anomalous crop images using Voyage.ai embeddings and Qdrant vector search. It compares image embeddings to cluster medoids of a crops dataset and flags unknown or rare crops. Tech: Voyage AI API, Qdrant Cloud, Python code for scoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TspJRxpCP0pVGHjbUeGj1Nq_K-Cg-oiq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1719" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1720</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Links to Readeck &amp; Hoarder Bookmark Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching links from a specific Telegram channel using the Telegram Bot API and syncs new links to Readeck and Hoarder bookmark management platforms via their APIs, ensuring links are saved without duplication. Built with n8n workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15h5eli05AWHpG0gNUFuHLmLKDi_FP-gZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1720" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1721</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow AI Model Usage Tracker</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow fetches all n8n workflows via n8n API, filters nodes containing AI model references (modelId), and logs node and workflow details including AI model info into Google Sheets. It uses n8n API and Google Sheets API for centralized AI model usage tracking.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1f26WCz2RDhkJ_m35iy-Hq5UtLEvwS9gX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1721" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1722</div></th><td class="s6">Docker MinIO WHMCS API Deployment</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to deploy and manage MinIO Docker containers for WHMCS/WISECP integration. Utilizes SSH for Docker commands, Basic Auth API webhook, dynamic Docker Compose and NGINX config generation, and supports lifecycle actions like deploy, start, stop, suspend, and ACLs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Tz_P6-g3YdIL1jGpl-HReICjyL_HB5UW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1722" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1723</div></th><td class="s6">Zammad Data Export to Excel</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that exports users, roles, groups, and organizations from Zammad via API calls authenticated by token. It transforms data into universal objects and converts them into Excel files (XLSX). Ideal for helpdesk admin reporting and data management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ymJRMQwFue70hIJWB93eJFyh5T7k24Up">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1723" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1724</div></th><td class="s6">3-View Orthographic to Dynamic Video Converter</td><td class="s7">Automates conversion of three orthographic views into a rotating 3D-style video. Uses GPT-4o for front and side image generation and PiAPI&#39;s Kling model for dynamic video synthesis with rotation. Ideal for 3D visualization and animation workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1P4YYoPesfJBzxhZ0fN0aO8rfpZIOApgt">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1724" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1725</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable Markdown to HTML Converter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Airtable API and markdown node to convert video descriptions from markdown format stored in Airtable to HTML, then updating single or multiple Airtable records with the HTML content. Automates content formatting for Airtable video entries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MEpW2aurXCrD6F1FGZcgkxLiJNlyG3ss">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1725" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1726</div></th><td class="s6">PG&amp;E Daily Energy Cost Email Reporter</td><td class="s7">Automates daily login to PG&amp;E&#39;s mobile website to extract electricity and gas cost data, formats it into an HTML email, and sends it via Gmail. Uses n8n&#39;s AirTop nodes for browser automation and Gmail API for emailing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jQXEDi0HV2icDYhGvZY4RZoh7yWSrN37">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1726" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1727</div></th><td class="s6">Scaleway Servers Info Retrieval &amp; Filter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches and aggregates Scaleway instance and baremetal server details across multiple zones using Scaleway API. It supports dynamic filtering by tags, name, public IP, or zone and returns results via authenticated webhook. Built with HTTP Request, Code, Switch, and Webhook nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XzaoA8MMwsAIzZIx0SvvgDdBxwC4MhpW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1727" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1728</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Supabase AI Agent Manager</td><td class="s7">Automates management of AI agent interactions using n8n with Supabase as a vector store and data backend, integrating OpenAI embeddings for knowledge retrieval and Langchain MCP triggers for agent workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1C_WBVetzN5pchdWfzl2cuc_B4RC1xFFi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1728" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1729</div></th><td class="s6">OpenAI Chat Assistant with Country Capitals Tool</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI Assistant via LangChain to enable interactive chat. It includes custom tools for returning fictional countries&#39; capitals and listing them, plus a date/time tool. It automates conversational AI with dynamic data retrieval using JavaScript code nodes and summarization.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SmpOMZli1UgXGjueTNVa3g8pOpW8GC9u">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1729" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1730</div></th><td class="s6">Generate &amp; Save CSV User Lists with GPT-4</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses GPT-4 (OpenAI API) to generate mock user data in JSON, parses it, converts to CSV in batches, fixes UTF BOM issues, and saves files locally. Ideal for creating randomized CSV datasets quickly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Z3rpOZCYGaZQEiwJG-Bjq0HnAjWJ7vkV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1730" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1731</div></th><td class="s6">LINE BOT Receipt OCR to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates receipt image processing from LINE chat by extracting text via OCR Space API, then parsing transaction info. Uses LINE Messaging API, Google Drive for storage, and Google Sheets for recording data, enabling efficient financial record keeping.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17vSGnK-EGO1KYeUK7i3dpn0WMU6lhLCK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1731" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1732</div></th><td class="s6">Immich Docker Deployment API Backend</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow deploying and managing Immich Docker containers via API webhook. Integrates SSH for remote Docker commands. Supports container lifecycle, disk mounting, ACL management, NGINX config, and admin user operations. Designed for WHMCS/WISECP integration by PUQcloud.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rAU7qkQebltx1z85WMWXBMrI2zB4wLtP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1732" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1733</div></th><td class="s6">Dynamic Dropdown Form with Google Sheets Data</td><td class="s7">Automates updating an n8n form&#39;s dropdown field dynamically using values fetched from a Google Sheets document. Utilizes n8n API, Google Sheets node, and formTrigger for real-time dropdown updates, enabling seamless form customization and data-driven options.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14Xxr305V1gXIuhz2m3uYfgZcn-fzWtkC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1733" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1734</div></th><td class="s6">News Web Scraper with AI Summarization</td><td class="s7">Automates weekly scraping of news from Colt telecom site using HTML extraction and CSS selectors. Utilizes OpenAI GPT-4 API to generate concise summaries and technical keywords. Stores results in a NocoDB SQL database for easy management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IaH-W45edw9mNivA71KFXxp5IUkairK_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1734" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1735</div></th><td class="s6">Ollama LLM Chat Processor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that processes chat messages using Ollama&#39;s Llama 3.2 model via LangChain integration. It receives chat inputs, processes them through an LLM chain, and returns structured JSON responses. Requires Ollama API credentials and n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ffFtqV4pt42TnDvlUMGx7aDUKrBPRqll">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1735" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1736</div></th><td class="s6">Line + DALL·E Lego Style Image Transformer</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses LINE Messaging API and OpenAI&#39;s DALL·E to receive images via LINE, generate LEGO-style prompts with GPT-4o-mini, create LEGO-style images, and send them back to users. Integrates LINE webhook, HTTP requests, and OpenAI API for image manipulation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1o1_YWYQbAYweWGfW6ICTDr6bsRJnntJ4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1736" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1737</div></th><td class="s6">Google Maps Email Scraper</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating email extraction from Google Maps business listings. It uses HTTP requests to search Google Maps for queries, scrapes URLs and emails with regex, filters duplicates and irrelevant data, and saves results to Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kpcyw7V7YVkcysRNI6dG3_LpbIUTrmUA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1737" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1738</div></th><td class="s6">Bluesky Auto Welcome Message Sender</td><td class="s7">Automate sending personalized welcome DMs to new followers on Bluesky social. Uses Bluesky API to track followers, store follower data in JSON files, detect new followers, and send predefined private messages with links at hourly intervals.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VQTjOcydFb2SqAhoIVBm5RSCWFaXDz7r">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1738" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1739</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Magic Positioning AI</td><td class="s7">Automates dynamic positioning of nodes in n8n workflows using AI. Integrates n8n core nodes, OpenAI APIs (Chat and Embeddings), LangChain AI Agents, and a custom IA2S positioning API. Enables effortless and smart workflow layout management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10CpajiRbRc43P8qFRe9Q5yrlMhwh4WQ4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1739" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1740</div></th><td class="s6">Strava Activity Logger to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching the latest cycling activities from Strava via API every 2 hours, filters out already logged rides, and appends new activity data (distance, time, elevation, date, link) to a Google Sheets spreadsheet using n8n workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xU6WFRACLLSKZgPatiGUgkOa29pl1Fae">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1740" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1741</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Async Workflow Coordination Example</td><td class="s7">Demonstrates asynchronous workflow coordination in n8n using manual triggers, HTTP webhooks, wait nodes, and HTTP requests. Integrates with an external JokeAPI and simulates independent workflows communicating via resume URLs for joined execution flow handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gv2G9JRrIBGsIHYGf9AoWCz42AbUTeU8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1741" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1742</div></th><td class="s6">Ko-fi Payment Webhook Handler</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that receives Ko-fi payment webhooks, validates verification tokens, and categorizes payments into Donations, Subscriptions or Shop Orders for further automation. Uses n8n webhook, if and switch nodes for processing Ko-fi webhook JSON data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1muN-ltWBsQy0af5RmMvDFBaBMizitttI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1742" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1743</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Credential Transfer Between Instances</td><td class="s7">Workflow automates copying credentials from one n8n instance to another using n8n CLI exports, HTTP API POST requests with dynamic authentication, and user forms for selection. Utilizes n8n executeCommand, HTTP Request, Form, and Code nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SpimeqJPhpiAkeH2uJo8aDvtAuNVlDlO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1743" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1744</div></th><td class="s6">Todoist Task Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates creating new tasks in Todoist using n8n with manual trigger and Todoist API integration. Enables easy task management by adding tasks on demand through a simple workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QDMST_rEglny1ZpJD_JONTyFfqEvd2zM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1744" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1745</div></th><td class="s6">Merge Interviewers and Employee Records</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that merges interviewers&#39; scheduling data with employee records by matching unique IDs. Uses built-in function and merge nodes to convert and combine JSON arrays, enabling synchronized personnel and interview data management in workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jG28Y0sFbS4v0Lsj3o3K-WSJ149eTzuf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1745" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1746</div></th><td class="s6">CRM Contact Data to Spreadsheet</td><td class="s7">Automates loading mock HubSpot CRM contacts into a spreadsheet-like system. Uses n8n&#39;s manual trigger and function nodes to format data, ready for integration with Google Sheets, Airtable, or databases.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13hXBqps5bFwBSu8MHMdCJJXhTiA2e4er">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1746" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1747</div></th><td class="s6">Insert Row into Coda Table</td><td class="s7">Automates inserting data into a new row of a Coda table using n8n. Utilizes the Coda API and n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger and Set nodes to define column values and push them into a specified Coda document and table.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18BzEDkuFPh086ITFpmxIkNkYXC8_Qh-o">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1747" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1748</div></th><td class="s6">Google Slides Thumbnail Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Google Slides API via OAuth2 to retrieve all slides from a specific presentation and download their thumbnails automatically upon manual trigger. Ideal for quick slide image extraction and automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yG9tug6kmS7PveouUh70CbBTegcdoh3U">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1748" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1749</div></th><td class="s6">Chargebee New Customer Creation</td><td class="s7">Automates creating new customers in Chargebee using the Chargebee API and n8n workflow automation. Triggered manually, it captures customer details and creates a customer record in Chargebee for subscription billing management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16yHENaX0TkprKmcZdqjphltDv3ZeN3iH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1749" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1750</div></th><td class="s6">Emelia Replies to Mattermost Alerts</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that triggers on Emelia campaign replies and sends customized notifications to Mattermost channels. Uses Emelia API for webhook triggers and Mattermost API to post messages, enabling real-time campaign response alerts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12zSkAWFWho3cqO7js-sLe4cTHKOekKYm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1750" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1751</div></th><td class="s6">Workflow Update Notification via Mattermost</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers upon workflow updates and sends notifications to a Mattermost channel using Mattermost API. It includes a webhook that sets a message and a workflow trigger that detects updates, automating alert delivery for workflow changes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qZ0rGceHI7DNWCdKRk3Q08hrb_r13KGD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1751" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1752</div></th><td class="s6">Publish Storyblok Stories Starting with &#39;release&#39;</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches all Storyblok stories with names starting with &#39;release&#39; using Storyblok Management API and publishes them automatically. Utilizes manual trigger and Storyblok nodes to automate content deployment in Storyblok CMS.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1POgFBePYGL5zezkF8Nw6-4yM_BpArtyz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1752" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1753</div></th><td class="s6">Company Lookup by Name &amp; Country</td><td class="s7">Automates company data retrieval using n8n and Uproc API. Inputs company name and country, fetches detailed info via &#39;getCompanyByName&#39; tool, checks if the company exists. Useful for CRM enrichment and business research.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1j-AVt5yhzfgb8prIder64luZ3v2eNpew">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1753" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1754</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram GitHub Release Info Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates GitHub release retrieval via Telegram commands. Uses Telegram API to trigger workflow on messages containing &#39;/deploy&#39;, extracts version, then fetches GitHub release data using GitHub OAuth2 API. Ideal for quick release info checks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rt1d7otRdgSQctgeRFFUfxDTrRuPNrBc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1754" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1755</div></th><td class="s6">DNS Records Retrieval Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automating DNS record retrieval for a domain using uproc API and function node. Triggered manually, it creates a domain item, then queries DNS entries for automation and monitoring purposes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MbEycV-OSJ6rguvQhG9eKMkDsZOTwJWI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1755" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1756</div></th><td class="s6">Phone Number Validation Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that verifies phone numbers using the Uproc API. It creates a phone item, parses and validates the number, and checks validity in an automated flow triggered manually. Useful for data quality and contact management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NeC_GgmhcdnKgEBc-yo4ISsqTbwwsvo6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1756" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1757</div></th><td class="s6">Pipedrive Change Updates Listener</td><td class="s7">Automate receiving real-time updates for all changes in Pipedrive using the Pipedrive API and n8n&#39;s Pipedrive Trigger node. Ideal for syncing CRM updates or triggering workflows on any change inside Pipedrive accounts.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bQGWQZVRLoEC2eOFFnG0vYJ55wqo46jP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1757" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1758</div></th><td class="s6">Webhook to Netlify Site Creator</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of Netlify sites via POST webhook. Uses n8n, Netlify API; receives JSON with site title and triggers site creation. Useful for integrating custom site deployment workflows or CMS systems.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1eRwdygDuQCum74uA7C2UmJ9m1AdTXqNP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1758" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1759</div></th><td class="s6">Create Contact in Drift via API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates a new contact in Drift CRM using Drift API. It is triggered manually and requires Drift API credentials. Ideal for automating lead management and contact creation in sales processes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zjUaK-_jNSbOFY6gPCkaiRbjLnGPn8lD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1759" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1760</div></th><td class="s6">Create Company in Salesmate CRM</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to create a new company record in Salesmate CRM using manual trigger. Integrates with Salesmate API for CRM automation, ideal for sales and marketing teams to streamline company data entry.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1SGhQUb1DORYxBxpVVx9RZQVE8kdPhmlW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1760" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1761</div></th><td class="s6">Company Info Lookup via UpLead</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches detailed company information using the UpLead API. Triggered manually, it retrieves data for companies like Apple, enabling easy integration of business data enrichment in automation setups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ok7ncx2sgCgLVf4SK9DDVZi1HfTF8-EC">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1761" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1762</div></th><td class="s6">Facebook Profile Update to Mattermost Alert</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on Facebook user profile updates using Facebook Graph API and sends a formatted notification message to a specified Mattermost channel via Mattermost API, enabling real-time alerts on profile changes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ELFOiiCjsrfmA6k6aVMpTmnpOARrcf6P">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1762" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1763</div></th><td class="s6">Daily Image Joke Twitter Poster</td><td class="s7">Automates posting a daily image joke on Twitter at 17:00. Uses the Blablagues API to fetch joke images and text, retrieves the image file, then tweets with text and image using Twitter OAuth1 API. Scheduled via n8n Cron node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12QM4twjVG-T7tufwmwy0au161mIDCybG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1763" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1764</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Torrent Search &amp; Download</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating torrent search using &#39;torrent-search-api&#39; on KickassTorrents and Rarbg, integrates with Transmission RPC to start downloads, and uses Telegram bot for notifications. Enables POST webhook input with movie title to trigger torrent fetching and download.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LpOyHRbAZrfzxpthgIcwWDUP6M56P8i4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1764" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1765</div></th><td class="s6">Toggl New Time Entries Trigger</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses the Toggl Trigger node to automatically fetch new time entries from the Toggl API in real-time. Ideal for integrating time tracking data into other systems or automations, it simplifies monitoring and processing of time logs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fV9sQ6L1C_oIIgMPUggozWqDQrouwUEh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1765" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1766</div></th><td class="s6">XML Fetch Edit &amp; Dropbox Upload</td><td class="s7">Fetches XML from httpbin.org, converts it to JSON for modification (changes title), converts back to XML, and uploads to Dropbox. Uses n8n nodes: HTTP Request, XML, Set, and Dropbox API integration for XML data processing and cloud storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KmQPfJ5Io9aCGCD6NlnA_k5eUFaGIvm1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1766" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1767</div></th><td class="s6">Baserow Blog Releases to RSS Feed</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching and parsing Baserow blog release posts using HTTP requests and HTML extraction in n8n, then formats them into an RSS 2.0 feed served via webhook. Tech stack: n8n, HTTP Request, HTML Extract, JavaScript function nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wE7nuH8fyxYqH_nwS4T1VfBV_GdJzKto">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1767" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1768</div></th><td class="s6">Webhook HMAC SHA256 Token Validator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that receives webhook requests, uses a Crypto node to compute HMAC SHA256 of incoming crc_token values with a secret key, and sets the response token for validation. Uses n8n built-in Webhook, Crypto, and Set nodes for secure token verification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xwhPLwNs4KeHrRCdMt5CEF8iPquGCAtW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1768" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1769</div></th><td class="s6">Cocktail Instructions Translator with LingvaNex</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches a random cocktail recipe from TheCocktailDB API and translates its instructions into Italian using the LingvaNex translation API. Automates multilingual cocktail instruction delivery via API integration and workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cvpvhmQ5HDMqfrogUdFCmf8UyiHJm-S3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1769" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1770</div></th><td class="s6">Shopify Tag Updater on Onfleet Delayed Tasks</td><td class="s7">Automates updating Shopify product tags based on Onfleet delivery task delays using Onfleet webhook triggers and Shopify API integration to synchronize delivery status with product metadata.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rynerTKZwAdxtmUP8w3J1KitWZe3zi2j">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1770" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1771</div></th><td class="s6">CSV to JSON Spreadsheet Converter</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that converts a CSV spreadsheet file to JSON format using native n8n nodes: manual trigger, read binary file, spreadsheet file parser, binary data mover, and write binary file. Automates file format transformation locally.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EcddRgvkH7mXFljFyWZ9WPp20eMgsUM-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1771" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1772</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Merge Node Data Aggregation Demo</td><td class="s7">Demo workflow showcasing n8n&#39;s Merge node with code-generated datasets to simulate SQL joins and unions in data aggregation. It uses n8n core nodes (Code, Merge) illustrating inner, left, and union joins with example data for ingredients and band members.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FlnZdbDXQbAb4UM251YV6r7rKGqb6yNH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1772" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1773</div></th><td class="s6">ISS Position Updates via RabbitMQ</td><td class="s7">Automates retrieval of the International Space Station&#39;s position every minute via the &#39;wheretheiss.at&#39; API and publishes latitude, longitude, and timestamp updates to a RabbitMQ queue. Utilizes n8n Cron trigger, HTTP Request node, Set node, and RabbitMQ node for real-time messaging.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pnKy9RYCKxKF2q9lHaIY6qbWgWw6QNcU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1773" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1774</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Update Trigger to Home Assistant Light</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow triggering on any GitHub repository update using GitHub API. Automatically turns a specified Home Assistant light red via Home Assistant API. Ideal for developers wanting visual notifications of repo changes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B0HbvqEw9Q6rbJxlQT_F6MSrkJFzWwUX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1774" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1775</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Download and Merge Files</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that downloads multiple files from predefined URLs using HTTP Request nodes, then merges them into one item with multiple binary objects for streamlined processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yQW9RWcK-oyQvhf-F5tCXJCVnSiDAlC7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1775" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1776</div></th><td class="s6">AI-Powered Random Color Selector</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using LangChain and OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to return a random color excluding specified ones. It integrates a code tool for color selection and AI agent for processing chat inputs via webhook, ideal for AI-driven color choice automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wx6RxOxed7Hwx212H3GcKVs1ndxdvYnc">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1776" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1777</div></th><td class="s6">Add Event to Google Calendar</td><td class="s7">Automates adding an event to Google Calendar using n8n workflow with manual trigger and Google Calendar API integration. Ideal for scheduling tasks by specifying start/end times and calendar account.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1RldX1azqKReE6oZuEFRl9FPxfR_QePa4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1777" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1778</div></th><td class="s6">Image Text Overlay from Internet URL</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads an image via HTTP request and adds custom text using the built-in Edit Image node. Automates adding text overlays on images from any URL quickly without coding.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11RCUR0w-ubOVwb8i9RFiGjOrz3plHXb7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1778" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1779</div></th><td class="s6">Excel to PostgreSQL Importer</td><td class="s7">Automates importing Excel spreadsheet data into a PostgreSQL database using n8n. Reads a binary XLS file, parses it, then inserts rows into a PostgreSQL &#39;product&#39; table with columns &#39;name&#39; and &#39;ean&#39;.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KVhazZM6CHJgaDkJii7eeQO0I5wP4oQo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1779" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1780</div></th><td class="s6">Airtable Image URL to Attachment Updater</td><td class="s7">Automates moving image URLs to attachment fields in Airtable. Uses Airtable API nodes in n8n to fetch records with image URLs and update attachment fields, making image management in Airtable seamless and automated.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HKYWgZH2a2pr2jbs63vBAGLGVZuMdteM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1780" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1781</div></th><td class="s6">USDT TRC20 Wallet Tracker</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that tracks USDT TRC20 token transfers for a specified wallet using TronScan API. It fetches recent transactions, filters for incoming transfers within the last 15 minutes, formats and aggregates data. Built with n8n nodes, HTTP Request to TronScan API, and schedule trigger.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1E3CumkWlSurr1d41ospysuDtjbefqymJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1781" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1782</div></th><td class="s6">Website Email Scraper API via Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that scrapes emails from any website URL passed as a query parameter to a webhook. It uses HTTP Request to fetch website HTML, regex to extract emails, removes duplicates, and returns the emails in the webhook response. No external API needed.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KdvyM3ns9YyHnt24rhqBO_7SqX6V_SEu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1782" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1783</div></th><td class="s6">Google Sheets Data Fetch via Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that exposes a webhook to fetch data from a Google Sheets spreadsheet (range A:D on &#39;Problems&#39; sheet) via Google Sheets API. It enables integration of external apps with spreadsheet data retrieval through HTTP requests.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rohSKugdNr1oSwAOUvEwt51h1njfwx9r">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1783" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1784</div></th><td class="s6">Zotero Collection Items Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to fetch and paginate items from a Zotero user&#39;s specified collection using Zotero API with HTTP header authentication. It includes looping for pagination, filtering, and optional field editing, automating retrieval of research references.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dBnQTfIEU4UFLmhxNgzaTA0IpWEYLdzg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1784" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1785</div></th><td class="s6">Twitch Stream Online Status Checker</td><td class="s7">Checks if a specified Twitch user is currently streaming live using Twitch&#39;s GraphQL API. Utilizes n8n nodes for GraphQL queries and conditional logic to determine online status based on stream data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1y-sfphajilf-OOjpdcrLp3mA8lxYlj1U">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1785" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1786</div></th><td class="s6">ConvertKit Form Subscriber Alert</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers notifications when a new subscriber submits a specified ConvertKit form using ConvertKit API&#39;s webhook integration. Ideal for keeping track of list growth and automating subscriber management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19EvvFQ-P_C0s4mv_AQh6CMml7f9hfB4u">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1786" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1787</div></th><td class="s6">Dynamic Image Generator Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that generates custom images via a dummyjson.com API, allowing dynamic setting of size, colors, text, font, and output type. Utilizes Manual Trigger, Set, and HTTP Request nodes for creating images with personalized properties.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1CIjrWXYLHL5X5p3-nWQ1S5QVxzBSLc9T">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1787" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1788</div></th><td class="s6">Add Task to Google Tasks List</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that adds a new task to a specified Google Tasks list using Google Tasks API with OAuth2. Triggered manually, it allows users to quickly create tasks in their Google account tasklist through seamless automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1G5tjnFDZLzFXZdnci9wmgiAPmQUSGOo5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1788" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1789</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Weather Info Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Telegram API and OpenWeatherMap API to provide current weather updates on-demand via Telegram messages. It triggers on Telegram messages, fetches weather for Berlin, and replies with detailed conditions and temperature info.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1jcS7geGjDaUYrZChm0WTwkw93oqDLQ13">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1789" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1790</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Node.js Library Installer</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates installing Node.js libraries using npm. It processes a comma-separated string of library names (e.g., axios, cheerio, node-fetch), splits them, and runs shell commands to install each library if not already installed.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Aj7oRhNKRCKO94QOI8bSqmy5CnUqpm39">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1790" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1791</div></th><td class="s6">Text-to-Speech Audio Generator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts text to speech using a Python script (voicegen.py) and plays the resulting audio file. It uses local Python execution for TTS and reads an MP3 output file for playback, automating voice generation from specified text inputs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vVIyXspinO63iQaC7Nnxe5OA2f618Kk0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1791" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1792</div></th><td class="s6">Mailchimp Email Subscriber Add</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates adding subscribers to a Mailchimp email list via API. Uses Mailchimp node triggered manually to subscribe an email with merge field data. Ideal for simple email marketing subscriber management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1a2wMDO_RQk_nRUSYqQzWDMXYKbN0F7zD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1792" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1793</div></th><td class="s6">Instagram Stats Daily Report to Mattermost</td><td class="s7">Automates daily reporting of Instagram statistics using Google Sheets for data storage, formats date with n8n DateTime node, and posts formatted stats to Mattermost channel via API for team updates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12PWRZ3PmeFCawK0e5olMQh8j4hCLcYtJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1793" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1794</div></th><td class="s6">Dynamic Text Overlay on Image via Webhook</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow fetches an image from a public URL, then overlays dynamic text received via webhook query parameter onto the image using built-in HTTP Request and Edit Image nodes, enabling automated personalized image generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12F8qhCc1Jixffj10gPuDVqG3h1cSLUjv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1794" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1795</div></th><td class="s6">Twilio SMS Sending Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that sends SMS messages using the Twilio API. It triggers manually and connects n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger node to the Twilio node, enabling easy SMS automation with Twilio credentials.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AtdR12WVn32mEIrbj_PTcClnTGreBalI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1795" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1796</div></th><td class="s6">ActiveCampaign Contact Upsert Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers manually to add or update a contact in ActiveCampaign via API, using the manual trigger node and ActiveCampaign node to manage contacts efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JmLBjRulFPiNt_W1yHJJGz60QdtOYpWB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1796" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1797</div></th><td class="s6">HackerNoon Article Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches HackerNoon homepage HTML via HTTP Request, then extracts article titles and URLs using HTML Extract nodes. Useful for content aggregation or monitoring HackerNoon articles without coding.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dHA2E8uTqWcABc8QYxJD4JHGSWotsrav">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1797" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1798</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Journal Reply to Google Sheets</td><td class="s7">Automates saving Telegram reply messages as journal entries into a Google Sheets spreadsheet. Utilizes Telegram Trigger to capture replies, a Function node to parse message content, and Google Sheets API to append entries. Ideal for personal journaling via Telegram.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1cTBAWGjn54SFIFQhLcrsm8N6_HRGMQej">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1798" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1799</div></th><td class="s6">AWS SES Email Sender Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to send emails via AWS SES. Triggered manually to send predefined messages to multiple recipients using AWS SES API, useful for automated email notifications or testing email sending automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WUR9ypZUaidYXKdbIywUKzmDx1MajgBg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1799" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1800</div></th><td class="s6">Send SMS via MSG91</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that sends SMS using the MSG91 API. It uses a manual trigger node to start the flow and the MSG91 node to dispatch messages. Suitable for automating SMS notifications or alerts with MSG91&#39;s messaging platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1L323CxfXr2U-EMjr4x-6pmxlETPPXUH3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1800" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1801</div></th><td class="s6">TravisCI Build Trigger Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to manually trigger builds on TravisCI using the TravisCI API. It features a Manual Trigger node and TravisCI node, enabling easy integration with continuous integration pipelines for automated build execution.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1V0Wd1mk39NugqakWgBBdp9zANoiYLV2E">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1801" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1802</div></th><td class="s6">Invoice Ninja Invoice Creation Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers actions when a new invoice is created in Invoice Ninja using its API webhook integration. Designed to automate workflows based on invoice creation events in Invoice Ninja accounting software.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FJ5y9HRGezi_hUf9EIpChn-W6xpbyB9w">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1802" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1803</div></th><td class="s6">Calendly Event Webhook Listener</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using the Calendly API to trigger actions upon invitee creation or cancellation events. It listens to Calendly webhooks and enables automation based on scheduling changes, ideal for appointment management integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Y-z7TTRYHsEjzFbgJOexKU-RqMZsqqpb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1803" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1804</div></th><td class="s6">Xero Data Fetch on Manual Trigger</td><td class="s7">This workflow uses n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger node to initiate and connects to the Xero API via OAuth2 to fetch all organization data. It automates retrieving accounting data from Xero on-demand using n8n integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1VuN4Tt94eMMVSwvz93gn2YS8dmkuX5I8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1804" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1805</div></th><td class="s6">Fetch All Wordpress Posts</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Manual Trigger and Wordpress API to fetch all posts from a Wordpress site. Ideal for automating content retrieval from Wordpress blogs or websites.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17tibnO8RIcOZJ7XSRkLrctLSW1coKScz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1805" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1806</div></th><td class="s6">Paddle Coupon Creator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates discount coupons on Paddle using its API. Triggered manually, it automates coupon generation with customizable codes and discount amounts, ideal for e-commerce promotions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kv_49dQupBaCeSPDQBdYzzKJm7DpNCK0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1806" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1807</div></th><td class="s6">SurveyMonkey Response Listener</td><td class="s7">Automates workflows triggered by new SurveyMonkey survey responses using SurveyMonkey Webhook and OAuth2 authentication. Ideal for instantly processing or forwarding fresh survey data via n8n automation platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1S1AZrB44DfZMaXd8CcynA19QKV3QtzwD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1807" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1808</div></th><td class="s6">Monday.com Board Data Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that manually triggers a data retrieval from a specified Monday.com board using the Monday.com API credentials, aiming to fetch and use project management data easily within automation pipelines.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1n1iZRTZSjls-MLpdxd8DMyw6CrxkRegv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1808" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1809</div></th><td class="s6">SpaceX Launches Data Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches the latest 5 SpaceX launches using the SpaceX GraphQL API. It retrieves mission details, launch dates, sites, rocket info, payload, and ship data, triggered manually via n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gNhWSuXIEoT4tsdlzb_1KXZgnh5XSTkm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1809" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1810</div></th><td class="s6">Excel Data Fetch on Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves all data from a Microsoft Excel spreadsheet using Microsoft Excel OAuth2 API upon manual trigger. Ideal for automating data extraction from Excel files into connected systems.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1bDZtBhp3fPJw-ajYGj_vjL88QWYmaLd1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1810" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1811</div></th><td class="s6">HelpScout Mailbox Fetcher</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow uses HelpScout API via OAuth2 to retrieve all mailboxes on manual trigger, enabling streamlined support mailbox management and automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zC0VNvwzC5ltUFRmU2jywCx0bHYnol5J">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1811" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1812</div></th><td class="s6">Jira Event Listener Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow node that listens to all Jira events via Jira Software Cloud API webhook integration. It triggers automation whenever any event occurs in Jira, enabling real-time Jira activity monitoring and workflow automation using n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BRni7aKG_bZKsvhtv7Xf0vwCy-MlI0eq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1812" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1813</div></th><td class="s6">IMAP Email Fetcher</td><td class="s7">Workflow to fetch emails from an IMAP server using n8n&#39;s Email Read IMAP node. It connects to an email inbox via IMAP protocol, enabling automated email retrieval for further processing or automation tasks. Uses n8n automation platform with IMAP credentials.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1En6Ig7SZRwOrD_rRce6ZFrkYneZHKk6D">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1813" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1814</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Cocktail Image Bot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on Telegram messages, fetches a random cocktail from TheCocktailDB API, and replies with the drink&#39;s image and name. Utilizes Telegram Bot API and HTTP Request node for API integration to provide fun cocktail suggestions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16KmSOq1KNDaEVdlh7u_72HNI_rFcNgLK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1814" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1815</div></th><td class="s6">Send SMS via Mocean API</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow sends SMS messages using the Mocean API. It starts with a manual trigger and connects to the Mocean node to dispatch SMS by specifying recipient, sender, and message content. Useful for integrating SMS alerts or notifications in automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XZuM35AxIBEGw4vfG_WnRN5pZPr7bnp3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1815" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1816</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Message Relay via Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using a webhook and Telegram API to forward incoming HTTP requests as Telegram messages. It receives a query parameter, sends it to a predefined chat ID via Telegram Bot API, and confirms message delivery. Tech stack: n8n, Telegram Bot API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1g-HphtxI8qpDz81YDS7gM5pn9_p9aCt6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1816" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1817</div></th><td class="s6">GitHub Repository Profile Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves detailed profile information of a specific GitHub repository using the GitHub API. Triggered manually, it fetches data for the &#39;n8n-io/n8n&#39; repository via authenticated API credentials, enabling integration in automation pipelines.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zXbOmdNNOyNcsQJNoDQlscHN25kkmEO_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1817" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1818</div></th><td class="s6">Append Data to Google Sheets Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that appends predefined data to a specified Google Sheets spreadsheet using OAuth2 authentication. It triggers manually, sets data values, appends them to the sheet, and reads back the updated data, ideal for simple data entry automation with Google Sheets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OO8p3GE7WtlB2cPTsdMyBHe_wDmY0A0o">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1818" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1819</div></th><td class="s6">MySQL Execution History Purge Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates deletion of MySQL n8n execution logs older than 30 days to maintain database performance. Utilizes n8n&#39;s Cron trigger and MySQL node with SQL DELETE queries. Useful for n8n users managing execution history retention.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ov2XBjGQB1jcYDBpELC0jSJWIRJ574Vq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1819" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1820</div></th><td class="s6">Mattermost Video Call Invite via Webhook</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow listens for POST requests via a webhook, extracts channel and user data, and sends a customized video call invite message through the Mattermost API, using dynamic URLs based on usernames. Useful for team communication automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Q46AdchMi_w3P-FsohLazqVZ3XWCAzq7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1820" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1821</div></th><td class="s6">Dropbox File Fetch and List Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating Dropbox operations: fetching a folder, downloading a file from URL, uploading it to Dropbox, then listing folder contents. Utilizes Dropbox API and HTTP Request node to manage files programmatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_syD2i0JI1Spn-pFXNXIgOBU2dFYU1_1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1821" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1822</div></th><td class="s6">HelpScout Customer Created Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on new customer creation events in HelpScout using the HelpScout OAuth2 API. It listens for &#39;customer.created&#39; events via a webhook to automate updates or integrations when a new customer is added.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1unNXn_EvCWQGR5UV78sJmj6sFnd6aX7w">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1822" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1823</div></th><td class="s6">HubSpot Contact Change Trigger</td><td class="s7">Triggers workflows based on HubSpot CRM contact changes using HubSpot Developer API in n8n. Ideal for automations reacting to contact updates or creations via webhook integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1A5uarCqEVZfXCX-bQmz_Qt_rxZ8SBT9Z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1823" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1824</div></th><td class="s6">Automated Email Excuse Responder</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automatically reads emails from a specific IMAP inbox, filters emails from a particular sender, generates randomized excuses using data from an Excel spreadsheet, replies to the sender via SMTP, and sends notifications to Slack channels. It integrates Email (IMAP/SMTP), Excel parsing, Slack API, and custom JavaScript logic to automate personalized email replies.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1QI4iFloUZd-m7ubcSq0ZSB9UcD3lnwFE">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1824" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1825</div></th><td class="s6">Affinity List Creation Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers when a new list is created in Affinity CRM. It uses the Affinity API via a webhook to receive real-time updates, enabling automated responses to list creation events.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Skl98s0B9iWMMbtty_NOwkCVSkZEELTx">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1825" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1826</div></th><td class="s6">Upload &amp; List Files in S3 Bucket</td><td class="s7">Automates downloading a file via HTTP, uploading it to an Amazon S3 bucket, then retrieving and listing all files in that bucket using n8n&#39;s HTTP Request and S3 nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1KOafGlBWVFK8xML5vUSCf0WrR1rLO70G">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1826" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1827</div></th><td class="s6">Save Random Cocktail Data as JSON File</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow fetches a random cocktail recipe from the CocktailDB API using an HTTP Request node, converts the JSON response to binary data, and writes it to a local JSON file named cocktail.json. Useful for drink recipe collection and automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1X3KZH2yeG7qgdoVXA-dW3RXU68Gk6-ag">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1827" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1828</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Error Email Notifier</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on workflow errors and sends detailed error reports via Gmail API. It captures error messages, execution details, and stack traces, emailing them to specified recipients to facilitate quick debugging and monitoring.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18L1rKp04nhHksGBlDQiH6Oxasf38AJ1M">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1828" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1829</div></th><td class="s6">Taiga Issue Create-Update-Get Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates issue management on Taiga using n8n nodes. It creates an issue, updates its description, and retrieves the issue details via Taiga Cloud API, triggered manually in n8n. Useful for project tracking automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1NYn9pJKH_nViWGienXioQX-XhImATMyh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1829" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1830</div></th><td class="s6">Periodic Google Sheets Sync</td><td class="s7">Automates syncing data within the same Google Sheets document every 2 minutes using n8n&#39;s Cron trigger and Google Sheets API nodes. It reads data from a specified range and updates two sheet areas simultaneously, ensuring data consistency and automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-yTbac1iqc9YFyj3rDV9a6wAh1IH9jO-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1830" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1831</div></th><td class="s6">Wufoo Form Submission Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers an automation when a Wufoo form named &#39;n8n&#39; is submitted. Uses Wufoo API webhook integration to receive real-time form submission data, enabling seamless triggering of further automations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Mz3NKnFbLlTzelP2a-oq26ByHh_ugexm">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1831" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1832</div></th><td class="s6">Restore n8n Credentials from GitHub Backup</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates restoration of instance credentials from GitHub repo backups using GitHub API and n8n API. It fetches credential JSON files from a specified GitHub repository path, converts them, and restores them into n8n for seamless credential recovery.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14y2szrwv0luxVg7JkNI11beEq3Lc4VOR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1832" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1833</div></th><td class="s6">Hubspot Contacts Export Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers manually to fetch all contacts from Hubspot CRM using the Hubspot API. Ideal for syncing or exporting contact data for further processing or analysis.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sDu7KBj7Qs47ykw2YQQn8YJrvGPNFatb">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1833" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1834</div></th><td class="s6">Medium Publication Post Publisher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to publish posts directly to a Medium publication using the Medium API. Triggered manually, it streamlines content publishing by automating the posting process to a specified Medium publication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_iBAUc_UG6OCF2BcV25z3SeMlGZHsh4y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1834" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1835</div></th><td class="s6">Fetch CircleCI Pipeline Data</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to manually trigger and retrieve pipeline details from CircleCI using the CircleCI API. Ideal for developers and DevOps teams to automate CI/CD monitoring and integration tasks seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1g3YBiHu-eWcK_GBsoF7v04wmGMl2sx9Y">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1835" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1836</div></th><td class="s6">SMS Sending with MessageBird</td><td class="s7">Automate SMS sending via MessageBird API using n8n. This workflow triggers manually and sends customizable SMS messages through the MessageBird node. Ideal for quick integration of SMS notifications in automation pipelines.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1j0lEzgchcuR6O6Ws6P70N1XLV4-ZEBqw">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1836" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1837</div></th><td class="s6">Current Weather Fetch for a City</td><td class="s7">Fetch current weather data for a specified city using n8n and OpenWeatherMap API. Triggered manually, it retrieves weather info like temperature, humidity for cities like Berlin. Useful for weather monitoring and integration workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-T4T-2Z9zrVUdiwpj8EyW69owFUlqhQ0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1837" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1838</div></th><td class="s6">Image Fetch and Dropbox Upload Zip</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads two images via HTTP requests, compresses them into a ZIP archive, and uploads the ZIP file to Dropbox. Utilizes n8n HTTP Request, Compression, and Dropbox nodes for efficient file handling and cloud storage automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1wZ3szUjUGp51C6-xoYU_7hPU56rUZb4G">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1838" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1839</div></th><td class="s6">Post Message to RocketChat Channel</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that posts a predefined message to a specified RocketChat channel using RocketChat API credentials. Triggered manually, it automates simple communication tasks in team chat using n8n&#39;s RocketChat node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1w9yPlbo1S7eIzHfkiOUPQGxd17YMYnZV">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1839" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1840</div></th><td class="s6">Intercom New User Creation</td><td class="s7">Automatically create a new user in Intercom via n8n workflow using Intercom API triggered manually. Enables seamless user onboarding and management through API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1yWg4eqDbz0EQCRjRiVPn74BvE9Qs54j5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1840" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1841</div></th><td class="s6">Send SMS Alert When Leaving Home</td><td class="s7">Automates sending an SMS via Twilio whenever the Pushcut app triggers the &quot;Leaving Home&quot; action. Integrates Pushcut API for location-based triggers and Twilio API for messaging to notify a specified phone number in real-time.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=199L1k18rPLMVOgb8p4INa493BJNTh-sT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1841" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1842</div></th><td class="s6">Stackby Data Insert and Retrieve</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that inserts a record with ID and Name into a Stackby table and then lists all records. It uses n8n&#39;s manual trigger, Set node for data setting, and Stackby API to manage table data seamlessly.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1nomHaTAr_2k9ISBPTYblKzUHUkJZHUzY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1842" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1843</div></th><td class="s6">Website Availability &amp; Metadata Checker</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that checks if a given website URL is available using Peekalink API, then fetches detailed metadata if available. Useful for monitoring website status and extracting info. Implements manual trigger, conditional logic, and Peekalink API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19JpEKBPzGL5tU1LsBI-QCYx23G38zaPr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1843" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1844</div></th><td class="s6">Strava Activity Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that connects to Strava API using OAuth2 to create, update, and retrieve running activity data. Automates managing Strava activities by creating a run, updating its description, and then fetching its details.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1b27evQQJbWiMeMLAsMMkSoBJT1R19ROQ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1844" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1845</div></th><td class="s6">Emelia Campaign &amp; Contact Management</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Emelia API to create an email campaign, add a contact to it with name and email, and retrieve campaign info. Automates email marketing campaign setup and contact management using Emelia API within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FMzMoKlHxqVcx3i4MW-dBu7uEfpZ9FFR">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1845" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1846</div></th><td class="s6">Agile CRM Contact Creation</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of new contacts in Agile CRM using n8n&#39;s manual trigger and Agile CRM API integration. Enables users to add contacts with basic info efficiently, streamlining CRM management without coding.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fBi439yMobuqhBadxg_81pvU8dC_P7Yo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1846" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1847</div></th><td class="s6">ISS Position Updates to Kafka Every Minute</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow fetches the International Space Station’s current position every minute using the public &#39;wheretheiss.at&#39; API, processes the latitude and longitude data, and publishes updates to a Kafka topic &#39;iss-position&#39;. Tech stack: n8n, HTTP Request, Cron, Kafka nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17JPqH1EefEOraGt0oolNRa7OGWd5qpTM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1847" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1848</div></th><td class="s6">Autopilot Email List &amp; Contact Management</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Autopilot API to list email lists, add contacts to lists, update contact details, and retrieve all contacts from a list. Automates email marketing list and contact management with step-by-step Autopilot API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1_ncMrAkadXib34oIxm3wnASNe7AGTT1Z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1848" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1849</div></th><td class="s6">Wise Transfer Automation Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating Wise money transfers: it creates a quote, then a transfer, executes it, and retrieves transfer details using Wise API credentials. Useful for automating EUR currency transfers with a preset profile and target account.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JtAgrP-dlUpPH9UE6fYGeJBCZ1ES5uV3">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1849" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1850</div></th><td class="s6">Zammad User Role Reset to Default</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow automates resetting all users&#39; roles in Zammad ticketing system to default values via Zammad API, using HTTP requests and manual triggers with role and user data processing in JavaScript expressions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gETeEtOpIjWV6zlVg7YN1RQyKBL8TRh0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1850" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1851</div></th><td class="s6">Baserow Markdown to HTML Converter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts video description data stored as Markdown in Baserow databases into HTML format. It supports single or bulk record updates and uses Baserow API with n8n&#39;s Markdown node for conversion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sRouaJa7ZRDs4VJ1X-5_Y2vLXvw_wDTa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1851" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1852</div></th><td class="s6">Bitrix24 Chatbot with Webhook Integration</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow implementing a Bitrix24 chatbot using webhook to handle events like messages, joins, installs, and deletes. Utilizes Bitrix24 REST API for bot registration and message sending with token validation to enable interactive communication within Bitrix24 chats.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16IeIRjCstcx33eijnVesxoCZAz6ThrbB">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1852" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1853</div></th><td class="s6">Humantic AI Profile Management Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating Humantic AI API to create, update, and retrieve LinkedIn-based user personality profiles. Utilizes manual triggers, Humantic AI nodes, and HTTP requests to automate profile handling and enhancement.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Hm5ce2Z8rvwDBt6GtOcBJB5QCdFBdAm_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1853" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1854</div></th><td class="s6">License Plate Number Extractor from Image</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that extracts license plate numbers from uploaded car images using OpenRouter&#39;s GPT-4o model within LangChain. Users upload an image via a form, and the AI processes the image prompt to return the license plate text, automating vehicle identification.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1O1EqzY-sRx5pykkM_acTddYrnc7opVCi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1854" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1855</div></th><td class="s6">Scheduled URL Pinger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that pings a predefined list of URLs every 15 minutes using HTTP requests. It uses Schedule Trigger to automate, Set node for URL list, Split Out to iterate, and HTTP Request node to check each URL status.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12p8F73ySv4jnwDGrxWZsioZLSeWYWIbe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1855" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1856</div></th><td class="s6">Send Message in Lark Suite via API</td><td class="s7">Automates sending text messages in Larksuite chats using Larksuite Open API. Uses HTTP requests to obtain tenant access token and send messages. Includes manual trigger and environment input setup for app_id, app_secret, chat_id, and message text.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1fSGsqoW7j8FMdEpPEYBpj_FvpZNKW0PM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1856" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1857</div></th><td class="s6">Icypeas Domain Search Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates single domain/company scans using Icypeas API. Utilizes HTTP POST requests with API key, secret, and user ID authentication via custom HMAC-SHA1 signature generated in n8n code node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1trYz3mP1l8KkJkMsA5SWmJx6UyweCbBA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1857" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1858</div></th><td class="s6">Telegram Echo Bot for Debugging</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that listens to all Telegram bot messages and echoes back the full JSON content to the sender. Utilizes Telegram API triggers and message nodes, ideal for debugging Telegram bot incoming data and learning the Telegram JSON structure.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1n24KLdAHVdxjEJaRxVj1BN2tWqqzyEYT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1858" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1859</div></th><td class="s6">AMQP Trigger for ActiveMQ Queue</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow with an AMQP Trigger node that listens and receives messages from an ActiveMQ queue using the AMQP protocol. Useful for integrating messaging systems in automation workflows. Utilizes n8n&#39;s AMQP node to connect and trigger on message arrival.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dkYYAyk1dOFEEgPnaRiLTKU8n4AhCKpJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1859" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1860</div></th><td class="s6">CSV Concert Data to MySQL Importer</td><td class="s7">Automates importing concert data from a local CSV file into a MySQL database using n8n. Utilizes n8n core nodes: Manual Trigger, Read Binary File, Spreadsheet File, and MySQL node to parse CSV and insert records into the &#39;concerts_2023_csv&#39; table.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1111xEVlFdbZudX2rEL9zXniwZaQsPk7g">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1860" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1861</div></th><td class="s6">Retell Dynamic Variable Populator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that handles Retell AI inbound call webhooks. It uses a POST webhook filtered by IP, fetches user data from Google Sheets by phone number, and returns dynamic variables for Retell voice agents. Uses Google Sheets API and webhook nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EuvAtBd_dqsGsAnzVPG7W_bNXvXRuoE8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1861" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1862</div></th><td class="s6">n8n GitHub Release Notifier</td><td class="s7">Automates monitoring of n8n GitHub releases via RSS, filters new releases published within last 4 hours mentioning &#39;n8n@&#39; and &#39;.0&#39;, then sends notifications via Telegram and AWS SES email. Uses n8n nodes: Cron, RSS Feed Read, Function, IF, Telegram API, AWS SES.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1U0PFy3jdCLMDyl4TLaVmQlc1AseW3mQG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1862" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1863</div></th><td class="s6">Email Body Parser Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that extracts structured data from raw email bodies by parsing labeled fields using a custom JavaScript snippet. It uses n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger, Set, and FunctionItem nodes to process emails with labels like Name, Email, Subject, and Message.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-C0AflLOEo4nfkWEeRcW48ovu4Auj5as">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1863" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1864</div></th><td class="s6">Freshdesk Ticket Fetcher by Email</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches open Freshdesk tickets for a requester based on their email. Uses Freshdesk API integrated into n8n with a manual trigger to initiate the process. Ideal for customer support automation and ticket management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Ct6WrGbTzulxjW55deAmeXAUKyno6IdT">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1864" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1865</div></th><td class="s6">Mautic Contacts Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that fetches all contacts from Mautic CRM using OAuth2 authentication. Triggered manually, it connects n8n with Mautic API to retrieve contact data for marketing automation workflows.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=176Msf5zcrzSg-CC5NdFPcXggkKlzCROi">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1865" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1866</div></th><td class="s6">Multi-Source RSS Feed Reader</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that reads RSS feeds from two sources (Medium and Dev.to) using built-in RSS Feed Read node, triggered manually and looped over URLs defined in a JavaScript Code node for scalable feed retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1beNggDlWUhfCKf8c6IWHcgaFUPiAEhMJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1866" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1867</div></th><td class="s6">Trello Card Creation Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates creating a new card in Trello using n8n&#39;s manual trigger node and Trello API integration. Triggered manually, it adds a card with defined title and description to a Trello list. Useful for task automation within Trello boards.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14W7m4p51osfwygZFessNgStGsdwGvGw7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1867" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1868</div></th><td class="s6">Trello List Change Updates Listener</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on changes in a specified Trello list using the Trello API, enabling automation based on Trello list updates. Ideal for task and project management notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=18g4gDta9McUbiKNRkkWB9F2kFx2OLrAs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1868" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1869</div></th><td class="s6">TOTP Code Generator Workflow in n8n</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating Time-Based One-Time Password (TOTP) generation using the built-in TOTP node with configured TOTP credentials. Triggered manually, it produces secure, time-sensitive codes for multi-factor authentication setups.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LcK3y9Yy2Kk8dNTxqNmbnF5JjMFYF5jj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1869" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1870</div></th><td class="s6">Used Car Sale Price Estimation Bot</td><td class="s7">Automates used car price estimation via web interaction with Peddle.com. Uses Airtop API for browser automation including session management, clicks, typing, screenshots, and AI-driven page analysis to extract offer prices from the site in a dynamic workflow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1BGNc2uO34PXI-byyKTlpDYYUyXrAq1qe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1870" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1871</div></th><td class="s6">Seatable Webhook HMAC SHA256 Validator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to securely validate Seatable webhooks using HMAC SHA256 authentication. It verifies webhook payloads by hashing with a shared secret, comparing to x-seatable-signature header, then conditionally responding with 200 OK or 403 Forbidden. Uses n8n Webhook and Crypto nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1X8iOxxwFs9Dg3S-4SPTgH8nS_MUPRqUd">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1871" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1872</div></th><td class="s6">Upload and Rename Video on Google Drive</td><td class="s7">Automates video uploading via a Google Apps Script web app and renames the file in Google Drive. Uses n8n with HTTP Request node to post video URL to Google Script, and Google Drive node to update file name. Ideal for streamlining video management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sMSYoQKXRSOXoXQIMIkx-piKaBFpS2zl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1872" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1873</div></th><td class="s6">Icypeas Email Search Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates performing single email searches using the Icypeas API via n8n. Utilizes API key, secret, and user ID for authentication, generates HMAC signatures, and executes secured HTTP POST requests to fetch email data based on lastname, firstname, and company/domain inputs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zydy9m3veTF2loFYcAcLh-tKaI2eS4E0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1873" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1874</div></th><td class="s6">n8n v1 Upgrade Expression Checker</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to scan active workflows for parameters using expressions affected by n8n v1 changes. Utilizes n8n API and custom JavaScript code to identify impacted expressions like beginningOf, endOfMonth, plus, minus, helping ensure workflow stability post-upgrade.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14KT1FkRdv18GCr2kOnzBXlMnP_7A2QCZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1874" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1875</div></th><td class="s6">Dataset Comparison with n8n</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to compare two datasets of fruit attributes using the built-in Compare Datasets node, triggered manually. Utilizes JavaScript code nodes to supply datasets and analyzes differences and matches. Useful for data reconciliation and validation tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1HlaeuoI2G3y50oXBjUk2zJ7iZRIrMoTf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1875" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1876</div></th><td class="s6">US Phone Number Formatter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that cleans, validates, and formats US phone numbers. It strips input formatting, verifies country code and number length, and outputs several standardized formats (E.164, national, international). Uses n8n nodes without external APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1I2gMV-fODbxaRVdVAlqoef7niXQn4ArX">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1876" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1877</div></th><td class="s6">Reddit n8n Post Classifier</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that fetches recent Reddit posts about &#39;n8n&#39;, filters by upvotes and date, classifies relevance using OpenAI, and summarizes content. Integrates Reddit API and OpenAI. Useful for monitoring community discussions about n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aqJqv7Z620n-lEq-9mNA3gD-EcFUmjdl">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1877" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1878</div></th><td class="s6">Dub.co URL Shortener Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating URL shortening via the Dub.co API. It creates or updates short links using Dub.co&#39;s REST API with customizable slugs, domains, and project slugs. Includes manual triggering and HTTP request nodes for seamless link management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1c7AVtE-IOQfdxwLcRLQdtHaueeKvNjnS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1878" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1879</div></th><td class="s6">Nostr Damus Hashtag AI Analytics</td><td class="s7">Automated social media analytics that monitors Nostr&#39;s #damus hashtag, uses Google Gemini AI to analyze themes and generate reports, then sends insights via Gmail and Telegram. Tech: Nostr API, Google Gemini AI, Gmail, Telegram. Perfect for tracking decentralized social trends.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ONRi13uvxE_du0rtikXOjqEYhHdUCyx_">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1879" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1880</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Mattermost Startup Notification</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow sends a Mattermost message notification when the n8n instance starts. It uses the n8n trigger node to detect the init event and the Mattermost node to post a message including the startup timestamp, leveraging Mattermost API for team communication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZiBpKL6-VbwY6cFydVc3xVjvRCsFXXvz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1880" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1881</div></th><td class="s6">FileMaker Record Create-Edit-Get Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating data handling in FileMaker: creates a record with first and last name, edits the record to add a country field, then retrieves the record. Uses FileMaker API and manual trigger for process start.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1q-e1ZaUzkrIlinV1jKL5JXCOykbBeJmA">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1881" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1882</div></th><td class="s6">Standup Bot Initialization Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to initialize Standup Bot configuration for Mattermost integration, setting default tokens and URLs, converting JSON config to binary and saving it. Uses n8n core nodes and works with Mattermost API for bot setup.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ctOFwcqqpvNjzRuKUwcxt5rKQbUDj3ju">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1882" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1883</div></th><td class="s6">ActiveCampaign Admin Account Add Alert</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers real-time notifications when an admin adds a new account in ActiveCampaign using the ActiveCampaign Trigger node. Enables seamless monitoring of account creations via the ActiveCampaign API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17sTjJiqOVOv7AWljLCsz3hEpmbXX_7S0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1883" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1884</div></th><td class="s6">Create Deal in Pipedrive CRM</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to manually create a new deal in Pipedrive CRM using the Pipedrive API. Triggered manually to add deal info seamlessly to Pipedrive for sales pipeline management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11N4zhgHNc9_MwHmUAz0VVxKsxswhs0PJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1884" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1885</div></th><td class="s6">Webhook JSON to XML Converter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that listens on a webhook, sets static JSON data, converts it to XML format using the XML node, and responds with XML content. Useful for converting JSON to XML via HTTP requests.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1TRfr72ST_sQxbyr9MTY9FrhteDyjRve7">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1885" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1886</div></th><td class="s6">Harvest Client Creation Workflow</td><td class="s7">Automates client creation in Harvest using n8n workflow with the Harvest API and manual trigger. Simplifies adding new clients to Harvest time tracking software without manual input.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1dVNhR99PlDa8VQbeKuDQz0oDkBaeF-MK">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1886" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1887</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Post Customer Data via HTTP</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves all customer records from a datastore, processes them one-by-one in batches, and sends each record as a POST request to a public JSON placeholder API. Uses n8n core nodes: Manual Trigger, Customer Datastore, SplitInBatches, HTTP Request, and Wait for pacing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=19NryYFtCRu_Ks-TYIuEVYJzvdjqniv69">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1887" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1888</div></th><td class="s6">Zulip Private Message Sender</td><td class="s7">Automates sending private messages on Zulip using n8n workflow with manual trigger and Zulip API integration. Ideal for quick, programmable direct messaging within Zulip chat environments.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IyT0T4al-1cfZ_PZ20JFnCxyTgt4DaKv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1888" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1889</div></th><td class="s6">Create User Profile in Vero</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of user profiles in Vero via API using n8n workflow with a manual trigger and Vero node integration. Ideal for marketers managing customer engagement through Vero&#39;s platform.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16k8C_CUuGCLLaM7HgObgzjQdhpt9mhsg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1889" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1890</div></th><td class="s6">Retrieve All Tasks from Flow App</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to fetch all tasks from the Flow API using a manual trigger. Enables easy task management automation by connecting n8n with Flow&#39;s task system through its API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FfF-XXQf9rz_v8dnapN10bcIbWNMrUg5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1890" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1891</div></th><td class="s6">Customer Data Fetch &amp; Forward Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves all customer records from a custom datastore using n8nTrainingCustomerDatastore node, authenticates with an API key set manually, and posts each customer&#39;s name to a specified webhook URL via HTTP POST requests. Designed for easy triggering and API integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15D6jUNB0faPhMI5GyWB6G6UU8x43q3GO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1891" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1892</div></th><td class="s6">Flow Task Updates Receiver</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using the Flow Trigger node to receive real-time updates for specified tasks via the Flow API. It enables automation based on task changes, suitable for integrations and monitoring task progress.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1b-CVfxtnBKoPz9mFQZiy3HNvc2L7yY_p">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1892" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1893</div></th><td class="s6">Email Domain Extractor</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that extracts the domain name from a given email address using built-in nodes: Manual Trigger, Set (to input sample email), and Function (to process and extract domain). Helps automate email parsing tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JKQJ6v79JOSJ0KGi5kqa9FS-ZVmDeD94">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1893" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1894</div></th><td class="s6">German Word Synonym Finder</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves synonyms for German words using the OpenThesaurus API. Triggered manually, it helps users find alternative German terms quickly, leveraging n8n&#39;s manual trigger and OpenThesaurus integration for language enrichment tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1K2Y9EAM4Tm_F19sSyp5pWjokrMM03Dw-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1894" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1895</div></th><td class="s6">Webhook Reception and Adobe Sign Data Extraction</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that sets up POST and GET webhooks to receive requests, extracts Adobe Sign client ID from headers, processes the response to retrieve agreement details (ID, participants, status) using JavaScript Function and Set nodes. Uses n8n webhook nodes and custom code.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1L_UXEBpyUGwD6Bq9WMtH0JnMrOKShPDu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1895" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1896</div></th><td class="s6">Bubble API Data Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers a manual execution to fetch user data from Bubble.io&#39;s REST API using HTTP Header Authentication. Useful for integrating Bubble app data into automated processes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WoCI0uQhdwilLDAYQpvqzJz3oazvx5iY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1896" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1897</div></th><td class="s6">Download and Save File to Host</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads an image from a URL using HTTP Request node and saves it locally using Write Binary File node, triggered manually. Useful for automating file retrieval and storage on local machines.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xUon987sqziJH0Ex_Rq9lgbarMYbbJS5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1897" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1898</div></th><td class="s6">QuestDB Table Creation &amp; Data Insertion</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates a table and inserts data into QuestDB using manual trigger, Set node, and QuestDB node for SQL execution and data insertion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1LtGSkFQT4NjwFu4c7WSt4yiOgGmh57hj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1898" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1899</div></th><td class="s6">Download and Split Binary Files Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads a ZIP file via HTTP request, decompresses it, and splits the contained binary files into individual items. Uses HTTP Request, Compression, and Function nodes. Ideal for processing bulk file archives automatically.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1r7zt7ydndoIuUxMSkItcqGguqklWzfJj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1899" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1900</div></th><td class="s6">Date &amp; Time Manipulation Tutorial</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating date-time operations using n8n DateTime and Set nodes with Luxon expressions. It shows how to calculate, format, and convert dates for automation purposes without external APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1a5VTFLVi7NDyygL65KxfierfnSwwzXiW">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1900" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1901</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Workflow Connection Integrity Checker</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow identifies potentially broken multi-output node connections caused by version 0.214.3 upgrade issues. Using the n8n API, code logic, and a webhook, it scans all workflows, detects affected nodes, and serves an HTML report listing them for manual inspection.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13i-fVBL6oDkHHFkDjq4H7AGZpeYf9QE1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1901" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1902</div></th><td class="s6">Download PDF via Webhook</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow sets up a webhook that, upon an HTTP GET request, downloads a specific PDF file from Deutsche Bahn&#39;s website using HTTP Request node and responds with the PDF as an attachment, leveraging n8n&#39;s webhook and HTTP request capabilities.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=14Vho4TyJb-2LKpFKAoEQALi5lncpAvuh">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1902" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1903</div></th><td class="s6">Send Message on Twake</td><td class="s7">Automates sending messages to a Twake channel using the Twake API. Triggered manually via n8n, it posts content into specified channels, ideal for team communication integration and workflow automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=128YcwqJmPLy6B4gjc4pAJWySK7qfFK5p">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1903" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1904</div></th><td class="s6">n8n Error Trigger Webhook Extractor</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses the Error Trigger node to catch errors, then calls n8n&#39;s internal API to get execution details, and runs custom JavaScript to extract webhook payload data from the workflow execution. It automates error context retrieval using n8n API and JavaScript.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=168KuOAlpRoOcbuPzxEauUg1IvMqL6LQg">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1904" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1905</div></th><td class="s6">Manual PayPal Payment Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers a PayPal payout using a manual trigger node and the PayPal API. It enables sending payments programmatically with minimal setup, ideal for automating payout processes using n8n&#39;s built-in PayPal integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1YU8se5IqlZli9thu_wzN0bvmCBQzOSuI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1905" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1906</div></th><td class="s6">SIGNL4 Alert Notification Trigger</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow sends a test alert message to the SIGNL4 incident alerting service via its API when manually triggered. It uses n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger node linked to the SIGNL4 node for sending alerts with customizable titles and messages.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XYAc7xLmwID6uPfpZ5LBrHmRNPEuH9da">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1906" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1907</div></th><td class="s6">PayPal Billing Plan Activation Trigger</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow using PayPal API webhook to receive real-time updates when a billing plan is activated in PayPal accounts. Useful for automating billing processes and integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1t6lMkvb2wLgU_5qUR2rkGYcjfIYOplB6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1907" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1908</div></th><td class="s6">AWS SNS Trigger Listener</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on AWS SNS topic events using AWS SNS Trigger node. Utilizes AWS SNS API for real-time event-driven automation. Ideal for integrating AWS notifications with other automation tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1H9BSKeaSbv52prPAoYooAIF8_al5Kv2T">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1908" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1909</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Trigger to AWS Lambda Call</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers an AWS Lambda function via manual execution. It connects a manual trigger node to an AWS Lambda node using AWS credentials to call a specific Lambda ARN, enabling simple serverless function invocation within automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rHMWAmyZbJqau3SLeZyX-52ppNPneBCN">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1909" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1910</div></th><td class="s6">Fetch Facebook User Name via API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves the first and last name of a Facebook user using the Facebook Graph API. Initiated manually, it integrates n8n automation with Facebook API credentials to fetch user profile data efficiently.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17skVkfDzBKuEUovEEelX7dNnvKdAEFzU">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1910" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1911</div></th><td class="s6">Download Google Drive File to Local</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that downloads a specific file from Google Drive using Google API with service account credentials and saves it locally as a binary file. Triggered manually to automate file retrieval and storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1A03JXxBhNTdWeByy0_5q1X11cOlgpjOY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1911" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1912</div></th><td class="s6">Cockpit CMS Data Fetch Trigger</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that triggers manually to fetch data from Cockpit CMS using Cockpit API. Designed for easy retrieval of content from a &#39;samplecollection&#39; collection in Cockpit for further automation or processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1v2478Mb903k5UDUxzPby3qXoBAc2_yzp">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1912" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1913</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Triggered Email via Mailjet</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow sending test emails using Mailjet API upon manual trigger. It demonstrates basic email dispatch with parameters for subject, message, sender, and recipient using the Mailjet credential setup.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1f5_PfGbFHo3EbmcnzdPAV0oJFKggBh-T">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1913" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1914</div></th><td class="s6">Mailjet Email Sent Event Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that listens for &#39;sent&#39; email events via Mailjet&#39;s API using the Mailjet Trigger node, enabling automation based on outgoing emails processed through Mailjet.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pxPu1aVgLQqByrqYCe-ulmoz3MDWi1NO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1914" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1915</div></th><td class="s6">GitLab Repository Event Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers automation on any event within the &#39;n8n-docs&#39; GitLab repository using GitLab API webhooks. It listens to all repository events and requires GitLab API credentials for seamless integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lOswpazYlx3FPYVTkD1LvvFO8UffDkmI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1915" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1916</div></th><td class="s6">Bitbucket Repo Push Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow with Bitbucket Trigger node that activates upon repository push events. It uses Bitbucket API credentials to listen for &#39;repo:push&#39; events on a specific repo named &#39;test&#39;, enabling automation workflows on code pushes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1J9YwCYcTIyt6uebvgzttRes_AN9J15SY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1916" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1917</div></th><td class="s6">Acuity Appointment Scheduled Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers automation when an appointment is scheduled in Acuity Scheduling using its API. It listens for &#39;appointment.scheduled&#39; events via webhook to initiate further actions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1G3-PmoWtTwVfIRPFpWHk38DLQa33fhIG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1917" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1918</div></th><td class="s6">Clockify Time Tracking Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers every minute using the Clockify API to monitor time entries in a specific workspace. Ideal for automating time tracking data capture and workflow integration using Clockify and n8n&#39;s native trigger node.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MGEcGCwmXHKzRsvKoTHqf2jvja8p9UqZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1918" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1919</div></th><td class="s6">Copper CRM Project Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers actions when new projects are created in Copper CRM using the Copper API. Ideal for automating workflows based on project creation events within Copper.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17CO6nEh13GK3N0Uku21r32tW_ftmjprD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1919" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1920</div></th><td class="s6">Trigger Rundeck Job Manually</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers a Rundeck job manually using the manual trigger node and Rundeck API integration. It automates execution of predefined Rundeck jobs by leveraging n8n&#39;s Rundeck node and API credentials for job orchestration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1MpHTKPaIHJCSPd66C6xuS-N9IF94DX-V">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1920" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1921</div></th><td class="s6">JotForm Submission Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on new JotForm submissions via JotForm API webhook, automating follow-up actions upon form completion.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hbf6-3_ZHMl3rOtdJA7Gsya0Ut1_UyoS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1921" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1922</div></th><td class="s6">Bannerbear Image Generator Triggered Manually</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that manually triggers image generation using Bannerbear API. It customizes a template with text and color modifications and waits for the image to be created. Ideal for automated graphic content creation with Bannerbear integration.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1arSm_gh9k7TMEhibn_D7-5v9nQN3bTxj">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1922" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1923</div></th><td class="s6">Keap Contact Retrieval Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow triggered manually to fetch all contacts from Keap (Infusionsoft) CRM using its OAuth2 API. Enables easy integration and automation of contact data retrieval for business CRM tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1F9oCSuC3EROREq1TcVt6DmmEzUWI9QEf">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1923" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1924</div></th><td class="s6">Keap Contact Add Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on new contact additions in Keap CRM using its webhook API. It listens for &#39;contact.add&#39; events via Keap OAuth2 credentials, enabling automated actions immediately after a new contact is created.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16T5-QEruCKvzkE63beIpEV-_wlYDVGTu">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1924" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1925</div></th><td class="s6">CocktailDB JSON to XML Converter</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow fetches a random cocktail recipe from the CocktailDB API and converts the JSON response into XML format using n8n&#39;s HTTP Request and XML nodes. Useful for data format transformations and API integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1lNmTiMsYGtPcrIoYDRL_EFNEozHIAr7A">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1925" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1926</div></th><td class="s6">Box Folder Event Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using Box API to trigger automation on folder events like move or download within Box cloud storage using OAuth2 authentication.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OhCLpo4AUDZmduDa91zE9vAAuyL_CXrs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1926" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1927</div></th><td class="s6">OneDrive Folder Creator Triggered Manually</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow creates a folder named &#39;n8n-rocks&#39; in Microsoft OneDrive upon manual execution. It uses n8n&#39;s manual trigger and authenticates via Microsoft OneDrive OAuth2 API to automate folder creation in the cloud storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kdxJYfPqsgQTNufG2YaH2bf9FZV0CmJ0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1927" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1928</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Trigger to Send Mandrill Email</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that sends a templated email via Mandrill when manually triggered. Utilizes Mandrill API for email delivery. Ideal for testing or sending instant notification emails using customizable templates.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1hDyglfDgdrfVfuiU1D7ZI7R1pHT_7q8z">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1928" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1929</div></th><td class="s6">Image Fetch and Info Extraction</td><td class="s7">Automates fetching a random image from Picsum.photos and extracting image info using n8n&#39;s HTTP Request and Edit Image nodes. Ideal for workflows requiring quick image data retrieval and processing without coding.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XBA8rWpLksAr6RjhMApwDCQzV1EsziGJ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1929" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1930</div></th><td class="s6">PDF Text Extractor from Local File</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers manually to read a PDF file stored locally (/data/pdf.pdf) using built-in nodes: Manual Trigger, Read Binary File, and Read PDF. Extracts and outputs text content from a PDF for further automation or processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zS7GCdTK_40QyNsPD3D4pKWHKPWh_357">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1930" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1931</div></th><td class="s6">CrateDB Table Create &amp; Insert Demo</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating CrateDB integration: it creates a table, inserts a record with id and name, and retrieves the data. Utilizes manual trigger, CrateDB node for SQL operations, and data setting within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kBTjhqyLNYQ0mqAa_A4s5t8Y_F6cz1ky">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1931" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1932</div></th><td class="s6">Postgres Table Setup and Data Retrieval</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating creation of a PostgreSQL table, setting sample data, and retrieving this data. Uses PostgreSQL node with manual trigger and set node for data insertion and fetch, ideal for database initialization and testing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1B5I5NGyqjjA4Aym0To3p7ErNIWuV289F">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1932" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1933</div></th><td class="s6">Wekan Board and Card Automation</td><td class="s7">Automates creation of a Wekan board with &#39;To Do&#39; and &#39;Done&#39; lists, adds a card in &#39;To Do&#39;, then moves it to &#39;Done&#39;. Uses n8n workflow with Wekan API to streamline task management board setup and card handling.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1-11xxu8K10m7Ew_trg5buGfFLz_fTkki">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1933" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1934</div></th><td class="s6">File List Processor and Logger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that reads a text file containing filenames, splits them into an array, and sequentially logs each filename to an output file. Utilizes n8n&#39;s Read Binary File, Function, Execute Command, and IF nodes to automate file processing and command execution on Linux.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ovVRvwxgxrD5h4NjiV6LNu14HQpZW9pv">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1934" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1935</div></th><td class="s6">Send SMS via sms77 API</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that sends SMS messages using the sms77 API. It triggers manually and sends a customizable text message through the sms77 integration. Ideal for quick SMS notifications or alerts, leveraging n8n automation capabilities.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1IQ5Uml2nF-SOhCCTEcFzq74ACxqXy0ZD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1935" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1936</div></th><td class="s6">English to German Text Translator</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that uses Google Translate API via OAuth2 to translate fixed English text into German on manual trigger. Ideal for automating simple language translation tasks using Google Translate within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JjDiKLMttAEqq2jZRdL9hEVKjJBbBrYa">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1936" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1937</div></th><td class="s6">Discourse Post Create-Update-Get Workflow</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow automates Discourse forum interaction by creating a post, updating it, and retrieving the updated post using Discourse API nodes triggered manually. Ideal for managing forum content programmatically via the Discourse API.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1AcZTRHcMfy3_AMlQHLWY8qvlhk5Ccd0X">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1937" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1938</div></th><td class="s6">Create Organization in Affinity CRM</td><td class="s7">Automates organization creation in Affinity CRM via API using n8n&#39;s manual trigger and Affinity node. Enables quick setup of new organizations in Affinity for relationship intelligence and pipeline management.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1zQHqBQ4mjsB-_mUYiWOR9GNw_-FEiVp5">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1938" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1939</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Processing Loop with Manual Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates 10 items via a JavaScript function, processes them one by one in batches, and uses a conditional check to detect when all items are processed. Utilizes n8n nodes: Manual Trigger, Function, SplitInBatches, and IF node to control flow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=12V-UDiL1-B8bQW-cAplCT_O_Yn1KdooY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1939" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1940</div></th><td class="s6">Disqus Forum Details Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to retrieve detailed information about a Disqus forum using the Disqus API. Triggered manually, it fetches data for a specified forum ID (e.g., &#39;hackernoon&#39;) to help users monitor forum stats easily.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xPX6qDglb5SRlSw8bLd_Ul76NlAU9BIZ">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1940" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1941</div></th><td class="s6">FileMaker Contacts Data Extraction</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow extracting and processing contacts data from FileMaker Data API. It uses FileMaker Data API simulated responses and n8n nodes to parse and return detailed contact info in JSON, suitable for automation and data integration tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Zlls4NC1N_Yju0v_dZWikeyUpozITFVs">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1941" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1942</div></th><td class="s6">Extract PDF Pages from URL</td><td class="s7">Workflow that downloads a PDF from a specified URL using HTTP Request and extracts specific pages (2-3) with a custom PDF toolkit node. Utilizes n8n&#39;s manual trigger, HTTP Request node, and a custom-js PDF extraction tool for selective page extraction.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZVEEyBq2rDdOgoPQLyBxi2aQzEiUFnq2">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1942" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1943</div></th><td class="s6">Merge Multiple Data Runs into One Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to retrieve all customer records from a datastore, process them in batches with delay, and merge all batch outputs into a single consolidated dataset. Utilizes n8n nodes: Manual Trigger, Custom Customer Datastore API, SplitInBatches, Wait, NoOp, If, and Code node for aggregation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=11MV8kapmVsTCutIZjFPvQw5FKSp-rob6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1943" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1944</div></th><td class="s6">Fictional Country Capitals Chatbot</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow integrating OpenAI Langchain nodes to create a chat assistant that returns capitals of fictional countries like Wakanda or Narnia. Uses OpenAI API for chat, JavaScript code nodes for data mapping, and conditional logic to handle queries or list countries.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1JHwF1sDVV6H6TyOUD3LXtuhCd8pwyIBP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1944" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1945</div></th><td class="s6">JSON File Creator from Data Object</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow generates example JSON data, converts it to a binary buffer, encodes it in base64, and writes it to a local JSON file using built-in function and file nodes. Useful for simple data export automation without external APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1sEIEPl-SNGa46ZmqIQxEkBKdyBOwgcfO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1945" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1946</div></th><td class="s6">Standup Bot Config Reader</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow that reads a JSON configuration file for a Standup Bot from the local filesystem and converts it to JSON format for further processing. Uses n8n&#39;s File and Move Binary Data nodes to trigger and handle config data reading and parsing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Bqtm_KoitaDzX-EBTk0QwvwQCW_jzVC9">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1946" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1947</div></th><td class="s6">Twitter Auto Poster with Loop Control</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow posts &quot;Hello from n8n!&quot; to Twitter using Twitter OAuth1 API credentials. It triggers manually, then loops posting tweets until the run count reaches 4, controlled by an IF node. Includes a NoOp node for alternate flow.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1C8WNx8camysA1TSSRWg-fCcyJQtnGJgL">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1947" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1948</div></th><td class="s6">Standup Bot Config Override</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow to manually update and save the Standup Bot configuration by converting JSON to binary and writing it to a local file. Utilizes n8n built-in nodes: Manual Trigger, Move Binary Data, and Write Binary File.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1aEeOvinoQ0IE-FWM54xAVm-ClUXnXE-h">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1948" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1949</div></th><td class="s6">Simple HTML Response Webhook</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that creates a webhook endpoint (/my-form) which responds with a static HTML page styled using Bootstrap 5. It uses n8n&#39;s Webhook and Respond to Webhook nodes to deliver a basic &quot;Hello, world!&quot; webpage upon HTTP request.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xW4wXtyrRbseq6HSEQWZ3dsayZcZ51T4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1949" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1950</div></th><td class="s6">Conditional Close Date Setter</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow to set or validate a &#39;Close Date&#39;. Uses manual trigger, regex check, and date handling to either retain an original fixed date or update it to 3 weeks from today. Employs built-in n8n nodes only, for date automation tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1F0mn_jxbaPvCT6xCw8OL6x1v_xptJsXP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1950" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1951</div></th><td class="s6">Get Today&#39;s Date and Weekday</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using a Manual Trigger and Function node to output the current ISO date and weekday name in JavaScript. Useful for initiating date-based automation or logging within n8n without external API calls.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1soHqO-GdD7Qr4R1OaejK114fUDZkUgr6">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1951" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1952</div></th><td class="s6">Sum USD Amounts from Mock Data</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that sums USD amounts from mocked JSON data using Function nodes. It manually triggers, generates sample amounts, and calculates their total. Utilizes n8n core nodes without external APIs. Ideal for simple data aggregation demonstrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=156oQALCM3_Goiizfe19_Y__j6Rr7CS6V">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1952" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1953</div></th><td class="s6">Command Output Parsing and Conditional Check</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that executes a shell command returning JSON, parses the output, transforms it into flow data, and conditionally branches using an IF node based on parsed boolean value. Utilizes Execute Command, Function Item, and IF nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1j_0J8rBz8pOQWeq9HQ9plp9iNp12DJQ1">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1953" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1954</div></th><td class="s6">Quickstart Demo: Customer Data Fetch &amp; Format</td><td class="s7">An introductory n8n workflow demonstrating how to fetch fake customer data from the n8nTrainingCustomerDatastore node, then transform and map it into cleaner fields using the Set node. Uses manual trigger for testing. Great for beginners learning API data extraction and manipulation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1mHLxYW_Ska0XA9KoVnrrdyuBeW6EyI8b">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1954" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1955</div></th><td class="s6">Simple API Endpoint for Google Search URL</td><td class="s7">Creates a lightweight API using n8n with Webhook and Respond to Webhook nodes that generates a Google search URL from query parameters (first and last names). Perfect for beginners learning to create API endpoints. Tech stack: n8n workflow, HTTP webhook.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UtYi-icU7h_3sRA6y1Ibk9JkYHf6PDPq">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1955" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1956</div></th><td class="s6">Fetch and Count Customers from n8n Training DB</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow manually triggers retrieval of all customer records from the n8n Training Customer Datastore using the built-in n8nTrainingCustomerDatastore node, then counts the total number of customers. Ideal for simple database fetch and count automation within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1r3YUUg6xYGjVn5A-VCoGQJ-cYS2WoBDO">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1956" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1957</div></th><td class="s6">Scheduled Discord Meme Poster</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that automates posting memes to Discord channels using Discord Webhooks, triggered by cron schedules set for specific weekdays and intervals. It leverages n8n&#39;s Cron and Discord nodes to send customized memes on Wednesdays, Fridays, and every 30 minutes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1rHUCEE-SMkHvJ6_PHQXgfW4S1eLJN_FP">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1957" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1958</div></th><td class="s6">Discord Message Sender</td><td class="s7">Simple n8n workflow sending a &#39;Hello World!&#39; message to a Discord channel via webhook API. Triggered manually, it demonstrates basic Discord integration using n8n&#39;s built-in Discord node and webhook URI.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1oxvsM-wgHVcPZAwzA-ZgViu6crsSEH0v">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1958" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1959</div></th><td class="s6">Simple XML to JSON Conversion</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that converts a hardcoded XML string to JSON format using the built-in XML node. Ideal for learning XML parsing in n8n. Uses n8n core nodes: Manual Trigger, Set, and XML parsing nodes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1FbZVZARlHZ0wNjWjMho9UCzl5sa3Q9IY">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1959" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1960</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Trigger to Postgres Data Fetch</td><td class="s7">Workflow triggered manually to execute a SELECT query on a PostgreSQL database using n8n&#39;s Postgres node, retrieving all records from a specified table. Useful for simple database querying and testing integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1kgpVzMuFCvFEmEYfmhpucCWUcHg2J44e">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1960" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1961</div></th><td class="s6">AWS SNS Test Message Sender</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that sends a test message to an AWS SNS topic using a manual trigger. It integrates n8n with AWS SNS API to automate notification sending for testing or alerting purposes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EGHvFaGEeMmNxwJCc807eUmwVjknZ5n-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1961" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1962</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Trigger MongoDB Data Inserter</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow triggered manually to insert predefined key-value data into a MongoDB collection. Utilizes n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger, Set, and MongoDB nodes for simple data insertion tasks.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1UKQ5aFVPiDDW-snq4JkhnB6MtbQe6py4">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1962" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1963</div></th><td class="s6">Simple Email Sender via Mailgun</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that sends an email using the Mailgun API triggered manually. It includes a manual trigger node and a Mailgun node to dispatch emails with specified subject, sender, and recipient.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1XPmuOeXZXabsalZBaq4o8qtihgLMMFuy">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1963" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1964</div></th><td class="s6">Redis Key-Value Retrieval Trigger</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers manually and retrieves the value of a specified Redis key using Redis API. Uses n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger and Redis nodes to fetch the value of key &#39;hello&#39; from a Redis instance.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1OtkJMYsicPK1l_YS3eheUElG17uqKot0">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1964" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1965</div></th><td class="s6">Trigger Folder Access in Box</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow triggers manually and connects to the Box API via OAuth2 to access metadata of a specific folder named &#39;n8n-rocks&#39;. It demonstrates basic integration of manual trigger and Box cloud storage for folder resource retrieval.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1EIMuDe0fyZzXjtdZTYllsO6wFYM4z8fe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1965" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1966</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Date Parser</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers manually and converts a specified date string (&#39;14/02/2020&#39;) into a date object using n8n&#39;s Date &amp; Time node. Useful for beginners learning to handle date parsing and transformations without external APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1WnGFrCVz6z5JBsJXj2tgk6D01eXekmW-">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1966" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1967</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Trigger to Read Local Binary File</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that manually triggers the reading of a local binary file (e.g., image) from a specified path using the built-in Read Binary File node. Useful for workflows involving local file processing.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1tz9cvQaU2NSL0IRd-1fWmWU7FpIgeihe">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1967" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1968</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Trigger to Read JPG Files</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that manually triggers a process to read all .jpg files from the /data/lol/ directory using the Read Binary Files node. Useful for workflows requiring batch processing of image files on local storage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Vf2hhxcmXaQZft6BgrhnAUBVdywbZed8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1968" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1969</div></th><td class="s6">Simple Key Renaming Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow triggered manually that sets a key-value pair and renames the key from &#39;key&#39; to &#39;newkey&#39;. Uses native n8n nodes: Manual Trigger, Set, and Rename Keys. Demonstrates basic data transformation within n8n.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1F4gRBodtmQAFi0AL7WrS6xn3sY8h-mRM">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1969" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1970</div></th><td class="s6">RSS Feed Trigger Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that triggers on manual execution and reads an RSS feed from https://failedmachine.com/rss/. Uses n8n&#39;s Manual Trigger and RSS Feed Read nodes to fetch and process RSS data for automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=13rgO9GpFmZkUNzObfGIOY24VV_l_2ixr">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1970" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1971</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Trigger Email Sender</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that sends an email upon manual execution. It uses the built-in Manual Trigger and Email Send nodes, leveraging SMTP credentials to dispatch a predefined message. Ideal for testing or simple email notifications.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1pAXG25Xc9FvAe1NdQWxjLDvJuOciK53e">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1971" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1972</div></th><td class="s6">MySQL Table Setup and Insert Demo</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow creating a MySQL table &#39;test&#39;, inserting a row with id and name using MySQL node and Set node, triggered manually. Demonstrates basic MySQL operations automation in n8n with MySQL credentials.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16sGwbbEIvmUzSDgactgb0IyNAbXF96iG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1972" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1973</div></th><td class="s6">Sequential API Requests with ReqRes</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow automating sequential HTTP calls to the ReqRes API: GET users, POST to create a user, and PATCH to update a user. Demonstrates chaining of REST API requests using n8n’s Manual Trigger and HTTP Request nodes for testing and learning API interactions.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=17pX6aihUKhPt1bnFqVnA81oqANo9Xnor">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1973" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1974</div></th><td class="s6">SSE Stream Listener</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that listens to Server-Sent Events (SSE) from a specified URL using the built-in SSE Trigger node. Useful for real-time event streaming and automation based on live web data.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1uiM1EsGjdt0p1j6Z706-liOX9QOaKzmS">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1974" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1975</div></th><td class="s6">Merge Greetings with Names by Language</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that combines sample datasets of names and greetings based on their language code. It uses JavaScript code nodes to provide data samples and a merge node to join them by &#39;language&#39;. Useful for basic multi-language greeting generation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=16fAicFUA54Nnr-tPwZOQH6jW97Cg_I5x">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1975" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1976</div></th><td class="s6">CSV Spreadsheet Reader</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that reads a CSV spreadsheet file from local storage using the Read Binary File and Spreadsheet File nodes to parse and process data on manual trigger.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15c0KIJEbgq2iWCFlHk_czOoj1qNhtyAH">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1976" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1977</div></th><td class="s6">Spotify Track Fetcher</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that retrieves detailed data for a specific Spotify track using Spotify&#39;s OAuth2 API upon manual execution.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1xJbL-F2SCfvl86Eo1uKkeMgOPecgcOy8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1977" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1978</div></th><td class="s6">Batch Loop with Conditional Stop</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that generates 10 items, processes them one by one in batches of size 1, and conditionally stops the loop after the 6th item. Uses core n8n nodes: Manual Trigger, Function, SplitInBatches, IF condition, and Set to signal loop end.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1d3AdjQvBWbH9TDyTrZ7RyPlw6uLGgjAo">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1978" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1979</div></th><td class="s6">n8n itemMatching() Data Linking Example</td><td class="s7">Demonstrates using n8n&#39;s itemMatching() in Code node (Python) to restore linked email data from a customer datastore. Utilizes n8n Training Customer Datastore, Manual Trigger, Set node to isolate fields, and Python code for data retrieval and matching.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1D31wIH7dh_ELuK7uQ3YA7g6NkeEkSsQG">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1979" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1980</div></th><td class="s6">Local DateTime Retrieval Workflow</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow uses a manual trigger and a function node with moment.js to fetch and format the current local datetime based on an environment timezone variable. It outputs detailed datetime components for flexible usage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1gYt1Q-8DUKCIVYmbc1KRd-deVBc_qKTz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1980" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1981</div></th><td class="s6">Create Array from Mock Data Items</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that generates mock JSON data objects and consolidates them into a single array object using JavaScript functions inside n8n. Useful for testing and prototyping data handling workflows without external APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1vQtV1qyosgmT0kYEj3OnJs2loKhXwN09">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1981" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1982</div></th><td class="s6">Spanish Text Case and Replace Demo</td><td class="s7">n8n workflow demonstrating string manipulations like toLowerCase, toUpperCase and replace on Spanish text using executeCommand nodes triggered manually. Ideal for beginners learning text processing in n8n with simple command line snippets.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1L_iZqvNtjZ9ScGe41VyQC_J3MbOUR-74">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1982" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1983</div></th><td class="s6">Assign Variables Using Set Node</td><td class="s7">A simple n8n workflow demonstrating how to assign values to variables of different types (number, string, boolean) using the Set node triggered manually. Ideal for beginners learning value assignment in n8n automation.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Kt8XDLZJzJ6-770h6Ma7KmcbUbp2KC7V">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1983" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1984</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Trigger with Crypto Node Demo</td><td class="s7">This n8n workflow demonstrates a manual trigger that executes a Crypto node to process a simple string (&#39;n8n rocks!&#39;). It uses n8n&#39;s built-in manual trigger and crypto encryption tools for basic cryptographic operations. Ideal for learning node chaining and crypto usage.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1Pj-ZV7HFl52j9kAzPt07842YYfDqy2fI">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1984" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1985</div></th><td class="s6">Basic Conditional Workflow Demo</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow demonstrating manual trigger, creation of test data, conditional branching based on &#39;id&#39; field, and setting different string values. Uses n8n native nodes: Manual Trigger, Function, IF condition, and Set nodes for flow control and data assignment.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ASKxfYfepfxmIFpbglu5Xwv-2hbx4d5F">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1985" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1986</div></th><td class="s6">Manual Trigger to Execute Workflow</td><td class="s7">A simple n8n workflow that uses a manual trigger node to initiate the execution of another predefined workflow by its ID. Utilizes n8n&#39;s internal executeWorkflow node to chain workflows. Ideal for manual control and testing purposes.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=10xtz-eupwTX_IeSHj3UmGWmp6PZ38GVD">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1986" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1987</div></th><td class="s6">ID-Based Conditional Set Workflow</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow using manual trigger, function, and switch nodes to map IDs (0,1,2) to specific string values (n8n, nodemation, nathan). It demonstrates conditional branching and data transformation without external APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1qXE3ifklfmjQWPXgqxuKYS7SI9ITPs_8">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1987" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1988</div></th><td class="s6">Basic Array Mapper Workflow</td><td class="s7">Simple n8n workflow using Function nodes to generate mock array data and map each element into individual JSON objects. Demonstrates basic data transformation without external APIs or integrations.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=15larvb3MtsToynqDVIIrQzdz7WURqCpz">Download</a></td></tr><tr style="height: 20px"><th id="1909413307R1988" style="height: 20px;" class="row-headers-background"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 20px">1989</div></th><td class="s6">Create JSON Items from Mock Data</td><td class="s7">An n8n workflow that generates a mock list of user objects and converts them into individual JSON items using Function nodes. Useful for testing or prototyping JSON data processing without external APIs.</td><td class="s9" dir="ltr"><a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;id=1ZwdGCTmPUwpF5_IR4A7r5HuaA5VZktGZ">Download</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div>